   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E linite-n chilia btrnei, i-nsereaz...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub vatr rete un greier nestatornic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i leagn-n perete tic-tacul vechiul ornic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ntunec chilia i iar se lumineaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-alearg fusul spornic...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Topit de veghere, bunica toarce, toarce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu minile p-aiurea, ctnd la foc pierdut...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, ca purtat n umbr de-o mn nevzut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot fuge-n cercuri fusul i tot mai iute stoarce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din caier lna mut...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mhnit st Preasfnta sub candela de paz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se irosete-n aer cuceernic busuiocul;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe vatr lupt-n umbr mocnit i vnt focul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nstreinatul greier sub vatr aiureaz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Schimbnd ntr-una locul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, ca-ntr-o vraj, fusul se-nvrte i suspin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amurgu-ncet i cerne cenua obosit...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bunica-ngndurat zrete ca prin sit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trecnd pe dinainte-i o via n ruin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-o lume prsit...</text:span></text:p>
