   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De la fereastr, din vagon,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd satul alb sclipind n zare...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un uier lung... Tresar micat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simt inima btndu-mi tare.</text:span></text:p>
