   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E mult de cnd nu ne-am vzut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E-atta haz i bucurie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doar numai friorul mic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se uit lung: nu mai m tie...</text:span></text:p>
