   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mas  glume, glgie...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cea dinti mi toarn vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Drgu a doua m mbie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A treia-mi d paharul plin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E, cine-mi poate spune mie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n sntatea cui s-nchin?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trziu, cnd plec de ies n strad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i ntunerec peste tot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah! unde-s ele s m vad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orbit de viscol, cum not</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin valurile de zpad...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i drumu-i lung i nu mai pot...</text:span></text:p>
