   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cread cine cum o vrea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum crede s-i aleag;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-s doine ca n ara mea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe lumea asta-ntreag!</text:span></text:p>
