   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strluce sus aa tcut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i parc, izvornd scntei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrea s ptrund printre storuri...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, cte visuri, cte doruri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncred n taina ei!</text:span></text:p>
