   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E ziua crucii azi  zi sfnt!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E chef i chiot prin podgorii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici mustu-n cad se frmnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici trec glumind culegtorii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Romnii toi cu voie bun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cinstesc o datin strbun...</text:span></text:p>
