   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ce-i acolo? Ce minune?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce fug femeile i ip? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncepe lumea s s-adune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din toate prile-ntr-o clip,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alearg ca la urs, grmad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ndeas, se-mbrncesc s vad...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un satir mic, ncins cu vi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a prins n hor fr veste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, behind ca o cpri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D spaima-n fete i-n neveste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, pn&apos; s-l ia de scurt poporul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A ters-o grabnic drcuorul...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aive-a fost ori numai ag?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntreab toi i-ntreab zarea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnii doar i rd n barb:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i prinde-aa uor mirarea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci mai vrtos la chef se-ndeamn:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copii! belug i spor nseamn!</text:span></text:p>
