   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfiorat din vreme-n vreme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-o aurire de furtun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnul codru-n miez de noapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Visaz sub argint de lun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, socotindu-i, parc, frunza</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nenumrat-n vis, rsun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nsufleit de mii de oapte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub vraja mndrei nopi de var,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ceasul tainei, cine tie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce nluciri nu-i trec prin minte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce fermecat feerie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eresuri i minuni pgne</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din sfnta lui copilrie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De care-abia-i aduce-aminte...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De palidul pstor lunatic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ceaa nopilor tcute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sun-n vis ca o poveste...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deodat-n urma unei ciute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsare-n lumini Diana,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n adncimi necunoscute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se prpdete fr veste...</text:span></text:p>
