   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Convoi de umbre diafane</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plutind mre se risipete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe-n linitea de mituri...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ce blestem divin voiete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S rump farmecul visrii?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce vuiet surd se-nal, crete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ameninnd din rsrituri?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P31"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deodat-i zguduie btrnul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din somn puternica-i coroan!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De plns amar, de hohot jalnic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Huiete antica poian:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clri pe cai sirepi, slbatici,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Punndu-i visele pe goan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vin barbarii-n potop nvalnic!</text:span></text:p>
