   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd seara-n ceasuri de singurtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi sprijin fruntea vistor pe mn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Poveti strbune, cntece uitate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu glasuri de tilinci ndeprtate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi amgesc iar gndul i m-ngn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-atunci te vd plutind surztoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din negura de vremi bsmuitoare...</text:span></text:p>
