   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ai dat ndejde ca s lupt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu griji i cu necazuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i grmdeau nentrerupt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noianul de talazuri,</text:span></text:p>
