   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar eu atunci al cui rmi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, dragi credine moarte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe drumuri, fr cpti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai, cine-o s m poarte?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Melancoliei</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce timpuriu m-ai cucerit, iubit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Melancolie, credincioas sor!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era ntr-o duminec-nflorit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i satul tot, devale, strns la hor..</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-am dus i eu. La vesela serbare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Priveam aa pierdut, i-ntia oar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n sufletu-mi simii cum se strecoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiorul tu de dulce ntristare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">nstrinat de-atta veselie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am cutat singurtatea-n cetini...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci te-am cunoscut, melancolie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, vezi, de-atunci rmas-am buni prieteni...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Spre primvar </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vor nflori curnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe coast merii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i va suna curnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ceasu-nvierii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Schimba-va bruma grea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n strop de rou,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s rsfrng-n ea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O lume nou:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un cer aa senin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum nu mai fuse </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uita-vei orice chin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din zile-apuse...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un flutur d ocol</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctnd o floare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar bate-aa domol</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din aripi... moare...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce te prind fiori?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce gnd te pate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi tu, e trist s mori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd tot renate!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Rug</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uliele-nnegurate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luna n argint le-mbrac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Limpede un clopot bate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Straja cea dinti...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n grdin doarme floarea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doarme fluturul pe floare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn i privighetoarea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A tcut acum...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, natur, mprumut-mi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din odihna ta o clip...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vino, dulce somn, srut-mi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochii obosii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Bolnav</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">1904</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Afar iar e cer senin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i i-e aa de dor de soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C plngi pe patul tu de chin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plngi ca un rol n nchisoare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu plnge!... Nu te da nvins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ndjduiete i adast...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu vezi?... un flutura s-a prins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btnd din aripi, la fereastr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Primete-l pe acest pribeag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-albastru fulg al primverii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-o fi trimis vreun suflet drag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre a-i vesti sfrit durerii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La fereastra spre livad... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La fereastra spre livad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din copit murgul bate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fru de-argint s-i scot din lad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scump ea s-i pun n spate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S pornim iar mpreun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Peste vi i peste plai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C s-a-ntors iar vremea bun </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai, murgule, stai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Murgule, coam rotat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai pn-iese luna nou,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mndrua sprncenat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S trimit o slov-dou,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori pe soare, ori pe lun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori pe nor, ori pe senin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori s mergem mpreun?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lin, murgule, lin!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Murgule, fii bun i-adast,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mplinesc frumoas slova,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-a veni i vremea noastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ne ducem la Moldova,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La Moldova cea btrn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde ne-a-ngriji ca-n rai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mndra mea i-a ta stpn...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hai, murgule, hai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur i robit de jale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mngiam un dor ascuns:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ai ieit atunci n cale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ai zmbit  i-a fost de-ajuns.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Braele, ca niciodat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dornice mi s-au deschis:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Inima de-atunci mi-e dat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i triesc un mndru vis.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">S-a-nnoptat </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a-nnoptat ncet cu-ncetul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luan vraja i-o mbie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur-singurel poetul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bate ulia pustie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La perdelele nchise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai arunc o privire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde dorm attea vise,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fermecate, de iubire.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aiurit, apoi rmne</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu ochii dui n lun:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntectul cel nou, de mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot mai clar n minte-i sun...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1904</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pentru ce ne-am teme ? </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de ce ne-am teme, drag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de ce-am fi mai cumini,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd acelai gnd ne leag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i aceleai suferini?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd eu clar c-n toat firea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orict stau i m socot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legile ce-a pus iubirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Biruie i sfarm tot.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legi eterne sunt acele...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum s le nfrngem noi?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne-am lupta-n zdar cu ele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ne-ar pierde pe-amndoi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1903</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi, dragii oaspei le-au venit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pomii toi s-au premenit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De srbtoare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Grdina-i templu plin de zvon,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Albina-i psalt, i orice floare </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un sfnt amvon.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub streini cuiburile vechi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascund iar vesele perechi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De rndunele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cuiburi nou se cldesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar eu, furat de-un vis, privesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zmbind la ele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, spune-mi, drag rndunea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce zbori mereu n preajma mea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu ii mai bine:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O s-mi ajute Dumnezeu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mi pot alctui, ca tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un cuib al meu?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Terine</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A vrea s cnt, s-mbrac n mndre rime</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Norocul rar ce-n cntec nu ncape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C nu e vers pe lume s-l esprime.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci ca-ntr-un murmur nesfrit de ape</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce se revars-n valuri de-armonie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din mii de glasuri ce-l vrjesc de-aproape,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srmanul suflet cearc, i nu tie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ton s prind, ce cuvnt s-aleag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci toate-l cheam,-l strig i-l mbie...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar eu stau mut,  i-a sta vecia-ntreag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-ascult uimit la glasurile-acele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privind n ochii ti albatri, drag </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">Vis ntrupat al visurilor mele!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Icoane din Carpai </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I_(Un_uier_lung__gem_osii_ferecate_&amp;mdash)"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Un uier lung  gem osii ferecate <text:line-break/>Un strigt viu  nebun de libertate!<text:line-break/>Pe roi uruitoare<text:line-break/>Vagoanele urnite<text:line-break/>Alunec uoare<text:line-break/>Mai iute, mai grbite, <text:line-break/>Dar inima-mi nebun<text:line-break/>Mai iute-ar vrea s mearg<text:line-break/>i bate-n piept, s-l sparg,<text:line-break/>S zboare-n lumea larg<text:line-break/>De-atta voie bun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Griji amrte, zbuciumri dearte,<text:line-break/>V las de-acum!<text:line-break/>V las cu bine! La o parte!<text:line-break/>Voi n-avei ce-mi cta la drum!<text:line-break/>Pierii, ntunecate duhuri!<text:line-break/>Sunt liber ca ciocrlia-n vzduhuri!<text:line-break/>mi flutur prul n vnt,<text:line-break/>i cnt, <text:line-break/>M cheam-n zare munii, munii mei!<text:line-break/>Ce dor, ce dor adnc mi-era de ei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ce dor i-a fost poetului<text:line-break/>De freamtul brdetului,<text:line-break/>De murmurul izvorului,<text:line-break/>De fluierul pstorului,<text:line-break/>De glasul psrelelor<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i de vecinul stelelor <text:line-break/>De vrful Caraimanului,<text:line-break/>Ce dor, ce dor i-a fost srmanului!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II_.28St.C4.83_Caraimanu-nnegurat..._.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="II_(St_Caraimanu-nnegurat..._)"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">St Caraimanul &apos;nnegurat,<text:line-break/>Moneag n veci cu fruntea sus;<text:line-break/>Slvitul zilei mprat<text:line-break/>ncet se las spre apus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i cum se uit la moneag,<text:line-break/>Se mai oprete-o clip-n loc:<text:line-break/>I-azvrle cu un zmbet drag<text:line-break/>Pe frunte-un diadem de foc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Iar dup culmi, doi nourai,<text:line-break/>Urcnd tiptil, n zare, sus,<text:line-break/>Rd rsfai i drglai,<text:line-break/>Privind idila din apus.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III_.28F.C3.A2nu-i_str.C3.A2ns.2C_.C8.99i_de_pe_lunc.C4.83....29"/><text:bookmark text:name="III_(Fnu-i_strns,_i_de_pe_lunc...)"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Fnu-i strns, i de pe lunc<text:line-break/>Oamenii spre cas vin.<text:line-break/>Lacrim de-argint, scnteie<text:line-break/>Steaua serii n senin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vile-alburesc n zare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Satul se-nvelete-n fum.<text:line-break/>Cel din urm car rscoal<text:line-break/>Colbul adormit pe drum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dulce i ncet se-ntinde<text:line-break/>Tihna pe pmnt i-n cer...<text:line-break/>Sus pe deal rsare luna,<text:line-break/>Melancolicul strjer.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IV_.28Din_culmea_V.C3.AErfului-cu-Dor.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="IV_(Din_culmea_Vrfului-cu-Dor)"/>IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Din culmea Vrfului-cu-Dor<text:line-break/>M uit n zri senine<text:line-break/>i iar m-apuc aprig dor,<text:line-break/>Odorul meu, de tine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Departe, peste muni i vi,<text:line-break/>E casa ta cea mic...<text:line-break/>Snt dui n sat prinii ti,<text:line-break/>i-n prag stai singuric...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">C nu-s un vultur... s m salt<text:line-break/>Din plaiurile-aceste,<text:line-break/>i ca un fulger din nalt<text:line-break/>S cad fr de veste,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i s te iau cu mine, sus,<text:line-break/>i s te duc la mine,<text:line-break/>Departe, unde lacrimi nu-s,<text:line-break/>n zri n veci senine.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="V_.28Este_ceasul_c.C3.AEnd_truditul.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="V_(Este_ceasul_cnd_truditul)"/><text:soft-page-break/>V</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Este ceasul cnd truditul<text:line-break/>Muncitor voios arunc<text:line-break/>La o parte grija zilei<text:line-break/>i uneltele de munc;<text:line-break/>S-au ntors de la pune<text:line-break/>Linititele cirezi,<text:line-break/>Umbre cresc pe nesimite<text:line-break/>Prin grdini i prin livezi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar un zvon de mii de glasuri<text:line-break/>Umple zarea fr veste:<text:line-break/>Craiul zilei, stnd s-apun,<text:line-break/>A ncremenit pe creste.<text:line-break/>Vile rsun toate,<text:line-break/>Dealurile viu rspund<text:line-break/>i vijelios se-nal<text:line-break/>Pulberea departe-n fund.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sun dealul, valea sun,<text:line-break/>St vzduhul s se sparg<text:line-break/>De tlngi nenumrate<text:line-break/>Ce izbesc n bolta larg,<text:line-break/>Cci coboar de la munte<text:line-break/>Oile, i curg puhoi,<text:line-break/>Cu un greu potop de cea<text:line-break/>nainte i-napoi...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Un berbec cu coarne-ntoarse,<text:line-break/>Tacticos i prea cuminte,<text:line-break/>Dup gt c-un clopot mare,<text:line-break/>Merge singur nainte.<text:line-break/>Pe la margine dulii;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Urecheatul, la mijloc,<text:line-break/>Cu desagii grei n spate,<text:line-break/>Anevoie-i face loc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Iar prin pulberea de aur<text:line-break/>Tocma-n capul cellalt<text:line-break/>Crete umbra-ntunecat<text:line-break/>A ciobanului nalt:<text:line-break/>Cu cciula ntr-o parte,<text:line-break/>El pete plin de fal,<text:line-break/>Sara purpurie-i schimb<text:line-break/>Zeghea-n mant triumfal...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VI_.28Doina.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="VI_(Doina)"/>VI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">DOINA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Se tnguiesc<text:line-break/>Tlngi pe ci,<text:line-break/>i neguri cresc<text:line-break/>Din negre vi,<text:line-break/>Plutind pe muni...<text:line-break/>La fgdu,<text:line-break/>La Vadul-Ru,<text:line-break/>Sus, la rscruci,<text:line-break/>Vin trei haiduci<text:line-break/>Pe cai mruni...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Griesc ncet...<text:line-break/>Un scurt popas <text:line-break/>i spre brdet<text:line-break/>Pornesc la pas<text:line-break/>Cei trei clri...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Sus, peste plai,<text:line-break/>Tcutul crai<text:line-break/>Al nopii reci,<text:line-break/>Umbrind poteci,<text:line-break/>Se-nal-n zri...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i neguri cresc,<text:line-break/>S-anin-n crngi; <text:line-break/>Se tnguiesc<text:line-break/>i plng tlngi<text:line-break/>Pe ci pustii...<text:line-break/>Se duc uitai<text:line-break/>Cei trei frtai,<text:line-break/>Sltnd n a,<text:line-break/>Plutind aa,<text:line-break/>Ca trei stafii...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar cnd ajung<text:line-break/>La cotituri,<text:line-break/>Un chiot lung<text:line-break/>Din mii de guri<text:line-break/>Drm stnci...<text:line-break/>Haiducii mei<text:line-break/>Doinesc toi trei;<text:line-break/>i clocotesc,<text:line-break/>i hohotesc<text:line-break/>Pduri adnci...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VII_.28Ciob.C4.83na.C8.99ul.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="VII_(Ciobnaul)"/>VII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">CIOBNAUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">La curte vine-un ciobna<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd i abate lui s joace,<text:line-break/>i mult e ho i e pozna<text:line-break/>C e copil din muni, i pace!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Snt rupte bietele-i opinci,<text:line-break/>Cciula lui n fund e spart,<text:line-break/>Dar el c-un pumn doboar cinci<text:line-break/>De-i cat unul i-altul ceart.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i cum e scurt i ndesat,<text:line-break/>Rd, dar se tem de el ficiorii,<text:line-break/>i parc-i e mai mare-n sat,<text:line-break/>C joac tot n fruntea horii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">El d porunci la lutari,<text:line-break/>A lui e cea mai mndr fat,<text:line-break/>La el se uit mici i mari,<text:line-break/>i-apoi acela-i joc o dat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Acum o prinde frumuel,<text:line-break/>Acum o las i-o ngn,<text:line-break/>i moare fata dup el<text:line-break/>Cnd o-nvrtete pe sub mn...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Iar cnd ceilali se-arunc-n joc<text:line-break/>i-abia se-ndeamn slab din gur,<text:line-break/>Tot el arunc, la noroc,<text:line-break/>Cea mai frumoas strigtur...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="VIII_.28Cu_fruntea-n_m.C3.AEn.C4.83_alb.C4.83.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="VIII_(Cu_fruntea-n_mn_alb)"/><text:soft-page-break/>VIII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">CU FRUNTEA-N MNA ALB...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cu fruntea-n mna alb rzemat,<text:line-break/>Cnta frumoasa fat la fereastr,<text:line-break/>Cnta de dor,<text:line-break/>i glasu-i dulce i tremurtor<text:line-break/>Se nla n linitea albastr<text:line-break/>A luminoasei nopi de var...<text:line-break/>Cci era noapte-adnc, alb, clar<text:line-break/>i trist cnta copila fermecat<text:line-break/>De linite i de singurtate...<text:line-break/>i singur se asculta cntnd,<text:line-break/>i nu sfrea un cntec jumtate,<text:line-break/>C altul i venea mereu n gnd.<text:line-break/>i nu tia nici ea de unde vin<text:line-break/>Aceste triste cntece uitate...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnta de dor i chin,<text:line-break/>De lacrimi tinuite n tcere,<text:line-break/>De zile de zbucium i nopi de veghere,<text:line-break/>i de chemri, de patimi nenvinse<text:line-break/>n dezndejdea braelor ntinse,<text:line-break/>De ani pustii de lung ateptare,<text:line-break/>De zilnice-amgiri<text:line-break/>i hohote de plns la deteptare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">ncremenise brazii ascultnd<text:line-break/>n linite... pe ulii  nici un pas...<text:line-break/>Doar Prahova cea fr de popas<text:line-break/>Curgea n vale,<text:line-break/>Amestecnd n al copilei glas<text:line-break/>Tot murmuru-necat al apelor sale...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="IX_.28Jos.2C_.C3.AEntre_care.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="IX_(Jos,_ntre_care)"/><text:soft-page-break/>IX</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Jos, ntre care,<text:line-break/>Vitele rumeg;<text:line-break/>n deprtare<text:line-break/>Vile fumeg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dorm muncitorii<text:line-break/>Pe lng focuri;<text:line-break/>Apele morii<text:line-break/>Murmur-n scocuri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Scapr stelele...<text:line-break/>Ceasul n care<text:line-break/>Dnuie ielele<text:line-break/>Lng izvoare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sprintene, vesele<text:line-break/>Peste coline,<text:line-break/>Joac miresele<text:line-break/>Apelor line.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="X_.28La_gura_pe.C8.99terii.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="X_(La_gura_peterii)"/>X</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">LA GURA PETERII</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">La gura peterii adnci<text:line-break/>Stam lng foc, n fapt de sar,<text:line-break/>i flcrile, aruncnd pe stnci<text:line-break/>Roateca lor par,<text:line-break/>nchipuiau o hor de fantasme.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Iar apele erpuitoare,<text:line-break/>Cu scoborri i creteri<text:line-break/>De sute de izvoare,<text:line-break/>i ngnau eternele lor basme<text:line-break/>n fundul netiut al negrei peteri...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Trosneau din foc scntei din cnd n cnd,<text:line-break/>i sus, pe cer, s-aprinse-ntia stea.<text:line-break/>Ci eu stteam la foc, visnd,<text:line-break/>i ascultam la pustnicul btrn,<text:line-break/>Ce-mi povestea<text:line-break/>Minuni adnci din cuibul lui de brazi...<text:line-break/> ...Demult, demult, tria un neam pgn<text:line-break/>De oameni mai puternici i mai mari<text:line-break/>Ca oamenii de azi,<text:line-break/>P-aceste plaiuri binecuvntate...<text:line-break/>Ei nu tiau de sap i de plug,<text:line-break/>C-aveau de toate cele din belug,<text:line-break/>Aa precum le-a fost lsat Preasfntul...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i au venit din locuri deprtate<text:line-break/>Puhoi de seminii<text:line-break/>i au umplut pmntul<text:line-break/>Cu zgomotul neostoitei lupte<text:line-break/>i strigte pustii...<text:line-break/>Un beac ntreg luptar n zadar<text:line-break/>n frmntri nentrerupte<text:line-break/>Cu-aceti vrjmai,<text:line-break/>Dar, biruii, n-au mai putut s ie<text:line-break/>i au fugit, i s-au ascuns<text:line-break/>Departe-n fundul fr de hotar<text:line-break/>Al peterii, de nimeni neptruns...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-acolo au i-acum mprie<text:line-break/>Btrnii uriai,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-adese-n nopile senine,<text:line-break/>Cnd linitea domnete-n boli, pustie<text:line-break/>Pn-la urechea noastr vine<text:line-break/>Un vuiet surd de pai...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Astfel mi povesti sihastrul,<text:line-break/>Apoi tcu...<text:line-break/>O linite de vraj se fcu,<text:line-break/>i fumul se-nla albastru,<text:line-break/>Iar flcrile, aruncnd pe stnci<text:line-break/>Potopul lor de par,<text:line-break/>nchipuiau o hor de fantasme,<text:line-break/>i apele, fierbnd clocotitoare,<text:line-break/>Cu scoborri i creteri<text:line-break/>De sute de izvoare<text:line-break/>i ngnau eternele lor basme<text:line-break/>n noaptea fr fund a negrei peteri...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="XI_.28Fantastic_norii_se-nve.C8.99m.C3.AEnt.C4.83.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="XI_(Fantastic_norii_se-nvemnt)"/>XI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Fantastic norii se-nvemnt,<text:line-break/>Strpuni de sulii lungi de aur,<text:line-break/>i ca-ntr-un lac de snge crete<text:line-break/>ntreaga zare-nspre coclaur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Semn de rzboi!... Un glas de bucium,<text:line-break/>Din vi, m face s m speriu...<text:line-break/>Visam, Austrie, c-n flcri<text:line-break/>Se darm vechiul tu imperiu...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="XII_.28Dar_soarele_coboar.C4.83-n_asfin.C8.9Bit.29"/><text:bookmark text:name="XII_(Dar_soarele_coboar-n_asfinit)"/><text:soft-page-break/>XII</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar soarele coboar-n asfinit,<text:line-break/>Din vi cresc neguri cenuii,<text:line-break/>Nval dau pe culmi n sus,<text:line-break/>i clopotele-au amuit.<text:line-break/>Pe gnduri dus,<text:line-break/>Clugrul descul a-nchis<text:line-break/>Strvechiul paraclis,<text:line-break/>i intr n chilia-i de sihastru.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar negurile cresc, mereu ntind<text:line-break/>Zabranicul lor lung, ntunecat...<text:line-break/>Pe rnd s-aprind<text:line-break/>Fcliile vzduhului albastru,<text:line-break/>Luceafrul scnteielor rsare,<text:line-break/>i luminie licresc prin sat...<text:line-break/>Departe, orga surd a pdurii,<text:line-break/>Cu mii de oapte, taine de izvoare,<text:line-break/>Rsun-ncet, rsun lin,<text:line-break/>Pe urm tace...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, ceas divin!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Acum ncepe mndrul parastas<text:line-break/>n templul venic al naturii...<text:line-break/>Sus, peste lumea adormit, mut.<text:line-break/>Potir de-argint n mna nevzut<text:line-break/>A ngerului purttor de pace,<text:line-break/>Se-nal luna dintre brazi...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Gigantic preot n odjdii sfinte,<text:line-break/>Strluce Caraimanul solitar...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>i tu, pierdut, o, suflet, n extaz.<text:line-break/>Cazi n genunchi...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe deal </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe deal st vechea cetuie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Popas din tainice visri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Arare vreun drume mai suie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre dnsa strmtele crri...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De veacuri zace-n prsire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cetatea unde-un voievod</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i doarme somnul n netire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu credinciosul su norod...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-adesea, cnd se face sar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i glas de tain toate au,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus, la ruina solitar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub lun, dus pe gnduri, stau.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar cnd cobor, i, dintr-o dat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lumea ce de astzi vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n manta mea ntunecat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trec prin ora ca un strin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lebda</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doarme tainica grdin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i departe, -asemeni unei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brci de-argint rtcitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dus lin de unda mut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numai lebda e mic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n singurtatea lunei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur purtnd solie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dintr-o lume disprut.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mndra apelor crias</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lunec-n micri ncete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vslind la ntmplare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dat visurilor prad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Leagn pe-oglinda apei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Basmul vechi al unei fete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-mprat, mireas trist</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vesmntu-i de zpad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cum i nclin gtul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De omt i trece printre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umbrele de slcii triste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea viseaz-ntotdeauna</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C palatele-i de aur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Porile-i deschid s intre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n iatacurile mndre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde lumineaz luna...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel toat noaptea-i poart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Palida-i melancolie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lunecnd rtcitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prad visurilor dat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dorm palatele de aur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scufundate pe vecie...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tainic stuful doar suspin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lng rm: A fost odat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Copil srman... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din raiul mndrilor Bucegi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce te jelesc de ani ntregi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce dor att de neneles</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te-a ndemnat s vii la es?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Credeai c este la ora</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Norocul tu, biet pstora...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca un copil nepriceput,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amar de tine, n-ai tiut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce griji, ce patimi, ce nevoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne bntuie n veci pe noi...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, n-ai tiut, biet, pstora,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce trist-i viaa la ora!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ne-ai venit aa curat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca gndul care te-a furat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-att de blnd te-ai ncrezut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n toate cte le-ai vzut.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C nu tiai, biet pstora</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce lume rea e la ora!</text:span></text:p>
