   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legate-s apele de-acum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea-n umbr st i-ateapt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un clre trudit de drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre cei doi plopi se-ndreapt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre gura nsetat el</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gleata o apleac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bea apa descntat el,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-arunc-n ea i pleac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar nici doi pai nu face-n drum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St roibul, sforiete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dou brae-l prind acum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe clre n clete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se apr cu suflet stns,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i lupt, i se zbate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar vrjitoare-l ine strns</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i clrete-n spate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pintenii el bate-n cal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St zrile s soarb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pdure, holde, vale, deal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se pierd n noapte oarb.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n zori de zi au fost gsii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo, la fntn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cal, i clre, zdrobii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De goana cea pgn. </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, fetelor, i voi, feciori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ap cnd v-ei duce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Suflai asupr-i de trei ori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i facei sfnta cruce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci la fntna dintre plopi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St baba blestemat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu dezleag zece popi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce leag ea o dat!</text:span></text:p>
