   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mori de spaim, ari de sete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zboar cal i lupttor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puurile-s otrvite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Peste arini pustiite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pasri mari de prad, cete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trec i ip speriete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s-abat departe-n zbor...</text:span></text:p>
