   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, i-n linitea de moarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se aude-un glas, pierdut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc vine de departe...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cine ar putea s fie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La o vreme-aa trzie?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Poate i s-o fi prut...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St, ascult, vrea s vaz...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Calul sforie... o groaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr margini ncleteaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe voinic...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai vrea acum s tie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici de drum, nici de nimic...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aiurit, ntoarce calul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scapr schintei i sar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub copite...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Peste rpe i ponoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cal i clre dispar...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neagra zare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nghite...</text:span></text:p>
