   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aolic, ce pcate!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Turci au dat, ttari au dat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-au nchis crmele-n sat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-au nchis crmele toate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eu tot m-am mbtat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici de turc, nici de ttar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-am avut i n-am habar!</text:span></text:p>
