   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoal, Gruio, drag copil,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoal, Gruio drag!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Au nu vezi cum vin tiptil</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Turcii i te leag?</text:span></text:p>
