   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi, dar greu ce-am fost dormit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zice i se mir.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori piangeni au venit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i m nvelir?</text:span></text:p>
