   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hei, bun vremea, mtuic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Drgua unde mi s&apos;a dus? </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe pat de moarte-i, srmnica,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo &apos;n cmru, sus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voinicul urc scara &apos;n prip</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu gnd pierdut, cu suflet stins</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De u, biet, se sprijinete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate &apos;nainta de plns.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O vino, vino, mult dorite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci n curnd m vei dori:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curnd aceti doi ochi albatri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pnz s&apos;or acoperi.</text:span></text:p>
