   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M&apos;or duce cioclii s m &apos;ngroape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vei plnge tu nemngiat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi te-i logodi cu alta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci snt destule fete &apos;n sat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu ce mi-ai fost de-apururi drag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i&apos;n veci de veci nu m &apos;ntristai </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-ai tii n inima&apos;mi, srman,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu vorba ta ce ran tai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lung se privir plini de jale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa duios, cei doi iubii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu mnile npreunate </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copii de moarte logodii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci ea lin nchide ochii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El scoate-atunci ncetinel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Inelul ce-l purta pe deget;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe gur-i puse-acel inel.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dac&apos;a plns n clip&apos;aceea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M &apos;ntrebi pe mine-acuma tu? -</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chiar eu am isbucnit n lacrimi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i n&apos;am vzut: a plns ori nu!</text:span></text:p>
