   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trece-aa, cntnd, n sus</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dispare la rscruce.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar izvorul murmurnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai departe doina-i duce,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn unde, sub stejar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se deteapt vntorul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El repet fermecat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doina ce-o cnta izvorul;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Echo ce dormea-n pduri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">l aude i-i rspunde:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pe uierul de vnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doina la pstor ptrunde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">El o zice din caval</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai duios, cu jale mult,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu ei o duc spre sat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi drumei cari l ascult.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O-ntlnesc nite feciori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd se-ntorc de la fnea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fetele torcnd la pori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prind de veste i-o nva.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i din gur-n gur-acum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umbl doina cea pribeag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar azi o cnt toi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De rsun ara-ntreag!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1903</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Srbtoare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se plimb prin grdina mnstirii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Domnia, alb-n ras cenuie.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amurgu-i cerne umbra-i viorie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lung sun toaca-n toiul tnguirii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">optesc ncet prin flori de iasomie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i parc vor s-o mngie zefirii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se scutur pe straturi trandafirii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i crinii mor, dar ea nu vrea s tie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe,-n zri, e vraj, cntec, via...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea trece alb,-nvluit-n cea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asemeni unei palide vedenii...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uitat de prini i de rudenii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De bucurii i de dureri strin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se stinge-n rnd cu florile-n grdin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">1903</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Isus</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vegheaz-n col a candelei lumin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nvluind icoana-n raze pale:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Isus, copil, la snul maicei sale;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pstori se mir, magi i se nchin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un zmbet linitit, blnd, fr vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui nu tiu ce ascuns jale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce presimiri de chinuri ideale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umbresc n tain faa lui divin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiai de-atunci, Isuse, tu c-odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubind prea mult pe oameni, drept rsplat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vei ndura batjocura i-amarul,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ncununat cu spini, urcnd Calvarul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe umr crucea singuri i-o vei duce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vei muri, strignd la cer, pe cruce?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Harpistul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Wer nie sein Brot in Trnen ass<text:note text:id="ftn13" text:note-class="footnote"><text:note-citation>13</text:note-citation><text:note-body>
      <text:p text:style-name="Footnote">Cine nu i-a mncat niciodat pinea udat cu lacrimi... (Germ.)</text:p></text:note-body></text:note>...<text:line-break/>GOETHE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsare vechiul soare iari</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i trebuie s-mi prsesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din nou acuma adpostul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mi cat pe ziua de-astzi rostul </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai, cine tie de-l gsesc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ulii, umbre zgribulite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici-colo, tot mai des rsar </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chemai de strigtul vieii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Grbii, prin ceaa dimineii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trec oamenii la munc iar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pasul hotrt alearg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici un copil, ici un brbat </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt veseli; unii rd sau cnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci fiecare are-o nt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-un vis de care e purtat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se duc, i trist le cat n urm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n col de strad cum dispar </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice noroc, orice plcere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ascund o tainic durere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-aduc n ochii-mi lacrimi, iar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M simt aa, pe zi ce merge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot mai pierdut, tot mai strin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">-ades m-ademenete gndul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mi fac pe lumea asta rndul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C snt stul de dor i chin...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar totui nu m-ndur de moarte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd glasul ei misterios</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M cheam blnd i m-nfioar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n toate cte m-mpresoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Resimt un farmec dureros.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">C nu tiu, ah! ct eti de dulce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Via, cei ce-o zi n-au fost</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dai frigurilor foamei prad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nici n-au tremurat pe strad</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O noapte fr adpost!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici cei ce n-au purtat blestemul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubirei fr de noroc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cei ce uitai de lumea ntreag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orfani de-orice fiin drag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-au rtcit din loc n loc...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Legend</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fost un tnr mprat </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De la miei a smuls averea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-a smuls de la tirani puterea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i muli nebuni a spnzurat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar patru ini vorbind n oapte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-au dus n giulgiuri nvlit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n codru cel mai tinuit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-au ngropat trziu n noapte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cei tari au zis: A fost miel!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne-a prigonit prea mult vreme.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar popii fulgerau blesteme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">In cei ce mai vorbeau de el:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici voie s-i cerneasc portul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici drept s-l plng n-au avut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i niciodat n-au tiut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ce pmnt le doarme mortul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu vor ti! Cci groapa lui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n blestemat pmnt s-ascunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici soare-acolo nu ptrunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici plngerile nimnui.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jurat-a Iadul s-ngrdeasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu nopi de veci acest mormnt;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar brazii tac, c nici un vnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i clatin ca s vorbeasc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar noaptea-n zare uneori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd e furtun-n deprtare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La margini de-orizont rsare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un fulger alb, trziu spre zori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntr-una spre pduri arat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i scapr spre ea mereu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E, parc arat Dumnezeu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre groapa cea de veci uitat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar ntr-o noapte va lovi -</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spintecat de lumin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugi-va noaptea cea hain,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i brazii-n flcri or vorbi:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-atunci, cu fulgerul tovar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iei-va mortul mprat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n Iadul lor, de unde au plecat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-or prbui tiranii iari.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Zmeoaica</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zorete-i fugarul, o, drag Ft-frumos!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zorete-i fugarul i-aine-te bine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci iat Zmeoaica cu chipul hidos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe urmele noastre pornit-a, i vine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Purtat n goan, ca norul de vnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-o falc n cer i cu alta-n pmnt!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, copil de crai, cci cu noi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E Galben-din-soare, copil, n-ai team!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Arunc nframa cea scump-napoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S creasc un codru nstrunic de-aram:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn&apos;dinii Zmeoaicei, roznd, s-or toci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi fi-vom departe, departe de-aci!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zorete-i fugarul, o, drag Ft-frumos!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu simi tu dogoarea arzndu-te-n spate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E crunta Zmeoaic cu chipul hidos:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Roznd la copaci, prin pdure strbate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea vine cumplit, cu prul vlvoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dac ne-ajunge, Aman e de noi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, tu, mndr copil de crai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, al inimei mele tezaur!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Arunc-i tu pieptenul de-aur ce-l ai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe loc s se fac un munte de aur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, iat-l cum crete cu vrful n cer </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l road Zmeoaica cu dinii de fier!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zorete-i fugarul, o, drag Ft-frumos!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci muntele, iat, se clatin, crap:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zmeoaica cumplit, cu chipul hidos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin borta deschis se vr i scap.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea vars catran i pucioas pe nri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-auzi tu vlvoarea cum clocot-n zri?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, tu, scump copil de crai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, cci leac i gsim noi ndat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Arunc-i oglinda vrjit ce-o ai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S creasc o balt adnc i lat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci apa cea lat va pune hotar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe care-o s-ncerce s-l treac-n zadar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zorete-i fugarul, o, drag Ft-frumos!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ntunec cerul, pmntul vuiete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te uit! Zmeoaica cu chipul hidos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se zbate-n mocirl i se zvrcolete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea url turbat i-azvrle spre noi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ghearele-i hde buci de noroi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai team, tu, dulce copil de crai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo rmne de-acum nainte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi ns trecut-am pe cellalt plai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lumea de visuri curate i sfinte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nlnuie-mi gtul cu braul tu drag! </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, las&apos; s ne duc fugarul pribeag!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P36" text:outline-level="1">Din zile mari</text:h>
