   <text:p text:style-name="P12">ALTE ZNE N ALAIUL CRAIULUI OBERON I AL TITANIEI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">SUITA LUI THEZEU SI A HIPPOLYTEI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Aciunea: SE PETRECE N ATENA I N PDUREA NVECINAT.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="Actul_I"/>Actul I</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">LA ATENA. SAL N PALATUL LUI THEZEU. INTR THEZEU, HIPPOLYTA, PHILOSTRAT I SUITA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Acum, frumoas Hippolyta, ceasul<text:line-break/>Unirii noastre i zorete pasul.<text:line-break/>Trec patru mndre zile de-ateptare<text:line-break/>Ce-aduc o alt lun; dar mi pare<text:line-break/>C prea ncet de tot cea veche scade,<text:line-break/>i-mi tot amn dorul meu cel viu.<text:line-break/>Ca matera btrn care roade<text:line-break/>Prea mult din ctigul unui vitreg fiu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Curnd n ale nopilor abisuri<text:line-break/>Cad patru zile i degrab pier;<text:line-break/>i patru nopi cu-alaiul lor de visuri,<text:line-break/>Cnd arc de-argint nou-ncordat pe cer<text:line-break/>Va strluci din bolile albastre<text:line-break/>Crai-Nou la srbtoarea nunii noastre.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Adun, Philostrat, tot tineretul<text:line-break/>Atenei, la petreceri i la jocuri,<text:line-break/>Deteapt-al veseliei duh zburdalnic,<text:line-break/>Gonind melancolia, palid oaspe,<text:line-break/>Ce n-are niciun rost pe-aceste locuri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PHILOSTRAT IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu spada te-am peit eu, Hippolyto!<text:line-break/>Iubirea, ca vrjma i-am cucerit-o;<text:line-break/>Dar ziua nunii noastre vreau s fie<text:line-break/>Prilej de pace i de bucurie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR EGEU, HERMIA, LYSANDER I DEMETRIUS.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, slav lui Thezeu, preanaltul Duce!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce veti preabunul meu Egeu mi-aduce?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De Hermia vin, Doamne, a m plnge,<text:line-break/>Fiica mea, i inima-mi se strnge.<text:line-break/>Demetrius, apropie-te. Iat<text:line-break/>Stpne, cel pe care eu, ca tat,<text:line-break/>Copilei mele l-am menit de mire<text:line-break/>Lysander, vino-ncoace: Vezi, o, duce,<text:line-break/>Aceasta-a scos pe fata mea din fire.<text:line-break/>Da, tu, Lysander. I-ai trimis aceste<text:line-break/>Scrisori, i-n nopi cu lun, sub ferestre,<text:line-break/>I-ai ngnat cu glas neltor<text:line-break/>neltoare stihuri de amor;<text:line-break/>Tu ai momit-o cu brri din plete,<text:line-break/>Cu jucrii, cu broe, cu inele,<text:line-break/>Cu vorbe fermecate i preioase,<text:line-break/>Cu fleacuri, glume proaste, dar frumoase,<text:line-break/>Solii primejdioase pentru fete.<text:line-break/>Mi-ai scos din mini copila-asculttoare<text:line-break/>i ascultarea ce-mi era datoare<text:line-break/>Ai prefcut-o-n oarb rzvrtire.<text:line-break/>De-aceea eu, stpne preamrite,<text:line-break/>Fiindc ea nu vrea s se mrite<text:line-break/>Cu tnrul ce eu i-l dau de mire,<text:line-break/>Aa cum este legea din btrni:<text:line-break/>Prinii-s pe copiii lor stpni.<text:line-break/>S-mi fac voia, sau, dac nu vrea,<text:line-break/>Pe Thanatos de mire s i-l ia!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce spui, frumoas fat? Eti datoare<text:line-break/>S vezi un zeu n tatl tu. El doar<text:line-break/>Te-a nzestrat cu-al frumuseii dar<text:line-break/>n mna lui eti ca un chip de cear,<text:line-break/>Ce-i pori tiparu-n forma omeneasc:<text:line-break/>El poate s-l pstreze-ori s-l zdrobeasc.<text:line-break/>Demetrius e-un tnr demn de tine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Lysander e de-asemeni demn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Prea bine,<text:line-break/>Dar e, Demetrius, mai prejos de tine,<text:line-break/>Cci n-are-ngduina ctigat<text:line-break/>A celui care, Hermia, i-e tat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, de-ar vrea,<text:line-break/>De-ar ti cu ochii mei s vad tata!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S vad ochii ti cu judecata<text:line-break/>Btrnului tu tat, s-ar cdea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cer, duce, ndurare, cu-ndrzneal,<text:line-break/>M-ndeamn feciorelnica-mi sfial.<text:line-break/>Dar nu tiu ce putere m supune<text:line-break/>i-mi d-naintea ndurrii tale<text:line-break/>Curaj sfielii mele feciorelnice,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S-mi spun pe fa cugetele mele.<text:line-break/>Doresc s tiu la ce pedepse grele<text:line-break/>Voi fi supus, de m-mpotrivesc<text:line-break/>S iau de so pe-acel ce nu-l iubesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ar trebui s mori, or s strpeti<text:line-break/>n tine toate poftele trupeti.<text:line-break/>ntreab-i dar, frumoasa mea copil,<text:line-break/>Pornirile ce-abia mijesc n tine<text:line-break/>i sngele ce-i clocotete-n vine<text:line-break/>Aa zglobiu, i dac nu i-e mil<text:line-break/>De anii ti cei tineri s-i petreci<text:line-break/>De-a pururi ntre zidurile reci<text:line-break/>Ale-unui schit, n haine de vestal,<text:line-break/>Slvind n imnuri stearpa lunii pal?<text:line-break/>O, fericite de trei ori acele<text:line-break/>Ce-i stpnesc pornirile, c ele<text:line-break/>Sporesc alaiul sfintelor fecioare!<text:line-break/>Mai fericit-i totui mndra floare<text:line-break/>Ce prin mireasm-i supravieuiete;<text:line-break/>Pe spinu-i feciorelnic vezi cum crete<text:line-break/>Ursita sa tnjeasc i s piar<text:line-break/>n trista-i fericire, ca s moar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai bine-atunci s cresc i s tnjesc,<text:line-break/>S mor,  dect vreodat s-mi mnjesc,<text:line-break/>Jertfind acestui tnr viaa mea,<text:line-break/>Al crui jug urt de l-a purta,<text:line-break/>Mi-ar umili i cuget i simire.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ai nc patru zile de gndire,<text:line-break/>Dar cnd Crai-Nou rsare  zi aleas<text:line-break/>De mine i iubita mea mireas<text:line-break/>Spre-a ne serba unirea  te gtete<text:line-break/>De moarte, sau de nu, ndeplinete<text:line-break/>Voina printeasc, sau n faa<text:line-break/>Altarului Dianei te nchin,<text:line-break/>Jurnd c-n veci rmne-vei strin<text:line-break/>De dragoste, i cast toat viaa!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ascult, mndr Hermia, povaa<text:line-break/>Mritului stpn, i tu, Lysander,<text:line-break/>Nu cuteza s ceri ce nu se poate,<text:line-break/>C nu eti nici iubit, nici n-ai dreptate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Demetrius, dac-o iubeti pe Hermia, i tatl<text:line-break/>Iubitei tale te iubete, iat-l!<text:line-break/>nsoar-te cu el! i las-mi mie,<text:line-break/>Pe Hermia, fiica lui, soie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>M iei n rs, Lysander! Da, el are<text:line-break/>Iubirea mea, i-i drui tot ce am.<text:line-break/>Copila e a mea, i, prin urmare,<text:line-break/>I-o dau acestui om de nobil neam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu, duce, sunt de neam bogat la fel,<text:line-break/>i sunt iubit mai mult dect e el.<text:line-break/>Norocul mi-a surs mereu i-n toate,<text:line-break/>La fel cu-al lui, de nu mai mult chiar, poate.<text:line-break/>Un lucru ns meritul mi-l crete:<text:line-break/>Cci Hermia pe mine m iubete.<text:line-break/>Cum deci s las eu drepturile mele?<text:line-break/>Demetrius a izbutit s-nele <text:line-break/>O spun aci  pe fata cea frumoas<text:line-break/>A lui Nedar, Helena  i o las<text:line-break/>Acum s plng i s-i duc dorul,<text:line-break/>Cci ea-i ador i-azi amgitorul,<text:line-break/>i astzi l iubete ca pe-un sfnt,<text:line-break/>Pe-acest om crud, nedemn de crezmnt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Mrturisesc c-am auzit i eu<text:line-break/>Vorbindu-se de-aceasta; gndul meu,<text:line-break/>Demetrius, era dorit s-i cear<text:line-break/>O lmurire; dar m-mpresurar<text:line-break/>Attea treburi mult mai nsemnate,<text:line-break/>N-avui rgaz s m-ngrijesc de toate.<text:line-break/>Ci vino, tu, Egeu, i tu, biete,<text:line-break/>Vreau s vorbesc cu voi mai pe-ndelete.<text:line-break/>Iar tu, frumoas Hermia, alege:<text:line-break/>Ori i supui voinei printeti<text:line-break/>Voina ta, ori, de nu voieti,<text:line-break/>Vei fi jertfit dup vechea lege,<text:line-break/>Ce n Atena-i nc n fiin,<text:line-break/>i-a crei puternic sentin<text:line-break/>Noi nu putem nicicum s-o ndulcim:<text:line-break/>Sau intri-n schit, sau dormi n intirim.<text:line-break/>S mergem, Hippolyta mea! Egeu,<text:line-break/>Demetrius, urmai alaiul meu:<text:line-break/>Am trebuin s vorbesc cu voi<text:line-break/>Asupra marilor serbri, i-apoi<text:line-break/>Purcede-vom aa cum legea cere</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Supui noi te urmm, i cu plcere!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">THEZEU, HIPPOLYTA, EGEU, DEMETRIUS I OAMENII CURII IES.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ei, dar ce-i plir trandafirii<text:line-break/>Obrajilor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Din pricina mhnirii<text:line-break/>C ochii mei, nvluii de nori,<text:line-break/>Nu pot stropi aceste biete flori</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vai, din mulimea crilor cetite,<text:line-break/>Din basmele ce-mi fur povestite,<text:line-break/>tiu c iubirea cnd e-adevrat,<text:line-break/>n cursul ei e-ntruna tulburat<text:line-break/>i foarte rare-s zilele-i senine<text:line-break/>De pild-atunci cnd s-ar ti de toi,<text:line-break/>O mare deosebire ntre soi<text:line-break/>De natere Poi plnge cu suspine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd cel iubit e mai prejos de tine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd, altdat, iar, nepotrivire<text:line-break/>De ani</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd btrneea se unete<text:line-break/>Cu tinereea, ce nenorocire!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd unul din prini nu se-nvoiete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, chin din iaduri! S-i alegi brbat<text:line-break/>Prin ochi strini</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sau dac s-a-ntmplat<text:line-break/>Ca doi ce se iubesc s se aleag,<text:line-break/>Rzboiul, boala, moartea, lumea-ntreag,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Toi mpotriva lor acum se-ncheag,<text:line-break/>Fcnd norocul lor fugar s piar<text:line-break/>Ca sunetul, ca umbra sau ca visul,<text:line-break/>Ca fulgerul ce-o clip scnteiaz,<text:line-break/>C nici n-apuc cineva s-l vaz,<text:line-break/>S-i strige: ,,Stai!  i e-nghiit de-abisul<text:line-break/>ntunecimii Vai, aa se duce<text:line-break/>De repede tot ceea ce strluce!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar dac-aceasta-i voia sorii rele,<text:line-break/>S ndurm i noi primejdii grele.<text:line-break/>Ca toi iubiii,  noi s-avem rbdare,<text:line-break/>C nu-i pe lume-amor lipsit de chin,<text:line-break/>De gnduri negre i de-adnc suspin,<text:line-break/>De dor, de lacrimi i de griji amare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Un sfat cuminte, Hermia. Ascult:<text:line-break/>Am o mtu cu avere mult,<text:line-break/>Avut-n ani, srac n copii,<text:line-break/>Ea st la apte pote de aci<text:line-break/>i m iubete ca pe-un fiu al ei.<text:line-break/>n casa-acestei vrednice femei<text:line-break/>Vom merge i ne vom cstori;<text:line-break/>Acolo nu ne poate urmri<text:line-break/>Urgia vreunui jude din Atena<text:line-break/>O, Hermio, mi-eti drag! Te strecoar,<text:line-break/>Din casa printeasc, mine sear;<text:line-break/>Te-atept n crngul unde cu Helena,<text:line-break/>Frumoasa ta prieten, te-aflai,<text:line-break/>ntia oar la o srbtoare<text:line-break/>A unei mndre zile-nti de mai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Lysander, jur pe arcul cel mai tare<text:line-break/>Al lui Amor, pe agera-i sgeat<text:line-break/>Cu vrful de-aur, pe cea mai curat<text:line-break/>i alb porumbi a Cytherei,<text:line-break/>Pe milostiva zn-a-mperecherii<text:line-break/>Acelora ce se iubesc, pe-aleanul<text:line-break/>Ce-o mistuia pe Dido, cnd vicleanul<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Troian a prsit-o, i pe toate<text:line-break/>Fgduinele de-amor sfrmate<text:line-break/>Mai multe de brbai ca de femei <text:line-break/>La miezul nopii, mine, vin unde vrei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Te-atept, iubito Uite pe Helena!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR HELENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine-ai venit, frumoasa mea Helena!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Tu-mi zici frumoas? Nu-mi mai zice astfel!<text:line-break/>Tu eti pentru Demetrius frumoas,<text:line-break/>Luceferi ochii ti sunt pentru el<text:line-break/>i vocea ta e mai armonioas<text:line-break/>Ca trilul ciocrliei, cnd pstorul<text:line-break/>L-ascult vesel, cnd d-n verde-ogorul<text:line-break/>Cnd vezi mceul scnteind n floare<text:line-break/>O! Dac boala e molipsitoare,<text:line-break/>De ce n-ar fi i vraja frumuseii?<text:line-break/>i-a lua din ochi vpaia, nurii feii<text:line-break/>i armonia dulcelui tu glas.<text:line-break/>i lumea, dac-ar fi a mea, te las<text:line-break/>Pe-ntreaga lume s rmi stpn,<text:line-break/>Demetrius al meu doar s rmn!<text:line-break/>nva-m cum s-l privesc i spune<text:line-break/>Prin ce ascunse vrji l poi supune,<text:line-break/>Arat-mi taina frumuseii tale</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>El m iubete, chiar de-i fug din cale,<text:line-break/>Dei m uit la el urt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, dac<text:line-break/>A ti cum s m uit la el, s-i plac!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dei-l gonesc i-l cert, el tot m cere</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vai, plnsul meu nu are-acea putere!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dei-i art dispre, el m slvete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu l slvesc, el m dispreuiete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce-s vinovat eu dac-i nebun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, de-a putea i eu la fel s spun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ascult, i fii vesel, Helena:<text:line-break/>Eu i Lysander prsim Atena.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd pe Lysander-nti eu l-am vzut,<text:line-break/>Ce paradis oraul mi-a prut!<text:line-break/>i vezi, aa puternic e misterul<text:line-break/>Amorului, c-n iad mi schimb cerul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cuvintele acestea nu te mint:<text:line-break/>Cnd mine, n oglinda apei clare<text:line-break/>i scald Hebe faa ei de-argint,<text:line-break/>Stropind cmpia cu mrgritare,<text:line-break/>Pe lng zidul falnic al arenei,<text:line-break/>Ne furiam prin porile Atenei</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>i-n poienia unde amndou,<text:line-break/>Pe stratul de brndue plin de rou,<text:line-break/>Ne hodineam n diminei senine,<text:line-break/>M va-ntlni Lysander-al meu pe mine.<text:line-break/>Pe urm, ntorcndu-ne privirea<text:line-break/>De la Atena,<text:line-break/>i vom cuprinde totul din privire<text:line-break/>S cutm cu grij, n netire,<text:line-break/>Prieteni noi, tovrii strine<text:line-break/>Tovar de-amor, rmi cu bine,<text:line-break/>Te las, i fac-ndurtorul Joe,<text:line-break/>Demetrius al tu s-i intre-n voie<text:line-break/>Lysander, nu uita De-acuma, cat<text:line-break/>S ne lipsim privirea nsetat<text:line-break/>De dragoste, cci noaptea va veni.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE HERMIA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>mi in cuvntul, Hermia, s tii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE PRIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">HELENA SE NDREAPT SPRE PALAT, N VREME CE CORTINA CADE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Ct poate fericirea s-i rsfee!<text:line-break/>Nu-s mai prejos de ea n frumusee.<text:line-break/>Dar ce folos? Demetrius nu se-ncrede<text:line-break/>n ce tiu alii, n ce Atena vede.<text:line-break/>Robit de ochii Hermiei se-nal<text:line-break/>Cum eu, robit lui, cad n greeal.<text:line-break/>Din tot ce-i josnic, gunos, din pleav,<text:line-break/>Iubirea furete-un chip de slav.<text:line-break/>Ea nu cu ochii vede, ci cu gndul.<text:line-break/>nchipuindu-l orb, naripndu-l.<text:line-break/>Pe Cupidon, tim c smintit prip<text:line-break/>St-n ochii lui legai, pe-a lui arip<text:line-break/>Iubirea, tim cu toii c-i un copil;<text:line-break/>Se-nal i orbecie umil,<text:line-break/>Precum trengarii care jur-n ag,<text:line-break/>Nimica de iubire nu o leag.<text:line-break/>Cnd n-avea ochii Hermiei n minte,<text:line-break/>M amgea-n potop de jurminte.<text:line-break/>Dar i-a simit aprinsa ei vpaie,<text:line-break/>i tot potopul s-a-nmuiat n ploaie.<text:line-break/>Demetrius va afla din gura mea<text:line-break/>C mine va fugi iubita sa.<text:line-break/>i mine-i va porni n cutare,<text:line-break/>Aflnd prin mine-aceast tain mare.<text:line-break/>M voi alege doar c-l voi vedea,<text:line-break/>Tot cutnd-o pe rivala mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_II"/>Scena II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ODAIE NTR-O COLIB. SEAR. SCEN-NGUST.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR SNUG, BOTTOM, FLUTE, SNOUT, QUINCE I STARVELIG.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Suntem toi n pr?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ar fi mai bine s-i strigi pe toi, unul dup altul, dup list.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Iat-i, aci-s trecui toi pe care i-am socotit destoinici s joace la reprezentaia de gal ce-o d naintea ducelui i-a ducesei, n seara de nunt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai nti, cinstite Quince, povestete-ne subiectul piesei, apoi citete numele actorilor, i pe urm s ne apucm de treab.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Piesa se cheam: ,,Prea jalnica comedie i<text:line-break/>cumplita moarte a lui Pyram i a Thisbeei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E un cap de oper, s m credei, i foarte hazlie. Acuma, Quince drag, strig pe actori dup list. Scumpi maetri, nu v-ngrmdii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S rspund fitecare! Nick Bottom, estorul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aci. Spune-mi rolul pe care am s-l joc i apoi vezi de altul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dumneata, Nick Bottom, ai s faci pe Pyram.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce-i Pyram sta? Un amorez ori un tiran?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Un amorez care se omoar foarte frumos din dragoste.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, are s fie nevoie de ceva lacrimi ca s ias bine rolul sta! De l-oi juca eu, n-am s cru deloc ochii adunrii! Voi strni o furtun de lacrimi, voi geme cumsecade Cu toate c mai drag mi-ar fi s joc pe un tiran! Sunt n stare mai bine ca oricine s fac pe Herculea! E un rol sta n care toate se prvlesc i se duc de rp!<text:line-break/>Dar stnca se prvale<text:line-break/>Sfrmnd ce-i iese-n cale,<text:line-break/>Rzbubuind n treact<text:line-break/>i sparge orice lact,<text:line-break/>Iar Phoebus peste unde<text:line-break/>Cu caru-i strlucit<text:line-break/>Ar vrea s se cufunde<text:line-break/>n cruntul nesfrit.<text:line-break/>E frumos, hai? Zi-i acum pe ceilali confrai. Iat ce ton trebuie s ia Herculea sau un tiran oarecare; amorezul e mai dulceag, mai plngtor</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Francisc Flute, crpaci de foale!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aci!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dumneata vei juca pe Thisbeea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cine-i Thisbeea? Vreun cavaler rtcitor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu; Thisbeea e domnia pe care Pyram trebuie s-o iubeasc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba nu, zu, rogu-te, nu m face s joc un rol de femeie, c uite, ncep s-mi dea tuleiele</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>N-are a face; ai s joci cu masc i-i vei subia glasul ct vei putea mai tare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dac pot s pun masc, las-m pe mine s joc i rolul Thisbeei! Am s-mi fac un glscior ngrozitor de subire: ,,Thisbea! Thisbea! Ah, Pyrame! Scumpul meu dulce! Thisbea ta, iubita ta Thisbea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu, nu; dumneata ai s joci pe Pyram, i dumneata, Flute, pe Thisbeea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine, fie. Treci la altul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Robin Starveling, croitorul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>STARVELING:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aici, Peter Quince!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Robin Starveling, dumneata ai s-o joci pe mama Thisbeei. Tom Snout, tu vei fi cldrarul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aici-s, Peter Quince!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dumneata ai s faci pe tatl lui Pyram.<text:line-break/>Eu nsumi pe tatl Thisbeei. Snug tmplarul s fac pe Leul. n sfrit, cred c am mprit bine toate rolurile!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNUG:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E copiat rolul Leului? Dac da, d-mi-l, te rog, s-l nv, c sunt cam greu de cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>N-ai nevoie s-l nvei, n-ai dect s-l ragi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, lsai-m s joc i eu rolul Leului! A rcni-n aa fel, c a rni toate inimile simitoare! A rcni-n aa fel, c ducele ar striga: ,,Bis rgetul! Bis rgetul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Dac ragi aa fioros, te pomeneti c faci pe ducesa i doamnele ei s leine de spaim  i-ar fi destul ca s ne spnzure pe toi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TOI:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i spnzurai ar fi copiii mamelor noastre.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Fr doar i poate, scumpi maetri, dac speriem damele, toate au s aib un singur gnd: s ne trimit la spnzurtoare! Dar eu pot s-mi prefac aa de bine glasul, c voi rage ginga ca o turturea cnd gngurete. Voi rcni ca o privighetoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>N-ai s joci alt rol dect al lui Pyram.<text:line-break/>Pyram sta e un om dulce la chip, ca un om pe care i-ar plcea s-l ntlneti<text:line-break/>ntr-o lung zi cu soare; un cavaler drgu i nostim.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine, s-l joc. Dar ce fel de barb s-ar potrivi mai bine cu rolul meu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Care i-o plcea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A putea s joc rolul sta cu o barb n culoarea paiului, sau cu o barb portocalie ca bronzul, sau cu o barb de culoarea coroanei Franei, galben de tot.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Cele mai multe tivde de culoarea Franei i-au pierdut prul; vei juca deci i tu fr barb. Acum, scumpi maetri, avei fiecare rolul vostru. V conjur, v cer, v poruncesc s le tii pn mine sear i s ne ntlnim cu toii n poiana de lng palatul ducal, la o leghe de ora, am fi opcii de toi gur-casc i toat lumea ar afla de planul nostru. Eu acuma dau fuga s fac o nsemnare de toate lucrurile ce ne trebuie pentru reprezentaie. V rog s nu care cumva s lipseasc vreunul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu vom lipsi. Acolo putem s repetm n toat voia. Cutai s fii cu toii la nlime.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S ne-ntlnim la stejarul ducelui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Venim, venim, orice s-ar ntmpla!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="Actul_II"/>Actul II</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I_2"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">O POIAN LNG ATENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR PUCK DIN STNGA. O ZN DIN CEALALT PARTE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hei, ncotro, grbite duh?<text:line-break/>ZNA:<text:line-break/>Rtcitoare prin vzduh,<text:line-break/>Peste arcuri i grdini,<text:line-break/>Peste mrcini, hrtoape,<text:line-break/>Peste gropi i peste ape,<text:line-break/>Trec plutind i-ntrec n zbor<text:line-break/>Globul lunii plutitor,<text:line-break/>i stropesc cu rou rece<text:line-break/>Cercurile ce le las<text:line-break/>Doamna znelor cnd trece<text:line-break/>Peste iarba de mtase,<text:line-break/>Cu-ale sale jupnie,<text:line-break/>Care-s naltele crie,<text:line-break/>Pe-ale lor fuste-aurite<text:line-break/>Tu zreti aceste pete,<text:line-break/>Sunt rubine, mult dorite<text:line-break/>De galnicele fete,<text:line-break/>Pete care cu parfumul<text:line-break/>Lor mblsmeaz drumul.<text:line-break/>Dar merg s strng vreo civa stropi de rou,<text:line-break/>S-anin de orice floare-o perl nou.<text:line-break/>Hai, pleac! Vine-aici criasa mea,<text:line-break/>Cu-alaiul ei de zne dup ea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i Craiul meu dorete, mi se pare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>S dea aici, la noapte, o serbare.<text:line-break/>Ferete-i pe stpna ta s-o vad;<text:line-break/>Cci Oberon e, tii, pornit pe sfad<text:line-break/>i dornic e de rzbunare Craiul,<text:line-break/>Fiindc ea trte cu alaiul<text:line-break/>Ca paj, pe-un drgla prunc dolofan,<text:line-break/>Rpit de la un rege indian.<text:line-break/>Prunc de furat mai scump ea n-a avut,<text:line-break/>i Oberon, gelosul, ar fi vrut<text:line-break/>S-l aib printre scutierii si,<text:line-break/>S-l poarte la vnat prin muni i vi<text:line-break/>Iar ea nu vrea cu niciun pre s-l piard,<text:line-break/>Cu flori l ncunun i-l dezmiard,<text:line-break/>i-l ine lng ea, cu mare dor<text:line-break/>Acum, de se-ntlnesc la vreun izvor,<text:line-break/>Sub licrul de stele n dumbrav,<text:line-break/>Sau n hi, s-apuc de glceav<text:line-break/>i se sfdesc i hojma se defaim<text:line-break/>C bieii silfi se-ascund prin ghimpi de spaim<text:line-break/>ZNA:<text:line-break/>Sau chipul i fptura ta m-nal,<text:line-break/>Sau dac-mi dau eu bine socoteal,<text:line-break/>Eti duhul htru cruia i spun<text:line-break/>Cei ce te tiu ,,Robin-biatul-bun.<text:line-break/>Nu eti tu cel ce vri pe fete-n boale,<text:line-break/>i noaptea furi smntna de pe oale,<text:line-break/>Te-ascunzi n ie i ncurci urzeala,<text:line-break/>Faci morile s umble alandala?<text:line-break/>Tot tu mpiedici untul s s-aleag,<text:line-break/>C biata gospodin ziua-ntreag<text:line-break/>Asud n zadar i unt nu iese;<text:line-break/>Strici vinurile care fierb, i-ades<text:line-break/>neli pe cltor i rzi de el,<text:line-break/>Pe-acel ce-i zice ns ,,Prichindel,<text:line-break/>Sau ,,micul Puck  pe-acela tu-l slujeti<text:line-break/>i chiar i-aduci noroc Aa-i c eti<text:line-break/>,,Robin-biatul-bun, cel sclipitor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Sunt Puck, biatul bun, rtcitor<text:line-break/>i ca s-l fac pe Oberon s rd,<text:line-break/>Obinuiesc s-mi iau o fa hd.<text:line-break/>Cnd, necheznd ca iepele, atrag<text:line-break/>Pe hrmsarul brudnic n huceag.<text:line-break/>Mr copt m fac adesea n cuptorul<text:line-break/>Cumetrei, i cnd vrea s ia ulciorul<text:line-break/>S beie, eu de nasul ei m-anin<text:line-break/>i berea curge-n vetedul ei sn!<text:line-break/>Ades, cea mai sftoas din bunici,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd e rugat de nepoii mici<text:line-break/>S spuie-un basm, m ia drept scunel<text:line-break/>Cu trei picioare: vrea s stea pe el,<text:line-break/>Atunci alunec, baba se trezete<text:line-break/>Jos pe podele, blastm, tuete,<text:line-break/>Iar toi ceilali fac haz, se in de ale<text:line-break/>De rd, pufnesc, strnut n basmale<text:line-break/>i jur c de cnd sunt ei pe lume,<text:line-break/>N-au pomenit aa poznae glume!<text:line-break/>Dar uite-l pe-Oberon. Adio, zn!<text:line-break/>ZNA:<text:line-break/>Ah, uite i pe mndra mea stpn!<text:line-break/>Oh, dac n-ar zri-o Craiul tu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">OBERON INTR CU ALAIUL SU PRIN DREAPTA,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TITANIA CU AL EI, DIN STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aici, pe lun, ne-ntlnim cam ru,<text:line-break/>Titanio, semeao!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Oberon!<text:line-break/>Gelosul! Haidem, zno, s fugim:<text:line-break/>Doar am jurat s ocolesc pe veci<text:line-break/>Tovria i-aternutul su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nesocotito! Te grbeti s pleci?<text:line-break/>Ce? Nu mai sunt eu oare soul tu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Atunci eu s-ar cdea s-i fiu soia,<text:line-break/>Dar tim c, prsind mpria,<text:line-break/>Tu zile-ntregi, sub chipul lui Corin,<text:line-break/>Cntai pe fluier versuri de amor,<text:line-break/>Culcat n al Philidei sn de crin.<text:line-break/>De ce te-ntorci acum cu-atta zor<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Din India cu plaiuri deprtate?<text:line-break/>Ori pentru mndra amazoan, poate,<text:line-break/>Rzboinica-i ibovnic-ngmfat<text:line-break/>De care te topeai de dor odat,<text:line-break/>Se mistuie pentru Thezeu de-amor<text:line-break/>i-aduci belug n csnicia lor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum de-ndrzneti, Titanio, s-mi faci,<text:line-break/>Cnd tim c pe Thezeu ce mult l placi,<text:line-break/>Mustrri, pe Hippolyta c-o iubesc?<text:line-break/>Ai vrea cu orice pre s-i amintesc<text:line-break/>C tu l-ai smuls, pe-o noapte nstelat,<text:line-break/>De lng Perigenia-nelat<text:line-break/>Atunci de el? i cine l-a mpins<text:line-break/>S-i calce jurmntul dat, nestins,<text:line-break/>Egleei, Ariadnei, Antiopei?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De mine mai cutezi s te apropii?<text:line-break/>Ca om gelos eti foarte priceput!<text:line-break/>Din toiul verii nu ne-am mai vzut<text:line-break/>S ne jucm zburdalnicele hore<text:line-break/>Pe melodia harfelor sonore,<text:line-break/>n vi, n lunci, n huciuri, la izvoare,<text:line-break/>i nici pe rmul nisipos de mare.<text:line-break/>Eoliane , fr ca deodat<text:line-break/>Tu s nu vii cu certurile tale,<text:line-break/>S nu ne tulburi veselia toat<text:line-break/>De-aceea, mnios pesemne, vntul<text:line-break/>C n-ascultm la cntecele sale,<text:line-break/>Sorbi din ape neguri otrvite<text:line-break/>Care-au fcut, acoperind pmntul,<text:line-break/>i cele mai nepricopsite grle<text:line-break/>S rup malul i s se azvrle<text:line-break/>Din albia umflat de trufie<text:line-break/>Zadarnic boii ndurat-au jugul.<text:line-break/>Zadarnic omul i trudete plugul,<text:line-break/>Cci putrezete grul n cmpie<text:line-break/>Pnce s prind spic, i e pustie<text:line-break/>Punea, corbii-n cete nesfrite<text:line-break/>Se-abat pe cmpul plin de moarte vite<text:line-break/>Popicele n glod zac ngropate,<text:line-break/>Potecile sunt prsite toate<text:line-break/>Prin lunci, prin luminiuri, prin poiene,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De nu le mai cunoti din buruiene.<text:line-break/>i-n nopi de iarn nu s-aud poveti<text:line-break/>Prin case, nici colinde la fereti<text:line-break/>i nimeni la petreceri nu se-ndeamn<text:line-break/>De-aceea luna, peste ape doamn,<text:line-break/>Umple vzduhul, palid de ciud,<text:line-break/>Cu cea-mprtiind rceala ud;<text:line-break/>i timpurile anului se-ntoarn<text:line-break/>Anapoda pe crug: cci alba iarn<text:line-break/>Srut roii roze parfumate;<text:line-break/>Pe capul nins, de tmplele-mbrumate<text:line-break/>Ale lui Criv spnzur-o tiar<text:line-break/>De ghiocei Zglobia primvar,<text:line-break/>Senina var, toamna-mbelugat,<text:line-break/>Zgrcita iarn , i schimbar toate<text:line-break/>Vemntul Lumea-ncearc-nspimntat<text:line-break/>S le cunoasc, ns nu mai poate<text:line-break/>Nici dup road, nici dup culoare.<text:line-break/>i-acest noian de zpceli i rele<text:line-break/>De unde crezi c izvorte oare?<text:line-break/>Din certurile noastre, da, din ele,<text:line-break/>Noi suntem vinovai de toate cele</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>ndreapt-le, c-i st doar n putere!<text:line-break/>De ce-l jigneti pe Oberon? Ce-i cere<text:line-break/>Titaniei? Nimic, dect s-i dea<text:line-break/>Un prunc pierdut, pe care dnsul vrea<text:line-break/>S-l fac paj de-cinste-al Curii sale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ct despre asta, Oberon, nici ale<text:line-break/>mpriei znelor comori<text:line-break/>Nu-mi pot plti pe-acest copil din flori.<text:line-break/>Cu maica lui eram ca i o sor,<text:line-break/>i-ades n miresmata auror<text:line-break/>A Indiei, pe rmul lui Neptun<text:line-break/>Cu perle vream cu ea s m-ncunun.<text:line-break/>Stam, i privind ades cum de la maluri<text:line-break/>Corbii grele se-mbarcau pe valuri,<text:line-break/>Fceam mult haz de albele vntrele<text:line-break/>De vnt umflate, ce preau c-s grele;<text:line-break/>Atunci i ea s-noate ncepea,<text:line-break/>Cu pntecul rotund, fcnd ca ele <text:line-break/>(Cci chiar p-atunci era i dnsa grea<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu pajul meu de azi) Dar, muritoare,<text:line-break/>Muri n ceasul chiar cnd l-a nscut.<text:line-break/>De dragul ei, l-am luat i l-am crescut<text:line-break/>Pe-acest copil, i tot de dragul ei<text:line-break/>Nu-l dau, c-mi este drag ca ochii mei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ct stai pe-aceste locuri?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>tiu i eu?<text:line-break/>Plec poate dup nunta lui Thezeu.<text:line-break/>De vrei s facem hora mpreun,<text:line-break/>i s ne vezi cum dnuim n lun,<text:line-break/>Rmi cu noi; de nu, cu-att mai bine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De-mi dai biatul, o s merg cu tine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nu-l dau pe toat-mpria ta!<text:line-break/>S mergem, zne. C, dac-am mai sta,<text:line-break/>S-ar face sfad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TITANIA CU SUITA EI PLEAC.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Caut-i de cale!<text:line-break/>Dar nu vei prsi aceast vale<text:line-break/>Mai nainte de-a-mi plti ocara,<text:line-break/>De nu ajung cumplit s m rzbun.<text:line-break/>Hai, vino, drag Puck, biatul bun.<text:line-break/>i-aduci aminte tu de ziua cnd<text:line-break/>Stam noi pe-un promontoriu , i cntnd<text:line-break/>Veni acea siren pe-un delfin,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Un cntec dulce i aa de lin,<text:line-break/>C amui rzboinica fanfar<text:line-break/>A mrii, i, desprini, alunecar<text:line-break/>Vreo doi luceferi din naltul zrii,<text:line-break/>Spre-a asculta cum cnt fata mrii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mi-aduc aminte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Tot atunci vzui<text:line-break/>(Tu nu puteai s-l vezi), cu arcul lui,<text:line-break/>Pe-Amor zburnd ntre pmnt i lun,<text:line-break/>intind cu-un vrf aprins cu mtrgun<text:line-break/>Pe o vestal care sta pe tron.<text:line-break/>i cum ntinse arcul, Cupidon<text:line-break/>Putea rni cu sprintena-i sgeat<text:line-break/>O sut mii de inimi dintr-odat;<text:line-break/>n casta raz-a lunei umezi ns,<text:line-break/>Vzui sgeata lui de par stins<text:line-break/>i fata de-mprat trecu senin,<text:line-break/>Ca o fecioar ginga, strin<text:line-break/>De dragoste Dar eu atunci vzui<text:line-break/>n care loc pic sgeata lui:<text:line-break/>Czu-n apus, pe-o mic buruian,<text:line-break/>Cu albe flori, dar de-a sgeii ran<text:line-break/>De-atuncea roii Fetele, la ar,<text:line-break/>i zic ,,nvalnic. Du-te, aadar,<text:line-break/>i ad-mi-o. i-am artat-o o dat.<text:line-break/>De picuri, la brbai sau la femei,<text:line-break/>Pe ochii lor nchii, cnd somnu-i fur,<text:line-break/>Un strop din sucul fermecat al ei,<text:line-break/>Se-ndrgostesc de cea dinti fptur<text:line-break/>Pe care-o vd cnd se trezesc din somn<text:line-break/>Alearg dar, i sunt stpn i domn,<text:line-break/>i ad-mi fermecata buruian<text:line-break/>Ca fiara din adnc, leviatan,<text:line-break/>Pe cnd strbate-oceanu-ntr-o clipit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Vreau s ncing, n fuga mea zorit,<text:line-break/>ntreg pmntu-n patruzeci de clipe.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:soft-page-break/>PUCK IESE REPEDE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Voi iscodi, cu fragede aripe,<text:line-break/>Titania n somn de-o fi culcat<text:line-break/>i-atunci cu buruiana fermecat,<text:line-break/>Pe-oricine-l va vedea la deteptare,<text:line-break/>Un leu, un urs, un taur, oriicare,<text:line-break/>Un lup sau o maimu de-o zri,<text:line-break/>Fr de margini s-o ndrgosti.<text:line-break/> Stropind-o cu o alt buruian,<text:line-break/>S-mi deie-atuncea pajul de poman.<text:line-break/>Dar cine vine? Eu sunt nevzut,<text:line-break/>S aflu ce-i vor spune, netiut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR DEMETRIUS I HELENA DIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-a dus iubirea noastr. O poveste?<text:line-break/>Cu Hermia, Lysander unde este?<text:line-break/>Pe el l voi ucide. M-a ptruns<text:line-break/>Iubirea ei. n codru s-au ascuns,<text:line-break/>Aa mi-ai spus. Dar mintea-mi se destram<text:line-break/>De nu pot s-o gsesc, de bun seam,<text:line-break/>Pe Hermia Tu, nu m mai urma!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar nu pot s nfrng iubirea ta!<text:line-break/>S nu-mi mai farmeci sufletul de dor<text:line-break/>i n-am s-i mai pstrez att amor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Te-am cucerit? Nu i-am vorbit deschis?<text:line-break/>Te-ncrezi degeaba ntr-al iubirii vis.<text:line-break/>Nu te iubesc! Nu pot s te iubesc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai mult n chipu-acesta te-ndrgesc!<text:line-break/>i sunt, Demetrius, cinele de paz.<text:line-break/>M bai, i simt n inim o raz<text:line-break/>De dragoste-nlndu-se spre tine.<text:line-break/>M simt, de tine alturi, foarte bine<text:line-break/>Chiar de m bai, chiar dac m loveti,<text:line-break/>C te-nsoesc, dei nu m iubeti.<text:line-break/>O! Las-m s merg pe urma ta,<text:line-break/>Chiar de m-ai bate, chiar de m-ai certa!<text:line-break/>M las calea s i-o nsoesc,<text:line-break/>Dar tot te voi gsi, cci te iubesc.<text:line-break/>Un col din suflet vreau s-mi hrzeti,<text:line-break/>Chiar dac azi nu poi s m iubeti.<text:line-break/>Dar totui i-l ceresc, s-l am i mine.<text:line-break/>M rog de tine cum se roag-un cine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu cuteza mnia s-mi strneti,<text:line-break/>Cci doar la ur tu m ispiteti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd nu te vd, de oriice mi-e sil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum poate s se-ndure o copil<text:line-break/>S ias din cetate, urmrind<text:line-break/>Pe-acel iubit de ea cu-atta jind,<text:line-break/>Dar care n-o iubete? i la noapte<text:line-break/>S-nfrunte doar primejdii, crunte fapte,<text:line-break/>Primejduind, i fr de temei<text:line-break/>Comoara scump-a fecioriei ei?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mi-e cinstea ta de paz-n orice fapte.<text:line-break/>De tine-alturi cnd m vd n noapte<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vd ochii ti scnteietori mereu:<text:line-break/>Nu-i noapte, nici pustiu n jurul meu.<text:line-break/>M simt alturi de fiina-i drag,<text:line-break/>i pentru mine este-o lume-ntreag.<text:line-break/>Nu-s singur, i nici nu-s prsit,<text:line-break/>Cnd sunt de lumea-ntreag ocrotit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>M-ascund printre tufiuri, ca n gheare<text:line-break/>S te cuprind aprigele fiare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nici sufletul de fiar nu-i hain<text:line-break/>Ca sufletu-i, tios cum este-un spin.<text:line-break/>Hai, pleac i m las, ca pe dos,<text:line-break/>Legenda s se-ntoarc: ruinos<text:line-break/>Apollo fuge, la i mielete,<text:line-break/>Iar Daphne peste tot l urmrete.<text:line-break/>Un uliu-i urmrit de-o turturic;<text:line-break/>Iar biata cprioar, fr fric,<text:line-break/>Spre tigrul fioros se npustete:<text:line-break/>De-avntul ciutei fiara se ferete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu stau s-i mai rspund la nerozii.<text:line-break/>Hai, pleac, ori altminteri vei pi<text:line-break/>n codru o nprasnic ocar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>i-e inima cumplit i amar:<text:line-break/>n templu, n cetate-n toat ara,<text:line-break/>Batjocoreti ce-am mai de pre, comoara<text:line-break/>Iubirii nesfrite pentru tine.<text:line-break/>Brbatul se cuvine, prin suspine,<text:line-break/>S-i urmreasc tot mereu iubita.<text:line-break/>Aicea eu m simt nedreptit,<text:line-break/>Cci i ceresc, din inim, iubirea,<text:line-break/>Iar tu nu mi-ai pstrat nici amintirea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:soft-page-break/>DEMETRIUS IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Te-oi urmri i-oi face rai din iad,<text:line-break/>Ucis de cel drag de-o fi s cad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Iei din pdure, nimf: s tii bine:<text:line-break/>Tu vei fugi de el, el, dup tine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PUCK VINE DIN ADNCIME, CU O FLOARE MARE, ROIE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">(LUI PUCK): Hai, vino, spiridu rtcitor!<text:line-break/>Adus-ai floarea ginga de-amor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>(I-O ARAT): Da, iat-o!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pune-o-n locul singuratic.<text:line-break/>Plin de mireasma cimbrului slbatic,<text:line-break/>i unde cresc criele nalte,<text:line-break/>Alturi cu mucatele nvoalte.<text:line-break/>Umbrit de-un rug cu-o-ntunecat floare<text:line-break/>De trandafiri, de crini, de lcrmioare.<text:line-break/>Aicea, lin de zne legnat,<text:line-break/>Titania voioas se desfat<text:line-break/>n cuib nmiresmat de flori, ce bine<text:line-break/>Se odihnete-n nopile senine!<text:line-break/>Aicea-i las smluita piele<text:line-break/>oprla, pentru-o rochie cu inele.<text:line-break/>Strai destul de larg s-mbrace<text:line-break/>Pe-oricare dintre znele acele.<text:line-break/>Aici voi atepta s-o ung pe gene<text:line-break/>C-un strop din sucul astei buruiene,<text:line-break/>Umplndu-i ochii ei cu fel de fel<text:line-break/>De nluciri nebune. Ia din el<text:line-break/>i tu un strop, i cat prin poian<text:line-break/>Pn ce-ntlneti o mndr-atenian<text:line-break/>De-un tnr atenian namorat,<text:line-break/>De care el vrea cu-orice pre s scape.<text:line-break/>Mergi i, cnd doarme, unge-l pe pleoape<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cu buruiana aceasta fermecat.<text:line-break/>Dar s purcezi cu-atta iscusin<text:line-break/>nct, firete, cea dinti fiin<text:line-break/>Pe care-o va zri, s fie ea.<text:line-break/>l vei cunoate dup-mbrcmintea<text:line-break/>Lui de-atenian. F tot ce-i spun, aa<text:line-break/>Ca el de dragul ei s-i piard mintea,<text:line-break/>Precum ea i-o pierdu de dragul lui<text:line-break/>M vei gsi aici mai naintea<text:line-break/>Cntatului. Mergi dar i ia aminte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Stpnul meu feeric, vorba ta<text:line-break/>Se va-mplini aidoma cum spui! (IESE.)<text:line-break/>(OBERON SE ASCUNDE-N DREAPTA-N FA I ST LA PND.)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_II_2"/>Scena II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">O ALT PARTE A PDURII.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TITANIA VINE CU ZNELE EI DIN FUND, N STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Acuma, zne, cntecul i hora!<text:line-break/>i toate-apoi la rostul tuturora!<text:line-break/>Toi mugurii de viermi s-i curii<text:line-break/>S par trandafirii strlucii.<text:line-break/>S prindei prin dumbrav lilieci.<text:line-break/>i s le smulgei aripile reci,<text:line-break/>Croind uor rochie pentru iele.<text:line-break/>i pentru spiridui, la fel, din ele.<text:line-break/>Silii i cucuvaia s-i ia zborul,<text:line-break/>Cu iptu-i de ru prevestitorul.<text:line-break/>i-acum legnai-m domol<text:line-break/>n cntecele voastre. Pn m scol<text:line-break/>La munc! i lsai-m s dorm!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">CNTECUL ZNELOR.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">NTIA ZN:<text:line-break/>erpi vrgai, epoi arici,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Salamandre verzi, plecai!<text:line-break/>Doamna noastr doarme-aici,<text:line-break/>Nu cumva s-o tulburai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CORUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nani, nani, dormi uor!<text:line-break/>Fie lin<text:line-break/>i senin<text:line-break/>Somnul tu,<text:line-break/>i pzit de ceasul ru<text:line-break/>Nani, nani, dormi uor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">II</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A doua ZN:<text:line-break/>Voi, bondari, nari, uor,<text:line-break/>Negri crbui, tcei!<text:line-break/>Voi, pianjeni estori,<text:line-break/>Mergei, esei, unde vrei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CORUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nani, nani, dormi uor!<text:line-break/>Fie lin<text:line-break/>i senin<text:line-break/>Somnul tu,<text:line-break/>i pzit de ceasul ru<text:line-break/>Nani, nani, dormi uor!<text:line-break/>NTIA ZN:<text:line-break/>Una dintre noi vegheaz<text:line-break/>i s stea aici de paz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ZNELE SE DUC I DISPAR N FUND. TITANIA DOARME N STNGA, N FA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR OBERON I SE APROPIE DE TITANIA, APSND FLOAREA PE PLEOAPELE EI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cnd din somn vei tresri<text:line-break/>S-ndrgeti ce vei gsi:<text:line-break/>Tigru, leopard, motan,<text:line-break/>Urs, mistre ori obolan,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ct de prost ar fi i-orict<text:line-break/>De slbatic i urt,<text:line-break/>Drag s-i pice, cum l vezi<text:line-break/>i de doru-i s oftezi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PLEAC RZND PRIN STNGA, N FUND.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR LYSANDER I HERMIA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ai obosit de-att amar de drum<text:line-break/>i ne-am pierdut, iubita mea, crarea.<text:line-break/>S ne culcm, cci toate dorm acum,<text:line-break/>Doar s-a lsat de mult ntunecarea.<text:line-break/>S poposim aicea n pdure,<text:line-break/>Hai, Hermio, i somnul s ne fure.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Lysander drag, fie-aa cum zici,<text:line-break/>Eu mi-am ales culcuul meu aici,<text:line-break/>Pe-acest rzor Tu unde-i vei aterne?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aceste flori ne vor sluji de perne:<text:line-break/>O inim, un pat i o credin!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu te culca alturea de mine,<text:line-break/>Lysander, nu se cade mi-e ruine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>n tot ce-am spus e nevinovie:<text:line-break/>Iubirea se rostete-aa cum tie.<text:line-break/>Ni-s inimile strns mpreunate,<text:line-break/>i nu te-ndemn, iubito, la pcate.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Avem n piept o singur credin,<text:line-break/>Fcnd din noi o singur fiin.<text:line-break/>ngduie-mi alturea de tine<text:line-break/>S m ntind, pe ierburi i verbine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, ce drgu mperechezi cuvinte!<text:line-break/>A fi nebun de-a fi vrut s spun<text:line-break/>Mcar o clip c Lysander minte!<text:line-break/>Dar, scump Lysander, fii aa de bun<text:line-break/>Din dragoste, ca i din curtenie,<text:line-break/>Treci mai departe, dar nu mai departe<text:line-break/>Dect o bun cretere desparte<text:line-break/>Pe-un so de viitoarea lui soie<text:line-break/>Adio, drag Lysander, noapte bun!<text:line-break/>Dea cerul ca iubirea-i s n-apun<text:line-break/>Dect cnd scumpa-i via va apune</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>nal i eu aceeai rugciune:<text:line-break/>Cnd nu te-oi mai iubi m ieie Domnul;<text:line-break/>Te nvemnte-acum, n tihna-i, somnul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ba, jumtate din urare caz<text:line-break/>Pe ochii celui ce aa-mi ureaz!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">AMNDOI SE CULC I ADORM.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PUCK INTR PRIN FUND, N STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Prin pdure, peste tot,<text:line-break/>Am umblat i n-am gsit<text:line-break/>Atenian afurisit<text:line-break/>Pe ai crui ochi s pot<text:line-break/>Pune sucul meu vrjit.<text:line-break/>Noapte i tcere Dar<text:line-break/>Cine doarme-aci-n umbrar?<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cel de care mi vorbi<text:line-break/>Oberon c n-ar iubi,<text:line-break/>Ticlosul, pe-ateniana!<text:line-break/>i dincoace doarme dulce<text:line-break/>i nenorocita de fat<text:line-break/>Pe pmntul ud i rece!<text:line-break/>Uite, n-a-ndrznit, srmana.<text:line-break/>Lng dnsul s se culce<text:line-break/>Ei, neghiobule! Voi trece<text:line-break/>Farmecul asupra ta,<text:line-break/>Cnd te vei redetepta,<text:line-break/>Dragostea alunge-i somnul!<text:line-break/>De pe ochi Te vei trezi<text:line-break/>Cnd eu nu mai sunt aci!<text:line-break/>Cci m duc s-mi caut Domnul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PLEAC PRIN MIJLOC N STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR DEMETRIUS I HELENA, ALERGND.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Oprete-te, chiar dac-ar fi s mor<text:line-break/>De mna ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De ce m urmreti?<text:line-break/>i-am spus s pleci!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vrei s m prseti<text:line-break/>Aci pe ntuneric? O, fii bun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Rmi i f ce vrei! Atta-i spun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PLEAC PRIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Doar Hermia-i att de fericit!<text:line-break/>A dragostei statornic ispit,<text:line-break/>Duios a mai cuprins-o! Ochii ei<text:line-break/>Lucesc De ce lucesc aa de viu?<text:line-break/>O, nu de focul lacrimilor, tiu,<text:line-break/>C n-ar luci atunci mai viu ai mei?<text:line-break/>Ce vd? Lysander zace la pmnt!<text:line-break/>E mort? Sau doarme? Ran nu zresc,<text:line-break/>Nici snge Nu rostete un cuvnt!<text:line-break/>Deteapt-te, Lysander, de trieti!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER (DEZMETICINDU-SE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Iubita mea Helena! nger sfnt,<text:line-break/>Atta de fermectoare eti!<text:line-break/>Heleno, ah, ce strvezie eti!<text:line-break/>Cum toate se schimbar fr veste!<text:line-break/>Vd inima-i, o vd prin snul tu!<text:line-break/>Demetrius ce face? Unde este?<text:line-break/>Un nume-al unui om ce-i demn s cad<text:line-break/>Ca un miel, strpuns de-aceast spad!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, taci, Lysander! Nu-l vorbi de ru!<text:line-break/>Cci Hermia i lui i este drag!<text:line-break/>E ndrgita sufletului tu,<text:line-break/>Tu singur ai iubirea ei ntreag.<text:line-break/>Nu poate fi un om mai fericit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum pot s fiu, Heleno, mulumit,<text:line-break/>C Hermia m place? Nu! Mi-e sil<text:line-break/>De timpul risipit cu-acea copil<text:line-break/>Nu Hermia , Heleno, tu mi-eti drag!<text:line-break/>Ce om ar sta la gnduri s n-aleag<text:line-break/>O porumbi-n locul unei cioare?<text:line-break/>Voina noastr minii se supune<text:line-break/>i mintea mea abia acum mi spune<text:line-break/>C tu eti cea mai dulce din fecioare.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Oricare rod i are vremea lui<text:line-break/>Eu, pn azi, prea tnr, nu avui<text:line-break/>O minte coapt Simurile mele<text:line-break/>Sunt azi desvrite, i prin ele,<text:line-break/>Stpn pe voina, mintea mea,<text:line-break/>M-ngenuncheaz azi n faa ta<text:line-break/>i-n ochii ti m face s citesc<text:line-break/>Poveti de-amor cum nu se mai gsesc<text:line-break/>n cea mai mndr carte a iubirii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ah! m-ai ursit, legi metere-ale firii,<text:line-break/>S fiu batjocorit cu-orice pre?<text:line-break/>Vai, merit eu asemenea dispre?<text:line-break/>Nu mi-e de-ajuns c nu pot cpta<text:line-break/>O vorb bun, o privire-a lui,<text:line-break/>M faci s-ndur i ironia ta?<text:line-break/>Te las. Mrturisesc, nu m-ateptam:<text:line-break/>Aa se poart-un cavaler de neam?<text:line-break/>Se poate ca o fat prsit<text:line-break/>De dragul ei s fie osndit?<text:line-break/>i luat-n rs ntr-astfel de-un brbat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ea pleac i m las fermecat.<text:line-break/>Nici n-a vzut pe Hermia O! Dac<text:line-break/>Nici eu n-a mai vedea-o niciodat,<text:line-break/>Chiar dac e de mine-amorezat,<text:line-break/>i mierea, ct de miere-i, i se-apleac;<text:line-break/>Cei care-ntr-o credin nu mai jur<text:line-break/>Mai aprig dect alii-i poart ur,<text:line-break/>i alii te-or ur stins credin,<text:line-break/>Dar ur ca a mea-i peste putin.<text:line-break/>De-acum nchin Helenei tot ce firea<text:line-break/>Mi-a hrzit ca daruri, viaa toat<text:line-break/>Mi-o voi jertfi s-i cuceresc iubirea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PLEAC PE URMA HELENEI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vai, ajutor, Lysander! Ajutor!<text:line-break/>O, smulge acest arpe-ngrozitor.<text:line-break/>O, fie-i mil Doamne, ce-am visat?<text:line-break/>M vezi? De spaim tremur toat nc!<text:line-break/>Lysander drag! Se fcea c vine<text:line-break/>Asupra mea un arpe-nfricoat<text:line-break/>C inima-mi cuprinde i-o mnnc,<text:line-break/>Iar tu priveti surztor la mine,<text:line-break/>La chinul morii-n care eu m zbat<text:line-break/>Lysander, unde eti? Ce? Ai plecat?<text:line-break/>M-ai prsit, Lysander? Nu se poate!<text:line-break/>Lysander drag, te implor pe toate<text:line-break/>Iubirile din lume! Nu-mi rspunde?<text:line-break/>Atunci, da, m-a lsat s-a dus dar unde?<text:line-break/>Se poate, vai, s-i calce el cuvntul?<text:line-break/>Merg s-mi gsesc iubitul sau mormntul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="Actul_III"/>Actul III</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I_3"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">N PDURE. TITANIA DOARME.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR QUINCE, SNUG, BOTTOM, FLUTE, SNOUT I STARVELIG.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ei,suntem toi n pr?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Suntem n pr, suntem n pr! i iat un loc minunat pentru sindrofia noastr! Luminiul acesta verde va fi scena, iar n dosul mrcinilor de colo, culisele  i o s repetm piesa nainte ntocmai cum vom face-o n faa ducelui!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Peter Quince!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce e, zurbagiule?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vezi c-n comedia aceasta a lui Pyram i a Thisbeei sunt nite lucruri care n-au s fie pe placul tuturor. Mai nti, Pyram sta vrea s trag spada i s ucid, ceea ce n-are s fac plcere damelor, ce zici de asta?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe legea mea, au s se sperie cumplit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">STARVELING:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu cred c am putea s tiem mcelul de la urm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba nicidecum. Am aflat eu tertipul ca toate s mearg strun. Scriei-mi un prolog n care s se spun publicului c nu ne pricinuim nicio meteahn lovindu-ne cu sbiile i c Pyram nu se ucide cu adevratelea. i ca toat lumea s fie mpcat, mai spunei acolo c eu, Pyram, nu sunt Pyram, ci Bottom, estorul! i aa scutim publicul de orice neplcere!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine, vom avea un prolog de felul sta! i va fi scris n stihuri de cte opt i ase picioare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai pune dou, s fie opt i opt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar nu credei c s-ar speria damele de leu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">STARVELING:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba se vor speria, de bun seam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Scumpi maetri, gndii-v bine. S aduci, Doamne ferete, un leu printre femei, e ceva grozav! Nu e pe lume fiar mai nfricoat ca leul viu, i cat s inem sama de asta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S se scrie un alt prolog ca s se arate c nu e leu adevrat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, i cel care-l joac s-i spun numele i s fac aa ca s i se vad faa prin gura leului. Prin coama leului s vorbeasc. S spun, de pild: ,,DOAMNELOR! sau ,,FRUMOASELOR DOAMNE , sau ,,V-A RECOMANDA, sau ,,V-A RUGA S NU V SPRIAI, ,,S NU TREMURAI. DAC V-AI NCHIPUI C SUNT LEU N CARNE I-N OASE, A MURI DE NECAZ. NU SUNT AA CEVA. SUNT OM CA TOI OAMENII. i aci s-i dea pe fa numele. S spun rspicat: ,,SUNT SNUG, TMPLARUL!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bun. Aa s fie. Dar mai sunt dou lucruri grele de fcut. Mai nti, cum aduci, m rog, luna-n cas? tii doar c Pyram i Thisbeea se-ntlnesc noaptea pe lun?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar va strluci luna n noaptea n care vom juca?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Un calendar! Un calendar! Cutai n almanah! Cutai luna! Gsii lumina lunei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, e lun mine-sear.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Atunci n-avei dect s lsai o fereastr deschis n odaia n care jucm. Luna va bate prin fereastr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da. Sau unul din noi ar putea s intre n scen cu o povar de mrcini i un felinar i s spun c el desfigureaz i reprezint Luciul Lunei. Alta la rnd. Ne trebuie un zid n odaia cea mare, deoarece, dup cum spune istoria, Pyram i Thisbeea i vorbesc prin crptura unui zid.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu vom putea nicicum s aducem co-geamite zid pe scen. Ce zici de asta, Bottom?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Se poate prea bine ca cineva s fac Zidul. N-are dect s se mnjeasc cu puin moloz i tencuial, i s-i rsfire degetele uite aa; prin deschiztura acestora vor opti Pyram cu Thisbeea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Atunci, toate merg strun. Haidei, stai<text:line-break/>jos, copii ai mamelor voastre, i ncepei repetiia. Pyrame, dumneata ncepi. Dup ce-i sfreti tirada, treci dup tufi i aa fiecare la rndul su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">APARE PUCK N FUND, LA STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce ntri! S fac-atta larm!<text:line-break/>De-abia a prins Criasa s adoarm!<text:line-break/>A! Teatru! Ia s-l fac pe spectatorul,<text:line-break/>i de-oi avea prilejul, pe actorul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Hai Pyram! Tu, Thisbeea, nainteaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aceste flori atta de greoase</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Graioase! Graioase</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cu miresme graioase,<text:line-break/>Ca rsufletul tu, Thisbeea, dulce i frumos miroase.<text:line-break/>Dar auzi! Un glas acolo! Ce s nsemneze oare? Stai! Oprete-te o clip. n curnd voi reapare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK (APARTE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Un Pyram mai ciudat ca oriicare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E rndul meu acuma? S vorbesc?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Firete. Ai priceput bine? El s-a dus numai s vad ce zgomot a auzit i se ntoarce numaidect.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>,,O, preastrlucita Pyram, ca un crin de alb i pal,<text:line-break/>i mai rou dect roza pe cotorul triumfal,<text:line-break/>Cel mai falnic dintre tineri, mai drgu dintre evrei,<text:line-break/>i fidel ca cel mai sprinten cal ce-n veci nu obosete,<text:line-break/>Vin, Pyrame, la mormntul lui Nini de m gsete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mormntul lui Ninus, omule! Dar nu trebuie s spui asta acum. E un rspuns al lui Pyram. Dumneata recitezi tot rolul dintr-o bucat, cu replici cu tot. Intr iar, Pyrame, dumneata ncepi la:  ,,cal ce-n veci nu obosete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Uf! ,, i credincios ca cel mai sprinten cal ce-n veci nu obosete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PUCK SE-NTOARCE. BOTTOM VINE CU EL, PURTND PE UMERI UN CAP DE MGAR.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>,,Dac-a fi frumos, Thisbeo, a fi tot numai al tu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Grozvie! Minune! Drace, suntem toi fermecai! Scumpi maetri, s fugim! Ajutor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES TOI, AFAR DE BOTTOM.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Acum v iau la goan i la joc!<text:line-break/>Prin tufe, bli, la vale i la deal,<text:line-break/>Prin bunget i prpstii, i n orice loc<text:line-break/>M-oi face cnd un cine, cnd un cal,<text:line-break/>Cnd porc, cnd urs fr de cap, cnd foc,<text:line-break/>i mormi, grohi, rnchez, ard<text:line-break/>Ca urii, porcii, cinii, caii, focul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:soft-page-break/>IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Oare de ce fug ei de mine? Au pus la cale vreo pcleal ca s m sperie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SNOUT SE NTOARCE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNOUT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vai, Bottom, eti preschimbat de tot. Ce vd pe gtul tu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ce s vezi? Ia, un cap de mgar! Pe-al dumitale, nu-i aa?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">QUINCE SE NTOARCE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Zeii cu tine, Bottom. Zeii cu tine! Te-au preschimbat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PLEAC.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Acum neleg eu iretenia lor. Vor s fac din mine un mgar, ca s m sperie, dac s-ar putea. Dar n-am s plec de-aici, uite-aa. Am s m plimb n sus i-n jos, ca s vad ei c nu mi-e fric.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">CNT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Mierloiu-n negru nvemntat,<text:line-break/>Portocaliu la cioc,<text:line-break/>i sturzul meter la cntat,<text:line-break/>Vrbioiul la joc</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA (DETEPTNDU-SE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Ce nger m deteapt dintre flori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM (CNTND):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vrbietele i cinteza,<text:line-break/>Cristeiul, cucul sur<text:line-break/>Ce brbel ar cuteza<text:line-break/>S-i afle vreun cusur<text:line-break/>i-ntr-adevr, cine-ar putea s-i pun mintea cu o pasre aa de smintit, cnd i strig n fa: cucu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai cnt, muritor frumos, mai cnt<text:line-break/>Cntarea ta auzul mi-l ncnt<text:line-break/>i ochii mi-s orbii de-a ta fptur!<text:line-break/>M-ai cucerit la cea dinti vedere<text:line-break/>i inima mea dornic mi cere<text:line-break/>S-i jur c te iubesc peste msur!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pare-mi-se, doamn, c nu prea ai cuvnt<text:line-break/>s-mi vorbeti astfel; dar la drept vorbind, mintea i dragostea nu prea fac tovrie-n ziua de astzi. Vedei c m pricep la glume cnd vreau.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eti nelept pe ct eti de frumos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Asta nu. Nu-s nici una, nici alta. Dar de-a avea destul nelepciune s pot iei din pdurea aceasta, a fi destul de nelept ca s m folosesc de ea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>O, nu dori s pleci de lng mine,<text:line-break/>Chiar fr voia ta, s tii, te voi reine.<text:line-break/>Eu sunt din alt lume, sunt din ara<text:line-break/>n care nflorete primvara,<text:line-break/>i uite! Te iubesc! Cu mine vei rmne<text:line-break/>Vei fi slujit de ceata mea de zne<text:line-break/>Ce-i vor aduce perle din abisuri,<text:line-break/>i-i vor cnta cnd, desftat de visuri,<text:line-break/>Vei adormi pe aternut de flori<text:line-break/>i te voi face apoi s nu mai mori,<text:line-break/>Asemenea cu duhul din vzduh.<text:line-break/>S vin-ncoace fiecare duh!<text:line-break/>Venii, Mzriche, Tort-de-Pianjen, Molie i Bob-de-Mutar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">MZRICHE, TORT-DE-PIANJEN, MOLIE I BOB-DE-MUTAR INTR PE LA MIJLOC N STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">MZRICHE:<text:line-break/>i eu!<text:line-break/>Tort-de-Pianjen:<text:line-break/>i eu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">MOLIE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i eu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOB-DE-MUTAR:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i eu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TOI:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce vrea stpna?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Purtai-v frumos cu-acest strin,<text:line-break/>Jucai sub ochii lui i facei tumbe<text:line-break/>De st pe loc sau vrea s se preumble;<text:line-break/>Aduce-i-i smochine din pdure,<text:line-break/>Cpuni i struguri purpurii i mure,<text:line-break/>Prdai de miere harnicele-albine,<text:line-break/>Alctuii lumnrele mici<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Din ceara care-o poart prin stupine<text:line-break/>i-aprindei-le de la licurici<text:line-break/>Spre-a-i lumina cnd doarme ori se scoal.<text:line-break/>Umbrii-i ochii cu albe-aripi de fluturi,<text:line-break/>Ferindu-i de-ale lunii reci sruturi,<text:line-break/>i fiecare-n fa-i s se nchine<text:line-break/>Cu toat cinstea ce i se cuvine!<text:line-break/>MZRICHE:<text:line-break/>Slav ie, muritorule!<text:line-break/>Tort-de-Pianjen:<text:line-break/>Slav!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">MOLIE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Slav!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOB-DE-MUTAR:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Slav!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Din toat inima v mulumesc, domniorii mei, binevoii, v rog, s-mi spunei cum v cheam?<text:line-break/>NTIUL SPIRIDU:<text:line-break/>Tort-de-Pianjen!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A dori s fac cunotin mai de aproape, musiu Tort-de-Pianjen! Dac m-oi tia cumva la deget, am s apelez la mata. Numele matale, cinstite domniorule?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">AL DOILEA SPIRIDU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mzriche!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Spune-i, m rog matale, salutri din parte-mi doamnei Pstaie, mama mtlu, i lui co-nu Vrej, tatl mtlu. Acum scarpin-m puin la ceaf, musiu Mzriche! A dori s facem cunotin mai de-aproape. Numele dumitale, domniorule?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">AL TREILEA SPIRIDU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bob-de-Mutar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Scumpe Bob-de-Mutar, cunosc rbdarea matale. Uriaul Roastbeaf a-nghiit ca un miel o sumedenie din fameliunea dumitale. Amabilitatea matale, te asigur, mi-aduce lacrimi n ochi. Doresc s facem cunotin mai de-aproape i cu mtlu, scumpe Bob-de-Mutar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Venii acum i-l ducei la culcare!<text:line-break/>Scldat-n lacrimi ns luna-mi pare,<text:line-break/>i cnd ea plnge, florile plng toate<text:line-break/>De jalea vreunei fete nelate!<text:line-break/>Un farmec lege-i limba i-l adoarm!<text:line-break/>Purtai-l lin de tot i fr larm!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES TOI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">(TOI INTR SUB UMBRARUL CE SE DESCHIDE N FUNDAL. RAZE DE LUN VERZI, ROII I VIORII SE AMESTEC-NTRE ELE. CND AU INTRAT CU TOII, UMBRARUL SE NCHIDE.)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_II_3"/>Scena II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">N ALT PARTE A PDURII.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR OBERON.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ce dornic sunt s tiu cum s-a trezit<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Titania din somn; i ce fptur<text:line-break/>Privirea ei nti i-nti i-o fur,<text:line-break/>i ea pe loc de ea s-a-ndrgostit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PUCK VINE DIN FUND.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Zburdalnicul meu crainic iscusit<text:line-break/>Sosete-n zbor, s spun ce isprav<text:line-break/>A potrivit, cu duhu-i ascuit,<text:line-break/>i ce s-a petrecut aci-n dumbrav.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Stpne, preafrumoasa ta Titanie<text:line-break/>S-a-ndrgostit, iertai, de o dihanie.<text:line-break/>Pe cnd dormea-n culcuul ei aici,<text:line-break/>O leaht de meteugari calici,<text:line-break/>Biei derbedei ce-abia ctig-o pine,<text:line-break/>Prin crciumile Atenei, de-azi pe mine,<text:line-break/>S-au adunat, vezi Doamne, s repete<text:line-break/>O comedie ce-au de gnd s-o joace<text:line-break/>n seara nunii ducelui Atenei.<text:line-break/>Cel mai nerod, podoaba astei cete<text:line-break/>De ntri, acela care face<text:line-break/>Pe Pyram, intr la sfritul scenei<text:line-break/>Aci-n tufi, pe cteva minute<text:line-break/>Eu prind prilejul i pe umeri, iute,<text:line-break/>I-aplic un drgla cap de mgar<text:line-break/>Nu peste mult, comediantul meu,<text:line-break/>Vrnd s rspund Thisbeei, intr iar.<text:line-break/>Dar cnd l vd cum l schimbasem eu,<text:line-break/>Ca liii cnd presimt un psrar<text:line-break/>n ascunziul lui, mai bine-a spune<text:line-break/>C-s ciori ce umplu de croncnituri<text:line-break/>i mtur vzduhu-n zbor, nebune<text:line-break/>La zgomotul unei detunturi,<text:line-break/>Aa o iau nspimntai la goan,<text:line-break/>Mncnd pmntul bunii mei prieteni.<text:line-break/>Eu, dup ei, i-i fugresc o toan<text:line-break/>Prin mrcini, ciulini, hiuri, cetini<text:line-break/>i-n spaima lor i fac s vad-n toate<text:line-break/>i pretutindeni duhuri necurate.<text:line-break/>S dea din col n col i-n crengi s-i lase<text:line-break/>Fii ntregi din straiele soioase,<text:line-break/>Pe cnd iubitul Thisbeei l ateapt<text:line-break/>Pe tnrul acela cu dispre,<text:line-break/>Nebnuind ce s-a-ntmplat cu ei.<text:line-break/>Titania atunci se redeteapt<text:line-break/>(Precum era de ateptat) i-astfel<text:line-break/>Zri i ndrgi pe-acest mgar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E mai frumos de cum crezusem, dar<text:line-break/>Pe tnrul acela din Atena<text:line-break/>L-ai fermecat cu sucul, cum i-am spus?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>O, da, pe cnd dormea n iarb dus<text:line-break/>Alturea de el dormea i fata,<text:line-break/>Cnd s-o trezi o va vedea , i gata!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">N VREME CE INTR HERMIA URMAT DE DEMETRIUS, OBERON A INTRAT, MPREUN CU PUCK, DUP UN TUFI, N STNGA, I OBSERV TOTUL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Taci! Uite-l pe-atenian. El vine-acu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe fat-o recunosc, pe tnr, nu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De ce m-alungi cu-atta dumnie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i voi pstra o aprig mnie.<text:line-break/>Ar trebui s fiu mai rea: m tem<text:line-break/>C voi avea prilej s te blestem.<text:line-break/>O, dac l-ai ucis pe cnd dormea<text:line-break/>Pe scumpul meu Lysander, nu-i rmne<text:line-break/>Dect s stingi acum i viaa mea!<text:line-break/>Cci soarele la scumpa-i zi nu ine<text:line-break/>Mai mult ca el la Hermia-i iubit!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Putea el s m lase adormit?<text:line-break/>Nu, niciodat! Tu mi l-ai rpus.<text:line-break/>Cum m priveti aa rpus i dus<text:line-break/>mi pari un uciga.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba un ucis,<text:line-break/>C tu, nendurato, mi-ai trimis<text:line-break/>Sgeata morii-n inima-mi zdrobit!<text:line-break/>i totui, ucigaa mea iubit,<text:line-break/>Cum strluceti ca falnica Cyther<text:line-break/>Acolo sus, n luminoasa-i sfer!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce-i cu Lysander? Unde e? Rspunde!<text:line-break/>O, bunule Demetrius, spune-mi, unde?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>La cini l-a azvrli, cu mulumire!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>n lturi, cine, cci m scoi din fire!<text:line-break/>i feciorescu-mi cumpt. L-ai rpus?<text:line-break/>Atunci te blestem: te ursc nespus.<text:line-break/>i tu din lumea omului, de-a pururi.<text:line-break/>De mi-ai ucis iubitul adorat<text:line-break/>Pe veci de veci tu fi-vei blestemat!<text:line-break/>Oh, spune-odat, fr nconjururi,<text:line-break/>De dragul meu curatul adevr!<text:line-break/>I-ai fi atins mcar un fir de pr<text:line-break/>De nu-l gseai dormind! Nu, tlhrete,<text:line-break/>L-ai omort n somn. Ce mai isprav!<text:line-break/>Nprca n-are coli mai plini de-otrav<text:line-break/>Ca tine, arpe trtor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Oprete!<text:line-break/>De unde poi avea aa prepus?<text:line-break/>C pe Lysander eu l-a fi rpus?<text:line-break/>El, pe ct tiu, ntreg i teafr este!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E teafr, zici? Ah, poi s-mi dai vreo veste?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i de-a putea, m-aleg cu vreo rsplat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cu-aceea ca de-acuma niciodat<text:line-break/>S nu ne mai vedem, i de-i n via<text:line-break/>Sau mort Lysander, s-mi lipseti din fa!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE PRIN FUND, LA STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>S-o urmresc ar fi zadarnic chin,<text:line-break/>Mai bine stau i m-odihnesc puin.<text:line-break/>Povara suferinei e mai grea,<text:line-break/>Cnd somnul uit vama s i-o ia,<text:line-break/>Dar poate, de-l atept, tot va s vin<text:line-break/>S-mi mprumute-o clip de hodin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SE CULC N DREAPTA I ADOARME.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON (INTR DIN NOU):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Puck, ce-ai fcut?<text:line-break/>Ai ncurcat-o, Puck.<text:line-break/>Ai folosit greit vrjitul suc,<text:line-break/>Schimbnd prin lipsa ta de chibzuin<text:line-break/>Iubirea-adevrat-n necredin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Aa st scris, ca pentr-un credincios<text:line-break/>S-i calce mii de alii jurmntul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mergi n hi, mai repede ca vntul,<text:line-break/>Cutreier-l i afl pe Helena.<text:line-break/>Pe-aceea frumoas fat din Atena<text:line-break/>Ce plnge i se zbucium amar,<text:line-break/>De tnrul acela nelat<text:line-break/>Mergi i ad-o printr-o vraj-aci la mine.<text:line-break/>Eu-l voi vrji pe dnsul, pn vine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Plec, zbor mai abitir ca o sgeat<text:line-break/>Din arcul celui mai dibaci ttar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Floare, care-ai sngerat,<text:line-break/>Amor cnd te-a sgetat,<text:line-break/>Sucul tu pe ochi i-l pui<text:line-break/>S-i apar draga lui<text:line-break/>Cum strluce sus, n cer,<text:line-break/>Venus plin de mister!<text:line-break/>Cnd te vei redetepta<text:line-break/>i la ea te vei uita<text:line-break/>S-o implori, s-o rogi, s-o ceri<text:line-break/>i s mori de dragul ei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PUCK SE RENTOARCE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Crai al znelor, privete<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pe Helena cum sosete!<text:line-break/>Tnrul de mine uns<text:line-break/>i cerete un rspuns.<text:line-break/>Ce nebuni, ah, uneori<text:line-break/>Sunt srmanii muritori!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Larma lor l-o detepta,<text:line-break/>Dragostea-i se va schimba.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>i-amndoi o vor pei<text:line-break/>Pn cnd vor amei.<text:line-break/>Cnd se-ntmpl vreun bucluc,<text:line-break/>Bine mai petrece Puck!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">MERGE N STNGA. INTR LYSANDER I HELENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Poi crede c batjocura se-mbrac<text:line-break/>n lacrimi? O, de ce n-asculi ce spun!<text:line-break/>Nu vezi c plnsul glasul mi-l neac,<text:line-break/>Azi, cnd i jur c te iubesc nebun?<text:line-break/>Aa rostite-asemeni jurminte<text:line-break/>Sunt sincere. Cum poi s crezi c minte<text:line-break/>Acela care-n faa ta se-nchin<text:line-break/>Ca robul care-ntmpin-o regin?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Din ce te-ascult, te cred tot mai puin.<text:line-break/>Nu pot s cred aceste jurminte,<text:line-break/>Cci Hermiei i le spuneai nainte<text:line-break/>Nu mie, jurmintele aceste?<text:line-break/>Ce vrei s fac, la rndul meu, cu ele,<text:line-break/>Cnd vd c sunt att de uurele,<text:line-break/>Mai mincinoase chiar ca o poveste?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd o-ndrgeam pe ea, am fost smintit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Erai smintit, i-acuma eti orbit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Demetrius e-ndrgostit de ea<text:line-break/>i nu de tine; poi s fii a mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS (DETEPTNDU-SE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Helen! Zn! Nimf! Vis! Minune!<text:line-break/>Cu ce s-asemui ochii-i limpezi, spune!<text:line-break/>Pe lng ei e tulbure cristalul<text:line-break/>i buzele ce-ar ruina coralul<text:line-break/>Par dou gemene ciree coapte!<text:line-break/>Omtul de pe Taurus n zare<text:line-break/>Mai negru dect corbul mi se pare,<text:line-break/>Cnd braul tu cel alb se-nal-n noapte!<text:line-break/>ngduie-mi s pun pe alba-i mn<text:line-break/>Acest sigil al fericirii, zn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Vai! Ce isprav! Ce frumos v ade<text:line-break/>S rdei, s v batei joc de mine!<text:line-break/>O, de-ai avea ct de puin simire<text:line-break/>M-ai fi cruat de-aceast umilire!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nu vi-i de-ajuns c m uri i vrei<text:line-break/>S-adugai la ur i dispre?<text:line-break/>O, dac-ai fi voi oameni, v-ar fi mil<text:line-break/>De-o inim srman de copil<text:line-break/>i n-ai glumi cu-asemeni jurminte<text:line-break/>i vorbe seci, cnd tiu de mai-nainte<text:line-break/>Ct m uri,<text:line-break/>De dragul Hermiei v nfruntai<text:line-break/>i haz de mine-a face v-ai prins frai.<text:line-break/>Halal isprav! Prea frumos v ade<text:line-break/>C m uri! Frumos de tot v ade.<text:line-break/>E fapt demn de-oameni cumsecade<text:line-break/>S-i bat joc de-o fat i s-o fac<text:line-break/>S plng-amar, doar ei ca s petreac?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Demetrius, fii sincer, tu iubeai<text:line-break/>Pe Hermia: i-o dau, poi s i-o iei,<text:line-break/>n schimb, mi las mie pe Helena;<text:line-break/>Nicio fecioar nu-i att de drag<text:line-break/>i nu va fi un om pe lumea-ntreag<text:line-break/>Mai fericit ca mine la Atena!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, ticloii! Cum i rabd firea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Voi fi, iubito, dar s-a dus iubirea<text:line-break/>Ca un pribeag ce-i vede rtcirea<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i se ntoarce iar la scumpa-i ar,<text:line-break/>Aa m-ntorc eu la Helena iar,<text:line-break/>Spre-a rmnea la ea de-aci-nainte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, nu-i adevrat! Heleno! Minte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Ia seama la ce spui, s nu plteti<text:line-break/>Prea scump aceste vorbe nebuneti.<text:line-break/>La Hermia privete! Mergi la ea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">INTR HERMIA PRIN STNGA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O noapte-n codru! Fericirea mea!<text:line-break/>Prin bezn, noapte, ne-agereti urechea,<text:line-break/>Chiar dac ochii i slbesc perechea.<text:line-break/>Urechea mea i-a prins, Lysander, glasul<text:line-break/>i-i mulumesc Cum te-ai fcut, Lysander, nevzut?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>N-am mai rmas, fiindc n-am mai vrut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Lysander totui cred c trebuia<text:line-break/>S mai rmn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu-i ngduia<text:line-break/>Iubirea s rmn. Da, iubirea<text:line-break/>Helenei care-ntrece-n strlucirea<text:line-break/>Acestei mndre nopi de stele plin<text:line-break/>i-ntunec toi ochii de lumin.<text:line-break/>De ce m caui dar, cnd vezi prea bine<text:line-break/>C ura m-a fcut s fug de tine?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, nu se poate s gndeti aa!<text:line-break/>(De-aceasta are Hermia de tire.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i ea-i amestecat-n uneltire!<text:line-break/>Pricep acuma. S-a-nvoit i ea,<text:line-break/>S fac haz pe socoteala mea!<text:line-break/>O, Hermia, te-ai neles cu ei,<text:line-break/>Ingrato! Asta nu-i prietenie!<text:line-break/>Nu-i demn de-o fat! Este-o mielie!<text:line-break/>Cnd stam de tain oare ai uitat<text:line-break/>i ne legam surori, cu gnd curat?<text:line-break/>Cnd clipele erau nesuferite<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cci ne preau c zboar prea zorite?<text:line-break/>i ne despart? Frumoase colrie,<text:line-break/>Ne giugiuleam ca nite porumbie<text:line-break/>i la gherghef brodam aceeai floare,<text:line-break/>Iar cntecele noastre rpitoare<text:line-break/>Ne nfreau mai mult i se prea<text:line-break/>Un singur glas c, dulce, le rostea.<text:line-break/>i minile, i cntul, se-mpleteau,<text:line-break/>i, cu iubire, se mperecheau,<text:line-break/>Ca dou dulci ciree pe-o codi<text:line-break/>Ca dou boabe pe-un lstar de vi.<text:line-break/>O inim n dou trupuri doar,<text:line-break/>i dou scuturi doar pe un pieptar:<text:line-break/>Deasupra lor, o singur coroan.<text:line-break/>Cum ne jucam, voioase, n poian?<text:line-break/>Prietenia noastr s-a-ncheiat?<text:line-break/>Ce ne-a unit e astzi spulberat?<text:line-break/>Vrei s-i bai joc de mine, surioar?<text:line-break/>Ceea ce faci nu-i vrednic de-o fecioar!<text:line-break/>i nici prietenos. Orice copil<text:line-break/>Ar osndi ceea ce faci, n sil,<text:line-break/>Vznd cum cu flcii mpreun<text:line-break/>i faci de rs prietena mai bun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce ptimae vorbe: n necaz<text:line-break/>Le spui cnd crezi c fac de tine haz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>N-ai pus tu pe Lysander s se-nchine<text:line-break/>n faa mea, ca rob, unei regine?<text:line-break/>i lui Demetrius, care m privea<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De sus, i-mi rspundea cu vorb rea,<text:line-break/>S-mi spun nimf, i s m numeasc<text:line-break/>Divin, zn, raz i cereasc?<text:line-break/>De ce vorbeti aa unei femei<text:line-break/>Pe care o urti? Pentru ce-i<text:line-break/>Lysander drz cu tine, dac nu<text:line-break/>L-ai pus la cale dinainte tu?<text:line-break/>N-am haruri, cum ai tu, i nici noroc,<text:line-break/>i nimenea nu m-a iubit cu foc<text:line-break/>Cum eti iubit tu. i-mi este sil<text:line-break/>C, dac sunt iubit, sunt de mil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Stau i te-ascult tot mai nedumerit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ah, da! Pref-te! Arat-te smerit!<text:line-break/>Aa! La spate, facei-v semne!<text:line-break/>Dispreul mpotriva-mi s v-ndemne.<text:line-break/>Ai pus la cale-un joc mrav, dar jocul,<text:line-break/>mi pare ru, dar nu-i prea afl locul.<text:line-break/>Pe socoteala mea v facei semne!<text:line-break/>Dac-ai avea n voi simiri mai demne<text:line-break/>De cinste, i o umbr de ruine,<text:line-break/>N-ai face-o int-a glumelor din mine.<text:line-break/>V las! Greeala tot a mea-i, n parte;<text:line-break/>Prin deprtare, dac nu prin moarte,<text:line-break/>Am s-o rscumpr</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Draga mea Helen!<text:line-break/>mi pari frumoas cum e o siren!<text:line-break/>Icoana ta n inim-mi lucete<text:line-break/>i inima-mi nprasnic te iubete!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Frumos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Lysander, drag, las-o-n pace!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i dac rugminile n-ajut,<text:line-break/>O voi sili.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cu sila n-o vei face<text:line-break/>S te asculte, i de-o amenini<text:line-break/>N-obii mai mult dect prin rugmini!<text:line-break/>Pe tine te iubesc, Helena mea!<text:line-break/>Din mini m scoate frumuseea ta.<text:line-break/>i druiesc viaa mea ntreag,<text:line-break/>Pe-acel ce-ar spune cum c nu-mi eti drag<text:line-break/>Cu sabia sunt gata s-l silesc<text:line-break/>i dragostea s mi-o adeveresc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i jur c te iubesc ca el mai mult!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cu sabia s-o juri, ca s te-ascult!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sunt gata!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum? Lysander, sunt uimit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S pleci de-aici, iganc afurisit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A! Face pe grozavul! S m-nfrunte<text:line-break/>El nu va cuteza, n lupte crunte.<text:line-break/>Doar face pe viteazul! E fricos!<text:line-break/>Doar fa de fecioare e flos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER (HERMIEI):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai du-te i te spnzur, pisic!<text:line-break/>Nu te msori i tu ct eti de mic?<text:line-break/>Hai, du-te i arunc-te n grl,<text:line-break/>S nu m scutur ca de o oprl!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce i-a venit ntr-astfel, dintr-odat?<text:line-break/>i e, desigur, mintea tulburat,<text:line-break/>Iubirea mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Iubirea ta! iganco! Haide, piei!<text:line-break/>Iubirea ta o vei primi, ct vrei!<text:line-break/>O vei sorbi, bezmetic licoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Glumeti, dar gluma i-e ngrozitoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>ngrozitoare ca i gluma ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cu sabia acum ne vom lupta, Demetrius</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-mi dai n scris, pecete,<text:line-break/>Cci vd c te-ai legat de dou fete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce vrei? Pe asta chiar vrei s-o omor,<text:line-break/>S-o bat, s-o schilodesc ngrozitor?<text:line-break/>Chiar de-o ursc, nu pot s-i fac vreun ru.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai ru dect s mor de dorul tu<text:line-break/>Nu poi s-mi faci! Nu-s Hermia? Nu eti<text:line-break/>Lysander? Nu spuneai c m iubeti?<text:line-break/>Spuneai c sunt frumoas i acum<text:line-break/>M prseti la mijlocul de drum!<text:line-break/>M faci s cred  fereasc Dumnezeu <text:line-break/>C numai te-ai jucat cu dorul meu!<text:line-break/>C dragostea i s-a mpletit cu gluma!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu vreau s te mai vd n veci,<text:line-break/>de-acuma.<text:line-break/>Poi s te-ntorci pe uliele Atenei:<text:line-break/>Eu te ursc i m nchin Helenei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA (HELENEI):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A! Prefcuto! Vierme-ascuns n floare!<text:line-break/>Ai vrut s-mi furi norocul, vrjitoare,<text:line-break/>i ai venit n noaptea-aceasta-anume<text:line-break/>S m lipseti de ce-am mai scump pe lume?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Frumos de tot i st! Nu i-e ruine?<text:line-break/>Sileti tu astfel buzele-mi blajine<text:line-break/>S-i zvrle vorbe aspre i amare?<text:line-break/>Tu, ppuico</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vrei s mor de ciud?<text:line-break/>Pricep acum: eti nalt, eu sunt mic.<text:line-break/>n ochii lui eti o prjin lung.<text:line-break/>Numai s tii c nu-s aa pitic<text:line-break/>i unghiile mele pot s-ajung<text:line-break/>S-i scoat ochii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Haide, ncetai<text:line-break/>Cu glumele. Mai bine m-aprai,<text:line-break/>Cci eu nu sunt i nici nu pot fi rea:<text:line-break/>Eu n-am o fire aprig ca ea.<text:line-break/>Sunt ginga i n-am puterea-n brae.<text:line-break/>V rog s n-o lsai s m nhae,<text:line-break/>Dei, precum vedei, ea e mai mic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A! Iar m faci, Heleno, mititic!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu, Hermio, cu mine nu fi rea,<text:line-break/>Eu te-am iubit mereu, iubita mea.<text:line-break/>i singura mea vin-i c prin mine,<text:line-break/>Demetrius aflat-a despre tine<text:line-break/>C-ai prsit Atena; i astfel<text:line-break/>n codru, din iubire pentru el,<text:line-break/>L-am urmrit i eu. El m-a certat,<text:line-break/>Cu vorbe grele-apoi m-a alungat,<text:line-break/>Cu pumnii lui a vrut s m msoare,<text:line-break/>i pn la urm, chiar s m omoare!<text:line-break/>Ah! Patima iubirii, nebuneasc,<text:line-break/>A vrea s-o duc la casa printeasc.<text:line-break/>Nici n-am s v urmez, de-acum nainte:<text:line-break/>Vedei cu toii c-s copil cuminte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hai, pleac-odat! Cine te oprete?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Iubirea doar aici m pironete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Lysander i-e iubit, de bun seam!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Demetrius!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu cumva s-i fie team,<text:line-break/>De Hermia, Heleno!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Niciun ru<text:line-break/>Nu-i poate face. i sub scutul tu<text:line-break/>O iei, Lysander</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vrea s m sfie!<text:line-break/>Doar are-o fire iute la mnie.<text:line-break/>La coal toate o tiam de fric.<text:line-break/>E fioroas, ct o fi de mic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i bate joc de mine c sunt mic,<text:line-break/>Iar voi rbdai ca tot aa s-mi zic!?<text:line-break/>Lsai-m, vreau s-o nv eu minte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pitico! Strpitur! Fii cuminte!<text:line-break/>Un fir de iarb eti! O biat ghind!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mnia prea o lai s te cuprind.<text:line-break/>Doar te iubete! Dac te gndeti<text:line-break/>Helenei dragostea s-i dovedeti,<text:line-break/>Btndu-i joc de Hermia, s tii<text:line-break/>C neghiobia greu i-o vei plti.<text:line-break/>Nu te mai face-aprtorul ei<text:line-break/>Cci te voi pedepsi cu mult temei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Acuma c de Hermia am-scpat<text:line-break/>Sunt gata s te-nfrunt ca un brbat,<text:line-break/>Ca s vedem Helena a cui este.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Urmeaz-m acolo, sus, pe creste.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">LYSANDER I DEMETRIUS IES.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Din vina ta se bat.<text:line-break/>Stai! De ce pleci?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Nu! Nu! M tem de tine. Tu m-ntreci<text:line-break/>La mini, eu ns am picioare lungi.<text:line-break/>ncearc, dac poi, s m-ajungi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">IESE ALERGND SPRE DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>M minunez i nu tiu ce s spun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">O URMEAZ PE HELENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON (NAINTEAZ):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vezi, Puck, c te-ai purtat ca un nebun!<text:line-break/>Sau poate c-ai fcut-o dinadins?<text:line-break/>Cu-ncurcturi de-acestea eti deprins</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>M iart, Crai al umbrelor, dar poate<text:line-break/>C gndurile mele-au fost curate.<text:line-break/>Am cutat s-i mplinesc cuvntul<text:line-break/>i c-am s-l recunosc dup vemntul<text:line-break/>De atenian. Purta acest vemnt<text:line-break/>i sta culcat, azi-noapte, la pmnt.<text:line-break/>Acuma vine-un alt atenian<text:line-break/>i-al celui uns la ochi e-un crunt duman.<text:line-break/>Sunt gata acuma s se ia de pr!<text:line-break/>M-ncnt ce-am fcut, ntr-adevr!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Se poate! Dar se iau la lupt crunt:<text:line-break/>Un atenian pe altul l nfrunt.<text:line-break/>Hai, du-te fuga: bolta nstelat<text:line-break/>S-o faci s fie-acum ntunecat<text:line-break/>Cu-o cea neagr, Aheron cumplit.<text:line-break/>Dumanul s le fie-nvluit<text:line-break/>Cu-o mantie de negur. Rostete<text:line-break/>Cu glasul lor, blesteme, i-i gonete<text:line-break/>Pe unul dup altul, fr s poat<text:line-break/>S se-ntlneasc-n goana lor turbat.<text:line-break/>Cu glasul lui Lysander, plin de ur,<text:line-break/>Mereu a-l, fr de msur,<text:line-break/>Pe cellalt, Lysander va socoate<text:line-break/>Demetrius c-l pndete pe la spate.<text:line-break/>i poart pe-amndoi n jos i-n sus,<text:line-break/>i f-i s se nfrunte, cum i-am spus,<text:line-break/>Dar pe-amndoi i f s stea departe,<text:line-break/>i f-i apoi s-i prind-un somn de moarte<text:line-break/>i s se culce amndoi, sleii.<text:line-break/>Tu picur pe ochii ostenii<text:line-break/>Ai lui Lysander, sub stufoasa-i gean,<text:line-break/>Aceast fermecat buruian<text:line-break/>A Cynthiei, ce-ascunde n ea puterea<text:line-break/>De-a limpezi de nluciri vederea;<text:line-break/>Cnd s-or trezi cu toii, tot ce-a fost<text:line-break/>Le va prea un vis fr de rost<text:line-break/>i s-or ntoarce veseli la Atena,<text:line-break/>Cu Hermia Lysander, cu Helena<text:line-break/>Demetrius , i vor tri n pace.<text:line-break/>n timpu-acesta vreau s vd ce face<text:line-break/>Regina mea, i farmecul avan<text:line-break/>L-oi risipi, iar pajul meu indian;<text:line-break/>l voi recpta, slvitu-mi har.<text:line-break/>S-i smulgi lui Bottom capul de mgar<text:line-break/>i s-l ari, rznd, soiei mele.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, rege al zburdalnicelor iele,<text:line-break/>Porunca iute am s i-o-mplinesc!<text:line-break/>Cci zmeii iui ai nopii se grbesc<text:line-break/>Spre rsrit s sparg-n dou norii,<text:line-break/>Prilejuind mijirea Aurorii.<text:line-break/>Cnd ea se-nal, tristele nluci<text:line-break/>Oprindu-i hora de pe la rscruci<text:line-break/>n gropile din negre cimitire<text:line-break/>i caut odihna-n adormire,<text:line-break/>n lutul plin de viermi, de erpi, de groaz,<text:line-break/>S nu apuce lumea s le vaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ci noi nu suntem duhuri chiar de rnd<text:line-break/>Eu sunt cu favoritul Aurorii<text:line-break/>Prieten bun, i pot, ca vntorii<text:line-break/>S vntur vi i codri pn cnd<text:line-break/>Din ale rsritului portaluri,<text:line-break/>Deschise-asupra lui Neptun, mijete<text:line-break/>Strlucitoarea zi i poleiete<text:line-break/>Cu aur galben verzile lui valuri.<text:line-break/>Oricum d-i zor, pn se face zi<text:line-break/>S descurcm ce-ai ncurcat aci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE N DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Puck aici i Puck colea,<text:line-break/>Puck i duce-aa cum vrea.<text:line-break/>Peste muni i vi, hai-hui,<text:line-break/>tiu cu toi de frica lui!<text:line-break/>Unul, iat-l, se ivete!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR LYSANDER.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hei, Demetrius, unde eti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i rspund prietenete:<text:line-break/>Doar la lupt m gseti.<text:line-break/>Unde eti? Unde-ai fugit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Te ajung numaidect!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>La un loc mai potrivit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">N VREME CE LYSANDER IESE URMRIND GLASUL LUI PUCK, INTR DEMETRIUS.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A voi s te-ntrt,<text:line-break/>Cci eti la i nu-mi rspunzi!<text:line-break/>n ce tuf te ascunzi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Iei de martor stelele<text:line-break/>S-i ascunzi belelele.<text:line-break/>Prin tufiuri te ascunzi<text:line-break/>i n codru te ascunzi.<text:line-break/>Hai, viteaz copilresc,<text:line-break/>Iute s te biciuiesc.<text:line-break/>Spada-ncrucind cu tine<text:line-break/>Eu m-a face de ruine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum? Pe-acolo eti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Rbdare! Ia-te dup glasul meu:<text:line-break/>Vreau s pun la ncercare<text:line-break/>Chiar acum curajul tu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">N VREME CE DEMETRIUS IESE URMNDU-L PE PUCK, REINTR LYSANDER.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Mereu m strig, merg pe urma lui,<text:line-break/>i cnd l caut, ia-l de unde nu-i.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mielul e mai iute de picioare:<text:line-break/>Am alergat, dar fuge el mai tare.<text:line-break/>Alerg mereu pe ci necunoscute,<text:line-break/>Dar e mereu pe drumuri nevzute;<text:line-break/>Simt c un somn de nenvins m fur,<text:line-break/>mi copleete-n suflet orice ur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SE NTINDE LA PMNT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">O, vino mai degrab, dulce zi!<text:line-break/>ndat ce lumina ta zglobie,<text:line-break/>Cznd pe ochii mei, m va trezi,<text:line-break/>Demetrius s-o lovi de spada mea<text:line-break/>i pentru Helena l voi nfrunta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ADOARME. REVINE PUCK, CHEMNDU-L PE DEMETRIUS.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hai, laule, pe unde rtceti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cu mine de-ai curaj s te-ntlneti,<text:line-break/>nfrunt-m! Dar fugi pe unde-i place:<text:line-break/>Te-aud chemnd ncolo i ncoace.<text:line-break/>S stai pe loc, s lupi, nici nu-ndrzneti.<text:line-break/>Poftim la lupt-odat! Unde eti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu sunt aici! Poftim!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>i rzi de mine,<text:line-break/>Dar mine diminea, tii prea bine,<text:line-break/>C-mi vei plti batjocura cumplit,<text:line-break/>Cu sabia n lupt mnuit.<text:line-break/>Acuma poi s pleci pe drumul mare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cci oboseala-a prins s m doboare.<text:line-break/>M culc aici, pe roua de pe flori,<text:line-break/>Dar pn la moarte ne-om lupta n zori!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">SE NTINDE LA UMBRA UNUI TUFI I ADOARME.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">INTR HELENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Cumplit noapte, fr de sfrit!<text:line-break/>O, de s-ar scurge ceasurile tale!<text:line-break/>S vd lucind o raz-n rsrit,<text:line-break/>i la Atena s m-ntorc cu jale.<text:line-break/>S-ncep acolo-o via nou, iari,<text:line-break/>Departe de mieii mei tovari.<text:line-break/>Un somn uor adeseori alin<text:line-break/>Dureri ce par fr de leac. O! Vin,<text:line-break/>i pn ce lumina va s vie<text:line-break/>O! Fur-m pe mine nsmi, mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">SE NTINDE N PARTEA OPUS LUI DEMETRIUS.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Pn acum nu-s dect trei.<text:line-break/>Mai lipsete una. Dar<text:line-break/>Iat-o! Vai de capul ei!<text:line-break/>Cupidon, eti un trengar!<text:line-break/>Cum prosteti tu pe femei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR HERMIA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nicicnd n-am fost aa nenorocit,<text:line-break/>i nici, cum sunt acuma, obosit,<text:line-break/>Abia m mic, prin ghimpi i rdcini.<text:line-break/>Zei a iubirii, nu m-alini?<text:line-break/>Abia mai pot s merg, nsngerat<text:line-break/>De mrcini. M culc aici pe dat.<text:line-break/>De-ajung la lupt mine diminea,<text:line-break/>Pzeasc ceru-a lui Lysander via!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SE TRAGE LA O PARTE I ADOARME LA UMBRA UNUI TUFI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Te-ntinde pe pmnt,<text:line-break/>Dormi, frumoaso, dormi visnd.<text:line-break/>Somnul e mntuitor:<text:line-break/>Am s-i fac<text:line-break/>Eu de leac<text:line-break/>Cu-acest suc mntuitor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">APAS O BURUIAN PE OCHII LUI LYSANDER.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Cnd te vei trezi n zori,<text:line-break/>Fermecatele comori<text:line-break/>Vor fi iari druite<text:line-break/>Oropsitei de iubite<text:line-break/>S-o-mplini zicala veche:<text:line-break/>Fiecare-ntr-o ureche<text:line-break/>i-oricine-i va gsi<text:line-break/>Ceea ce i s-ar cuveni.<text:line-break/>Jack o va avea pe Jill,<text:line-break/>Nu va mai ceri umil.<text:line-break/>Fiecare-i vede visul mplinindu-se tiptil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="Actul_IV"/>Actul IV</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I_4"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ACELAI DECOR, N ZORI. LYSANDER, DEMETRIUS, HERMIA I HELENA ADORMII LA UMBRA DE TUFIURI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">NTR, CU ALAIUL EI DE ZNE, TITANIA NSOIT DE BOTTOM CU CPUL DE MGAR I DE CEI PATRU SPIRIDUI-SLUJITORI. OBERON, NEVZUT DE CEI DE PE SCEN, SUPRAVEGHEAZ TOTUL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA (LUI BOTTOM):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O, vin pe-acest covor de flori frumos.<text:line-break/>(Se aaz cu Bottom pe dmbul de flori.)<text:line-break/>Vreau s-i dezmierd obrazul tu duios,<text:line-break/>S-i ncunun iubitul tu cpor<text:line-break/>Cu-un trandafir frumos mirositor.<text:line-break/>i s-i srut, cu dra lor de rou,<text:line-break/>Urechile frumoase, amndou.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM (CU O CUNUN DE FLORI PE CAP):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar unde e Mzriche?<text:line-break/>MZRICHE:<text:line-break/>La porunc, stpne!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Freac-m puin pe cap, jupne Mzriche. Dar Musiu Tort-de-Pianjen pe unde-o fi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TORT-DE-PIANJEN:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>La porunc, stpne!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Drag musiu Tort-de-Pianjen, ia apuc o arm n mn i omoar-mi albina aceea mic avnd picioruele roii care st acolo cocoat pe un scaiete; i pe urm, bunule Monsieur, adu-mi sculeul ei cu miere. Dar nu-i da prea mult osteneal n toate aceste treburi, Monsieur; i ai grij s nu se sparg punga cu miere. Tare mi-ar prea ru s te vd nclit de miere peste tot. Dar unde-i Monsieur Bob-de-Mutar?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOB-DE-MUTAR:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>La porunc, stpne!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>D lbua ncoace, Monsieur Bob-de-Mutar!<text:line-break/>Las toate curteniile astea, drag Monsieur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOB-DE-MUTAR:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce-mi poruncii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nimic, Monsieur drag. Poate doar att, s-l ajui pe Cabalero Mzriche s m scarpine la ceaf. Trebuie s merg la brbier, Monsieur. Fiindc mi s-a nzrit c mi-ar fi crescut o droaie de pr pe obraz, m simt foarte necjit dac simt c m mnnc puin capul; i trebuie neaprat s m scarpin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu vrei s-asculi i muzic, iubite?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Ce-i drept, ureche muzical a avea eu destul. Ia s rsune vtraiele i fusele!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar n-ai vrea s-mi spui, dulcea mea iubire, ce-ai pofti s mnnci?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Zu dac n-a mnca o bani de grune. Ca, de pild, nite boabe de ovz bine uscat. i a mai avea poft i de o furc de fn proaspt. Fnul dulce, nmiresmat, e fr de pereche!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA (UNEI IELE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Tu, zn drag, du-te s-i aduci,<text:line-break/>Dintr-un hambar de veveri, nuci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mi-ar prinde mai bine o mn sau dou de mazre uscat. Numai c v-a ruga din suflet s nu se osteneasc pentru mine niciunul din slujitorii ti. Simt c m fur somnul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>O, dormi, i eu cu braul te-mpresor.<text:line-break/>S plece ielele la rostul lor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES IELELE I SPIRIDUII.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">i astfel rourusca-mbriat<text:line-break/>De ieder, ncolcete toat<text:line-break/>Al ulmului trunchi vechi i noduros.<text:line-break/>Iubitul meu! Ah! Ct eti de frumos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TITANIA SE CULC PE SNUL LUI BOTTOM. ADORM AMNDOI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR PUCK I SE NCHIN LUI OBERON.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Ei, Puck, bine-ai venit! Vezi ce idil?<text:line-break/>De nebunia ei mi-e totui mil.<text:line-break/>mi pare ru c am npstuit-o<text:line-break/>Mai adineauri chiar am ntlnit-o<text:line-break/>Cum rtcea prin gropi, printre ponoare,<text:line-break/>S-i caute miresme-adormitoare<text:line-break/>Acestui dobitoc i ntru,<text:line-break/>Acela ce-i acum iubitul su.<text:line-break/>Atunci am dojenit-o, mnios,<text:line-break/>Cci vrea s-ncing botul lui scrbos<text:line-break/>Cu iruri lungi de flori mirositoare,<text:line-break/>Ca nite tufe de mrgritare<text:line-break/>Ce strluceau aievea, triumfale,<text:line-break/>De-a lungul vetejitelor petale,<text:line-break/>Ca nite lacrimi stoarse de ruine.<text:line-break/>Ea, dup ce-am mustrat-o mult i bine,<text:line-break/>Prea umil i, cu vorbe bune,<text:line-break/>S-a nvoit, curnd, s m mbune.<text:line-break/>Cnd i-am cerut copilul, ea mi-l dete<text:line-break/>i-a poruncit la una dintre fete<text:line-break/>S-l duc n mpria mea<text:line-break/>Acum c pajul e al meu, a vrea<text:line-break/>S-o mntui de orbirea-i nebuneasc<text:line-break/>Ridic, drag Puck, aceast masc<text:line-break/>Strin, de pe tigva stui prost,<text:line-break/>Ca deteptat, ca i ceilali tovari,<text:line-break/>S se ntoarc la Atena iari,<text:line-break/>ncredinat c vis urt a fost<text:line-break/>Tot ce i s-a-ntmplat n noaptea-aceasta.<text:line-break/>Dar mai nti merg s-mi dezleg nevasta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ATINGE CU O BURUIAN OCHII TITANIEI.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">F-te iari ce erai,<text:line-break/>Vezi din nou, precum vedeai,<text:line-break/>Pentru ca prin Oberon,<text:line-break/>A Dianei floare cast<text:line-break/>S-o nving pe cea proast,<text:line-break/>Roie , a lui Cupidon!<text:line-break/>Titania, trezete-te din somn,<text:line-break/>Criasa mea cea dulce!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA (DETEPTNDU-SE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Al visurilor domn.<text:line-break/>Parc am visat un vis nespus de rar:<text:line-break/>Eram ndrgostit de-un mgar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON (ARTNDU-I CAPUL DE MGAR):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, te-ai ndrgostit de-aceast fiin!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar cum a fost aceasta cu putin?<text:line-break/>Cu scrb-l vd acuma ochii mei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Titania, vreau muzic. Acei<text:line-break/>Ce zac acum nlnuii prin somn,<text:line-break/>S-i mntuiasc-al Duhurilor Domn!<text:line-break/>Legnd cele cinci simuri ale lor,<text:line-break/>Cci prea s-au chinuit ngrozitor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Hai, muzic, n ritm adormitor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">CNT MUZICA, TRIST.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK (LUI BOTTOM):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cnd i-oi deschide ochii ti de prost,<text:line-break/>S vezi ce fel de dobitoc ai fost!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hai, zicei, cntreilor! Tu vin<text:line-break/>S ne-mpcm, frumoasa mea regin.<text:line-break/>Mine pe la miezul nopii, tu i eu,<text:line-break/>Vom dnui la nunta lui Thezeu<text:line-break/>i-i vom aduce spor i bucurie<text:line-break/>n fericita lor cstorie.<text:line-break/>Tot n aceeai sear se cunun<text:line-break/>Perechile ce dorm aci-mpreun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Crai al znelor, ne-am dus:<text:line-break/>Cnt ciocrlia sus!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Hai, regin, n tcere,<text:line-break/>Dup umbra care piere,<text:line-break/>S cltorim mai iute<text:line-break/>Ca icoana lunii mute.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Haidem i n zbor s-mi spui<text:line-break/>Cum se face c zcui<text:line-break/>Pe pmnt i printre flori<text:line-break/>Printre simpli muritori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">CORURI DE VNTOARE N CULISE. INTR THEZEU, HIPPOLYTA, EGEU I SUITA DE VNTOARE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-l cutai acum pe pdurar.<text:line-break/>Aducei-mi i noul armsar.<text:line-break/>Ritualul e-ncheiat. Se-nal zorii.<text:line-break/>Vreau s-mi asculi, iubito, vntorii,<text:line-break/>i-n fruntea tuturora, cercetaii,<text:line-break/>Cum i ndeamn cinii i hitaii.<text:line-break/>Auzul ni-l vor desfta nespus,<text:line-break/>Noi vom edea pe-o culme, spre apus;<text:line-break/>Vom asculta ltratul lor sonor<text:line-break/>Cum l ndeamn orice vntor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Am fost odat la o vntoare<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De uri, prin Creta, ca nsoitoare<text:line-break/>A lui Heracles i a lui Cadmos.<text:line-break/>Spectacol ct se poate de frumos<text:line-break/>Ltrau copoi spartani de diminea:<text:line-break/>N-am pomenit o larm mai mrea.<text:line-break/>Aici ai cini de neam atenian?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba cinii mei sunt toi de neam spartan.<text:line-break/>Li-e blana doar n negru i n aur,<text:line-break/>Au labe-strmbe i au gui de taur.<text:line-break/>Li-s clpuge-urechile-amndou,<text:line-break/>Culeg cu ele boabele de rou.<text:line-break/>Nu-s iui gonaci, dar latr laolalt,<text:line-break/>Orice vnat, cnd latr ei, tresalt.<text:line-break/>Copoi mai buni nu s-au vzut vreodat<text:line-break/>n Creta, n Thesalia bogat<text:line-break/>Nici chiar la Sparta Cine oare sunt<text:line-break/>Aceste nimfe-ntinse la pmnt?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Copila mea, stpne, e culcat<text:line-break/>Aici. Aici, Lysander. Alt fat,<text:line-break/>Helena e, copila lui Nedar.<text:line-break/>Mai e Demetrius, tnr plin de har,<text:line-break/>M mir c-i vd, tuspatru, mpreun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-or fi vorbit, plimbndu-se sub lun,<text:line-break/>De ziua de-nti mai s se desfete<text:line-break/>i, ca i noi, s-i pun verighete.<text:line-break/>Egeu, nu-i astzi ziua sorocit<text:line-break/>Cnd Hermia cu Lysander se mrit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba da, stpne</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cred c nelept e<text:line-break/>Ca-n sunete de corn s se detepte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SUNETE PUTERNICE DE CORN N CULISE. DEMETRIUS, LYSANDER, HERMIA I HELENA SE DETEAPT I SAR N SUS VZND ALAIUL DUCAL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Demult trecut-a Sfntul Valentin.<text:line-break/>n codru-acesta psrile vin<text:line-break/>Atta de trziu s se-mpreune?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER (N VREME CE TOI PATRU CAD N GENUNCHI NAINTEA DUCELUI.):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ascult-ne umila rugciune,<text:line-break/>Mria Ta, i iart-ne!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Odat<text:line-break/>tiam c o peeai pe-aceeai fat<text:line-break/>Cu gelozie. Astzi, cum se face<text:line-break/>C v gsesc pe amndoi, n pace,<text:line-break/>Culcai alturi. Ura lng ur?<text:line-break/>V dumneai, i fr de msur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, duce, mintea mi era semea,<text:line-break/>Acum plutete ntre vis i via.<text:line-break/>i totui parc mi aduc aminte:<text:line-break/>Fusese gndul nostru tinuit<text:line-break/>S prsim Atena, negreit<text:line-break/>i Hermia cu mine, mpreun,<text:line-break/>S ne aflm o soart, rea sau bun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">EGEU (LUI LYSANDER):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ajunge! Duce, tiu acum de-ajuns:<text:line-break/>Voiau s se cunune pe ascuns.<text:line-break/>S-l surghiuneti! Voia s-mi fure fata!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Iar ea inea cu dnsul, blestemata,<text:line-break/>Dei tia c i-am fgduit-o,<text:line-break/>i lui Demetrius chiar i-am druit-o.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mria Ta, copila cea frumoas<text:line-break/>A lui Nedar mi-a spus c fug de-acas<text:line-break/>Lysander i cu Hermia-mpreun<text:line-break/>i c-n pdurea-aceasta se cunun.<text:line-break/>I-am urmrit, nespus de suprat;<text:line-break/>Helena m iubea i m-a urmat.<text:line-break/>Dar o putere supraomeneasc <text:line-break/>Doar nu e o putere pmnteasc<text:line-break/>Mi-a destrmat iubirea-nflcrat<text:line-break/>Ce Hermiei purtatu-i-am odat.<text:line-break/>Da, s-a topit iubirea mea ca spuma,<text:line-break/>Aa c pentru mine este-acuma<text:line-break/>Ca amintirea unei jucrii<text:line-break/>Ce m-ncnta, pe cnd eram copii.<text:line-break/>Acuma chipul care m desfat<text:line-break/>E al Helenei, preafrumoasa fat<text:line-break/>A lui Nedar. Nainte de-a vedea<text:line-break/>Pe Hermia, a fost aleasa mea.<text:line-break/>Acum pe veci de veci i voi rmne<text:line-break/>Helenei credincios. M jur, stpne.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Copiii mei! Vorbi-vom cu mirare<text:line-break/>De minunata voastr ntmplare.<text:line-break/>Norocul v slujete de minune.<text:line-break/>Acum, Egeu, tu te vei supune<text:line-break/>Poruncii mele. Fi-vor pe vecie<text:line-break/>i printr-o ndoit cununie,<text:line-break/>Perechile acestea-ndrgostite<text:line-break/>n templul din Atena, fericite.<text:line-break/>Da, tinerii acetia se cunun,<text:line-break/>Acum, cu nunta noastr mpreun.<text:line-break/>E dimineaa, vd, naintat.<text:line-break/>Rmne vntoarea pe-alt dat.<text:line-break/>Venii dar la Atena. La altar<text:line-break/>Trei cununii primi-vor sfntul har.<text:line-break/>S mergem, Hippolyta mea iubit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES THEZEU, HIPPOLYTA, EGEU I ALAIUL DUCAL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vai! mintea mi-e nespus de nclcit,<text:line-break/>Aa precum se-ntmpl, uneori,<text:line-break/>S crezi c-n loc de muni vezi numai nori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu vd ponci, nu limpede, ce este.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Demetrius mi pare o poveste,<text:line-break/>Un giuvaier: l-am regsit cu greu:<text:line-break/>tiu c-i al meu, dar parc nu-i al meu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S fim noi treji? Sau poate mai dormim?<text:line-break/>Pe ducele pe care l slvim<text:line-break/>Nu l-am vzut aici? Suntem chemai<text:line-break/>S fim tusase astzi cununai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HERMIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i tatl meu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HELENA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i Hippolyta-a fost.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ne-ateapt la altarul unui zeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Deci suntem treji. S mergem. i pe drum<text:line-break/>Aflm ce s-a-ntmplat, i cnd, i cum!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IES TOI. BOTTOM SE DETEAPT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Dac se ntmpl s trebuiasc s-mi spun partea mea, n-avei dect s m strigai i voi rspunde. n scrisul meu st aa: ,,Preafrumosul meu Pyram. Hei-ho, tu Flute, crpaci de foale! i tu, Peter Quince, dulgher. i Snout, cldrarul. Starveling, croitorul. Ce dracu! Au plecat cu toii i m-au lsat dormind! i ce vis grozav am avut! St mintea omului n loc i nu are cum s povesteasc o asemenea vedenie! S-ar cuveni s fie omul mgar s poat povesti un asemenea vis! Mi se prea c a fi fost i se prea c a fi avut Numai o paia ntr-un costum trcat ar putea spune lmurit ce anume ajunsesem s fiu! Ochiul omului n-a mai auzit pn acum asemenea minunie, urechea omeneasc n-a mai vzut pn acum aa ceva, nici mna omeneasc n-ar fi n stare s pipie, nici limba omeneasc s-i nchipuiasc, i nici inima s se rosteasc, ce anume vedenie am avut. Am de gnd s-l pun pe Peter Quince s alctuiasc o balad pe seama acestei vedenii. Are s-i spun: VISUL LUI BOTTOM, cci tot se va spune la fundul piesei. i am s-l cnt la partea de pe urm a comediei, naintea ducelui. Din ntmplare, ca s-l fac s fie i mai ginga, am s-o cnt atunci cnd i d duhul Thisbeea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_II_4"/>Scena II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">DUP APUSUL SOARELUI. DIN PILASTRUL DIN COL AL PALATULUI, SPRE FUNDUL SCENEI, SPNZUR-N NLIMEA FRIZEI O CANDEL DE ULEI CARE ABIA LUMINEAZ SCENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR FLUTE, SNOUT, STARVELING I QUINCE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ai trimis acas la Bottom? nc tot nu s-a mai ntors?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">STARVELING:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nu se tie nimic despre el. De bun seam e fermecat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dac nu vine, piesa e compromis. Nu se poate juca, nu-i aa?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Firete! Nu-i n toat Atena un al doilea care s poat juca pe Pyram.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu, asta se tie, e cel mai iste dintre toi meteugarii din Atena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i cel mai chipe. Aa-i; i e un cineva c are o voce taman de amant, att de dulce e.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Zi ,,diamant; un amant, Doamne pzete, e lucru de ruine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR SNUG.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">SNUG:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Maestre, ducele se-ntoarce la templu; mai vin cu doutrei perechi de cavaleri i dame, cununai totodat. Dac am putea s dm reprezentaia, ne-ar bate fericirea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FLUTE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>O, drag Bottom! i-ai pierdut cele ase drahme pe zi, pe care puteai s le ai o via-ntreag! C mai puin de ase drahme nu putea s capete, i dac ducele nu i-ar da ase drahme pe zi e nimica toat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:soft-page-break/>INTR BOTTOM.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Unde-s flcii notri? Unde-s scumpii notri tovari?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bottom! Ce zi nemaipomenit! Ce zi plin de noroc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Scumpi maetri, a putea s v spun cte n lun i-n soare. Dar mai bine nu m-ntrebai, cci dac v-a spune, n-a mai fi atenian de omenie. i cu toate astea, nu fac dect s v povestesc ce-am pit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">QUINCE:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-auzim, drag Bottom!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Pune-i pofta-n cui! Att v spui, c ducele a cinat. mbrcai-v. Punei-v baieri bune la brbi i nojie bune la papuci! Ducele vine. Fiecare s-i repete rolul, cci, ca s nu mai lungim vorba, piesa noastr a fost aleas! n orice caz, Thisbeea s se primeneasc; i cel care face pe Leul s nu-i road unghiile, care trebuie s-i atrne afar ca nite gheare de leu. i, scumpii mei confrai, nu mncai ceap, nici usturoi; avem de spus lucruri frumoase i nu m ndoiesc c ducele, auzindu-le, va spune c e o comedie foarte dulce Nicio vorb mai mult i nainte! Vine ducele!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TOI IES PRIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="Actul_V"/>Actul V</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I_5"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">THEZEU, HIPPOLYTA, CURTENI I SUITA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">VIN DIN DREAPTA I STNGA PE SCRI, N FUND. N FRUNTE, PURTTORI DE TORE I MUZICANI, CU FLUTE, CLARINETE I TROMPETE. MUZICANII RMN SUS, PURTTORII DE TORE SE MPART N SPAIUL CE-L AU DE LUMINAT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce povestesc acetia e ciudat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai mult ciudat dect adevrat.<text:line-break/>N-am pus vreodat, orice-ar spune ei,<text:line-break/>Pe basmele cu zne vreun temei.<text:line-break/>n mintea lor, ades ndrgostiii<text:line-break/>Pot judeca ntocmai ca smintiii<text:line-break/>i furesc poveti de bun tire,<text:line-break/>Mult mai presus ca orice-nchipuire.<text:line-break/>Poeii i lunaticii, rsad<text:line-break/>De draci mai muli dect ncap n iad;<text:line-break/>i-nchipuie c-ar fi. Cel ce iubete<text:line-break/>Iubita lui, adesea, socotete,<text:line-break/>C i iganc dac-ar fi, ea, Helena<text:line-break/>El tot i-ar nchina o cantilena.<text:line-break/>nchipuirea lui e un mister<text:line-break/>Suit de el de la pmnt la cer<text:line-break/>i-n mintea-i de poet ntruchipeaz<text:line-break/>Minuni la care nencetat viseaz.<text:line-break/>Iar pana lui d suflet i d nume,<text:line-break/>Unor nimicuri care nu-s pe lume.<text:line-break/>nchipuirea lui e-att de mare<text:line-break/>C-i gata, numai dac i se nzare<text:line-break/>Vreo bucurie, s-i urzeasc trainic<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ca sol al bucuriei lui, un crainic<text:line-break/>Iar noaptea, dac bezna-l nfioar,<text:line-break/>Ia un tufi drept urs sau alt fiar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar cele ce s-au petrecut azi-noapte<text:line-break/>Par s fi fost adevrate fapte.<text:line-break/>Orict ni s-ar prea de minunate,<text:line-break/>Au fost, fr-ndoial, ntmplate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Vin logodiii, sprinteni i vioi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTRE LYSANDER, HERMIA, DEMETRIUS I HELENA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Bine-ai venit! V ateptam pe voi,<text:line-break/>S mergem, mpreun, la altar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe toi ne-ateapt-al fericirii har,<text:line-break/>La drum, la mas i la aternut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Trei ceasuri mai avem de petrecut<text:line-break/>De la ospul nunii la culcare.<text:line-break/>S-a pregtit aleasa srbtoare.<text:line-break/>Cel care pregtete desftri,<text:line-break/>Sau comedii, sau altfel de serbri<text:line-break/>Ce-a pus la cale vrem s ne vesteasc<text:line-break/>Punnd actorii s se pregteasc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-ajung s v desft n ast-sear<text:line-break/>Am pus la cale o istorioar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cu muzic, cu dansuri i cu mti,<text:line-break/>Cu sulie, cu arcuri i cu cti,<text:line-break/>Greoiul pas al vremii s-nelm,<text:line-break/>i ca la nunt s ne desftm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Mria Ta-i rugat s aleag<text:line-break/>Ce pies vrea de pe-o hrtie-ntreag.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">I NMNEAZ O LIST.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU (CITETE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A! ,,Lupta cu centaurii, poveste<text:line-break/>I-am povestit-o vrednicei neveste.<text:line-break/>Cu Hercules, cum tii, m nrudesc.<text:line-break/>A! ,,Ceata de bacante mbtate,<text:line-break/>Pe cntreul trac nverunate.<text:line-break/>E-o pies s-a jucat cu-un bun decor,<text:line-break/>Din Theba cnd veneam biruitor.<text:line-break/>,,Acele muze, de trei ori trei,<text:line-break/>Se dau de ceasul morii, cu temei.<text:line-break/>Ca tiina s cereasc a ajuns.<text:line-break/>Vreo satir ateapt un rspuns.<text:line-break/>Nu cred c-ar fi vreo pies potrivit<text:line-break/>Cu srbtoarea noastr fericit.<text:line-break/>(Citete) ,,O scen scurt i cam plicticoas<text:line-break/>Cu Pyram i Thisbeea cea frumoas.<text:line-break/>O comedie plin de amar.<text:line-break/>N-am mai vzut un lucru-att de rar:<text:line-break/>E deci o comedie dureroas,<text:line-break/>i scurt, i nespus de plicticoas!<text:line-break/>Ciudat-mperechere de cuvinte:<text:line-break/>O ghea cald i-un omt fierbinte!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mria Ta, e-un fel de pantomim,<text:line-break/>Cu stihuri proaste, toate sunt cu rim.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>mi pare plicticoas, cam hai-hui:<text:line-break/>Nici un cuvnt nu e la locul lui,<text:line-break/>i nici vreun actor n rolul su.<text:line-break/>E-o fat ndrgostit de-un flcu.<text:line-break/>Cu sabia flcul se strpunge<text:line-break/>i fata dup el n iad ajunge.<text:line-break/>Am rs cu lacrimi cnd am auzit-o<text:line-break/>Gndindu-m la cel ce-a ntocmit-o.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i cine joac piesa? Ce actori?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Flci cu palma groas, muncitori.<text:line-break/>Sunt din Atena toi, i pnacuma<text:line-break/>Nu cred c s-au mai ntrecut cu gluma,<text:line-break/>Jucnd vreo pies proast, pentru care<text:line-break/>Au vrut s-i pun mintea la-ncercare.<text:line-break/>La nunta-Alteei Voastre vor s-o joace,<text:line-break/>Ndjduind c piesa v va place.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-o auzim!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu cred c se cuvine<text:line-break/>S-ngduim s joace oriicine.<text:line-break/>Nu face nici o ceap degerat,<text:line-break/>Aa precum de ei va fi jucat.<text:line-break/>Dei meteugarii s-au trudit,<text:line-break/>Altea Ta s fie mulumit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ca s le fac pe plac, vreau s-o ascult.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Eu la supuii mei in foarte mult.<text:line-break/>Cu zel curat ei vor s ne desfete,<text:line-break/>Chiar dac-or spune stihuri deuchiete.<text:line-break/>Iubite Philostrat, s-i chemi actorii,<text:line-break/>i-n sal s se-aeze spectatorii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE PHILOSTRAT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu-mi place s privesc cum neputina<text:line-break/>Se zbucium-n zadar, cnd srguina<text:line-break/>Nu-i ajutat de-nsuiri fireti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar, Hippolyta mea, n-o s priveti<text:line-break/>Aa ceva.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar nu ne-a spus pe leau<text:line-break/>C-i o prostie, chiar de se trudeau?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cu-att mai mult li se cuvine lor<text:line-break/>S ne purtm mai ngduitor.<text:line-break/>Orice greeli vor face, de tot felul<text:line-break/>n tot ce fac acum i pun tot zelul.<text:line-break/>Vor s ne-arate marea lor iubire<text:line-break/>i-a lor nemrginit preuire.<text:line-break/>Pe unde-am fost, mari crturari, n timp,<text:line-break/>M-au nlat cu slav n Olimp,<text:line-break/>Dar palizi i-am vzut, nfrigurai,<text:line-break/>i i-am simit c sunt ngrijorai<text:line-break/>C nu le-a dat atta minte-un zeu<text:line-break/>S se nale pn la rangul meu!<text:line-break/>Se poticneau n stihurile lor<text:line-break/>i se strmbau adesea-ngrozitor.<text:line-break/>n toate-acestea eu m pricepeam<text:line-break/>S-aleg ce-alege un erou de neam.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Muenia, sfiala, stngcia,<text:line-break/>La ei se mpletea cu datoria.<text:line-break/>Nu-ncap prea multe vorbe sclipitoare:<text:line-break/>Tcerea-i ia o alt-nfiare,<text:line-break/>Mai sincer i mai adevrat<text:line-break/>Dect poezia cea mai nlat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR PHILOSTRAT.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PHILOSTRAT:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Slvii asculttori, pe toi v rog,<text:line-break/>S ascultai n tihn un prolog.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Prologului s-i spui s intre-n scen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TRMBIE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">INTR PETER QUINCE, CARE REPREZINT PROLOGUL.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PROLOGUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De v-aducem suprare, ne vei crede, aa sperm,<text:line-break/>C nu vrem nicicum prin jocul nostru s v suprm.<text:line-break/>Ci ca s v dm dovad de ce tim i ce putem<text:line-break/>Asta e i cel din urm i ntiul scop ce-avem.<text:line-break/>De veneam spre-a v displace, n-am mai fi venit defel;<text:line-break/>De-a v place ni-i unicul i adevratul el.<text:line-break/>Nu pentru plcerea voastr suntem noi aci venii,<text:line-break/>Spre-a v face ca s plngei sunt actorii pregtii.<text:line-break/>Dar vedei-i i pe urm, dup ce-i vei fi vzut,<text:line-break/>Vei putea atunci cunoate tot ce e de cunoscut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Grmtic nu mi se pare c-i acest meteugar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O cam ia la sntoasa, ca un aprig armsar.<text:line-break/>Spune vorbe nclcite, netiind s se opreasc.<text:line-break/>Nu se cade ca actorul doar s tie s vorbeasc,<text:line-break/>Oriice cuvnt se cade s-l rosteasc cu msur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i-un copil ar fi n stare multe vorbe de strnsur<text:line-break/>Tot la fel s le rosteasc, sau la flaut s le cnte.<text:line-break/>S vedem ce mai urmeaz, cred c vor s ne-nspimnte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Vorbe goale, niruite pe un lan cam ncurcat.<text:line-break/>Toii actorii-acum pe scen pare c s-au adunat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR PYRAM, THISBEEA, ZIDUL, LUCIU-DE-LUN I LEUL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PROLOGUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Poate-aceast povestire s v mire, n-am ce zice,<text:line-break/>Spectatori, pn ce-adevrul vine totul s explice.<text:line-break/>Omul sta e Pyramus, dac vrei cumva s tii,<text:line-break/>Iar Thisbeea este fata cea frumoas ce-o privii.<text:line-break/>Omul plin de tencuial i cu var mnjit pe-o parte<text:line-break/>Este Zidul, ticlosul zid ce pe iubii desparte.<text:line-break/>Fericii cnd pot, srmanii, prin a zidului sprtur<text:line-break/>Pe furi i-n mare tain s-i opteasc gur-n gur.<text:line-break/>Omul sta cu fanarul, cu cel i mrcine<text:line-break/>Reprezint Luciul Lunii: cci, bgai de seam bine,<text:line-break/>Noaptea numai cnd din ceruri luna lumina de sus,<text:line-break/>Pyram cu Thisbeea vin la mormntul lui Ninus.<text:line-break/>Fiara asta crunt, creia Leu i place s se cheme,<text:line-break/>ntr-o noapte, cnd Thisbeea ajunsese prea devreme,<text:line-break/>A fcut-o ca s fug i-n acea sperietur<text:line-break/>Ea, fugind, ls s-i cad-n drum mantaua ei pe care<text:line-break/>Leul o mnji pe urm cu nsngerata-i gur.<text:line-break/>Tot atunci, Pyram, un tnr alb i-mbujorat apare;<text:line-break/>Gsind mantia Thisbeei de Leoaic nsngerat<text:line-break/>El pe loc i-nfipse vrful blestemat al spadei sale<text:line-break/>Drept n inima-i n care sngele fierbea de jale.<text:line-break/>Iar Thisbeea se oprise sub un pom, i-a scos ndat<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Junghiul i-a murit. i Leul, Zidul, Luciu-de-Lun<text:line-break/>i iubiii-n mndre stihuri ce-a urmat au s v spun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PROLOGUL, PYRAMUS, THISBEEA, LEUL I LUCIU-DE-LUN IES PRIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce minune ca pe scen s auzi vorbind un leu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu-i nicio minune, Alte, cci, aa precum tiu eu,<text:line-break/>Cnd mgarii stau la sfad uneori n sfatul rii<text:line-break/>Leul poate rage-n vorbe dinspre marginile zrii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ZIDUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>n aceast comedie s-a-ntmplat s m decid<text:line-break/>Ca eu, Snout, cldrarul, s joc rolul unui zid.<text:line-break/>Zidu-i vechi i are multe crpturi ce pot lsa<text:line-break/>Pe Pyram s schimbe vorbe cu Thisbeea scump-a sa.<text:line-break/>Tencuiala, piatra, varul ce-l vedei, vdesc curat<text:line-break/>C sunt zid n toat legea, c sunt zid adevrat.<text:line-break/>Iar la dreapta i la stnga prin sprturile aceste<text:line-break/>i optesc fricos iubiii amoroasa lor poveste.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cum se poate cere oare de la var i tencuial<text:line-break/>S vorbeasc-n stihuri spuse cu asemenea migal!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Cred, Mria Ta, poetul c aici s-a depit:<text:line-break/>N-am mai auzit vreodat zid att de mucalit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR DIN NOU PYRAMUS.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Stai! Acum de zid Pyramus s-apropie-n tcere.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Noapte neagr-ntunecat, noapte plin de mistere,<text:line-break/>Noapte trist, blestemat. Noapte groaznic! M tem<text:line-break/>C Thisbeea n-o s vin la-ntlnirea ce-o avem.<text:line-break/>Zidule btrn i ubred ce despari din vremuri vechi<text:line-break/>Dou neamuri, dnd prilejul iubitoarelor urechi<text:line-break/>S se-asculte tot rostindu-i vorbele ndrgostite,<text:line-break/>Cum a vrea s vd prin tine cea mai dulce din iubite.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">ZIDUL I RSFIR DEGETELE, PYRAM PRIVETE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Mulumesc, o, Zid prieten! Jupiter te-aib-n paz!<text:line-break/>Dar Thisbeea mea iubit nu e nimenea s-o vaz!<text:line-break/>Zid afurisit, tu, care-mi ascunzi comoara mea,<text:line-break/>Blestemat-i fie piatra, de te pori cu mine aa!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mi se pare c i zidul, fiind fiin nsufleit,<text:line-break/>S-ar cdea s-i zvrle-o vorb tot la fel de ascuit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nu, Alte! Nu se poate! Cci Thisbeea va veni.<text:line-break/>Da, a i venit. i-acuma tot prin zid vom glsui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR THISBEEA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Zidule, ce-att de-adesea n amara clip cnd<text:line-break/>M despart de mndrul Pyram, tu m-auzi cum gem plngnd,<text:line-break/>Gura-mi de cirea-adesea se apleac s-i srute<text:line-break/>Pietrele cu tencuial i cu var i-n veci tcute!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pare c zresc o voce: la sprtur m reped<text:line-break/>S ascult icoana celei mult iubite</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ah, tu eti, Pyram? M ncred<text:line-break/>n sprtura unde-i Pyram, mult duiosul meu iubit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, m vezi c sunt Pyramus, i la zid te-am ntlnit.<text:line-break/>Ca Limander, credinciosul tu iubit voi fi mereu,<text:line-break/>Pn mi-or vesti sfritul Parcele i-un tainic zeu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Credincioas ca Helena i voi fi ct voi tri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ca Saphala pentru Procrus, scumpa mea, aa-mi vei fi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Eu, ca Procrus, pe Saphala, tiu c fr de msur,<text:line-break/>Te-oi iubi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>S-mi dai, iubito, srutare prin sprtur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Vai, simt zidul doar pe buze, nu i buzele-i, s tii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vin s ne-ntlnim la noapte la mormntul lui Nini. (Peter QUINCE: AL LUI NINUS)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Vin, Pyrame, chiar de-ar trebui s mor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PYRAM I THISBEEA IES DIN SCEN.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ZIDUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Mi-am jucat acuma rolul. Nu-s de niciun ajutor.<text:line-break/>Pot s plec i eu din scen. Zidul nu mai are rost.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE ZIDUL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Drmat e-acuma zidul care-ntre vecini a fost.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cred c este foarte bine, pentru c, din vremuri vechi,<text:line-break/>tie bine oriicine: zidurile au urechi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu cred c-am vzut vreodat o mai mare nerozie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Totul este nchipuirea, dac muza o mbie.<text:line-break/>Restu-s numai biete umbre. Dac mintea nu te-ajut,<text:line-break/>Orice pies-ar fi mai bine s rmn venic mut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Deci nchipuirea-i totul, nu talentul de poet!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nu, talentul se strecoar n subiect, ncet-ncet.<text:line-break/>Iat c vin dou nobile dobitoace: o lun i un leu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR LUCIU-DE-LUN I LEUL.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEUL:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Doamne-ale cror inimi se fac foarte mititele<text:line-break/>Chiar de frica unui oarec care fuge pe podele,<text:line-break/>Vei sri n sus de spaim, tremurnd ca varga, poate,<text:line-break/>Cnd un rcnet groaznic leul din gtlejul lui va scoate.<text:line-break/>Deci aflai c eu sunt leul, Snug, de felul meu tmplar,<text:line-break/>i c nu-s, fereasc Domnul, leu i nici leoaic chiar.<text:line-break/>Cci e fr de-ndoial: de-a fi leu, i de-a intra<text:line-break/>n mijlocul dumneavoastr, ar fi vai de pielea mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cumsecade fiar, n-am ce zice! i pare bine-crescut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cea mai desvrit vietate pe care mi-a fost dat s-o vd vreodat, Mria Ta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pare mai degrab o vulpe dect un leu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba vrea s fie tot att la locul lui pe ct e un gscan.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sau vulpe, sau gscan. Vulpea tot duce n colii ei gscanul, chiar dac ar da vreo dovad de nelepciune.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nici gscanul nu s-ar putea asemui cu un asemenea leu, cci doar vulpea nu s-ar dovedi vrednic s-l nfrunte. Destul cu asta. Ia s auzim ce are s ne spun Luna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LUCIU-DE-LUN:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>n fanaru-acesta este luna alb-ncornorat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>ns coarnele pe fruntea lunii s-au vzut vreodat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu e Craiul-Nou. i coarne poart numai luna plin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LUCIU-DE-LUN:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>st fanar nfieaz-a lunii galben lumin.<text:line-break/>Are coarne felinarul, taina lunii s ne-o spun<text:line-break/>Iar eu, Starveling, sunt masca sfnt-a omului din lun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Asta este o greeal. Totul ar fi bine, dar<text:line-break/>Omul care st n lun cum nu intr-n felinar?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>I-ar aprinde lumnarea hainele. Nici n-ar putea,<text:line-break/>Dac este om, s poat n fanar nici ncpea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De-ast lun sunt stul. N-ai gsit alta mai bun?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ai rbdare, mi se pare c e gata s apun?<text:line-break/>S-ateptm, s-avem rbdare, cine tie ce-o s ias.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Spune mai departe, Lun, sfnta stelelor crias!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LUCIU-DE-LUN:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Luna este tot fanarul, eu sunt omul cel din lun.<text:line-break/>Mrcinele, celul, vin cu toii mpreun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Toate-acestea se cuvine n fanar s se cuprind,<text:line-break/>Dar tcere, cci Thisbeea aripi-a-nceput s prind.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR THISBEEA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vreau iubitul s mi-l caut la mormntul lui Nini.<text:line-break/>Poate am venit devreme. Ce s fac spre a-l gsi?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEUL (SCOATE UN RGET NGROZITOR):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O! (THISBEEA O IA LA FUG.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine ai rgit, leule!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine te pricepi s fugi, Thisbeea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Bine te-ai mai priceput s luminezi, Lun! Ah! Cu ct duioie scnteiaz luna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">LEUL SFIE NTRE COLI MANTIA THISBEEI I IESE DIN SCEN.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Bine ai sfiat, leule!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i acuma, leul s-a fcut nevzut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dar iat-l pe Pyram c vine i el</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR PYRAM.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mulumesc, divin lun, pentru razele-i solare,<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi pot vedea iubita, pe Thisbeea, pe crare.<text:line-break/>Mulumesc din suflet pentru razele de aur<text:line-break/>La lumina lor vzndu-mi scumpul dragostei tezaur.<text:line-break/>ns vai, nenorocire!<text:line-break/>Blestemata mea privire<text:line-break/>Vede mantia-i ptat<text:line-break/>De o fiar-nsngerat.<text:line-break/>Furii crunte, aprei,<text:line-break/>Smulgei, rupei i tiei<text:line-break/>Firul tristei mele viei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>O! Durerea-i e cumplit:<text:line-break/>De-un omor pricinuit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>De bietul Pyram zu c-mi pare ru:<text:line-break/>M mic jalea sufletului su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PYRAM:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pentru ce, cumplit fire, ai adus pe lume lei,<text:line-break/>Pentru ca un leu s-mi frng a vieii mele floare?<text:line-break/>Ea, Thisbeea, n-a fost oare cea mai mndr din femei,<text:line-break/>Care-a strlucit vreodat pe acest pmnt, sub soare?<text:line-break/>Lacrime, pornii la vale,<text:line-break/>Cu-un potop cumplit de jale.<text:line-break/>Vino, spada mea srac,<text:line-break/>Iei mai repede din teac,<text:line-break/>Las-mi vrful s i-l frng<text:line-break/>Uite-aici, sub snul stng. (SE STRPUNGE I CADE.)<text:line-break/>Unde-mi este inima!<text:line-break/>Mori, Pyram! Aa, aa!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Moartea simt cum m cuprinde<text:line-break/>Trupul meu l simt c moare,<text:line-break/>Vrea spre glie s coboare,<text:line-break/>Sufletul mi este-n rai,<text:line-break/>Lun, rost tu nu mai ai. (LUCIU-DE-LUN DISPARE.)<text:line-break/>Viaa eu mi-o joc la zar (MOARE.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pun prinsoare pe-un mgar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nici mgar, nici zar, nici as.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cred c-att i-a mai rmas:<text:line-break/>Ca un felcer s-l nvie<text:line-break/>i mgar din nou s fie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>nc nu am mai vzut-o<text:line-break/>Pe Thisbeea, i-am pierdut-o,<text:line-break/>Fiindc luna a plecat<text:line-break/>Fr s fi ateptat<text:line-break/>S-l gseasc pe Pyram<text:line-break/>i s moar, cum tiam.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Stelele vor lumina-o<text:line-break/>i tot ele-or ngropa-o.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">REINTR THISBEEA.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">HIPPOLYTA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Pentru-un astfel de iubit<text:line-break/>N-ai prea mult pentru bocit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i Thisbeea, i Pyram<text:line-break/>Sunt dintr-un acelai neam,<text:line-break/>ntre ei, s nu v mire,<text:line-break/>Nu-i nicio deosebire.<text:line-break/>Nici o molie nu tie<text:line-break/>Care dintre ei s fie<text:line-break/>Un erou, o eroin,<text:line-break/>Un flcu sau o virgin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LYSANDER:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>L-a privit cu ochii dulcii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vin, Thisbeio, s te culci!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THISBEEA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Dormi, frumosul meu iubit?<text:line-break/>Cum? Pyramus! Ai murit?<text:line-break/>O! Deteapt-te din somn,<text:line-break/>Dulce-al vieii mele domn.<text:line-break/>Spune-o vorb! Cum? Eti mut?<text:line-break/>Zeilor! Cum s-a fcut?<text:line-break/>nveli-va un mormnt<text:line-break/>Chipul tu frumos i sfnt?<text:line-break/>Ochii ti dulci i senini<text:line-break/>i sprncenele de crini?<text:line-break/>Gura-i scump, drgla,<text:line-break/>Nasul tu ca o cirea?<text:line-break/>Cele trei surori cumplite<text:line-break/>Care-s morii zlogite,<text:line-break/>Moartea-ndat-mi pregtii,<text:line-break/>Nu vreau s m zlogii<text:line-break/>Pe pmntul blestemat.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pyram, spada mi-ai lsat<text:line-break/>Vezi cum mi-o mplnt n piept,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">SE NJUNGHIE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Nu mai pot s mai atept.<text:line-break/>Soarta mi-o voi mplini-o:<text:line-break/>Mor! Adio! Mor! Adio! (MOARE.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Luciu-de-Lun i Leul au rmas teferi s-i nmormnteze pe cei mori.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DEMETRIUS:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da, dar i Zidul le poate da o mn de ajutor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">BOTTOM (NVIE):</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ba ctui de puin! V nelai! Zidul care desprea cele dou neamuri s-a drmat! Acum, dac ai pofti s mai vedei un epilog, sau s ascultai un dans bergamasc dansat de ctre doi actori din breasla noastr?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">THEZEU:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nu! Nici un epilog. Te rog. Piesa jucat de voi nu are nevoie s fie lmurit spectatorilor. i cum actorii sunt acum aproape cu toii mori, nici de fluierat nu s-ar mai ncumeta s-i fluiere cineva. Dac actorul care a jucat rolul lui Pyram s-ar fi spnzurat de calaveta Thisbeei, stranic tragedie ar mai fi fost! Dar i aa cum a fost, tot ne-a plcut. Ia s urmrim danul vostru bergamasc. Epilogul s-l lsm pentru mai trziu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">PE SCEN SE DANSEAZ UN DANS BERGAMASC.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Cu glas de-aram miezul nopii sun,<text:line-break/>E ora cnd stafiile se-adun.<text:line-break/>Prieteni, la culcare! Cci m tem<text:line-break/>C toat vremea care o veghem<text:line-break/>n noaptea-aceasta, mine o vom dormi<text:line-break/>La revedere! Somn uor, copii!<text:line-break/>De-aci-nainte-nc cincisprezece<text:line-break/>Voioase zile-n ir vom tot petrece.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">TOI INTR N PALAT. LYSANDER, HERMIA, DEMETRIUS I HELENA IES PRIN DREAPTA.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_II_5"/><text:soft-page-break/>Scena II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">INTR PUCK.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Rage-acuma hmesit<text:line-break/>Leul! Url-n lun lupul,<text:line-break/>i plugarul obosit<text:line-break/>i red odihnei trupul.<text:line-break/>Lene plpie vpaia<text:line-break/>Pe tciuni, cobind a moarte,<text:line-break/>ip-n turnuri cucuvaia.<text:line-break/>Ceasul tainic nu-i departe<text:line-break/>Cnd strigoii-n intirim<text:line-break/>Ies din gropi ntredeschise;<text:line-break/>Iar noi, silfi ce-nsoim<text:line-break/>Carul Hecatei, cu vise<text:line-break/>Pe furi gonii de soare<text:line-break/>i ne-mprtiem ca vise<text:line-break/>Dup umbrele fugare.<text:line-break/>Niciun oricel nu stric<text:line-break/>Pacea-acestei case sfinte.<text:line-break/>Sunt trimis cu-o mturic<text:line-break/>Vreau s mtur dinainte.<text:line-break/>N-am s las nicio pisic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">INTR OBERON, TITANIA I IELELE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Rspndii ca o lucuare<text:line-break/>Dulce-a unui foc ce moare,<text:line-break/>Iele, i pornii n zbor<text:line-break/>i dansai apoi uor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">TITANIA:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cte-o not-ngne-n cor<text:line-break/>Fiecare vorb-a mea,<text:line-break/>Pn ce n-o rmnea<text:line-break/>Nesfinit niciun locor. (CNTECE I DAN.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>OBERON:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Mergei pn la revrsatul<text:line-break/>Zorilor prin tot palatul. (IELELE INTR N PALAT.)<text:line-break/>Iar noi vom cerceta<text:line-break/>Cel mai mndru pat de nunt,<text:line-break/>Ca ferii de soart crunt<text:line-break/>Fericii s vieuiasc<text:line-break/>Cei ce-n el au s se nasc.<text:line-break/>Iar perechile frumoase<text:line-break/>S rmn credincioase<text:line-break/>i s aib-n toate spor<text:line-break/>i noroc cu pruncii lor.<text:line-break/>Ielele, pn se face<text:line-break/>Zi, cu roua de pe vi<text:line-break/>S sfineasc-aceste-odi<text:line-break/>Rspndind o dulce pace,<text:line-break/>Ca-n aceste sli mree,<text:line-break/>Gloria s strluceasc<text:line-break/>i-o etern tineree<text:line-break/>Pe stpni s-i fericeasc! (IELELE SE NTORC N PALAT.)<text:line-break/>i acum,<text:line-break/>n zbor, la drum!<text:line-break/>Ne-ntlnim iar n amurg!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">OBERON, TITANIA I IELELE IES.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PUCK:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Dac umbre ce suntem<text:line-break/>V-am adus vreo suprare,<text:line-break/>Credei (i atunci avem<text:line-break/>Un cuvnt de aprare)<text:line-break/>C n somn v-au aprut<text:line-break/>Toate cte le-ai vzut.<text:line-break/>i atunci povestea noastr<text:line-break/>Nu-i dect un vis ciudat:<text:line-break/>Nu va fi nlturat<text:line-break/>De bunvoina voastr.<text:line-break/>Dar pe numele meu bun<text:line-break/>i cinstit m jur eu, Puck,<text:line-break/>n curnd am s v-aduc<text:line-break/>Ceva nou i mult mai bun.<text:line-break/>De n-o fi aa cum spun,<text:line-break/>Puck rmn de minciun.<text:line-break/>Puck e hotrt s fac<text:line-break/>Tot ce poate s v plac.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i acuma, noapte bun<text:line-break/>Tuturor i nu plecai<text:line-break/>Pn ce n-aplaudai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">IESE.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"> SFRIT </text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cidul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Tragedie n cinci acte - 1636</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">de Pierre Corneille</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:s/>traducere de tefan Octavian Iosif</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTORI"/>ACTORI</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">DON FERNANDO, ntiul rege al Castiliei<text:line-break/>DONA URACCA, infant a Castiliei<text:line-break/>DON DIEGO, tatl lui don Rodrigo<text:line-break/>DON GOMEZ, conte de Gormaz, tatl Ximenii<text:line-break/>DON RODRIGO, iubitul Ximenii<text:line-break/>DON SANCHO, ndrgostit de XIMENA<text:line-break/>SON ALONSO gentilomi castilani<text:line-break/>XIMENA, fiica lui don Gomez<text:line-break/>LEONORA, guvernanta infantei<text:line-break/>ELVIRA, guvernanta Ximenii<text:line-break/>UN PAJ al infantei</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTUL_I1"/>ACTUL I</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_I1"/>SCENA I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pot s m-ncred, Elvir, n tirile aduse?<text:line-break/>N-ascunzi nimic din cele ce tatl meu i spuse?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Snt nc fermecat de tot ce-am auzit:<text:line-break/>Rodrig, iubit de tine, de el e preuit<text:line-break/>i dac din cuvinte i-am neles gndirea<text:line-break/>Socot c i va cere ca s-i asculi iubirea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>O, spune-mi nc o dat, o, spune-mi-o mereu,<text:line-break/>Ce te ndeamn-a crede c-i place-alesul meu?<text:line-break/>Red-mi din nou ndejdea ce-o socoteam apus,<text:line-break/>Solie-aa de dulce n veci de-ajuns nu-i spus;<text:line-break/>Nu poi iubirii noastre ca s-i promii de-ajuns</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>C-i poate da pe fa tot focul ei ascuns.<text:line-break/>Ce-a zis de struina ce-o pun pe lng tine<text:line-break/>i Sancho i Rodrigo? N-ai da pe fa-n fine<text:line-break/>Nepotrivirea care m face s nclin<text:line-break/>Mai mult spre cel din urm?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Nu; ctui de puin,<text:line-break/>Ci tocmai dimpotriv i-am spus c tu, senora,<text:line-break/>Aceeai nepsare le-arei amindurora,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i fr ca pe vreunul mai mult s-l preuieti<text:line-break/>Te vei pleca smerit voinei printeti.<text:line-break/>Smerenia aceasta l-umplu de bucurie,<text:line-break/>Cum ochii lui i vorba-i mi dar mrturie,<text:line-break/>i dac vrei s afli curatul adevr,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ascult dar ce-n grab mi-a spus, de-a fir-a-n pr<text:line-break/>Ea-i face datoria, pot amndoi s-o cear,<text:line-break/>Cci amndoi snt nobili, de-o vrednicie rar;<text:line-break/>Snt tineri, ns arde n ochii lor focoi<text:line-break/>Virtutea strlucit a marilor strmoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Rodrig, el mai cu seam, nu are-o trstur,<text:line-break/>Un gest s nu-i vorbeasc de marea lui bravur<text:line-break/>i-i dintr-un neam ce dete ati eroi mrii,<text:line-break/>nct ei nasc de-a dreptul de lauri adumbrii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Viteaz a fost i tatl n zilele lui bune.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Virtutea lui pe vremuri trecea drept o minune;<text:line-break/>n creurile frunei spat e-al su trecut,<text:line-break/>Spunndu-ne i astzi de cele ce-a fcut.<text:line-break/>Eu cred c fiul calc pe urma lui, i dac<text:line-break/>Ximena vrea, iubeasc-l i n-are s-mi displac.<text:line-break/>Mergea la adunare, i ceasul ce grbea<text:line-break/>I-a ntrerupt cuvntul ce-l ncepuse-abea,<text:line-break/>Dar poi s vezi din vorba aceasta, mult-puin,<text:line-break/>Gndirea lui spre care din amndoi nclin.<text:line-break/>Azi regele e vorba s-aleag guvernor<text:line-break/>Infantelui; i, sigur, acest nalt favor<text:line-break/>Pe don Gomez l-ateapt, cci rara-i vrednicie<text:line-break/>Nu-ngduie de altul nlturat s fie.<text:line-break/>Cum marile lui fapte l fac fr egal,<text:line-break/>n dreapta-i ateptare nu va-ntlni rival.<text:line-break/>i cum Rodrig decise don Dieg s te cear<text:line-break/>Chiar azi, dup edin, te las s judeci dar<text:line-break/>De nu-s destule semne c toate-i merg n plin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Vai, inima mea totui cuprins e de chin<text:line-break/>i pare c refuz aceast veselie.<text:line-break/>O clip poate soarta s-o schimbe, cine tie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-n fericirea-aceasta aa de mare-a mea,<text:line-break/>Fr s vreau, mi-e team de-o-ntorstur rea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Din fericire, teama aceasta n-o s ie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>S ateptm sfritul, oricum ar fi s fie!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_II-a"/>SCENA a II-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">INFANTA, LEONORA, PAJUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Paj, du-te la Ximena, s-i spui din partea mea<text:line-break/>C astzi zbovete prea mult spre-a m vedea i lenea ei jignete iubirea mea de sor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Acelai dor te mn, slvit mea senor,<text:line-break/>Ca s o caui zilnic, i cnd cu ea vorbeti Te-aud de-a lor iubire cerndu-i zilnic veti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu fr de pricin; eu nsmi am silit-o<text:line-break/>S sufere sgeata ce-n suflet a rnit-o;<text:line-break/>Rodrig i-e drag i nsmi eu i l-am druit;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dispreul ei prin mine Rodrig l-a biruit,<text:line-break/>i cum iubirea-aceasta de mine-a fost legat,<text:line-break/>A vrea s se sfreasc i chinul lor odat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cu tot succesul, doamn, pe care l obii,<text:line-break/>Te vd in prada unei dureri aa de vii:<text:line-break/>Iubirea care-i face pe dnii s tresalte<text:line-break/>Pricinuiete jalea acestei inimi nalte?<text:line-break/>Te face oare grija pe care le-o pstrezi<text:line-break/>S fii nefericit cnd fericii i vezi?<text:line-break/>Merg ns prea departe i poate-s indiscret.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mai mare mi-este jalea de-ncerc s-o in secret;<text:line-break/>Ascult dar, ascult ce mult m-am zbuciumat<text:line-break/>i cum m zbucium nc i astzi necurmat,<text:line-break/>Cum dragostea mea crete orict a vrea s-o nrui;<text:line-break/>Da, tnrul acesta, iubitul ce i-l drui Mi-e drag</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pune mna aici, s tii de vrei<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cum bate cnd aude de-nvingtorul ei<text:line-break/>i cum l recunoate inima mea</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>O, doamn,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">M ieri c uit respectul ce s te cert m-ndeamn:<text:line-break/>Prinesa mea pe care feciori de regi o cer<text:line-break/>S-i plece ochii galei pe-un simplu cavaler?<text:line-break/>Dar regele, dar ara ce spun de toate-aceste?<text:line-break/>Stpna uit, poate, a cui odrasl este?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Nu uit; i mai degrab snt gata ca s mor<text:line-break/>Dect s-mi lepd rangul, dect s m cobor.<text:line-break/>Dar i-a putea rspunde c vrednicia are<text:line-break/>Pe lumea asta dreptul s-aprind-un suflet mare,<text:line-break/>i dac slbiciunea a vrea eu s mi-o iert,<text:line-break/>Exemple strlucite n-a cuta-n deert;<text:line-break/>Dar nu urmez o cale ce mi-ar scdea mrirea,<text:line-break/>Nu-ngdui s m-nving pn-ntr-att iubirea,<text:line-break/>i-mi zic ntotdeauna: fiind de neam de regi,<text:line-break/>Datoare eti un rege de mire s-i alegi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnd am vzut c totui slbete-a mea putere,<text:line-break/>Am druit eu nsmi ce nu-ndrzneam a cere:<text:line-break/>Am pus-o pe Ximena n locul meu, i-n ea<text:line-break/>Am aat vpaia ca s mi-o sting pe-a mea.<text:line-break/>S nu te mire dar c inima m-mbie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Ca s grbesc aceast fatal cununie,<text:line-break/>Vezi c de ea atrn acum hodina mea;<text:line-break/>O dat cu ndejdea, iubirea-mi va scdea,<text:line-break/>Precum un foc se stinge cnd e lipsit de hran;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-orict s-ndur m face ursita mea tiran,<text:line-break/>Rodrigo cu Ximena o dat cununat,<text:line-break/>Ndejdea mea e moart i dorul vindecat.<text:line-break/>Dar pn-atuncea sufr un chin fr de nume,<text:line-break/>Cci azi Rodrig mi este tot ce-am mai drag pe lume.<text:line-break/>ncerc s-l pierd, i totui, s-l pierd mi vine greu:<text:line-break/>De-aice izvorte, vezi tu, tot chinul meu!<text:line-break/>Fiina mea srmana-i silit s suspine<text:line-break/>Tnjind dup un lucru ce nu e demn de mine;<text:line-break/>S-abate bietu-mi suflet n dou sfiat:<text:line-break/>Curajul de m-ndeamn, simirile m-abat;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">M tem de nunta-aceasta i vreau aceast nunt,<text:line-break/>i-att mi sunt de scumpe n lupta-aceast crunt<text:line-break/>De-o parte-a mea mrire, de alta-al meu amor,<text:line-break/>nct de se va face sau nu, simt c-am s mor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Atuncea nu-mi rmne, senora mea cea bun,<text:line-break/>Dect s-i plng de jale cu tine dimpreun;<text:line-break/>Te osndeam, i-acuma te plng vznd ce-nduri;<text:line-break/>Dar pentru c n prada acestei dulci torturi<text:line-break/>Virtutea ta nvinge puterea ei i vraja</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zdrnicind asaltu-i i respingndu-i mreaja,<text:line-break/>Ea va reda hodina i sufletului tu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>ncrede-te n vreme, ce-alin orice ru,<text:line-break/>ncrede-te-n virtute i sper-n provedin,<text:line-break/>Ce trebui s se-ndure de-atta suferin!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sperana cea mai dulce e-n desperarea mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">PAJUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ximena, principes, dorete-a v vedea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Te du i o reine puin pe galerie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">LEONORA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vrei s mai stai, stpn, pierdut-n reverie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu; dar dei n suflet ascund atta chin,<text:line-break/>Doresc s-mi iau un aer mai vesel, mai senin.<text:line-break/>Viu dup tine.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_III-a"/>SCENA a III-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">INFANTA SINGUR</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Doamne, tu singur de la care<text:line-break/>n jalea-mi fr margini atept eu vindecare,<text:line-break/>Red-mi din nou hodina! Ia-mi cinstea-n paza ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n fericirea-altora cat fericirea mea.<text:line-break/>Pe toi trei ne privete aceast cununie.<text:line-break/>Grbete-i ceasul, Doamne, ori d-mi mcar trie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">nceat suferina-mi, se sfarm orice lan<text:line-break/>Cnd oi vedea prin tine unii cei doi amani.<text:line-break/>Dar pun prea mult rbdarea Ximenii la-ncercare;<text:line-break/>Vorbind cu dnsa, poate mai aflu alinare!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_IV-a"/>SCENA a IV-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">CONTELE, DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>A regelui favoare v dete n sfrit<text:line-break/>Un rang ce pentru mine era mai potrivit:<text:line-break/>V face guvernorul principelui Castilii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Prin naltul semn de cinste ce mi l-a dat familii<text:line-break/>Ct e de drept arat, i face cunoscut<text:line-break/>C tie s plteasc servicii din trecut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i regii snt tot oameni ca noi, ca oriicare,<text:line-break/>i ei pot s se-nele, i-aceast-mprejurare<text:line-break/>Slujete ca o vie dovad curii-ntregi<text:line-break/>C meritul de astzi e ru pltit de regi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>S nu vorbim de-un lucru menit s nu v plac.<text:line-break/>Favoarea sau vreun merit dac-a putut s-l fac,<text:line-break/>Respectul ctre rege nu iart nimnui<text:line-break/>De a crti-mpotriva unei voini a lui.<text:line-break/>Sporii-mi cinstea asta mai bine cu-alta nou:<text:line-break/>S-mpreunm a noastre vechi neamuri amndou!<text:line-break/>Avei o fat numai, eu numai un fecior:<text:line-break/>Ne-ar nfri de-a pururi cstoria lor.<text:line-break/>Fii bun dar i primii-mi de ginere feciorul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Partide mai de seam-i pstreaz viitorul<text:line-break/>i spre-alte culmi s-aspire e azi ndrituit<text:line-break/>De noua demnitate la care-ai fost suit.<text:line-break/>ndeplinii-o, facei pe prin ca s cunoasc<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cum trebuie o ar un domn s-o crmuiasc,<text:line-break/>S stea n faa legii smerii supuii si,<text:line-break/>S-nsufle-n buni iubire i groaz n cei ri;<text:line-break/>Unii aceste daruri cu-acele de rzboinic:<text:line-break/>i artai ct trebuie s fie de destoinic,<text:line-break/>S-ajung-n meteugul lui Mart fr egal;<text:line-break/>Cum s petreac zile i nopi ntregi pe cal,<text:line-break/>S doarm cu armura i cum s dea asaltul,<text:line-break/>i oriice izbnd s-o aib el, nu altul.<text:line-break/>Prin pilde, nu prin vorbe l facei n sfrit<text:line-break/>Ca s ajung-aieve un domn desvrit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Spre-a nva din pilde, n ciuda lumii rele,<text:line-break/>Ajunge s cunoasc povestea vieii mele.<text:line-break/>Acolo, n trecutul din fapte mari urzit,<text:line-break/>El va vedea cum trebuie-un neam cluzit,<text:line-break/>Cum iai o cetuie, i rnduieti otirea<text:line-break/>i pe isprvi mree ntemeiezi mrirea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cu mult mai mare este puterea pildei vii,<text:line-break/>nva ru din carte un prin a crmui,<text:line-break/>i-al anilor ti numr nu a putut s fac<text:line-break/>Nimic ce n-ar fi-n stare o zi de-a mea s-ntreac.<text:line-break/>De-ai fost viteaz pe vremuri, azi cel viteaz snt eu<text:line-break/>A rii cea mai tare proptea e braul meu;<text:line-break/>Tresar nspimntate Grenada i-Aragonul</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnd fulger-a mea spad; ea ocrotete tronul;<text:line-break/>De n-a fi eu, ai trece curnd sub alte legi:<text:line-break/>Curnd dumanii votri ar fi ai votri regi;<text:line-break/>Pe zi, pe ceas, victorii ctig peste victorii<text:line-break/>i lauri peste lauri adaug vechei glorii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Umbrit de brau-mi prinul ar mai avea apoi<text:line-break/>Prilejul s-i ncerce curajul n rzboi<text:line-break/>i-ar nva s-nving, vzndu-m pe mine,<text:line-break/>i pentru ca s poat ct mai curnd, n fine,<text:line-break/>S-i pun n lumin aleasa lui fiin<text:line-break/>i caracterul nobil ce-l are</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Am tiin; Slujii pe rege bine, doar v-am vzut luptnd<text:line-break/>i comandnd sub mine nti; i-acuma, cnd<text:line-break/>A vrstei slbiciune a stins in mine focul,<text:line-break/>Mrturisesc c-mi inei cu vrednicie locul;<text:line-break/>Ca s crum attea cuvinte fr rost:<text:line-break/>Voi azi sntei eroul ce eu pe vremi am fost. Monarhul ns-n ast ntrecere firete<text:line-break/>A vrut s dovedeasc pe cine preuiete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Voi mi-ai rpit aceea ce meritasem eu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">don diego Deci cu att mai mare era meritul meu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai demn e cine poate mai mult rvn pune</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">A fi respins nu-i tocmai un semn din cele bune.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ai amgit pe rege prin intrigi de curtean.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Mi-a fost trecutul mare unicul partizan.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cred c etii voastre i dete precdere.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Curajul e msura ce-o are n vedere.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Atunci onoarea asta era un drept al meu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Cin n-a putut s-o ieie n-a meritat-o.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Eu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">N-am meritat-o? Spune!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Voi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>O, de-a ta ndrzneal<text:line-break/>Vei fi silit, n-ai team, s-mi dai tu socoteal.<text:line-break/>i chiar n clipa asta, moneag nfumurat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(l plmuiete.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(scond spada)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sfrete, ia-mi i viaa, vai! dup-acest stigmat,<text:line-break/>ntiul ce pteaz a rasei mele faim!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Atta slbiciune crezi tu c-mi face spaim?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Puterile m las n ceasul cel mai greu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Pstreaz-i totui spada; st ruinos trofeu<text:line-break/>De l-a lua cu mine, i-ar face numai fal.<text:line-break/>Urmeze dar prinul a vieei tale coal<text:line-break/>n ciuda lumii rele deprins a crti,<text:line-break/>n paginele-acele nva-l a citi;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Pedeapsa meritat de vorba-i temerar<text:line-break/>i va sluji, firete, drept o podoab rar!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_V-a"/>SCENA a V-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Turbare! Dezndejde! Dumane btrnei:<text:line-break/>Acesta-i dar sfritul frumoasei mele viei?<text:line-break/>Albit-am oare-n lupte slvit pn-adineauri<text:line-break/>S vd o zi cum poate pli atia lauri?<text:line-break/>i braul meu de-o lume temut i preuit,<text:line-break/>El, care-acest imperiu ades l-am mntuit,<text:line-break/>i-a fost aproape-un secol a tronului trie,<text:line-break/>Azi mi refuz dreptul de aprare mie?<text:line-break/>O, crud amintire a vechei vitejii!<text:line-break/>Isprav-attor zile pierdut ntr-o zi!<text:line-break/>Rang nou plin de mrire i de urmri fatale,<text:line-break/>Pripor nalt de unde onoarea-mi se prvale!<text:line-break/>E cu putin oare s mor nerzbunat?<text:line-break/>Ori s triesc pe lume cu numele-ntinat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, ia-mi de-acuma, conte, aceast slujb care<text:line-break/>Nu poate s-o-mplineasc un om fr onoare,<text:line-break/>Geloasa ta trufie nevrednic m fcu<text:line-break/>De-nalta ndurare a regelui Iar tu,<text:line-break/>Unealt glorioas ce m-ai slujit o via,<text:line-break/>Netrebnic podoab a unui trup de ghea,<text:line-break/>O, fier temut pe vremuri, ce nu spre-a m-apra,<text:line-break/>Ci numai de parad atrni la coapsa mea,<text:line-break/>Te du, m prsete i treci n mni mai bune,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Care vor ti pe mine, cel slab, s m rzbune!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_VI-a"/>SCENA a VI-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON DIEGO, DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Ai inim, Rodrigo?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pe loc i-a arta<text:line-break/>De nu mi-ai fi printe!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>nflcrarea ta<text:line-break/>Ce dulce mi-e, i chinul cum tie s-mi aline<text:span text:style-name="T28">!</text:span><text:line-break/>n apriga-i pornire m recunosc pe mine<text:span text:style-name="T28">!</text:span><text:line-break/>Junia mea renate n sngele tu viu!<text:line-break/>Vin, nobilul meu snge, vin, vrednicul meu fiu,<text:line-break/>Vino i m rzbun!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ce?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P25">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>De cea mai mare<text:line-break/>Ocar ce ucide a ta i-a mea onoare!<text:line-break/>De-o palm. Ticlosul pe loc muca pmnt,<text:line-break/>Dar slbiciunea vrstei mi-opri orice avnt.<text:line-break/>Ia acest fier ce brau-mi nu poate s-l mai poarte,<text:line-break/>i-l dau s faci dreptate: s mori ori s dai moartei<text:line-break/>Mergi dar i pedepsete pe-acel om ncrezut:<text:line-break/>Mori sau ucide-l: iat ce ai tu de fcut.<text:line-break/>n snge doar se spal asemenea ruine.<text:line-break/>i spre-a trezi mndria strmoilor n tine<text:line-break/>i-o spun fr ncunjur c ai de combtut<text:line-break/>Un adversar puternic i mare. L-am vzut<text:line-break/>Acoperit de snge i pulbere odat,<text:line-break/>mprtiind teroarea ntr-o ntreag-armat;<text:line-break/>O sut escadroane vzutu-l-am rupnd,<text:line-break/>i pentru-a-i spune nc mai mult, n-a fost nicicnd<text:line-break/>Ca el printre rzboinici, nici printre cpetenii<text:line-break/>E</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Spune, fie-i mil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Printele Ximenii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>El este</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nici o vorb. Cunosc iubirea ta.<text:line-break/>Dar poi tri-n ruine? Insulta e mai grea,<text:line-break/>Cu ct mai scump i este acel ce te insult.<text:line-break/>Cunoti acum ocara. tii ce-ai s faci.<text:line-break/>Ascult: Rzbun-m pe mine, rzbun-te i tu!<text:line-break/>Arat-te de-un tat ca mine vrednic fiu:<text:line-break/>Pe cnd eu-mi plng amarul ce-asupra mea s-adun,<text:line-break/>Tu du-te, alearg, zboar, Rodrig, i ne rzbun!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_VII-a"/>SCENA a VII-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Strfulgerat n suflet de un nprasnic chin,<text:line-break/>Pe care nu putuse, vai, nimeni s-l prevad,<text:line-break/>S fac o nedreptate silit de-o dreapt sfad<text:line-break/>i-obiect de plns al unui nendurat destin,<text:line-break/>Stau mpietrit de spaim, i inima-mi zdrobit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Abia de mai palpit. Att eram de-aproape de raiul meu dorit!<text:line-break/>O, ce ursit plin de triste ciudenii!<text:line-break/>Iubitul meu printe e crunt batjocorit<text:line-break/>i vinovatul este printele Ximenii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, ce grozav lupt se d acum n mine!<text:line-break/>n contra cinstei mele iubirea mea-i pornit:<text:line-break/>A rzbuna un tat i-a pierde o iubit!<text:line-break/>El inima-mi a, ea braul mi-l reine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ca s-mi trdez iubirea ori cinstea mea hulit,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Durerea cea cumplit<text:line-break/>De-o parte i de alta e tot att de mult!<text:line-break/>O, ce ursit plin de triste ciudenii!<text:line-break/>S las fr pedeaps aa de grea insult?<text:line-break/>S pedepsesc pe mndrul printe al Ximenii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Onoare i iubire, dumane fa-n fa!<text:line-break/>Rzboi frumos i crncen! Plcut tiranie!<text:line-break/>Ori gloria apus, ori inima pustie!<text:line-break/>Nefericit pe lume, sau vai! nedemn de via!<text:line-break/>A unui suflet mndru, dar dragostei dat prad</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Chin i ndejde,  spad,<text:line-break/>Al fericirii mele clu cinstit, vrei oare<text:line-break/>n ziua-aceasta plin de triste ciudenii,<text:line-break/>Vrei tu acum n snge s speli a mea ruine,<text:line-break/>Vrei tu s-mi pierzi norocul i inima Ximenii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sfrit vieii mele mai bine vreau s-i pun!<text:line-break/>i tatei, i iubitei aceasta le priete.<text:line-break/>De m rzbun, Ximena m va ur, firete,<text:line-break/>Am s-i atrag dispreul de n-am s m rzbuni<text:line-break/>Ori mi reneg credina cea mai de pre a mea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ori snt nedemn de ea;<text:line-break/>Nefericirea-mi crete vroind s-o nconjor:<text:line-break/>Hai, inim, cuteaz! i dac-i scris s mor,<text:line-break/>Murind, s iau cu mine i dragostea Ximenii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar moartea mea nu poate ocara grea s-o spele!<text:line-break/>i gloria-mi o dat cu mine va s-apun!<text:line-break/>O, pot s rabd eu oare ca Spania s spun<text:line-break/>C n-am tiut s-mi apr onoarea casei mele?<text:line-break/>S cru un vis pe care l vede biata-mi minte<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pierdut de mai-nainte!<text:line-break/>Fugii departe, gnduri aa puin nalte!<text:line-break/>Departe de la mine, voi, josnice vedenii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">braul meu, onoarea s o salvm ncale,<text:line-break/>Cci, oricum, tot pierdut e dragostea Ximei<text:line-break/>Da, gndurile mele o clip-au rtcit!<text:line-break/>Nimic pe lumea-aceasta nu-i mai presus de-onoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i dac mor n lupt sau mor de ntristare,<text:line-break/>Jertfi-voi al meu snge curat cum l-am primit!<text:line-break/>Alearg dar, Rodrigo, i las ezitarea,<text:line-break/>Te cheam rzbunarea! De-atta ovial nedemn-s ruinat.<text:line-break/>Departe de la mine, o, josnice vedenii!<text:line-break/>Cci azi al tu printe e crncen ofensat,<text:line-break/>i-ofensatorul este printele Ximenii!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTUL_II1"/>ACTUL II</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_I_21"/>SCENA I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON ARIAS, CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cel mult pot recunoate c sngele-mi prea viu<text:line-break/>Prea s-a aprins de-o vorb, e ins prea tirziu,<text:line-break/>Cci lovitura fr de lecuire este.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S mblnzii pe rege cercai cu toate-aceste.<text:line-break/>El ia prea vie parte la tot spre-a nu lsa<text:line-break/>Ca s simii ntreag nemulmirea sa.<text:line-break/>i nici n-avei altminteri vreun drept la aprare,<text:line-break/>Cci deopotriv rangul nalt al celui care<text:line-break/>A ndurat ocara, cum i mrimea ei<text:line-break/>Cer datorii i jertfe mai mari ca de-obicei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe viaa mea stpn e monarhul, mi se pare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Greeala vi-i urmat de-o furie prea mare.<text:line-break/>El v iubete nc i-a-l mpca nu-i greu.<text:line-break/>Putei sta mpotriv cnd domnul zice: vreu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Ca s-mi pstrez, seniore, neatins-a mea onoare,<text:line-break/>Neascultarea-mi nu e-un pcat aa de mare,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-orct ar fi de mare, la urma urmei pot<text:line-break/>Prin meritele mele ca s rscumpr tot.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Poi s-i aduci servicii orict de mari i grele,<text:line-break/>Un rege nu-i rmne ndatorat de ele;<text:line-break/>i nu uitai un lucru: slujind pe domnitor,<text:line-break/>Orice supus nu face dect ce e dator.<text:line-break/>V credei prea puternic i viaa-n joc v-o spunei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Pn ce nu vd cu ochii, nu pot s cred ce spunei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">don arias Monarhul e puternic i face tot ce vrea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>O zi nu poate pierde pe-un om de seama mea. S-mi dea cea mai cumplit pedeaps, nu m speriu: De pier, cu mine piere i-ntreg acest imperiu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nesocotii pe-acela ce ine sceptru-n mni</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pe care fr mine l-ar pierde pn mni:<text:line-break/>Porneasc mpotriv-mi mria-sa prigoana:<text:line-break/>De voi cdea, voi face s-i cad i coroana.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, cugetai mai bine la cele ce v-am zis, Luai o deciziune mai bun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>M-am decis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mria-sa m-ateapt; ce vrei s i se spun?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>C nici o umilin nu poate s-mi impun. 462</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dar regilor la place s fie ascultai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Zadarnic e vorba; snt sorii aruncai.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu toi bogaii lauri ce fruntea v-ncunun<text:line-break/>Pzii-v de trsnet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>L-atept cu voie bun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dar nu fr urmare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Atuncea, n sfrit,<text:line-break/>Va fi i don Diego cu-att mai mulmit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">(singur)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mi-e sufletul deasupra nendurtoarei soarte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De-ameninri nu-i pas cnd nu te temi de moarte.<text:line-break/>Primesc s duc mai bine un trai nefericit,<text:line-break/>Dar nimenea nu-mi cear s vieuiesc hulit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_II-a_2"/>SCENA a II-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">CONTELE, DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Dou cuvinte, conte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Zi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Fr vorb mult:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Cunoti tu pe don Diego?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Da.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>M-ndoiesc, ascult.<text:line-break/>tii oare c btrnul acesta vrednic fu<text:line-break/>Virtutea i mndria epocii lui, tii tu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Se poate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">tii c-i snge de-al su vpaie vie<text:line-break/>Ce-mi scapr-n privire? O tii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ce-mi pas mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">La patru pai de-aice te-oi face ca s-o tii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Copil plin de trufie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu te neliniti!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>E-adevrat, snt tnr, dar pentru-un suflet mare<text:line-break/>Valoarea nu ateapt ca vrsta s-o msoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Tu, care-o spad nc n-avui n mn, vrei<text:line-break/>S te msori cu mine?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Fac parte dintr-acei<text:line-break/>Cari nu arat cine-s de dou ori pe lume</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i de la-ntia fapt tiu s-i ctige-un nume!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Curajul care-aceste cuvinte i-l vdesc<text:line-break/>M deprinsesem zilnic n ochi s i-l cetesc:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vznd n tine noua Castiliei mrire,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n gndul meu Ximenei te-am fost menit de mire.<text:line-break/>Eu i cunosc iubirea i-mi place a vedea<text:line-break/>C datoria-i este mai sfnt dect ea,<text:line-break/>C tot ce simi nu poate avntul s-i nele,<text:line-break/>C rara ta virtute rspunde stimei mele,<text:line-break/>i ginere voindu-mi un cavaler ntreg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De la-nceput tiut-am pe cine s aleg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n sufletul meu mila i face totui cale:<text:line-break/>i-admir curajul, ns de anii ti mi-e jale,<text:line-break/>Deci las gndul sta ce-i poate fi fatal,<text:line-break/>Cci ntre noi duelul ar fi prea inegal,<text:line-break/>Mi-ar face prea puin onoare-o biruin,<text:line-break/>Triumfu-i fr slav de-nvingi cu uurin,<text:line-break/>Te-or crede toi de-a pururi czut de braul meu<text:line-break/>i moartea ta la urm am s-o deplng tot eu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>De marea ta-ndrzneal nedemn i-e-ndurarea:<text:line-break/>Se teme s-mi ia viaa cel ce mi-a luat onoarea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Te du d-aici!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">S mergem fr-a mai discuta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">i s-a urt cu viaa?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i-o temi cumva pe-a ta?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">CONTELE</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vin, tu-i faci datoria i-i demn un fiu de jale<text:line-break/>Cnd supravieuiete onoarei spiei sale.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_III-a_2"/>SCENA a III-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON ARIAS, DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E contele-ntr-atta de van i ce ateapt?<text:line-break/>Cuteaz oare-a crede c-i iert aceast fapt?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>I-am zis din partea voastr tot ce aveam s-i zic,<text:line-break/>Cu toate-acestea, sire, n-am izbutit nimic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>O, ceruri! deci nutrete o rvn-aa srac<text:line-break/>i-aa puin grij arat ca s-mi plac!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Jignete pe don Diego, de rege-a ti nu vrea!<text:line-break/>El vrea s fac lege aici, la curtea mea!<text:line-break/>Orict de brav rzboinic, bun cpitan s fie,<text:line-break/>Voi ti scurta din vreme asemenea trufie.<text:line-break/>De-ar fi virtutea nsi i-al btliei zeu,<text:line-break/>Ce-nseamn neascultarea i-art acuma eu!<text:line-break/>Cu toate c-ndrzneala-i cerea o grea osnd,<text:line-break/>Vroiam s-l judec totui cu inima mai blnd,<text:line-break/>Dar pentru c s-arat prea drz i prea seme,<text:line-break/>Plecai i punei mna pe el cu orice pre.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Puin rgaz l-ar face s-i vin poate-n fire,<text:line-break/>li clocotea mnia n snge nc, sire,<text:line-break/>i-n cea dinti vlvoare nici o mirare nu-i<text:line-break/>C nu se pleac lesne un suflet cum e-al lui.<text:line-break/>Greeala i-o cunoate; dar inima-i semea<text:line-break/>Nu-l iart ca s-o deie aa curnd pe fa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Don Sancho, taci i afl: oricine-i nclinat<text:line-break/>S-l apere se face el nsui vinovat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ascult i tac; cer totui iertare de voi pune<text:line-break/>O vorb ca s-l apr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>i ce poi oare spune?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>C unuia ca dnsul, cu fapte mari deprins,<text:line-break/>I-e greu s se coboare ca oriicare ins.<text:line-break/>n orice lmurire el vede o ruine,<text:line-break/>i-acesta este numai cuvntul ce-l reine.<text:line-break/>Asprimea datoriei nu-l poate-ndupleca<text:line-break/>i de n-ar fi un suflet prea mndru, s-ar pleca.<text:line-break/>Ci dai porunc, sire, ca braul su cel tare<text:line-break/>Cu ascuiul armei insulta s-o repare,<text:line-break/>Pe loc se va supune; i vin cine-o vrea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Aci stau pentru dnsul cheza, pn ce-o afla.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Uii cui vorbeti; ci vrsta pe care-o ai m face<text:line-break/>S iert; i-nflcrarea aceasta nu-mi displace.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Dar e dator un rege s crue pe-orice ci<text:line-break/>Vrsrile de snge ntre supuii si;<text:line-break/>Pe-ai mei i in n paz, i-i am n grij mare,<text:line-break/>Precum un cap cuminte de membre grij are.<text:line-break/>Cuvntul tu nu poate s fie deci i-al meu:<text:line-break/>Tu judeci ca rzboinic, ca rege judec eu,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">i orice-ar vrea s spun i-ar ndrzni s cread,<text:line-break/>Supunerea nu poate pe contele s-l scad.<text:line-break/>i-apoi m-atinge-ocara, cci el a degradat<text:line-break/>Pe-acel ce-odraslei mele de guvernor l-am dat.<text:line-break/>Cel ce nu ine seama de-alegerea-mi fcut<text:line-break/>Nesocotete nsi puterea absolut.<text:line-break/>Dar s lsm acestea. De-altminteri, am veti noi<text:line-break/>S-ar fi vzut vreo zece corbii de rzboi<text:line-break/>Ce chiar la gura apei au ndrznit s-apar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dumanii notri mauri nu-s pentru-ntia oar<text:line-break/>Silii a v cunoate, spre a porni din nou Rzboi n contra unui aa temut erou.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>De-a pururi i va roade n suflet gelozia<text:line-break/>Ct m-or vedea pe mine stpn pe-Andaluzia,<text:line-break/>i ara peste care au fost prea mult stpni<text:line-break/>Va fi privit pururi cu ciud de pgni.<text:line-break/>Acesta-i i cuvntul c-n inima Sevilii<text:line-break/>De zece ani ncoace in scaunul Castilii,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">S-i pot veghea de-aproape i s zdrnicesc<text:line-break/>Pe loc ce bag de seam tot ce pe-ascuns urzesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Attea sngeroase infrngeri i nva<text:line-break/>C totul e zadarnic ct timp vei fi-n via.<text:line-break/>N-avei de ce v teme.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>i nici n-am ce lsa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/>ncrederea atrage primejdea-n urma sa.<text:line-break/>i-apoi, la urma urmei, s nu prea dm uitrii<text:line-break/>C pn-aici i poate aduce-un flux al mrii.<text:line-break/>Ar fi cu toate-acestea greeal oriicum<text:line-break/>S aruncm teroarea n inimi de p-acum,<text:line-break/>Fiind nesigur zvonul, fiind i pe-nnoptate,<text:line-break/>S-ar rspndi zadarnic nelinitea-n cetate.<text:line-break/>S se-ndoiasc straja la ziduri i n port.<text:line-break/>Ajunge pe-ast-sear.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_IV-a_2"/>SCENA a IV-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON ALONSO, DON SANCHO, DON ARIAS</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ALONSO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sire, contele-i mort.<text:line-break/>Prin fiul su, don Diego i-a rzbunat onoarea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe loc ce-aflai ocara, i-am prevzut urmarea<text:line-break/>i-am vrut nenorocirea aceasta s-o previn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ALONSO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ximena la picioare v cade n suspin<text:line-break/>i toat-n lacrimi vine dreptate a v cere.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dei adnc n suflet m-atinge-a ei durere,<text:line-break/>Socot c dup fapta ce contele-o fcu<text:line-break/>A meritat pedeapsa ce l-a ajuns acu.<text:line-break/>Orict de dreapt-i ns pedeapsa, tot m doare<text:line-break/>Pierznd din cpetenii pe cel mai de valoare,<text:line-break/>Cci dup-o lung via n slujba-acestui stat,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-un snge pentru mine de mii de ori vrsat,<text:line-break/>Orice simiri trufia lui oarb mi dicteaz,<text:line-break/>M simt slbit, pierzndu-l, i moartea-i m-ntristeaz.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_V-a_2"/>SCENA a V-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON DIEGO, XIMENA, DON SANCHO, DON ARIAS, DON ALONSO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Sire, sire, dreptate!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ah, sire, m-ascultai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Cad la genunchii votri</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Vi-i in mbriai</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>V cer dreptate!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Dai-mi o clip de-ascultare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">O, pedepsii-i, sire, trufaa cutezare!<text:line-break/>Cel mai puternic sprijin al rii l-a surpat:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mi-a ucis tatl, sire</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Pe-al su l-a rzbunat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dreptate de la rege orice supus ateapt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Nu merit pedeaps o rzbunare dreapt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">fernandoSculai i unul i-altul, i-apoi am s v-ascult<text:line-break/>Restritea ta, Ximen, m-ndurereaz mult.<text:line-break/>Mi-e inima cuprins, ca i a ta, de jale. (Ctre don DIEGO.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Ateapt; s n-o tulburi n plngerile sale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E mort tatl meu, sire; cu ochii mei vzui<text:line-break/>Cum sngele-i n clocot curgea din pieptul lui<text:line-break/>st snge, chezia regetei voastre case,<text:line-break/>st snge, ce attea victorii ctigase,<text:line-break/>Ce fumeg, cald nc, n mnios ivoi<text:line-break/>C se jertfete pentru un altul dect voi,<text:line-break/>st snge, ce avuse o nobil menire,<text:line-break/>Rodrig la curtea voastr l risipete, sire!<text:line-break/>Am alergat pierdut i mort, ah, l aflai<text:line-break/>Dar povestirea, sire, m las fr grai:<text:line-break/>Iertai-mi dezndejdea, amarele-mi suspine<text:line-break/>i lacrimele mele vorbeasc pentru mine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>F-i inim, copil, c eu de grije-i port<text:line-break/>i-i voi sluji de tat n locul celui mort.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/>Prea mult cinste-mi dete a mea restrite, sire!<text:line-break/>Precum spuneam, acolo l-aflai fr simire,<text:line-break/>Strpuns era de-o ran i singele-i vedeam<text:line-break/>n pulbere scriindu-mi ce datorie am.<text:line-break/>Ori poate vitejia-i ajuns-n aa stare<text:line-break/>Prin rana lui deschis m ndrjea mai tare,<text:line-break/>i-ntocmai ca o gur ce strig ctre cer,<text:line-break/>M ndemna mai grabnic dreptate s vr cer!<text:line-break/>Nu-ngduii, o, rege, astfel de volnicie<text:line-break/>Sub ocrotirea voastr stpn s devie,<text:line-break/>Ca viaa celor vrednici s n-aib nici un pre,<text:line-break/>Ca fr de pedeaps un tnr ndrzne<text:line-break/>Cu ei s se msoare, mrirea s le-o sape,<text:line-break/>Cu sngele lor nobil pmntul s-l adape!<text:line-break/>Nerzbunnd-o, astfel de moarte-ar veteji<text:line-break/>n ali supui oricare avnt de-a v sluji.<text:line-break/>Cer rzbunare, sire, i-o cer nu pentru mine,<text:line-break/>Ci pentru-a voastr slav i pentru-al vostru bine:<text:line-break/>Voi ai pierdut ntr-nsul un om de merit rar,<text:line-break/>Prin alt moarte, moartea-i rscumprai-o dar;<text:line-break/>Jertfii nu pentru mine, pentru dreptate, sire,<text:line-break/>i pentru a coroanei etern strlucire,<text:line-break/>Jertfii spre uurarea acestei ri ntregi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Pe cel ce se mndrete cu-astfel de frdelegi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Don Diego ce rspunde?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>C-i demn de pizmuire</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Acela care moare la vremea lui, o, sire!<text:line-break/>C dup-un veac de slav i strlucire plin,<text:line-break/>Adeseaori ne-ateapt cel mai amar destin!<text:line-break/>Eu, ale crui fapte uimesc i azi poporul,<text:line-break/>Eu, care pretutindeni eram biruitorul,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">M vd, slbit de vrst, acum, cu prul nins,<text:line-break/>Primind o grea ocar i rmnnd nvins!<text:line-break/>Ce nu putuse lupt, asediu, ambuscad,<text:line-break/>Nici Aragonul mndru, nici falnica Grenad,<text:line-break/>Nici toi dumanii votri, nici toi ai mei pizmai,<text:line-break/>Azi contele-a fcut-o, de-aici la civa pai,<text:line-break/>Gelos de noua-mi slujb i drz de-o preferin<text:line-break/>Ce i-o dedea asupr-mi a vrstei neputin.<text:line-break/>Astfel aceste plete albite-n vitejii,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>st snge care curse ades spre-a v sluji,<text:line-break/>st bra pe vremi teroarea dumanelor armate<text:line-break/>Se coborau n groap de-ocar-mpovrate,<text:line-break/>De nu nteam pe lume un fiu spre-a m-ajuta,<text:line-break/>Demn de aceast ar, demn de mria-ta!<text:line-break/>El a ucis pe conte, lundu-mi aprarea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">El mi-a splat ocara, el mi-a redat onoarea!<text:line-break/>De socotii c totui e-un uciga de rnd<text:line-break/>Cel ce curaj arat o palm rzbunnd,<text:line-break/>Asupra mea s cad blestemul i pcatul,<text:line-break/>Cci de greete braul, e capul vinovatul!<text:line-break/>De e sau nu o crim, o, sire, judecai:<text:line-break/>Eu, oriicum, snt capul, el doar viteazul bra.<text:line-break/>Ximena mpotriv-mi deci are a se plnge,<text:line-break/>Cci de-o puteam eu face, el nu vrsa st snge.<text:line-break/>Jertfii, deci, sire, capul ce anii-l vor rpi,<text:line-break/>Dar ngrijii de braul menit a v sluji,<text:line-break/>Dreptate-i dai Ximenii jertfind zilele mele,<text:line-break/>C tot nu am ce face de-acuma eu cu ele;<text:line-break/>Departe de-a m plnge de-osnda ce mi-ai dat,<text:line-break/>Murind cinstit, muri-voi cu sufletu-mpcat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">fernandoPricina-i nsemnat de-ajuns spre-a o aduce<text:line-break/>n adunarea rii. Don Sancho, vei conduce<text:line-break/>Acas pe Ximena. Tu, don Diego, vei sta<text:line-break/>Aici, drept nchisoare avnd credina ta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Ctai-mi pe Rodrigo. Am s v fac dreptate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E drept ca ucigaul s piar, maiestate i</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8">Copil, ai rbdare, orict ai suferi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Rbdare-a-mi cere-nseamn durerile-a-mi spori.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTUL_III1"/>ACTUL III</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="Scena_I_31"/>Scena I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON RODRIGO, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Tu, don Rodrig! Ce caui aci, nenorocite?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Vin s-mi urmez crarea srmanei mele-ursite! elvira</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">De unde-i iei tu ns curajul, de-ai venit<text:line-break/>Pe locurile-acestea pe care le-ai cernit?<text:line-break/>i urmreti i umbra n casa lui, haine?<text:line-break/>Nu l-ai ucis tu nsui?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Viaa lui, tii bine, Era o pngrire a numelui ce-l port.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar adpost s caui n casa-acelui mort!<text:line-break/>Gsi azil ntr-nsa vreun uciga vreodat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Dar tocmai de aceea eu vin la judecat.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nu mai privi la mine cu aerul mirat:<text:line-break/>Eu moarte-am dat, i-acuma cer napoi ce-am dat.<text:line-break/>Ximena mea iubit mi e judectorul,<text:line-break/>i moartea mea o merit, cci i-am pierdut amorul.<text:line-break/>i ca supremul bine acuma vin s cer<text:line-break/>Din gura ei osnda, de mna ei s pier!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Mai bine fugi din fa-i i nu-i mai sta n cale,<text:line-break/>Nu mai chema asupra-i urgia urei sale:<text:line-break/>Te-ascunde i-ocolete ntiele porniri<text:line-break/>La care pot s-o-mping mnia ce-i inspiri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Nu! nu! aceast scump i ginga fptur<text:line-break/>Pe care am jignit-o nu are-atta ur,<text:line-break/>i snt n stare-o mie de mori s ocolesc,<text:line-break/>S pot s mor de mna-i i ura-i s-o-nzecesc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Ximena e la Curte, n lacrime scldat,<text:line-break/>i va veni-nsoit de-amicii si ndat.<text:line-break/>O, fugi, Rodrig, ai mil: nu m mai chinui!<text:line-break/>Ce-or spune brfitorii de te-or vedea aici?<text:line-break/>Vrei tu s fie nc i-n gura lumii dat<text:line-break/>C rabd pe-ucigaul srmanului ei tat?<text:line-break/>Are s vin, vine, o vd. O, dac vrei<text:line-break/>S-i crui, Rodrig, onoarea, te du n calea ei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21">(RODRIG se ascunde.)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_II-a_3"/>SCENA a II-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON SANCHO, XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>V trebuie, senora, prinos bogat de snge:<text:line-break/>Mnia voastr-i dreapt i-avei dreptate-a plnge,<text:line-break/>i prin aceste vorbe nu vreau ct de puin<text:line-break/>Nici s v-nduplec ura, nici chinul s v-alin.<text:line-break/>Ci gura voastr numai o vorb de mi-ar spune,<text:line-break/>Aceast spad-i gata oricnd s v rzbune.<text:line-break/>O, punei la-ncercare, de vrei, al meu amor<text:line-break/>i, sub porunca voastr, voi fi biruitor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Vai mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>ndurare, primii, din buntate</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>A mnia pe rege, ce mi-a promis dreptate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>tii c dreptatea merge cu-attea aminri,<text:line-break/>nct o crim scap ades fr de urmri,<text:line-break/>i pn-atuncea lacrimi prea multe snt pierdute,<text:line-break/>Un cavaler prin arme v-ar rzbuna mai iute.<text:line-break/>E-un drum mai scurt, i-osnda n-ar mai ntrzia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>E leacul cel din urm; dar de va fi aa<text:line-break/>i dac trista-mi soart v-ar mai strni-ndurarea,<text:line-break/>Atuncea vei fi liber s-mi rzbunai onoarea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>E un noroc la care rvnesc necontenit<text:line-break/>i avnd ndejde-ntr-nsul, m duc prea mulumit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_III-a_3"/><text:soft-page-break/>SCENA a III-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Snt singur acuma i fr frie<text:line-break/>mi pot striga ntreag durerea mea cea vie!<text:line-break/>Acuma pot n voie s plng i s suspin,<text:line-break/>i pot s-mi dau pe fa nemrginitul chin.<text:line-break/>Vai, tata-i mort, Elvir, i viaa-i e curmat<text:line-break/>De spada ce Rodrigo o trage-ntia dat!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, curgei, curgei, lacrimi, praie pe pmnt:<text:line-break/>O jumtate-a vieii-mi mi-arunc n mormnt<text:line-break/>Cealalt jumtate, i-aceea care piere<text:line-break/>Pe-aceea ce-mi rmne s m rzbun mi cere.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Alin-te, stpn!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ah, ce nepotrivit<text:line-break/>Cuvntul de-alinare pe buze i-a venit!<text:line-break/>Cum s-mi alin durerea cnd eu, nesocotito,<text:line-break/>Nu pot ur pe-acela ce mi-a pricinuit-o?<text:line-break/>i ce m-ateapt oare dect un venic chin.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd urmresc o crim iubind pe asasin?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mai poi iubi pe-acela ce te-a lsat orfan?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Dac-l iubesc, Elviro? L-ador ca pe-o icoan!<text:line-break/>Iubirea i mnia n suflet mi se bat,<text:line-break/>i n duman descopr pe omul adorat<text:line-break/>i simt c-n ciuda urei n inima-mi speriat<text:line-break/>Rodrig combate nc, ah, pe srmanu-mi tat:<text:line-break/>L-atac, l-urmrete, se apr i-i cnd<text:line-break/>Mai slab cnd mai puternic, i-acuma triumfnd,<text:line-break/>i-n lupta aceasta ntre iubire i mnie<text:line-break/>El sufletul mi-l las, dar inima-mi sfie.<text:line-break/>Dar nu m-adoarme-amorul, orict m-ar stpni,<text:line-break/>i datoria-mi sfnt mi-o voi ndeplini;<text:line-break/>Alerg unde m cheam jignita mea onoare.<text:line-break/>Rodrig mi-e scump, i soarta-i nespus de-adnc m doare,<text:line-break/>i plng de jale, totui, orict grij-i port,<text:line-break/>tiu cine snt, Elviro, i tatl meu e mort!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>l urmreti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12">Ah! crud gndire i cumplit<text:line-break/>i crud urmrire la care snt silit!<text:line-break/>Cer capul su i totui m tem s-l dobndesc!<text:line-break/>De moare el, muri-voi i moartea i-o ceresc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Att de negre gnduri, alung-le, stpn,<text:line-break/>i nu-i impune-o lege ce-n contra ta te mn!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum? Tatl meu s aib sfrit aa de crud,<text:line-break/>S strige rzbunare i eu s nu-l aud?<text:line-break/>S-l vd murind sub ochii-mi i inima-mi ntng<text:line-break/>S cread c-i ajunge s geam ori s plng?<text:line-break/>S sufr ca iubirea s-nbue cum vrea<text:line-break/>Prin o tcere la mndria, cinstea mea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, crede-m, stpn, n-ar fi prea mare vin<text:line-break/>De-ai resimi n suflet mnie mai puin;<text:line-break/>n contra lui Rodrigo ai dobndit de-ajuns,<text:line-break/>Ai fost la rege, ateapt n linite rspuns.<text:line-break/>Nu strui-n aceast ciudat suprare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mi-e-n joc mndria-ntreag, ea-mi cere rzbunare!<text:line-break/>Dulci visuri de iubire orict m-ademenesc,<text:line-break/>Renun la tot mai bine dect s m-njosesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Dar l iubeti, senora, pe don Rodrig</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Vai mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>i rzbunarea totui mai poate s te-mbie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ca s-mi pstrez mndria, sfrind i chinul meu<text:line-break/>L-oi urmri, l-oi pierde, i voi muri i eu!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_IV-a_3"/>SCENA a IV-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON RODRIGO, XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ei bine, urmritul privete-l e de fa,<text:line-break/>A ta s fie slava de-a-l izgoni din via!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>O, ce snt eu silit, Elviro, a vedea?<text:line-break/>Rodrig la mine-n cas! Rodrig n faa mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ucide-m, Ximen, i gust fr jale<text:line-break/>Plcerea morii mele i-a rzbunrii tale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Vai mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO O, ascult!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P27"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Fugi, las-m s mor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O clip.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Du-te!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Numai o vorb, te implor, i-apoi cu-aceast spad viaa tu mi-o stnge.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum? ncruntat nc de-al tatlui meu snge?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ximen!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Fugi cu arma ce, vai, n faa mea<text:line-break/>M mustr pentru viaa i frdelegea ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu, mai curnd privind-o, mni ta sporeasc,<text:line-break/>i ceasul morii mele s nu mai zboveasc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Vopsit e de snge de-al meu!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i vine greu<text:line-break/>S o scufunzi, s-i piard culoarea ntr-al meu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Om crud care pe tat l-ucide fr mil</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Prin spad,  prin vederea ei crunt pe copil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">nltur-mi aceast unealt de omor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vrei s te-ascult, Rodrigo, i tu m faci s mor</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Fac ce doreti, dar totui nu prsesc dorina<text:line-break/>C nsi tu, Ximen, s-mi mplineti sentina.<text:line-break/>Cci orict mi-eti de drag, un la nu pot s fiu<text:line-break/>Ca s reneg vreodat chemarea mea de fiu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pe tatl meu czuse o groaznic ruine,<text:line-break/>Ce m privea-n aceeai msur i pe mine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">tii ce-nsemneaz-o palm pentru un om cinstit.<text:line-break/>Am cutat s aflu fptaul, l-am gsit,<text:line-break/>Am rzbunat onoarea-mi i pe iubitu-mi tat.<text:line-break/>i dac-ar fi nevoie a face-o nc-o dat.<text:line-break/>Nu crede c iubirea-mi n-a dus o lupt grea</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cu tatl meu i-n urm chiar mpotriva mea!<text:line-break/>O, judec-i puterea: aflnd c-am fost n stare<text:line-break/>S m-ndoiesc de poate s-ncap rzbunare.<text:line-break/>Silit s-ndur ocara ori, vai! dispreul tu,<text:line-break/>nvinuiam de-o grab prea mare braul meu;<text:line-break/>M dojeneam de-aceast pornire prea nebun<text:line-break/>i farmecele tale erau s m supun<text:line-break/>De nu-mi ziceam, Ximen, c nu te-ar merita,<text:line-break/>Un om lipsit de-onoare, lipsit de stima ta!<text:line-break/>C ochii ti iubirea i-ar fi schimbat-o-n ur<text:line-break/>Vznd miel pe-acela ce vrednic l tiur;<text:line-break/>C ascultnd amorul, urmnd al su ndemn,<text:line-break/>De-alegererea ta nsi m-a fi fcut nedemn.<text:line-break/>i-o spun din nou, i-oi spune-o, dei printre suspine,<text:line-break/>Pn la cel din urm: da, te-am jignit pe tine;<text:line-break/>Da, te-am jignit amarnic, fiind silit s-o fac<text:line-break/>Pe tine s te merit i-onoarea s mi-o-mpac.<text:line-break/>Mi-am mpcat onoarea i pe btrnul tat;<text:line-break/>Viu s te-mpac pe tine acuma, adorat.<text:line-break/>Am alergat aicea de mna ta s mor;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ce-am fost dator fcut-am i fac ce snt dator.<text:line-break/>Un tat scump te strig din fundul negrei groape<text:line-break/>i eu nu vreau victima cu nici un pre s-i scape:<text:line-break/>Jertfete-acestui snge pe care l-a pierdut<text:line-break/>Acel ce se mndrete cu ceea ce-a fcut!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Rodrig, ah, ai dreptate, cu toat vrjmia<text:line-break/>Nu pot blama pe-acela ce-i face datoria.<text:line-break/>i-n chinurile mele ce-asupra-i s rsfrng,<text:line-break/>Eu nu te-acuz pe tine, pe mine m deplng:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">tiu ce se cheam cinste si cum nflcreaz</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Asemenea insult o inim viteaz,<text:line-break/>Tu n-ai fcut, firete, dect ce se cdea,<text:line-break/>Dar mi-artai de-asemeni i datoria mea;<text:line-break/>Funesta-i vitejie mi-arat prin avntu-i</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cum i rzbuni un tat i-onoarea cum i-o mntui<text:line-break/>Aceeai rvn cat la rndul meu s pun<text:line-break/>Onoarea s mi-o mntui, pe tata s-l rzbun.<text:line-break/>Aceasta, vai, m face s fiu nemngiiat!<text:line-break/>O alt mn dac m-ar fi lipsit de tat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Gseam, ah, n norocul dorit de-a te vedea<text:line-break/>Unica alinare ce-o mai puteam avea;<text:line-break/>i-a fi simit un farmec n jalea mea cumplit<text:line-break/>S-mi zvni aceste lacrimi cu mna ta iubit.<text:line-break/>Ci caut a te pierde, cum l-am pierdut pe el,<text:line-break/>Aceast desprire m zbucium la fel:<text:line-break/>Cumplita datorie ce inima mi-o rumpe<text:line-break/>M-mpinge la jertfirea vieii tale scumpe,<text:line-break/>Cci orict in la tine, Rodrig, nu atepta<text:line-break/>S simt o la mil fa de crima ta.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>i-orict iubirea noastr ar vrea s m reie,<text:line-break/>Voi ti s dau dovad de-aceeai brbie:<text:line-break/>Ca s fii demn de mine, tu n-ai dat ndrt,<text:line-break/>La rndul meu vreau demn de tine s m-art.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu pregeta atuncea s faci ce eti datoare<text:line-break/>Spre-a mplini o jertf att de-nltoare!<text:line-break/>Mndria ta mi cere viaa  vin i-o ia!<text:line-break/>Osnda-mi va fi dulce i dulce moartea meal<text:line-break/>S-atepi pn ce legea i va rosti sentina,<text:line-break/>E s-mi ntrzii moartea i ie biruina.<text:line-break/>Prea fericit muri-voi, rpus de braul tu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Taci, dac-i snt duman, nu vreau s-i fiu clu<text:line-break/>Eu s-i ridic viaa, e cu putin oare?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dator eti s i-o aperi, s-o cer eu sunt datoare,<text:line-break/>Dar ntre noi e altul judector suprem,<text:line-break/>i eu am numai dreptul n fa-i s te chem.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Orict iubirea noastr ar vrea s te reie,<text:line-break/>Vei da i tu dovad de-aceeai brbie.<text:line-break/>Cci, rzbunnd un tat, alt bra dac-mprumui,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ximena mea, m crede, nsamn s m crui.<text:line-break/>Cum braul meu el singur mi-a rzbunat onoarea,<text:line-break/>Al tu s-i dobndeasc la rndu-i rzbunarea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Rodrig, la ce mai strui? Tu ajutor nu ceri<text:line-break/>Cnd te rzbuni, la nimeni, i mie mi-l oferi!<text:line-break/>Sunt tot aa de mndr i cred c se cuvine<text:line-break/>Ca slava rzbunrii s n-o mpart cu tine.<text:line-break/>Deci ajutor la rndu-mi nici eu nu voi cta<text:line-break/>n dezndjduirea sau n iubirea ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Mindrie nenfrntl vai! s nu pot obine<text:line-break/>Atta mngiere ncale de la tine!?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n numele iubirii i-al tatlui tu mort,<text:line-break/>Nu m lsa blestemul acestei viei s-l port!<text:line-break/>Mai vesel e Rodrigo de mna ta s piar<text:line-break/>Dect urt de tine, trind o via-amar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu te ursc eu, las!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Oh, trebuie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu pot.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Aa puin i pas de lume i de tot<text:line-break/>Ce poate s scorneasc n umbr clevetirea<text:line-break/>Cnd va s-mi tie crima i c-mi pstrezi iubirea?<text:line-break/>Silete-le s tac i n pofida lor</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Salveaz-i bunul nume, fcndu-m s mor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Lsndu-i viaa, vaza mi va luci mai vie;<text:line-break/>Vreau ca i cel din urm clevetitor s tie<text:line-break/>C te ador i totui pedeapsa ta o cer,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i toi s-mi cnte imnuri de slav pn la cer<text:line-break/>i soarta s-mi deplng Rodrig, acuma du-te,<text:line-break/>S nu mai vd comoara de fericiri pierdute<text:line-break/>Ascunde-n umbra nopii plecarea ta de-aci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Onoarea mea-i pierdut cumva de te-or zri.<text:line-break/>Tot ce-ar putea brfeala s zic despre mine<text:line-break/>E c-n aceast cas eu te-am primit pe tine<text:line-break/>i ca s fiu hulit nici tu nu o doreti</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A vrea s mor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vai, du-te!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Atunci, ce hotrti?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Dei cea mai frumoas vpaie amenin<text:line-break/>S-mi mistuie mnia, fac tot ce-mi st-n putin<text:line-break/>Ca s rzbun pe tata, mndria s mi-o-mpac<text:line-break/>i singura-mi dorin e s nu pot s-o fac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, vraj a iubirii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, culme-a suferinii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce de dureri i lacrimi ne vor costa prinii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, te-ateptai, Rodrigo?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ximen,-ai fi crezut?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Aa curnd norocul s ni-l vedem pierdut!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i c aa de-aproape de rm a fost s vie<text:line-break/>Ndejdea s ne-o sfarme o crunt vijelie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, jale fr margini!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, chin aa de mult!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Rodrig, de-acuma du-te, fugi nu te mai ascult!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pn la sfrit cnd dreapta osind mi-oi primi-o,<text:line-break/>Merg s-mi trsc o via nemernic Adio!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>De-o fi aa s fie, i dau cuvntul meu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">C-n urma ta o clip n-am s respir nici eu.<text:line-break/>Adio, dar ia sama s pleci pe nesimite</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">(RODRIG exit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Stpn, orice rele Preabunul ni trimite</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>O, las-m n pace cu sfatul tu ntng<text:line-break/>M duc s caut pacea i noaptea, ca s plng.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_V-a_3"/>SCENA a V-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON DIEGO (singur)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>n veci nu simi pe lume deplin desftarea;<text:line-break/>n orice bucurie s-amestec-ntristarea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i cele mai senine a noastre mulmiri<text:line-break/>Ni-s venic turburate de griji i-nchipuiri.<text:line-break/>O grij bucuria mi-o stric-n ast-sear:<text:line-break/>not n fericire i spaima m-nfioar.<text:line-break/>Vzui mort pe dumanul ce-onoarea mi-a ptat,<text:line-break/>i nu pot strnge mna care m-a rzbunat.<text:line-break/>Cutreier tot oraul, m zbucium n netire,<text:line-break/>i vlaga mult-puin ce mi-a rmas n fire<text:line-break/>Se mistuie zadarnic de trud i necaz,<text:line-break/>Ctnd fr de preget pe fiul meu viteaz.<text:line-break/>Mereu i pretutindeni, n noaptea asta sumbr<text:line-break/>Socot c-l strng n brae, i strng n brae-o umbr<text:line-break/>i mintea-mi tulburat, din vis cnd m trezesc,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i face mii de gnduri ce groaza mi-o sporesc.<text:line-break/>Nu aflu nicirea vreo urm-a fugii sale;<text:line-break/>M tem c, cine tie, i-or fi ieit n cale<text:line-break/>Cetaii ori amicii dumanului ucis:<text:line-break/>Rodrig nu mai triete sau poate zace-nchis<text:line-break/>O, ceruri! m-amgete i-acuma o prere<text:line-break/>Sau vd tot ce-al meu suflet ca s mai vad cere?<text:line-break/>El e, fr-ndoial; mi-e sufletu-mpcat<text:line-break/>i grija risipit i chinul mi-a-ncetat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_VI-a_2"/>SCENA a VI-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON DIEGO, DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rodrig, mi-ajut cerul s te revd n fine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Vai!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>n triumful nostru n-amesteca suspine.<text:line-break/>O, las-m o clip mcar s mai respir,<text:line-break/>S pot s-i laud fapta aa cum i-o admiri<text:line-break/>Tu mi-ai clcat pe urm, i-n tine renvie<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Eroii rasei mele i vechea-mi brbie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nscndu-te din mine, din ei cobortor,<text:line-break/>ntiia ta isprav ntrece pe-ale lor,<text:line-break/>i anii ti cei tineri, dar plini de-nflcrare<text:line-break/>Ajung al meu renume prin fapta asta mare.<text:line-break/>O, vino dar i-atinge, copilul meu viteaz,<text:line-break/>Aceste plete albe, srut-acest obraz<text:line-break/>i recunoate locul ntiprit de-ocar<text:line-break/>Pe care vitejia-i i spada-i o splar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>A ta e toat cinstea; eu nu puteam uita<text:line-break/>C snt nscut din tine, crescut prin grija ta.<text:line-break/>Snt mndru c ntiia isprav-a mea ii place<text:line-break/>Cui datoresc viaa. Ci bucur-te-n pace,<text:line-break/>i las-m pe mine acum, la rndul meu,<text:line-break/>De psurile mele s-mi vd acum i eu,<text:line-break/>O, las s-mi izbucneasc nemrginita jale:<text:line-break/>Destul ai stnjenit-o cu drepturile tale!<text:line-break/>Nu simt mustrri de cuget de ceea ce-am fcut,<text:line-break/>Dar cine-mi d azi mie norocul meu pierdut?<text:line-break/>S te rzbune brau-mi s-a narmat anume<text:line-break/>i-a biruit, rpindu-mi ce-aveam mai scump pe lume<text:line-break/>Nu-mi mai vorbi nimica; prin tot ce i-am jertfit<text:line-break/>De tot ce-i datorisem m cred acum pltit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu, a izbndei tale mai scump e valoarea!<text:line-break/>Eu viaa doar i-am dat-o, tu mi-ai redat onoarea;<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mai mult dect la via eu la onoare in,<text:line-break/>Cu-att mai mult deci ie datornic i rmn.<text:line-break/>Dar deprteaz jalea din sufletul tu mare:<text:line-break/>Onoarea-i datorie, amorul  desftare;<text:line-break/>Onoarea-i numai una; amorurile  mii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce-mi spui tu, vai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Aceea ce trebuie s tii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mi-e inima zdrobit de-aceast rzbunare<text:line-break/>i tu-i mai ceri iubirii s fie trdtoare?<text:line-break/>Snt tot aa de josnici, n mielia lor,<text:line-break/>Rzboinicul ce fuge i-amantul trdtor.<text:line-break/>O, las-m mai bine cum snt, avnd putina<text:line-break/>S fiu i demn de tine i s-mi pstrez credina.<text:line-break/>E prea puternic lanul spre a putea s-l rump;<text:line-break/>Ximena mea pe lume e tot ce am mai scump,<text:line-break/>i pentru c ursita cea crud ne desparte,<text:line-break/>Unica mntuire mi-o voi gsi-o-n moarte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Nu-i vreme mntuire n moarte-a cuta,<text:line-break/>Acum cnd e nevoie de brbia ta.<text:line-break/>A maurilor flot st gata de nval.<text:line-break/>Norodu-i plin de groaz, la curte zpceal,<text:line-break/>N-auzi dect jlanii la fiecare pas,<text:line-break/>De bun sam fluxul, la noapte, peste-un ceas;<text:line-break/>i va lsa pe mauri n port pe nesimite,<text:line-break/>n mijlocul acestor nenorociri cumplite<text:line-break/>Cari umplu de teroare pe mari ca i pe mici,<text:line-break/>Norocul mi trimise cinci sute de amici<text:line-break/>nsufleii cu toii de-aceleai gnduri bune,<text:line-break/>Venind de bunvoie ocara s-mi rzbune.<text:line-break/>Tu le-ai luat nainte; dar bravele lor mni<text:line-break/>Se vor sclda mai bine n snge de pgni.<text:line-break/>Mergi dar acolo unde te-ateapt numai slav,<text:line-break/>Mergi i-i condu n lupt, fcnd fr zbav<text:line-break/>Din pieptul tu, n calea pgnilor, zgaz:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De vrei s mori, ncale s mori ca un viteaz!<text:line-break/>F regele s-i fie dator pierzrii tale,<text:line-break/>Viaa sa i slava mpriei sale.<text:line-break/>Dar nu, mai bine fruntea-i cu lauri s-o-ncununi.<text:line-break/>Nu-i mrgeni mrirea o palm s rzbuni;<text:line-break/>Ci du-o mai departe; silete prin putere<text:line-break/>Pe rege la iertare, Ximena la tcere;<text:line-break/>i dac-i este drag Ximena ta, s tii<text:line-break/>C doar pe calea asta mai poi iertat s fii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar prea e scump vremea s-o pierdem n cuvinte<text:line-break/>A vrea s zbori la lupt c-un ceas mai nainte.<text:line-break/>nvinge dar, s vad monarhul n sfrit<text:line-break/>C ce-a pierdut n conte n tine-a dobndit!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTUL_IV"/>ACTUL IV</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_I_4"/>SCENA I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu este un zvon numai? tii bine tu, Elvir?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nici nu-i nchipui lumea ce clduros l-admir<text:line-break/>i-nal pn la ceruri n repetat ecou<text:line-break/>Isprava svrit de tnrul erou.<text:line-break/>A maurilor oaste e ruinos zdrobit:<text:line-break/>Grbit i-a fost atacul, i fuga mai grbit.<text:line-break/>Rzboinicilor notri nici chiar trei ore-ntregi<text:line-break/>Le deter izbnd i prizonieri doi regi<text:line-break/>Iar meritul e numai al lui, pe ct se spune!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum, braul lui Rodrigo fcu aa minune?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Pe-aceti doi regi, Rodrigo el singur i-a nvins<text:line-break/>Cu mna sa: el singur cu mna sa i-a prins.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>De unde-aflai tu ns aceste zvonuri stranii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Oraul tot rsun de imnuri i litanii,<text:line-break/>Numindu-l fericirea ntregului popor<text:line-break/>i ngeru-i de paz i-al su liberator.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i regele ce spune de-atta vitejie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Rodrig se teme nc n faa lui s vie.<text:line-break/>Don Diego ns vesel i-aduce-nctuai<text:line-break/>Ca s-i nfieze pe robii-ncoronai,<text:line-break/>Cernd mriei sale, ca o favoare rar,<text:line-break/>S vad pe viteazul mntuitor de ar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>N-o fi rnit? Ci spune!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Nu tiu dac-i rnit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar vino-i n simire! Cum te-ai nglbenii</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Mnia mea slbit de-asemenea-mi revine!<text:line-break/>S m-ngrijesc de dnsul i s m uit pe minei<text:line-break/>Toi l nal-n slav i eu l-nal cu eil<text:line-break/>Mndria mea-i uitat i mut e glasul eil<text:line-break/>Taci, inim srman, i-nbuete-i plnsul:<text:line-break/>De-a-nvins doi regi, pe tatl mi l-a ucis tot dnsul,<text:line-break/>i-oricte osanale mi sun n auz,<text:line-break/>Aice ns totul m face s-l acuz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Aceast hain trist ce spune neagra-mi jale<text:line-break/>E cea dinti dovad a vitejiei sale.<text:line-break/>Voi, ce-ntrii un suflet muncit de ndoieli,<text:line-break/>Zbranice i vluri, lugubrelor gteli,<text:line-break/>Podoab ce ntia izbnd-a sa-mi prescrie,<text:line-break/>Necontenit vorbii-mi de trista-mi datorie,<text:line-break/>i cnd mnia-n mine va lncezi din nou,<text:line-break/>Asmutei-o-mpotriva semeului erou!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Silii-o ca s-mi duc la capt rzbunarea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Infanta iat-o, vine; alin-i suprarea.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_II-a_4"/>SCENA a II-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">INFANTA, XIMENA, LEONORA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu viu aici, Ximen, durerea s-i alin,<text:line-break/>Ci ca s plng cu tine, cu tine s suspin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>mprtii mai bine obteasca bucurie,<text:line-break/>Lsndu-mi suprarea i lacrimile mie:<text:line-break/>Azi cine alta-n lume se poate tngui?<text:line-break/>Primejdia din care Rodrig ne mntui<text:line-break/>i pacea datorit doar vitejiei sale<text:line-break/>Snt numai pentru mine prilej de-adnc jale.<text:line-break/>Da, braul su puternic, de lume preaslvit<text:line-break/>E numai pentru mine funest i urgisit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>A svrit, Ximeno, minuni fr preche.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Suprtoarea veste mi-ajunse la ureche<text:line-break/>i laude rsun n gura tuturor<text:line-break/>De marea-i vitejie i tristul su amor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Te superi c poporul de laude-l ncarc?<text:line-break/>Dar i-era drag pe vremuri acest Rodrigo, parc,<text:line-break/>i tu-i erai lui drag i el i-era supus <text:line-break/>Poi s te simi dar mndr c-l vezi aa de sus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>S-l ridicai n slav uor v este, vou,<text:line-break/>Dar pentru mine-i venic o suferin nou<text:line-break/>Aceast preamrire a vitejiei lui:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vznd ct preuiete, vd astzi ce pierdui!<text:line-break/>Ah, neplceri amare a celei ce iubete!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cu ct l vd mai vrednic, cu-att iubirea-mi crete,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i totui datoria ce-o am, s m rzbun,<text:line-break/>Mai tare-i ca iubirea i-mi cere s-l rpun.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ieri datoria-aceasta fcu pe toi curtenii<text:line-break/>Ca s admire marea virtute a Ximenii<text:line-break/>i s-i deplng soarta, aa li s-a prut<text:line-break/>De-nltor curajul pe care l-ai avut.<text:line-break/>Dar vreai s-asculi tu sfatul unei amice bune?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>A fi nelegiuit de nu i m-a supune.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ce-a fost ieri nu mai este ndreptit i azi.<text:line-break/>Al nostru singur sprijin e-acum acest viteaz,<text:line-break/>El e-adoratul rii, srbtoritul zilii,<text:line-break/>A maurilor spaim i razemul Castilii.<text:line-break/>Chiar bunul nostru rege e azi ncredinat<text:line-break/>C tatl tu n mndrul Rodrig e renviat,<text:line-break/>i cu att i este greeala ta mai mare<text:line-break/>C urmreti prin moarte-i a statului pierzare.<text:line-break/>Ca s-i rzbuni un tat, cum? crezi c e permis<text:line-break/>S-mpingi o ar-ntreag pe margini de abis?<text:line-break/>Dar ctre noi purtarea-i e oare legitim?<text:line-break/>Luat-am oare parte i noi ceilali la crim?<text:line-break/>De bun sam-n urma acestui trist duel<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Nu te silete nimeni s te cununi cu el,<text:line-break/>Ci dac vreai, Ximen, s-asculi a mea pova:<text:line-break/>Din inim-i alung-l, dar las-ni-l n via!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Atita buntate, vai! eu nu pot avea:<text:line-break/>Cu mult mai nendurat e datoria mea.<text:line-break/>Dei la el mi-e gndul n fiecare or,<text:line-break/>Dei-l rsfa-un rege i un popor l-ador,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Toi strluciii lauri ce-i pun pe frunte ei,<text:line-break/>Eu vin ca s-i ntunec sub chiparoii mei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Da, e frumos, e nobil atuncea cnd, in dorul<text:line-break/>De-a-i rzbuna un tat, tii s-i jertfeti amorul,<text:line-break/>Dar crede-m c-i nc mai nobil, mai frumos<text:line-break/>S te jertfeti de dragul obtescului folos.<text:line-break/>Lipsindu-l de iubirea ce-i artai odat,<text:line-break/>E cea mai grea pedeaps ce-i poate fi lui dat.<text:line-break/>n joc e mntuirea ntregii-mprii:<text:line-break/>i-apoi chiar de la rege ce crezi s mai obii?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu pot s m astmpr chiar de nu-mi d dreptate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Gndete-te mai bine, Ximena mea, la toate.<text:line-break/>Adio; ca s cugei n tihn-acum te las.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Voi asculta, prines, al datoriei glas.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_III-a_4"/>SCENA a III-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON ARIAS, DON RODRIGO, DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Urma viteaz i nobil al unei vechi familii<text:line-break/>Ce-a fost un stlp statornic al falnicei Castilii,<text:line-break/>Neam de strmoi ilutri cu glorios trecut<text:line-break/>Pe care la-ntiul tu pas l-ai ntrecut.<text:line-break/>Oriice dar din parte-mi prea mic i prea puin e<text:line-break/>Spre-a-i rsplti izbnda aa cum se cuvine.<text:line-break/>Pmntul rii mele de prdciuni ferit,<text:line-break/>i sceptrul meu de tine n mna-mi ntrit,<text:line-break/>i maurii-n risip gonii de mica-i ceat,<text:line-break/>Nainte s porneasc viteaza mea armat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nu sunt isprvi de care m pot plti aa<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Precum mi-ar fi dorina i cum ar merita.<text:line-break/>Rsplata-i fie regii captivi cari te admir:<text:line-break/>Ei Cidul lor pe tine n fa-mi te numir,<text:line-break/>i dac Cid nsamn stpn pe limba lor,<text:line-break/>Nu-i pizmuiesc un nume aa de suntor.<text:line-break/>Fii Cidul deci de-acuma: l-a numelui tu faim<text:line-break/>Grenada i Toledo s tremure de spaim,<text:line-break/>i numele acesta s-arate tuturor<text:line-break/>Ct pre pun eu pe tine i tot ce-i snt dator.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>n faa voastr, sire, m simt plin de sfial,<text:line-break/>Isprava mi-e prea mic i-i dai prea mult fal,<text:line-break/>i laudele voastre m fac s m roesc<text:line-break/>C nu-s destul de vrednic de cinstea ce-o primesc.<text:line-break/>tiu c-s dator cu viaa i sngele din vine<text:line-break/>S m jertfesc, o sire, spre-al rii voastre bine,<text:line-break/>i-n lupta-aceasta sfnt de voi cdea rpus,<text:line-break/>mi fac doar datoria ca oriice supus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Toi cari se strng n juru-mi, chemai de datorie,<text:line-break/>Nu i-o-mplinesc cu-atta avnt i brbie,<text:line-break/>i dac tu ca dnii te mrgineai s fii,<text:line-break/>-ai fi putut atare izbnd s obii.<text:line-break/>Deci lauda primete-o i spune-mi pe-ndelete<text:line-break/>Povestea biruinei vitezei tale cete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>tii sire, c n spaima ntiului minut,<text:line-break/>La vestea c pgnii la pori au aprut,<text:line-break/>Cinci sute de prieteni la noi se adunar<text:line-break/>i-n starea-mi tulburat de ef m proclamar.<text:line-break/>Iertai-mi graba dac n zbuciumul de-atunci,<text:line-break/>Din partea voastr, sire, n-am ateptat porunci,<text:line-break/>Din pricina primejdii prea mari i-a vremei scurte:<text:line-break/>Dar mi riscam viaa de m-artam la Curte,<text:line-break/>i viaa-mi osndit mi-era mai dulce-apoi<text:line-break/>S-o pierd n chip mai vrednic n lupta pentru voi:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ii iert fireasca prip de-a-i rzbuna ocara:<text:line-break/>Precum ai aprat-o, te apr-acum ara:<text:line-break/>S te acuze poate Ximena ct de mult,<text:line-break/>Ca s-o mngi doar numai de-acum am s-o ascult.<text:line-break/>Dar spune mai departe.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Sub mine-nainteaz<text:line-break/>st plc, purtnd pe frunte a brbiei raz.<text:line-break/>Eram cinci sute numai, dar pn am venit<text:line-break/>n port, ca prin minune, trei mii ne-am pomenit,<text:line-break/>Aa de mult a noastr semea-nfiare<text:line-break/>Redetepta curajul n gloatele fugare!<text:line-break/>Ascund ndat dou treimi, cum am sosit,<text:line-break/>n vasele pe care acolo le-am gsit,<text:line-break/>i restul cetei care cretea din clip-n clip,<text:line-break/>Arznd de nerbdare, n juru-mi se-nfirip,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Se culc jos, i-n paza celei mai mari tceri<text:line-break/>Petrece-o bun parte a minunatei seri.<text:line-break/>Din ordinul meu streaja se face nevzut<text:line-break/>La rndul ei, i planul ea astfel mi-l ajut<text:line-break/>i plin de ndrzneal eu m prefac c am<text:line-break/>Din partea voastr, sire, lozinca ce-o dedeam<text:line-break/>Sub palida lumin ce picur din stele<text:line-break/>Spre noi, de flux aduse, vin treizeci de vintrele;<text:line-break/>Le salt ap-n spume i c-un obtesc avnt<text:line-break/>i maurii i marea n port acuma snt.<text:line-break/>Noi i lsm s treac; n pace tot le pare;<text:line-break/>Nici un soldat pe ziduri i nici n port n-apare,<text:line-break/>i de tcerea noastr viclean, amgii<text:line-break/>Nici nu le vine-a crede c snt primejduii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">La rm trag, ancoreaz, coboar i se-ndreapt<text:line-break/>Netemtori, de-a valma, n cursa ce-i ateapt.<text:line-break/>Noi nvlim atuncea c-un chiotit prelung<text:line-break/>i strigtele noastre pn la cer ajung.<text:line-break/>La rcnetul navalei rspund cei din corbii<text:line-break/>i maurii-i pierd capul, mpresurai de sbii!<text:line-break/>De-o groaza fr margini cuprini, dau napoi:<text:line-break/>Ei alergau la prad i ntlnind rzboi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Pierdui se cred nainte ca lupta s nceap:<text:line-break/>i prididim pe rmuri, i prididim pe ap,<text:line-break/>Rzbindu-i fr preget n groaznic vlmag,<text:line-break/>i nu apuc bine s-ncbege un irag,<text:line-break/>C pn s s-aeze n linie de btaie<text:line-break/>Noi facem snge maur s gilgie-n iroaie!<text:line-break/>Dar principii lor totui s-i strng reuesc,<text:line-break/>Curajul lor renate i-acum se rnduiesc;<text:line-break/>Vznd c fr lupt snt osndii pierzrii,<text:line-break/>ntr-nii se deteapt curajul desperrii:<text:line-break/>S-opresc pe loc i drumul acuma ni-l nchid,<text:line-break/>Fcnd n contra noastr din iatagane-un zid,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i apa, i uscatul, i flota, schela toat<text:line-break/>Se schimb-ntr-o imens aren-nsngerat,<text:line-break/>Pe care duhul morii se-ntinde-atotstpn<text:line-break/>O, ci eroi de-ai notri necunoscui rmn,<text:line-break/>i ce isprvi mree, ce strlucite fapte<text:line-break/>Rmn nvluite pe veci n neagra noapte,<text:line-break/>n care, martor siei, tot insul se lupta<text:line-break/>Nebnuind izbnda de partea cui va sta!<text:line-break/>Eu nsumi pretutindeni pe-ai notri ndemnndu-i,<text:line-break/>mbrbtam pe unii, pe alii stam s-i rndui,<text:line-break/>Ca s-i reped n lupt cnd vremea le-a veni,<text:line-break/>i n-am tiut nimica pn n zori de zi.<text:line-break/>Ele ne-arat-n fine ai biruinii lauri<text:line-break/>Atunci i pierd curajul nfricoaii mauri<text:line-break/>i dorul de-a nvinge cedeaz spaimei lor<text:line-break/>Cnd desluesc c trupe ne vin ntr-ajutor;<text:line-break/>S-arunc in corbii, odgoanele le taie<text:line-break/>i fug cu huiet mare din cmpul de btaie,<text:line-break/>Nemaivoind s tie aceti ostai miei<text:line-break/>De pot s se retrag i regii lor cu ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nu simul datoriei, ci groaza-i stpnete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i adusese fluxul, refluxul ni-i rpete!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n vremea asta regii, de-ai notri npdii,<text:line-break/>i aprai de-o seam de oameni, toi rnii,<text:line-break/>Mai lupt, cu ndejdea s-i vnd viaa bine<text:line-break/>Zadarnic le dau sfatul eu nsumi s se-nchine:<text:line-break/>Cu iataganu-n mn, ei stau ne-nduplecai;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar cnd i vd ostaii de moarte secerai,<text:line-break/>C singuri se mai lupt, c-nfrngerea-i deplin<text:line-break/>Ei cer s vin eful: m-art, i mi se-nchin.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vi i-am trimis ndat aici, pe amndoi<text:line-break/>Aa-ncet i lupta din lips de eroi,<text:line-break/>i-n felu-acesta, sire, luptnd pentru-aprarea</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_IV-a_4"/>SCENA a IV-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON DIEGO, DON RODRIGO, DON ARIAS, DON ALONSO, DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON ALONSO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ximena vine, sire, s cear judecarea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Suprtoare veste i datorie grea!<text:line-break/>Te du, s nu te vad; mai bine-i pentru ea.<text:line-break/>Drept oriice rsplat te-alung acum, viteze,<text:line-break/>Dar vin-nti la rege ca s te-mbrieze.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P40">(Don RODRIGO exit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ximena-l urmrete, dei s-l scape-ar vrea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>C-i este drag se spune. Acuma vom vedea.<text:line-break/>Pref-te plin de jale.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_V-a_4"/>SCENA a V-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON DIEGO, DON ARIAS, DON SANCHO, DON ALONSO, XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>De-acum, fii mulumit,<text:line-break/>Dorina ta, Ximen, i-a fost ndeplinit.<text:line-break/>De-a biruit Rodrigo pe-ai notri inamici,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De rnile primite el a murit aici.<text:line-break/>Poi luda pe Domnul cu inima-mpcat.<text:line-break/>(Ctr don DIEGO.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ia uit-te la dnsa cum a plit deodat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Dar iat-o c lein, i din acest lein<text:line-break/>Putei vedea dovada iubirii pe deplin.<text:line-break/>Durerea-i d pe fa vpaia tinuit<text:line-break/>A dragostei de care e nc chinuit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum? a murit Rodrigo!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu, nu; dumanul tu<text:line-break/>Triete, viu i teafr ca i amorul su!<text:line-break/>Nu te-ngriji, Ximen, de soarta vieii sale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Leini i de plcere, precum leini de jale,<text:line-break/>Prisosul bucuriei cnd vine din senin<text:line-break/>Simirile ni fur ca i-un prisos de chin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>La ce ncerci, Ximen, la ce mai strui nc?<text:line-break/>Nu, praa era vdit durerea ta adnc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>ngrmdii dar, sire, restritea mea mereu!<text:line-break/>Dovad-a ntristrii numii leinul meu!<text:line-break/>O ciud prea fireasc m-a-mpins aa departe:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De judecat dnsul ar fi scpat prin moarte,<text:line-break/>Cci pentru-al rii bine rnit dac murea,<text:line-break/>Era zdrnicit i rzbunarea mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mi-ar fi o nedreptate o moarte-aa frumoas:<text:line-break/>Cer moartea lui Rodrigo, nu ns glorioas,<text:line-break/>Nu ridicat n slav de rege i norod,<text:line-break/>Nu pe un pat de-onoare, ci pe un eafod;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">S moar pentru erima-i, nu pentru domn i ar<text:line-break/>De-a pururi amintirea s-i fie de ocar!<text:line-break/>Nu snt de plns aceia ce pentru ar mor,<text:line-break/>Ei numele prin moarte i-l fac nemuritor!<text:line-break/>Iubesc deci biruina-i, i nu mi-e greu pcatul,<text:line-break/>Ea ntrete ara, redndu-mi vinovatul</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mai nobil i mai mndru acum de mii de ori,<text:line-break/>Cci poart astzi lauri pe frunte-n loc de flori;<text:line-break/>i, ca s spun ce cuget cu-o vorb rspicat,<text:line-break/>Mai vrednic azi de umbra srmanului meu tat!<text:line-break/>Dar vai, n ce ndejde o clip am crezut?<text:line-break/>Rodrig din parte-mi n-are nimica de temut:<text:line-break/>Ce-i stric-aceste lacrimi i jalea mea amar<text:line-break/>Cnd pentru el azil e ntreaga noastr ar?<text:line-break/>Sub ochii votri totul i se permite-aici:<text:line-break/>M biruie pe mine, ca i pe inamici.<text:line-break/>Dreptatea-nbuit cu-al maurilor snge<text:line-break/>O nou strlucire asupra lui rsfrnge;<text:line-break/>Noi i sporim alaiul, i-acest dispre de legi<text:line-break/>La carul su ne-njug n rnd cu cei doi regi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">fernandoCopila mea, acestea-s porniri nemsurate.<text:line-break/>n cumpn pun totul atunci cnd dau dreptate. Ucis de-i este tatl, el fu provoctor<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i simul echitei m face ierttor.<text:line-break/>Dar cntrindu-mi fapta, tu inima i-o-ntreab:<text:line-break/>Rodrig stpn e-acolo i cred c mai degrab<text:line-break/>Ea mulmete-n tain dreptii ce-o brfeti<text:line-break/>C i-l pstreaz teafr pe-acela ce-l iubeti.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Cui? Mie! Pe-ucigaul srmanului meu tat!<text:line-break/>Pe-acela chiar pe care l chem la judecat!<text:line-break/>De-acestea nu v pas, ba v-ateptai s fiu<text:line-break/>Mulumitoare dac bocesc aci-n pustiu?<text:line-break/>O, dac-aceste lacrime zadarnic snt vrsate,<text:line-break/>ngduii prin arme s dobndesc dreptate:<text:line-break/>Prin arme el pe mine de tat m-a lipsit;<text:line-break/>Prin arme se cuvine s fie urmrit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cer de la toi vitejii s-l cheme-n lupt, sire:<text:line-break/>Pe-acel ce m rzbun eu mi-l aleg de mire;<text:line-break/>S lupte toi, i-o dat Rodrigo pedepsit,<text:line-break/>Voi fi rsplata celui ce biruie-n sfrit.<text:line-break/>Deci dai porunc, sire, s se proclame vestea</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>E-o datin strbun, dar luptele acestea,<text:line-break/>Pretinse c rzbun pe drept un atentat<text:line-break/>Strpesc pe lupttorii cei buni ai unui stat.<text:line-break/>Adeseaori se-ntmpl izbnda de nclin<text:line-break/>Spre vinovat i cade cel fr nici o vin.<text:line-break/>Scutesc deci pe Rodrigo; prea mult la dnsul in<text:line-break/>Ca s-l expun acestui prea schimbtor destin,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-orict de vinovat e c te-a lsat orfan,<text:line-break/>I-au dus cu dnii crima pgnii pui pe goan</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum? Sire, pentru dnsul clcai aceste legi<text:line-break/>De-a pururi respectate de cei mai mndri regi?<text:line-break/>Dar ce va zice lumea i pizma ce va spune<text:line-break/>Cnd viaa lui sub scutul monarhului i-o pune,<text:line-break/>Fugind de locul unde oricare om cinstit<text:line-break/>E bucuros s afle un ludat sfrit?<text:line-break/>Favoarea aceasta, sire, mrirea lui i-o scade;<text:line-break/>Pstreze-i nentinate a biruinei roade!<text:line-break/>Cel ce-a tiut s-nfrng pe-un conte de Gormaz<text:line-break/>Dator e s rmn pn la sfrit viteaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Mi-o ceri i tu, deci fie! i cum i-a fi norocul!<text:line-break/>Dar celui ce-a s cad mii au s-i cear locul<text:line-break/>i preul ce Ximena ni l-a vestit aici<text:line-break/>Din toi ai mei rzboinici i face inamici.<text:line-break/>S-l las cu toi s lupte ar fi nedrept, Ximen:<text:line-break/>I-ajunge de coboar o dat n aren.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Numete-l dar pe care l vrei din cavaleri,<text:line-break/>Dar dup-aceast lupt nimic s nu-mi mai ceri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Atunci cruai pe-aceia ce de Rodrig s-ar teme.<text:line-break/>Lsai deschis lupta  i nimeni n-o s-l cheme.<text:line-break/>Cci dup biruina-i de astzi, nu m-atept<text:line-break/>S mai cuteze vreunul s dea cu dnsul piept.<text:line-break/>Se-ncumet vreunul, orict de mare-i preul?<text:line-break/>Cine va fi viteazul sau, mai curnd, semeul?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Deschidei dar lupta; i chiar de-o fi s caz,<text:line-break/>Eu sunt semeu-acela ori poate-acel viteaz.<text:line-break/>Ardoarea mea nu cere dect s v rzbune:<text:line-break/>V amintesc, senora, a voastr promisiune.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>i lai, Ximeno, soarta ntr-ale sale mni?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fgduit-am, sire.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fii gata deci pe mni!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Nu. Sire, lupta poate s-nceap ct mai iute:<text:line-break/>Eti totdeauna gata atunci cnd ai virtute.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S-ncepi o lupt nou, ntors din lupt-abia!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Rodrig a prins putere pe cnd vi-o povestea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>S-i dm un ceas sau dou de linite deplin.<text:line-break/>Dar cum m tem ca pild cumva s nu devin<text:line-break/>i ca s-arat c-n sil s-admit m-am hotrt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Un obicei slbatec ce pururi l-am uit,<text:line-break/>M-abin s-asist, i Curtea i ea se va abine.<text:line-break/>(Ctre don Arias.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Arbitru-al ntlnirei te rnduiesc pe tine;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vei ngriji ca toate s mearg-n chip cinstit<text:line-break/>i-mi ad-nvingtorul cnd lupta s-a sfrit.<text:line-break/>Aceeai e rsplata, oricare s-ar alege,<text:line-break/>Vreau s i-l dau Ximenii cu mna mea de rege,<text:line-break/>i ea pe veci s-i jure credin-n faa mea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Cum, sire? mi impunei o lege-aa de grea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Te plngi; iubirea-i ns, departe de-a se plnge,<text:line-break/>De biruie Rodrigo, mndria-i va nfrnge.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">nceat orice murmur i-ascult-m ce spun:<text:line-break/>Oricare s-ar alege, cu-acela te cunun.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_2" text:outline-level="2"><text:bookmark text:name="ACTUL_V"/>ACTUL V</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_I_5"/>SCENA I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON RODRIGO, XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Rodrig, ce ndrzneal! Cum? n amiaza mare?<text:line-break/>Vrei s m pierzi? Ascult i fugi, aibi ndurare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>M duc s mor, Ximeno, i dac viu aci,<text:line-break/>Viu ca s-mi iau adio-nainte de-a muri;<text:line-break/>Amorul ce m ine sub dulcea ta robie<text:line-break/>Dac primete moartea, vrea s i-o nchine ine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Te duci s mori!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Merg vesel spre-acel minut dorit<text:line-break/>n care-am s-i rscumpr tot chinul suferit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Te duci s mori! Cum oare? Don Sancho te-nspimnt<text:line-break/>i tremur de groaz o inim nenfrnt?<text:line-break/>Ce s-a fcut avntu-i? De unde spaima ta?<text:line-break/>Rodrig nvins se crede-nainte de-a lupta?<text:line-break/>Cel ce-a-nfruntat pe mauri i pe viteazu-mi tat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n faa lui don Sancho se pierde-aa deodat?<text:line-break/>Curajul i-e de-acelea ce pot ngenunchea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Eu nu alerg la lupt, ci la jertfirea mea,<text:line-break/>i sufletu-mi respinge, plin de dispre, povaa<text:line-break/>Cnd moartea tu mi-o caui, eu s-mi mai apr viaa,<text:line-break/>Eu am rmas acelai; dar nu mai poi s-mi ceri<text:line-break/>Ca s pstrez aceea ce tu s pierd mi ceri,<text:line-break/>i-a fi czut desigur azi-noapte-ucis de mauri<text:line-break/>De-a fi avut s-mi apr doar propriii mei lauri;<text:line-break/>ns norodul, ara i tronul aprnd,<text:line-break/>De nu-mi feream viaa, ar fi-nsemnat s-i vnd.<text:line-break/>Un suflet mare viaa-ntr-attea n-o hulete,<text:line-break/>nct s vrea s ias dintr-nsa mielete,<text:line-break/>Dar cum e vorba numai de propriu-mi folos,<text:line-break/>Azi, cnd mi ceri tu moartea, eu o primesc voios.<text:line-break/>Mnia ta o mn strin mi alege <text:line-break/>De-a ta, Rodrig s moar nu-i vrednic, se-nelege.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De nici o lovitur nu vreau s m feresc:<text:line-break/>Cui te-apr, omagiul acesta-i datoresc,<text:line-break/>i fermecat la gndul c toate-s de la tine,<text:line-break/>Fiindc-a ta onoare don Sancho o susine,<text:line-break/>mi voi deschide pieptul n calea spadei lui,<text:line-break/>Slvind aceast mn prin care m rpui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>O, dac-asprimea unei ndatoriri severe<text:line-break/>Ce marea-i vitejie s-o osndesc mi cere<text:line-break/>Te-mpinge pn-acolo ca s te lai sfrmat<text:line-break/>De-un bra ce pentru mine s lupte s-a-narmat,<text:line-break/>Gndete-te, n ceasul acesta de orbire,<text:line-break/>C-n joc i e i viaa, dar i a ta mrire,<text:line-break/>i toi, orict de falnic Rodrig a vieuit,<text:line-break/>Czut dac-or s-l tie, l-or crede biruit.<text:line-break/>Onoarea i-e mai scump dect i snt eu scump,<text:line-break/>Dac-a putut chiar vraja amorului s-o rump<text:line-break/>i te-a fcut, n ciuda prerilor de tu,<text:line-break/>S nimiceti tu nsui i visul meu i-al tu:<text:line-break/>i totui, vd c-i pas aa puin de-onoare,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">C, fr s lupi, pe Sancho l lai s te omoare?<text:line-break/>Ce s-a fcut avintul pe care-l artai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De ce nu-l ai i-acuma, ori pentru ce-l aveai?<text:line-break/>i cum? Viteaz eti numai spre-a-mi cauza durere?<text:line-break/>Iar dac nu, deodat i vitejia-i piere?<text:line-break/>i tatl meu de tine-i aa despreuit,<text:line-break/>C tu, biruitoru-i, te lai azi biruit?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mergi, fr dor de moarte, la lupt hotrt<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-i apr onoarea, nu viaa ta urt!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Dac-am nvins pe conte i maurii barbari,<text:line-break/>Mai am nevoie oare de alte fapte mari?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">La ce s-mi apr slava cnd toat lumea tie<text:line-break/>Isprvile-mi mree, c-aceast vitejie<text:line-break/>S fac totul poate i c pe-acest pmnt<text:line-break/>Afar de onoare nimic nu mi-e mai sfnt?<text:line-break/>Nu, nu; n lupta-aceasta Rodrig s moar poate<text:line-break/>Fr s-i piard nimbul mririi ctigate,<text:line-break/>i fr ca s fie de nime-nvinuit<text:line-break/>C n-a czut el nsui de sine biruit.<text:line-break/>Dar se va zice numai: Ximena i-a fost drag,<text:line-break/>Avea ntre iubirea i ura ei s-aleag,<text:line-break/>i s-a supus el nsui ursitei, ce-o silea<text:line-break/>Pe dulcea lui iubit s-i cear moartea sa.<text:line-break/>Ea nsi i-a cerut-o, i inima-i, firete,<text:line-break/>Credea c de-o refuz, o crim svrete.<text:line-break/>Spre-a-i rzbuna onoarea, amorul i-l pierdu;<text:line-break/>Spre-a-i rzbuna iubita, el viaa i-o ddu,<text:line-break/>tiind ca s prefere n floarea tinereii<text:line-break/>Onoarea sa Ximenii i pe Ximena vieii.<text:line-break/>Astfel aceast moarte, departe de-a umbri,<text:line-break/>A mreiei mele splendoare-o va mri,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i voi avea, prin moartea-mi voit, mngierea<text:line-break/>C nimeni dect mine nu i-a-mpcat durerea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Viaa ta i-onoarea n stare dac nu-s<text:line-break/>S-abat gndul morii de care eti supus,<text:line-break/>De te-a iubit vreodat Ximena ta, ei bine,<text:line-break/>Rodrig, atunci ascult: ndur-te de mine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i scap-m de sila ce-o am s m mrit<text:line-break/>Cu omul care venic mi-a fost nesuferit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">S-i spun mai mult?<text:line-break/>Alearg i-arat-i vitejia<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi impui tcere, ca s-mi mpaci mndria,<text:line-break/>i de mai ii, la mine, orict va fi de greu,<text:line-break/>nvinge ntr-o lupt al crei pre sunt eu!<text:line-break/>Adio; vorba asta, vai, s roesc m face</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_II-a_5"/>SCENA a II-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Mai e duman pe care s-l tem? Venii ncoace,<text:line-break/>Voi, castilani, voi mauri, venii voi, navareji,<text:line-break/>i tot ce ara Spanii mai are ca viteji!<text:line-break/>Unii-v cu toii i facei o armat<text:line-break/>S biruii o mn astfel mbrbtat:<text:line-break/>Spre-a-mi nimici ndejdea, o mie de viei;<text:line-break/>S aib fiecare, tot prea puini sntei!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_III-a_5"/><text:soft-page-break/>SCENA a III-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Vei asculta mndria strbun care-i cere<text:line-break/>Acum ntre mrire i dragoste s-alegi?<text:line-break/>Sau dragostea a crei i vraj i putere<text:line-break/>Te-mbie fr preget s-nfrngi aceste legi?<text:line-break/>Ah, creia din dou vei da tu precdere,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Srman vlstar de regi?<text:line-break/>Rodrig, eti demn de mine i te-a putea alege,<text:line-break/>Dei viteaz, tu ns, vai! nu eti fiu de rege!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Destin fr de mil, a crui nendurare<text:line-break/>Desparte-a mea mrire de fericirea mea!<text:line-break/>E scris in ciuda unei virtui aa de rare<text:line-break/>Amorul meu s poarte o lupt-aa de grea?<text:line-break/>Ah, inima-mi srman ce-o s ndure oare<text:line-break/>i cum va geme ea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De n-o s izbuteasc n veci s se nchine<text:line-break/>Iubitului, nici focul iubirii s-i aline!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar totui stau i cuget i nu pot nelege:<text:line-break/>Cnd el e-att de vrednic, de ce-a mai ezita?<text:line-break/>Dei am fost nscut pe seama unui rege,<text:line-break/>E-o cinste pentru mine, Rodrig, s fiu a ta!<text:line-break/>Cnd ai nvins pe mauri, ar fi o frdelege</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Coroan de-ai purta?<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i numele tu falnic de Cid nu dovedete<text:line-break/>C faima ta mrea pe zi ce merge crete?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">El totui e-al Ximenii, dei e demn de mine!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">mi pare ru de darul pe care i-l fcui.<text:line-break/>Nici moartea unui tat nu poate s-i dezbine,<text:line-break/>i ea, de sil numai, proclam vina lui.<text:line-break/>n toat rzboirea aceasta pentru mine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nici o ndejde nu-i,<text:line-break/>Cci spre-a-mi mri pedeapsa, ursita, vai! permite<text:line-break/>Iubirei s dureze i-n inimi nvrjbite!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_IV-a_5"/>SCENA a IV-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Elviro, vai, ct sufr! Ce vrednic-s de jale!<text:line-break/>Nu vd nici o ndejde, am presimiri fatale!<text:line-break/>N-am nici un gind de care s nu m nfior<text:line-break/>i fr pocin nu pot avea un dor!<text:line-break/>Pe doi rivali n lupt mnia mea-i mpinge,<text:line-break/>Au s m coste lacrimi, oricare ar nvinge;<text:line-break/>i-n cartea sorii mele oricum mi este scris,<text:line-break/>Nerzbunat mi-e tatl, sau, vai! Rodrig ucis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>De-i una ori de-i alta, vei fi mai mpcat,<text:line-break/>Sau capei pe Rodrig, sau fi-vei rzbunat,<text:line-break/>i-apoi orict destinul va fi de nendurat,<text:line-break/>Ea-i mntuie onoarea i-un mire-i va fi dat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cum? pe-ucigaul tatei? pe-al lui Rodrigo, poate?<text:line-break/>Pe unul din fptaii acestor mari pcate?<text:line-break/>Oricum s-alege soarta, ea-mi d un so ptat<text:line-break/>De sngele pe care mai mult l-am adorat;<text:line-break/>Oricum s-alege soarta, durerea m ucide<text:line-break/>i m-ngrozesc de ceea ce lupta va decide,<text:line-break/>O, dor de rzbunare i tu, amor, tcei,<text:line-break/>Voi v sfdii pe seama srmanei mele viei,<text:line-break/>i tu, crmuitorul umanelor destine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sfrete-aceast lupt aa cum e mai bine:<text:line-break/>Nici unul s nu-nving i nici s fie-nvins.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ar fi prea aspr soarta; i lupta ce s-a-ncins<text:line-break/>i-ar da prilej la chinuri i mai amare poate,<text:line-break/>Lsndu-te, stpn, s ceri mereu dreptate,<text:line-break/>S-ari aceeai ur mereu, s urmreti;<text:line-break/>Mereu viaa celui pe care tu-l iubeti.<text:line-break/>Mai bine-i biruina de-ar fi s-l ncunune,<text:line-break/>Ea datoriei tale tcere i-ar impune<text:line-break/>i bunul nostru rege te va sili atunci<text:line-break/>S-asculi ndreptit de-a inimei porunci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>O, dac el nvinge, crezi c m dau nvins?<text:line-break/>Prea sfnt-i datoria-mi i jalea-mi prea nestins,<text:line-break/>i nu ajunge numai ca regele s vrea<text:line-break/>Sau lupta s decid n defavoarea mea!<text:line-break/>A-nvinge pe don Sancho nu-i greu, dar n-o s poat<text:line-break/>S-nving i mrirea Ximenii totodat;<text:line-break/>i chiar dac Rodrigo va birui acum,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Onoarea mea-i va scoate mii ali vrjmai n drum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Stpn mea, asemeni cuvinte nu mai spune,<text:line-break/>S nu se-ndure cerul cumva s te rzbune!<text:line-break/>Cum! vrei s pierzi prilejul acesta fericit<text:line-break/>Ce focul urei tale l-ar potoli-n sfrit?<text:line-break/>Dar ce vrea datoria aceasta nempcat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ori moartea lui Rodrigo i d-napoi un tat?<text:line-break/>O grea nenorocire i pare prea puin?<text:line-break/>Vreai lacrimi peste lacrimi, suspin peste suspin?<text:line-break/>Nu, nu, cu-astfel de gnduri stpna mea iubit,<text:line-break/>Nu-i merii fericirea ce-i este hrzit<text:line-break/>i-i va impune dreapta mnie-a Celui Nalt,<text:line-break/>Prin moartea lui Rodrigo, s-l iei pe cellalt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>Elviro, mi ajunge att amar i jale<text:line-break/>N-o mai spori tu nc prin prevestiri fatale,<text:line-break/>A vrea s fug de ambii, dac-a putea s sper,<text:line-break/>De nu, pentru Rodrigo-nal rugciuni la cer.<text:line-break/>Nu c mi-e drag, dar dac Rodrig nu biruiete,<text:line-break/>Voi fi a lui don Sancho, cum am promis, firete<text:line-break/>La gndul sta numai mi-e sufletul-ngrozit<text:line-break/>Ce vd, amar de mine? Elviro, s-a sfrit!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_V-a_5"/>SCENA a V-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON SANCHO, XIMENA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Silit aceast spad s v-o aduc plecat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De-al lui Rodrig scump snge, cum? nc-nsngerat?<text:line-break/>i mai cutezi, perfide, n faa-mi s te-arei<text:line-break/>Cnd mi-ai rpit norocul ntregei mele viei?<text:line-break/>O, izbucnete-n voie de-acum, iubire-ascuns,<text:line-break/>Onoarea mi-e-mpcat i inta ei ajuns!<text:line-break/>Aceeai lovitur de spad mi-a ucis</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Norocul i iubirii-mi drum liber i-a deschis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/><text:line-break/>De-ai fi mai linitit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Taci! taci! nu i-e ruine,<text:line-break/>Crunt uciga al unui erou slvit de mine?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, l-ai lovit hoete, cci un viteaz ca el<text:line-break/>N-ar fi putut, desigur, s fie-nvins altfel.<text:line-break/>Nu mai spera nimica; creznd s m rzbune,<text:line-break/>Nevrednica ta mn pe mine m rpune!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Ciudat rtcire, ce cu att mai mult</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Crezi tu c pot s sufr i vrei s te ascult<text:line-break/>Cu ce neruinare trufa-mi vei descrie<text:line-break/>Pcatul meu, i moartea-i, i marea-i vitejie?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_VI-a_3"/>SCENA a VI-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON DIEGO, DON ARIAS, DON SANCHO, XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Sire, nu se mai cade s fie tinuit<text:line-break/>Ce n-am putut ascunde orict m-am chinuit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">tii c iubeam i, totui, n dreapta mea mnie,<text:line-break/>Vream s jertfesc o via att de scump mie,<text:line-break/>i maiestatea-voastr chiar a putut vedea<text:line-break/>Iubirea-mi sugrumat de datoria mea.<text:line-break/>Rodrig e mort acuma, i moartea-i schimb, iat,<text:line-break/>n jalnic iubit vrjmaa nempcat,<text:line-break/>Ceruse rzbunare acel ce m-a nscut,<text:line-break/>Acum s plng mi cere amorul meu pierdut:<text:line-break/>Lundu-mi aprarea n oarba lui pornire,<text:line-break/>Don Sancho nu-mi aduse dect nenorocire,<text:line-break/>i-acum s fiu datoare, cum am fgduit,<text:line-break/>S-ajung rsplata celui ce m-a nenorocit!<text:line-break/>O, de ptrunde mila o inim de rege,<text:line-break/>ndur-te, stpne, revoac-aceast lege.<text:line-break/>Ca pre al unei lupte n care am pierdut</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Tot ce-aveam scump pe lume, i las a] meu avut,<text:line-break/>Don Sancho s m lase pe mine mie nsumi,<text:line-break/>ngduii-mi, sire, s-mi plng n tihn plnsu-mi,<text:line-break/>Jelind, la adpostul cel sfnt al unui schit,<text:line-break/>Pn ce-oi muri, pe tata i scumpul meu iubit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON DIEGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>S-a dat pe fa-n fine i nu mai crede, sire,<text:line-break/>C-i un pcat s-i spun nvalnica iubire.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6"><text:soft-page-break/>DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Ximena, eti greit, Rodrig nu a murit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Don Sancho-vins, pesemne, n-a spus-o lmurit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON SANCHO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>De-aprinderea-i prea mare, fu, sire, amgit,<text:line-break/>Veneam s-i spun cum lupta fusese svrit.<text:line-break/>Acest rzboinic nobil, ce-i adorat de ea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">N-ai nici o team,-mi zise pe cnd m dezarma,<text:line-break/>Te las mai bine teafr s prseti arena,<text:line-break/>Dect s vrs nu snge riscat pentru Ximena,<text:line-break/>Dar cum de datorie la Curte snt chemat,<text:line-break/>Te du i-i spune lupta aa cum s-a urmat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i ca trofeu prezint-i din parte-mi a ta spad<text:line-break/>Aa fcui eu, sire. i-a fost destul s-o vad,<text:line-break/>Spre-a crede fr preget c sunt nvingtor,<text:line-break/>i-atunci minia-i dete pe fa-al ei amor<text:line-break/>Cu-aa avnt nprasnic i-atta nerbdare</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">C n-am putut s capt o clip de-ascultare.<text:line-break/>Dei nfrint, eu totui acum snt fericit<text:line-break/>i dac-mi vd azi visul iubirii nimicit,<text:line-break/>nfrngerea mi-e scump, fiindc-a fost n stare<text:line-break/>S dea ca pilda lumii o dragoste-aa mare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:line-break/>Nu mai roi, copil, i nu mai cuta<text:line-break/>Zadarnice mijloace s-ascunzi iubirea ta.<text:line-break/>Ne-o spune doar sfiala ce-i nflorete faa.<text:line-break/>Punndu-i n pericol de-attea ori viaa<text:line-break/>Viteazului Rodrigo, destule-ai ncercat,<text:line-break/>i tatl tu azi poate s doarm mpcat.<text:line-break/>Vezi lmurit c alte sunt cile divine:<text:line-break/>Fcui tot pentru dnsul gndete i la tine,<text:line-break/>i-ascult fr murmur al regelui tu sfat,<text:line-break/>Ce-i d un so prea vrednic i-att de adorat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:bookmark text:name="SCENA_a_VII-a_2"/>SCENA a VII-a</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P20">DON FERNANDO, DON DIEGO, DON ARIAS, DON RODRIGO, DON ALONSO, DON SANCHO, INFANTA, XIMENA, LEONORA, ELVIRA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">INFANTA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Din partea mea, Ximena, a principesei tale,<text:line-break/>Pe-acest rzboinic nobil primete-l fr jale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>V cer iertate dac n faa voastr, sire,<text:line-break/>M-arunc la picioare-i sfioasa mea iubire.<text:line-break/>Nu vin aci rsplata izbnzii s mi-o cer,<text:line-break/>Vin capul meu, stpn, din nou s i-l ofer,<text:line-break/>i n a mea favoare nu chem a luptei lege,<text:line-break/>Nu chem nici chiar voina preabunului meu rege,<text:line-break/>Dar dac toate cele fcute-s prea puin,<text:line-break/>O, spune ce mijloace te-ar mpca deplin?<text:line-break/>Mii de rivali vrei nc, iubita mea, s birui,<text:line-break/>Voieti a mele fapte mree s le-nirui<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>De la un cap al lumii pn la cellalt?<text:line-break/>S iau o cetuie eu singur din asalt?<text:line-break/>S spulber o armat? S-ajung-al meu renume<text:line-break/>S-ntunece pe-al celor mai mari eroi din lume?<text:line-break/>O, dac prin acestea iertare-a dobndi,<text:line-break/>Le-a ndura pe toate i tot a izbndi!<text:line-break/>Dar dac-acea onoare, mereu nerzbunat,<text:line-break/>Cu moartea mea doar poate s fie mbunat,<text:line-break/>Puterea omeneasc de ce-o mai narmezi<text:line-break/>Cnd prosternat fruntea-naintea ta mi-o vezi!<text:line-break/>Rzbun-te tu nsi, cci astfel se cuvine,<text:line-break/>Cel nenvins de nimeni s fie-nvins de tine;<text:line-break/>Cu preul vieii mele atunci, de m-ai ierta,<text:line-break/>Nu m goni, Ximeno, din amintirea ta,<text:line-break/>i pentru c prin moarte-mi eu i pstrez mrirea,<text:line-break/>n schimb i tu pstreaz-mi, Ximeno, amintirea<text:line-break/>i spune cteodat, plngnd al meu sfrit:<text:line-break/>,,De nu-i eram prea drag, Rodrig n-ar fi murit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">XIMENA</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Ridic-te, Rodrigo. Adevrat, e, sire,<text:line-break/>Prea mult mi-am dat pe fa ascunsa mea iubire,<text:line-break/>E prea viteaz Rodrigo ca eu s nu-l iubesc,<text:line-break/>i la porunca voastr pot s m-mpotrivesc?<text:line-break/>tiu bine c-s datoare s-ascult a luptei lege,<text:line-break/>C sfnt e totdeauna cuvntul unui rege,<text:line-break/>Dar oriice pedeaps binevoii a-mi da,<text:line-break/>Aceast cununie voi o putei rbda?<text:line-break/>i datoriei mele de-i poruncii tcere,<text:line-break/>Dreptatea voastr oare nu sufer-o scdere?<text:line-break/>Dac Rodrig e-al rii cel mai de seam fiu,<text:line-break/>A slujbei lui rsplat se cade eu s fiu?<text:line-break/>i viaa mea ntreag s am mereu a plnge<text:line-break/>Cu minile ptate de-al tatlui meu snge?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:line-break/>Adesea vremea totui legitim a fcut<text:line-break/>Ce se prea o frdelege la-nceput.<text:line-break/>Te-a cucerit Rodrigo prin marea-i vitejie<text:line-break/>i de aci-nainte a lui eti pe vecie;<text:line-break/>Dar preul biruinei acum de i l-a da,<text:line-break/>Duman mririi tale s fiu ar nsemna:<text:line-break/>Cstoria-aceasta mai poate s s-amne<text:line-break/>O dat ce ntreag credina ta-i rmne.<text:line-break/>Ia-i dar un an de doliu, Ximeno, dac vrei</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P12"><text:soft-page-break/>Iar tu, Rodrig, la arme, cu toi vitejii mei!<text:line-break/>Dac-ai gonit pe mauri departe de limanuri,<text:line-break/>Zdrnicind nvala i-a lor viclene planuri.<text:line-break/>Cu-ntreaga mea otire alearg-n ara lor<text:line-break/>i prad-le pmntul ca un cuceritor.<text:line-break/>Eti Cidul, nainte-i vor tremura de groaz<text:line-break/>i-or s te vrea de rege; tu ins i pstreaz<text:line-break/>Credina ta jurat Ximenii-n faa mea.<text:line-break/>Revin-o, de se poate, mai demn nc de ea,<text:line-break/>i-att de sus te-nal prin faptele-i viteze.<text:line-break/>nct s fie mndr l-altar s te urmeze.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON RODRIGO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>Spre-a v sluji, stpne, i pentru-a nu displace<text:line-break/>Ximenei mele scumpe, ce n-a putea eu face?<text:line-break/>De ochii ei departe orict a ndura,<text:line-break/>Preafericit snt, sire, c pot mcar spera.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P6">DON FERNANDO</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Text_20_body"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P8"><text:line-break/>n vitejia-i sper, Rodrig, i-n vorba-mi dat,<text:line-break/>i inima Ximenii fiindu-i nchinat,<text:line-break/>ncrede-te n vreme, ce-alin orice ru,<text:line-break/>i-n braul tu puternic i-n suveranul tu!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_1" text:outline-level="1">Traduceri</text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un imn francez lui Eminescu</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Lucien Bazin </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">tradus n romn de<text:span text:style-name="T24"> </text:span>tefan Octavian Iosif </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Cunosc povestea trist i scurt-a vieii tale<text:line-break/>i scrba ta nscut din vanele plceri,<text:line-break/>i lumea ta de visuri, dorine i dureri...<text:line-break/>Nluca urmrit de tine-n veci pe cale.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">i am citit o parte din opera-i miastr;<text:line-break/>Sub biciul suferinei umane te zresc<text:line-break/>Trist, implornd n graiul tu dulce romnesc<text:line-break/>Pe amor, pe tiranul divin din lumea noastr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Dar mai presus citit-am poemul tu romantic,<text:line-break/>Bogat n idealuri i falnice avnturi<text:line-break/>Ce-o s-i rodeasc neamul, vrjit de-acele cnturi,<text:line-break/>n care se trezete al Romei geniu antic.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34"><text:soft-page-break/>i mi-am adus aminte atunci c-n voi renate<text:line-break/>Acelai snge nobil al rasei vechi latine,<text:line-break/>i-n ciuda deprtrii, m-apropie de tine,<text:line-break/>i m-a cuprins mndria c te-am putut cunoate!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">De-atunci i munca-i sfnt cu dragoste-o aleg.<text:line-break/>Ci, de n-am fi vlstare aceleiai tulpine,<text:line-break/>Te-a fi-neles eu totui, citindu-te pe tine:<text:line-break/>Poeii mari sunt domnii pmntului ntreg!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Aa toi cei ce-odat simit-au cu putere<text:line-break/>Delirul dezndejdii, cel plin de-amar i jale<text:line-break/>Vor plnge la accentul sublim al lirei tale,<text:line-break/>Imens rsuntoare cnd geme de durere...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Durerea e obteasc: acid e-al ei srut...<text:line-break/>Tu nsui, Eminescu, o cunoteai din fae:<text:line-break/>nlnuindu-i gtul cu braele-ucigae<text:line-break/>Te-a strns aa de tare, c lira i-a tcut...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">S-a stins a ta gndire n noaptea blestemat,<text:line-break/>Pn&apos; ce s treci n raiul etern scldat n raz...<text:line-break/>Dar opera-i rmne i duhul tu vegheaz<text:line-break/>Asupra rii tale n doliu-nvemntat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">n negrele amurguri, cnd ne-nfioar-un vaier<text:line-break/>Ca dintr-o alt lume, al psrii nocturne,<text:line-break/>Cnd strop cu strop, n tain, din nevzute urne<text:line-break/>Necunoscute lacrimi alunec prin aer,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">n tristele amurguri ce-mbrac-a noastre fruni<text:line-break/>Cu negur de visuri, cnd singur i ari<text:line-break/>Al lunii disc de aur vrjind singurti,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cnd raza ei coboar peste cmpii i muni,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">n ceasurile-acele de team ne-neleas,<text:line-break/>Cnd mrile respir o dulce adiere,<text:line-break/>Atunci pluteti, poete, scpat de-orice durere,<text:line-break/>i ara ta i-o legeni cu drag, ca pe mireas...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Poete, stai de straj! Spre culmile mririi<text:line-break/>Insufl-i, ca s lupte, a geniului scnteie,<text:line-break/>Copil al Romniei, o, bard menit s steie<text:line-break/>Alturi de stpnii slvii ai Nemuririi!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cel din urm oaspe </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de August von Platen-Hallermnde</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">BTRNUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce faci aici? E o urgie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ulia deart.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-ar ti c stai n vijelie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stpnul meu, m ceart.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n mndrele saloane vin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Auzi cum muzici cnt?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi danul vesel n lumin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E praznicul de nunt!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La srbtoarea cea voioas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia lumea toat parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i numai palida mireas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St trist deoparte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fii inimos, n-ai nici o team</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C vei veni cu mine:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stpnul e care te cheam;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bine-i venit oricine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">TNRUL</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrne, mulumesc. M las</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Proptit de colonad;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e muzic mai preioas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vifornia din strad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu merg acolo unde cur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ampania-n pahare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-amestec dulcea butur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ura mea amar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ar fulgera nici ochii mei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-a pururi bucurie;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mireasa ce-ndrgir ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mi-e ursit mie!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar nici stpnul tu voios</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i fericeasc soarta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-l mai ateapt-un oaspe jos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre-a-l logodi cu moartea!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lenore</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Gottfried August Brger</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din somn Lenore-n zori de zi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tresare tulburat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, Wilhelm, m-ai uitat? Eti mort?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Veni-vei tu odat?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubitul ei lupta sub steag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vile boeme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu-i scrisese nici un ir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-att amar de vreme.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">arina i viteazul crai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stui de jaf i par,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Au pus rzboiului sfrit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pace ncheiar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cling! i clang! oti dup oti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu flori mpodobite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n zvon de tobe se-ntorceau</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La vetrele iubite.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era un glas i-un forfot viu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din plaiuri pn-n vale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrni i tineri, cu alai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le alergau n cale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bucuria strlucea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ochii tuturora;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe Wilhelm ns n zadar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n cuta Lenora...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea alerga n sus i-n jos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin gloata de otire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici unul, vai! din ci veneau</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-aveau de Wilhelm tire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar cnd, pe rnd, trecur toi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerea o nfrnse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ipnd se tvli pe jos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i plnse, plnse, plnse...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrna o gsete-n drum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O scutur, o cheam</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah! mam, Wilhelm este mort!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E mort de bun seam!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S piar lumea! piar tot!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ar fi cu mult mai bine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nedrept i crud e Dumnezeu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Amar, amar de mine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copil, vino-i n simiri!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">F-i cruce i te roag;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce face bunul Dumnezeu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E drept i bine, drag!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, Dumnezeu e-n cer,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cerul e departe...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce bine, vai, mi-a dat n schimb</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe rugile-mi dearte?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copila mea, odorul meu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascult, fii cuminte!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu supra pe Dumnezeu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu astfel de cuvinte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, mam, e-n zadar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toate sunt pierdute!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici Dumnezeu, nici iadul chiar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate s-mi ajute!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, fat, dac te-a uitat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Necredinciosul mire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i poate el cu alta azi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Triete-n fericire?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La dnsul nu te mai gndi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-l vei uita cu anii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd el rsplata-i va gsi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ghearele Satanei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, ceea ce-am pierdut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pierdut rmne, mam!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ce, la ce m-am mai nscut?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, moarte, vino, ia-m!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mini! n zadar v frmntai;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochi! n zadar mai plngei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, viaa mea! Lumina mea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apunei i v strngei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, Doamne, nu te ndura</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De vorbele-i nebune!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n dezndejdea-i fr fru</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu tie, vai, ce spune!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascult, fat, sfatul meu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te du la mnstire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mireasa fr de noroc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n cer gsete mire!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, ce mi-e cer i rai!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, ce mi-e raiul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu el, cu el e raiu-ntreg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fr Wilhelm, iadul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici nu mai vreau s cred nimic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic din cte-mi spunei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, viaa mea! Lumina mea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strngei-v i-apunei!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa se zbucium mereu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ip, i blesteam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rbdarea Domnului cercnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu vorbe fr team.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pn-n ceas trziu de-amurg</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plng negrii ochi ntruna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd stelele pe cer lucesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ncet s-arat luna...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Auzi... deodat, trap-trap-trap,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copite bat afar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un clre s-oprete-n drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i urc-ncet pe scar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lin sun micul clopoel </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cling-cling-cling, fr veste...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de la u, lin de tot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vin oaptele aceste</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vegheaz nc, draga mea?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lumina nu e stins?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce face porumbia mea?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E vesel sau plns?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, Wilhelm, tu!... Aa trziu?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai, ce dureri cumplite!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De plns mi-e sufletul pustiu...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-unde vii, iubite?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi noaptea doar plecm la drum,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd zrile-s senine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tocmai din Boemia vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s te iau cu mine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, Wilhelm, intr-n cas-nti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreau s-i aud cuvntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreau s te strng la snul meu...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum geme-afar vntul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hei, geam vntul, ct o vrea,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubita mea, nu-mi pas!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugarul sforie grbit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-i chip de stat n cas!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncinge-te de drum curnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te-oi duce-n goan crunt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i jur c noaptea asta chiar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dormim n pat de nunt!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, dar porni-vom chiar de-acum?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Afar-i noapte rece.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascult!... clopotul din turn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vestete unsprezece!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">E luna sus... Noi i cei mori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne ducem iute foarte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca vntul ori ca gndul vrei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugarul s ne poarte?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar unde-i locul cel faimos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i patul nunii cum e?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe... strmt, ntunecos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i netiut de lume!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom ncpea noi?  Negreit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fii gata dar n grab;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deschis e balul; dup noi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nuntaii toi ntreab.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copila se gti; pe roib</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-avnt cu grbire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu brau-i ginga ncingnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe multdoritul mire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i hop, hop, hop, fugind cu ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugarul salt sprinten,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copitele nesc scntei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ies vpi din pinten.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La dreapta i la stnga lor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe drumul nins de lun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum zboar dealuri, vi, cmpii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Greu podurile sun!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urra!... E luna sus... Urra!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce repede merg morii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te temi, iubita mea, de mori?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, nu... dar las morii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hei, unde merge-acel norod</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i corbii, ce s-adun?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-nseamn ciocli, popi, prohod</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i clopotul ce sun?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntri i bocete-n convoi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-aseamn laolalt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu jalnicul orcit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al boului de balt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe mort lsai-mi-l n drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nengropat s steie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venii la cununia mea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu tnra femeie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aici, rcovnic i gropar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cioclii dimpreun!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, dascl, mormie un psalm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, pop, ne cunun!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dispare carul mortuar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntrile-amuir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe urma roibului fugar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Convoiul lung se-nir.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i hop, hop, hop, zburnd cu ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugarul salt sprinten,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copitele nesc scntei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ies vpi din pinten.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La dreapta i la stnga lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cmpii, orae, sate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ri i muni dispar n zbor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De goan fulgerate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urra!... E luna sus!... Urra!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce repede merg morii?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubita mea, te temi de mori?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, las-n pace morii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te uit! sus pe eafod</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stafii i draci s-adun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnt, i se nvrtesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n razele de lun!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aici, strigoi! aici, scripcari!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venii s-ntindem hora</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu noaptea asta m cunun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu mndra mea Lenora!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toi strigoii  f, f, f </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alearg pe-apucate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zburnd pe sus ca-ntr-un vrtej</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un roi de foi uscate.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i hop, hop, hop, fugind cu ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugarul salt sprinten,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copitele nesc scntei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ies vpi din pinten.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum zboar toate-n deprtri!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apar, dispar ntruna!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orae, sate, ri i mri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i stelele, i luna!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urra!... E luna sus... Urra!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce repede merg morii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te temi, iubita mea, de mori?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai... las&apos; s doarm morii!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Roib! roib! cocoii cnt-n sat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Miroase-a diminea...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Roib! roib! zresc la rsrit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O gean de roa...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mireasa mea, cred c-am ajuns!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Suntem n dreptul porii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i patul nunii ni-e gtit...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce repede merg morii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Convoi, i roib, i cavaler</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strfulger n treact;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lovit cu o vergea de fier,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se frnge vechiul lact;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aripile btrnei pori</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-arunc la o parte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i printre cruci, n cimitir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei zboar mai departe...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hu!... cavalerul s-a oprit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Minune blestemat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mantaua-i se destram-n vnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bucat cu bucat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O hrc goal-n loc de cap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rnjete fioroas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i trupul, n schelet schimbat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe umr poart coas...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tresare roibul viforos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Necheaz cu putere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe nri i gur vars foc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sforie, i... piere!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pmnt i ceruri gem amar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ceas de grea mnie...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lenora se frmnt greu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cuprins de-agonie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum se strng n cimitir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stafiile la lun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-o hor deucheat-ntind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnt mpreun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rbdare! Chinul pmntesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se mntuie cu somnul;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De bietul suflet rtcit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ndure-mi-se Domnul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n ciud </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Robert Burns</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se vede srman, ocolit cu dispre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fruntea i-o-nclin  n ciud?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar noi ne mndrim i-o-nlm mai mre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-aceasta doar numai n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciud i numai n ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciuda attor mizerii ce snt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic nu e rangul dect un cuvnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i omul e aur  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu pine i sare, cu coji de mlai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trim anevoie  n ciud!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nebuni i miei se rsfa ca-n rai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar om este omul  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciud i numai n ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciuda averii i-a tuturor chiar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot omul cel vrednic e mrgritar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orict de srac e  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedei voi pe-acela, el cic-i boier,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i anos ce umbl  n ciud!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asculte-l toi protii i-nale-l la cer,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El tot e-un netrebnic  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciud i numai n ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciuda podoabei ce-o poart la piept,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un om fr zgard, un om nelept</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se uit i rde  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un rege l poate-ncrca din prisos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu nume i-onoruri  n ciud!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar vrednic s fac din om ticlos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate nici dnsul  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciud i numai n ciud!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orict e de sus i orict de seme,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic nu-i mai sfnt, i nimic mai de pre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca mintea i cinstea  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-aceea rugai-v Domnului sfnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S lupte tot omul  n ciud!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca mintea i cinstea s aib cuvnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe lumea aceasta  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ciud i numai n ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Veni-va ea vremea nscris pe steag.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd om ctre om s-i ntind cu drag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O mn de frate  n ciud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Ctre copaci </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Giosu Carducci</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umbreti culmi repezi, largi singurti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar nu-mi eti drag, ntunecat stejar:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ramuri verzi tu-mpodobeai barbari</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pustiitori de tronuri i ceti.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, laur sterp, i mai prejos mi pari:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu mini, orict de falnic verde-ari</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe cmpul veted, sau cnd, alte di,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luceai pe fruni pleuve de chesari.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-eti drag, vi, tu ce creti bogat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din lut pietros, ca s-mi mbii paharul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uitrii nelepte-n vremuri grele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai scump mi-e bradul: el va-nchide-odat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n patru scnduri, neted, tot amarul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i zbuciumul, i visurile mele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ucenicul vrjitor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Johann Wolfgang von Goethe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar s-a dus n trg batrnul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Maistru vraci, i-s eu stapnul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hai, c pun eu azi la cale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toate duhurile sale!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiu pe dinafar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Farmecele lui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i minuni, ca dnsul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fac, fr s-i spui.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iute! iute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ad ap,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nceap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rotitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Valuri-valuri pe-ntrecute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S se verse-n scldtoare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vino dar, mtur roas!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia-i mantaua zdrenuroas!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Slug-ai fost, fii iar slug!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">F-mi pe voie dintr-o fug!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Capt-i picioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus rsar-i cap.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du-te, poart-mi, ad-mi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doniele-n trap!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iute! iute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ad ap,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nceap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rotitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Valuri-valuri pe-ntrecute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S se verse-n scldtoare!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iat-mi-l fugind pe cale!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umple doniele-n vale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca un fulger mi se-ntoarn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un potop de valuri toarn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pleac, vine iar!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Colcie-n bazin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Salt, crete apa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A, dar este plin!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ho! strine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scalda-i plin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La hodin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca-nainte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, pricep... amar de mine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vorba mi-a pierit din minte!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vorba, vai! ce cat spus</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s-l fac iar ce fuse!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fuge, vai, i vine-n grab!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mtur, de-ai fi de treab!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot mai mult aduce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toarn tot mereu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai, i mii de ruri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cad pe capul meu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">aga-i ag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-mi mai place!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai, tu, drace!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nc rde?!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Inima-n rcori mi-o bag!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ochi cruni! Ce schime hde!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, dar ai ieit din iaduri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s faci prin cas vaduri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde caut, pretutindeni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc-i un puhoi cu grindeni!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mtur netoat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai pe loc, i spun!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">B, ce-ai fost odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai fi nebun!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu ascult?!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hai tu numa!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu toporul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr de zbav mult</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am s-i potolesc eu zorul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iat-mi-l! Tr s-arat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De m-arunc la tine-odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici nu mntui tot cuvntul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Una fi-vei cu pmntul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-am crpat n dou!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-am lovit la mir!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pot s-atept acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i s mai respir!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iat! Iat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C nvie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi mbie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Donii pline</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doi acuma dintr-o dat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ajutor, puteri divine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i alearg! Curg praie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pretutindeni prin odaie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce privelite avan!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vraciul!  Maistre, f-i poman!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Duhurile tale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doamne,-i fac de cap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le-am chemat, i-acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mai pot s scap!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mturice!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stai cuminte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca-nainte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci la vreme</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doar btrnul vraci aice,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Duhuri, poate s v cheme!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Stropi de nectar </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Johann Wolfgang von Goethe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd Minerva, ca s-arate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Preuirea pentru-alesu-i</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prometeu, din cer i-aduse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De nectar o cup plin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre a-i ferici pe oameni</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spre-a le sdi n suflet</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simul artelor frumoase;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sprinten-i zori ea pasul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu cumva s prind veste</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Jupiter; i cupa de-aur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ovi i pe pmntul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Verde civa stropi picar...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iute-albinele-i luar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urma, i sorbir harnic;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fluturul s-afl n treab</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca i el un strop s fure;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chiar nslnicul pianjen</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lunec i supse stranic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Norocoase-au fost acestea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-alte gingae gngnii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci mpart cu muritorii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astzi deopotriv cea mai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mndr desftare </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">arta</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Loreley</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu ce poate s fie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C-mi sun mereu n urechi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu venica-i melancolie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un basmu din zilele vechi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-ntunec fr de veste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lin apele Rinului curg,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cresc ale munilor creste</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mre strlucind n amurg.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe stnc un chip de femeie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-arat din negur blnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brara-i de aur scnteie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea-i piaptn prul cntnd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea-i piaptn prul i cnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un cntec de vraj al ei;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te farmec i te-nspimnt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntarea frumoasei femei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pescarul, nebun, se repede</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu luntrea lui mic i, dus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici valuri, nici stnc nu vede,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El caut numai n sus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vltoarea-l izbete de coasta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stncoas, i moare-necat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Loreley a fcut-o aceasta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu viersul ei fermecat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Grenadirii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de tefan Octavian Iosif, traducere de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din Rusia doi grenadiri se pornesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voioi s-i revad iar Frana,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cnd au intrat n hotarul nemesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci i pierdur sperana.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci au aflat dureroasele tiri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C gloria Franei s-a stins:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfrnte, zdrobite sunt marile-otiri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cezarul, cezarul e prins!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci i plecar triti frunile lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i plnser cei doi tovari.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar unul a zis:  Cumplit m mai dor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cumplit m ard rnile iari!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A zis cellalt:  Un vis fuse tot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i moartea mi-ar fi mult mai bine!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am ns nevast, copii, i nu pot</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S mor, c-s pierdui fr mine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-am zor de nevast, n-am zor de copii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un dor mai frumos m-a cuprins;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cereasc pe drumuri ori fac ce-or ti:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cezarul, cezarul meu, prins!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curnd, o, prietene, mort voi zcea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascult-mi un singur cuvnt!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cadavrul cu tine n Frana mi-l ia,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-ngroap-n al Franei pmnt!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar crucea onoarei mi-o prinde la piept,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aproape de inima-mi stins;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aaz-mi i flinta la umrul drept</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spada la mijloc ncins.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa voi veghea n mormnt, ascultnd,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O straj ce pare c doarme...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci-n vis auzi-voi iar tunul urlnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tropot, i zngt de arme!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cezarul meu trece-n al luptei avnt</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe groap-mi, i-n spade ce scapr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci, narmat m nal din mormnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cezarul, cezarul s-mi apr!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">A pune cruce srciei</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P35">de Heinrich Heine </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A pune cruce srciei mele</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-a fi un pictor meter de icoane,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S zugrvesc tablouri dup toane,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mpodobind biserici i castele.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Potop de daruri, aur i coroane,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-a ti clavir, vioar ca, prin ele,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S desftez boierii-n cafenele</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ori s culeg aplauze-n saloane.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Nu-mi va zmbi norocul niciodat:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe lume tu mi-eti singurul tezaur,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tu, art fr pine, poezie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i, ah! cnd ali petrec i se desfat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd vinul spumeg-n pahare de-aur,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu nsetez, ori beau  pe datorie...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cavalerul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Lui D. Anghel</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A fost odinioar un cavaler tcut,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu ochii melancolici, obrajii de zpad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Trgnat i ubred, pustiu i abtut,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El hoinrea pe ulii, dat visurilor prad.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Era aa de eapn, stngaci, dus n extaz!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La geamuri flori i fete rdeau de el cu haz,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd, ovind n umblet, se poticnea, srmanul!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ades, pierdut n umbr, sttea-ntr-un colior,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fugind de ochii lumii, n casa-i solitar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i braele-amndou el le-ntindea cu dor,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ci nu scotea o oapt n linitea de sear.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La miezul nopii ns cretea un freamt lin</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-un cntec sau descntec bizar, ca din senin,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cineva la u uor de tot i bate...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iubita-i intr,  iat-o alunecnd uor</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntr-un vemnt de spum de valuri zgomotoase,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aprins i-nflorit ca un aprins bujor;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Strlucitor e vlu-i uor ca de mtase.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Blond chipul ei rsare din buclele-aurii,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Surd albatri ochii scnteietori de vii </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n brae unul altui se las ei s cad...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n brae unul pe-altul ei dornic se cuprind;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Stngaciul de-adineauri nici nu se mai cunoate;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Re-nvie vistorul; obrajii reci s-aprind;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din ce n ce mai teafr el simte c renate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea ns, ea-l rsfa zmbind alinttor,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu vicleug se-ntoarce ncet i-ncetior</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">L-acoper cu vlul cel alb, de diamante...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntr-un palat feeric, cu ziduri de cletar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se vede cavalerul, orbit de-aa splendoare:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Uimit se uit dnsul i se mai uit iar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tot aruncnd n preajm-i priviri ne-ncreztoare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Dar nimfa-l ine totui mbriat cu drag</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El  mire, ea  mireas, i-n jurul lor, irag</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din iter in hangul i cnt mndre zne...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din iter in hangul i cnt rpitor,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i, stnd s-nceap danul, ridic-n tact piciorul...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tresare cavalerul, nnebunit de-amor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mai ptima i strnge la piept acum odorul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci, fr de veste, luminile dispar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i iari cavalerul tcut i solitar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se pomenete-n trista poetului chilie...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Copii eram... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Surorei mele</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Copii eram pe-atunci, copil,<text:line-break/>Copii drgui, copii vioi;<text:line-break/>Ne cocoam printre cotee,<text:line-break/>Dormeam n paie amndoi...<text:line-break/>Iar oamenii veneau afar<text:line-break/>Cnd noi cucurigam drcoi,<text:line-break/>i ei credeau de bun seam<text:line-break/>C este cntec de coco...<text:line-break/>Cu lzile din curtea noastr,<text:line-break/>Grmad una peste alt,<text:line-break/>ntruchipasem noi o cas:<text:line-break/>Gospodria laolalt...<text:line-break/>De prin vecini btrna m<text:line-break/>Ne cerceta-n rstimpuri dese,<text:line-break/>O-ntmpinam cu plecciune,<text:line-break/>Rostind cuvinte ne-nelese.<text:line-break/>Ba o-ntrebam de sntate,<text:line-break/>Politicoi, care de care;<text:line-break/>De-atunci, la cte mi btrne<text:line-break/>N-am pus aceeai ntrebare!<text:line-break/>Ba stam adesea la taifasuri,<text:line-break/>Ca doi btrni din vremi uitate,<text:line-break/>Ne tnguiam c-n vremea noastr<text:line-break/>Erau aa frumoase toate;<text:line-break/>C dragostea, credina, cinstea<text:line-break/>Pe zi ce merge, tot dispar,<text:line-break/>i ct de scump e cafeaua,<text:line-break/>i banul ct e azi de rar!...<text:line-break/>S-a dus copilria noastr,<text:line-break/>i toate-s de vrtej furate <text:line-break/>i bani, i vremuri, i credin,<text:line-break/>i cinste, i iubire  toate!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Ca visurile </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ca visurile-ntunecate<text:line-break/>Cldirile se-niruiesc,<text:line-break/>i singur, nvelit n manta-mi,<text:line-break/>Tcut pe trotuar pesc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acuma-n turnul catedralei<text:line-break/>Se bate tainic miez de noapte...<text:line-break/>M-ateapt-acas adorata<text:line-break/>Cu srutri, vrjite oapte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prietenoas trece luna<text:line-break/>Cluzindu-mi pas cu pas;<text:line-break/>Dar eu m-opresc n umbra porii,<text:line-break/>Strigndu-i vesel:  Bun rmas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i mulumesc, amic veche,<text:line-break/>C-mi luminai frumos pe drum;<text:line-break/>Treci mai departe, lumineaz<text:line-break/>i celorlali pribegi, de-acum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar de gseti pe vreun ibovnic<text:line-break/>Ce plnge, tu s nu mi-l lai;<text:line-break/>O, mngie-l, precum pe mine<text:line-break/>De-attea ori m mngiai...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat prima oar n Viaa, 15 ianuarie 1895</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Ce trist mi-e inima... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce trist mi-e inima, trist!<text:line-break/>E-n mai i e cald i-i lumin.<text:line-break/>n deal, lng teiul de straj,<text:line-break/>Stau dus pe reduta-n ruin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Alunec grla-ntre slcii;<text:line-break/>n luntre-un copil de pescar<text:line-break/>Tot plescie undia-n ap<text:line-break/>i fluier micul trengar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n mii de culori mi s-arat<text:line-break/>Podoabele mndrei naturi:<text:line-break/>Grdine, i chiocuri, i oameni,<text:line-break/>i vite, i lunci, i pduri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Jos, fete albesc i bat rufe;<text:line-break/>Lin zbrnie din deprtare<text:line-break/>Subt scocul nalt, roata morii<text:line-break/>i prfuie mrgritare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe lng gheret se plimb,<text:line-break/>n turnul castelului sur,<text:line-break/>Strjeru-n tunica lui roe;<text:line-break/>El face la stnga-mprejur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu flinta la soare se joac<text:line-break/>i-i fulger-n mini acea flint;<text:line-break/>Salut, o pune la umr...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>A vrea s m ieie la int!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Stai i-asculi sub ramuri... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Stai i-asculi sub ramuri albe<text:line-break/>Cum departe geme vntul<text:line-break/>i priveti la cer prin ceaa<text:line-break/>Care-nvluie pmntul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vezi i crnguri, vezi i cmpuri<text:line-break/>Triste i pustii, departe:<text:line-break/>Iarn-n suflet, iarn-n fire,<text:line-break/>Iarn afli-n orice parte...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ns crngile se scutur<text:line-break/>Fr veste. Abtut,<text:line-break/>Crezi c valuri de zpad<text:line-break/>Peste tine au czut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah, nu-s valuri de zpad!<text:line-break/>Tresrind din vis, te sperii:<text:line-break/>Plou flori mirositoare,<text:line-break/>Joac razele puzderii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Farmec fioros de dulce!<text:line-break/>Iarna se preschimb-n var,<text:line-break/>Fulgii se preschimb-n floare,<text:line-break/>Inima iubete iar...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:soft-page-break/>Publicat prima oar n Viaa, 16 aprilie 1895</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Arborii-nflorii rsun... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Viaa</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 16 aprilie 1895</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Arborii-nflorii rsun,<text:line-break/>Cnt cuiburile-n slav...<text:line-break/>Cine-i oare capelmaistrul<text:line-break/>n orchestra din dumbrav?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Piigoiul care-ntr-una<text:line-break/>D din cap cu-atta fal?<text:line-break/>Ori pedantul cuc ce-i strig<text:line-break/>Numele fr greeal?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Este oare cocostrcul,<text:line-break/>Care, tacticos la pasuri,<text:line-break/>Calc-nfipt pe lungi picioare,<text:line-break/>n acest concert de glasuri?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Nu! n inim-mi triete<text:line-break/>Cela ce conduce corul...<text:line-break/>Tainic simt cum bate tactul,<text:line-break/>i socot c e amorul.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pduri i cmpuri se-nvesmnt...</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Viaa</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 23 aprilie 1895</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pduri i cmpuri se-nvesmnt<text:line-break/>Cu flori,  s-a desprimvrat...<text:line-break/>Voioas ciocrlia cnt<text:line-break/>Sus, n vzduhul fermecat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Tresare inima-mi pustie<text:line-break/>Din toropeala-i de mormnt,<text:line-break/>i tu m faci, o! ciocrlie,<text:line-break/>S plng ncet, i trist s cnt...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ea-mi strig ginga din trie:<text:line-break/> ce tot ngni acolo-ncet?<text:line-break/> un cntec, drag ciocrlie,<text:line-break/>i-s ani de cnd l tot repet!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">l cnt pe cmpuri vara-ntreag,<text:line-break/>De mult durerea mi-l urzi,<text:line-break/>i chiar, o! ciocrlie drag,<text:line-break/>Bunica ta mi-l auzi!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n saloane de pictur... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n saloane de pictur<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vezi pe omul care-a vrut<text:line-break/>Ca s lupte cu bravur,<text:line-break/>narmat cu lance, scut...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Amorai ns-l rsfa,<text:line-break/>Pn&apos; ce-i fur scut i arm,<text:line-break/>i, cu lan de flori pe brae,<text:line-break/>El st drz, ei tot nu-l sfarm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Astfel lncezesc i eu,<text:line-break/>Cu tot focul tinereii,<text:line-break/>Iar alii lupt greu<text:line-break/>n rzboiul mare-al vieii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat prima oar n Viaa, 22 octombrie 1895</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cavalerul Olaf </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat prima oar n Epoca, 5 martie 1898</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I5"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Doi brbai de-un ceas ateapt<text:line-break/>La biseric, n poart;<text:line-break/>Rege-i unul, gde-i altul,<text:line-break/>Haine roii ambii poart.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/> Dup cum aud eu, slujba<text:line-break/>Cununiei e sfrit.<text:line-break/>Regele s-a-ntors spre gde:<text:line-break/> Stai cu barda pregtit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Org, clopote... Norodul<text:line-break/>D nval din catedral:<text:line-break/>Lung alai; n mijloc mirii<text:line-break/>Strlucind ies la iveal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Firav, nespus de trist,<text:line-break/>Fiica regelui privete;<text:line-break/>Vesel i seme e Olaf:<text:line-break/>Gura-i rumen zmbete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnd spre-ntunecatul rege<text:line-break/>Gura-i rumen-i ndreapt:<text:line-break/> Ziu bun, tat-socru!<text:line-break/>Moartea astzi, tiu, m-ateapt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Rege, pn la miez de noapte<text:line-break/>Mai amn-mi ceasul morii;<text:line-break/>Vreau s-mi vd banchetul nunii,<text:line-break/>Danul la lumina torii.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Las-mi viaa pn ce cupa<text:line-break/>Cea din urm voi goli-o.<text:line-break/>Las-mi viaa, las-mi viaa<text:line-break/>Pn la danul de adio!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Regele s-a-ntors spre gde:<text:line-break/> Viaa-i fie-ngduit<text:line-break/>Pn azi, la miezul nopii <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Stai cu barda pregtit!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II7"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">St Olaf la praznicul su nupial,<text:line-break/>E ultima cup, e ceasul fatal,<text:line-break/>Femeia lui st lng dnsul<text:line-break/>i-o-neac plnsul...<text:line-break/>Clul st la u.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Pornete viu danul, i, dornic-pgn,<text:line-break/>i-apropie Olaf soia la sn:<text:line-break/>Ei joac la lumina torii <text:line-break/>E danul morii...<text:line-break/>Clul st la u.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cum sun viorile viu i voios!<text:line-break/>Cum uier flautul trist i sfios!<text:line-break/>Privind pe-amndoi juctorii,<text:line-break/>Te prind fiorii...<text:line-break/>Clul st la u.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i Olaf, n vuiet, ngn nebun:<text:line-break/> Mi-eti drag, mi-eti drag<text:line-break/>Ct nu pot s-i spun,<text:line-break/>Nici inim nu-i s priceap <text:line-break/>E frig n groap...<text:line-break/>Clul st la u.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III4"/><text:soft-page-break/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Olaf, bate miezul nopii,<text:line-break/>i la moarte-acum te cheam!<text:line-break/>Tu pe fiica unui rege<text:line-break/>Ai iubit-o fr team.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Rugi clugrii ngn;<text:line-break/>Omu-n haina roe ine<text:line-break/>Barda-n mn i te-ateapt<text:line-break/>Lng negrul stlp, pe tine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Olaf vede zid de sbii,<text:line-break/>Vede torele cum pic <text:line-break/>Gura-i rumen zmbete,<text:line-break/>Vesel ochii-n sus ridic:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Binecuvntate fie!<text:line-break/>Ceruri, soare, lun, stele!<text:line-break/>Blnd popor de psrele<text:line-break/>Vesele ciripitoare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Binecuvntate marea<text:line-break/>i cmpia-mpodobit!<text:line-break/>Ochii ti frumoi, iubit,<text:line-break/>Viorelele frumoase...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ochi frumoi, ochi viorele,<text:line-break/>Numai voi mi-ai stins norocul,<text:line-break/>Binecuvntat i socul<text:line-break/>Unde mi te-ai dat tu mie!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Pe-o diminea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Epoca</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 31 mai 1898</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe-o diminea strlucit<text:line-break/>Trec prin grdin trist... auz<text:line-break/>Cum florile optesc, suspin...<text:line-break/>Eu ns rtcesc ursuz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se uit-n calea mea duioase,<text:line-break/>optesc ncet, suspin-ncet:<text:line-break/> mpac-te cu sora noastr,<text:line-break/>O, palid i-ntristat poet!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nimfele</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Floare-albastr</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 10 ianuarie 1899</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bat valuri plescind n rmul<text:line-break/>Pustiu, i luna-i sus, pe mare...<text:line-break/>Pe dun zace cavalerul<text:line-break/>Cuprins de lene visare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ies albe nimfe din adncuri,<text:line-break/>Un vl uor e a lor hain;<text:line-break/>Creznd c doarme dus voinicul,<text:line-break/>S-apropie de el n tain.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>ntia st, i-admir coiful<text:line-break/>Cu penele strlucitoare,<text:line-break/>A doua i-afl joc cu lanul<text:line-break/>i ciucurii la cingtoare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i, fulgernd din ochi, a treia<text:line-break/>i trage spada sclipicioas:<text:line-break/>Proptit-n spad mi-l privete<text:line-break/>i-i rde-n fa, drgstoas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A patra drgla s-alint<text:line-break/>Pe lng el, optindu-i glume:<text:line-break/> O, de-a putea s-i fiu iubit,<text:line-break/>Drag ft-frumos din alt lume!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A cincea minile-i dezmiard!<text:line-break/>A asea parc nu se-ndur,<text:line-break/>Sfios s-apleac i-l srut<text:line-break/>nti pe ochi, apoi pe gur...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">iret, el nu deschide ochii,<text:line-break/>Se simte-aa nespus de bine:<text:line-break/>Sub farmecul tcut de lun<text:line-break/>Se las rsfat de zne.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Solia</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Biete, sus!  arunc aua<text:line-break/>Pe cal, i-alearg-n zbor cu el<text:line-break/>Mai repede ca rnduneaua<text:line-break/>La craiul Duncan, la castel.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i-acolo-ateapt pn&apos; ce-i iese<text:line-break/>Din grajd, n cale, vreun argat<text:line-break/>i-ntreab-l: Care-ntre criese<text:line-break/>S-a logodit cu-adevrat?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-i spune: Cea cu negre plete,<text:line-break/>S-mi vii-napoi ct ai clipi...<text:line-break/>De-i spune: Cea cu blonde plete,<text:line-break/>Atunci, te rog, nu te pripi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Te du atunci n trg i cere<text:line-break/>Un treang, i vino-mi napoi<text:line-break/>n trap domol; pstrnd tcere,<text:line-break/>S urci ca s mi-l dai apoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat prima oar n Familia, 24 octombrie/5 noiembrie 1899</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Amurg</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe prundul splcit al mrii<text:line-break/>Stam solitar i dus pe gnduri.<text:line-break/>Mreul soare scpta azvrlind<text:line-break/>Pe ap vlvti de par,<text:line-break/>i albele talazuri<text:line-break/>De flux mbrncite<text:line-break/>Nvleau mai aproape i tot mai aproape,<text:line-break/>Spumegnd n ropot mereu...<text:line-break/>Un ropot bizar; un opot i-un plnset,<text:line-break/>Un hohot i-un murmur, un freamt i-un geamt,<text:line-break/>Pe-alocuri o muzic dulce de leagn<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Tresrind pe furi dintre valuri <text:line-break/>Prea c-ascult epopei disprute,<text:line-break/>Strbune poveti nzdrvane pe care,<text:line-break/>Copil, pe de rost le tiam pe vremuri<text:line-break/>Din rostul altor copii din vecini,<text:line-break/>Pe cnd ne strngeam, n amurguri de var,<text:line-break/>Pe scara de piatr,<text:line-break/>i toi ascultam tiptil i cuminte,<text:line-break/>Cu ochii mari i cu inima mic;<text:line-break/>Iar gingaele fete,<text:line-break/>Pe dup-nflorite glastre,<text:line-break/>Steteau peste drum, la ferestre,<text:line-break/>Rozalbe figuri zmbitoare,<text:line-break/>Btute de lun...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 15 iunie 1900</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Furtuna</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Turbeaz furtuna,<text:line-break/>D bice gloatei de valuri,<text:line-break/>i ele, spumegnd de mnie-n rscoal,<text:line-break/>Se-ncalec-n goan, urnind i-mbrncind<text:line-break/>Muni albi i mictori de ap:<text:line-break/>Micua nav-i suie<text:line-break/>Cu trudnic prip,<text:line-break/>Ci fr de veste-alunec<text:line-break/>n negre prpstii cscate...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, mare!... Mama Frumuseii,<text:line-break/>Din spum de val rsrite!<text:line-break/>Strbuna Amorului! Aibi ndurare!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ah, iat! alba ta rndunea<text:line-break/>Din aripi flfie fantastic,<text:line-break/>Setoas de prad,<text:line-break/>i-adulmec inima mea ce rsun<text:line-break/>De slava zeiei din tine nscut;<text:line-break/>Adulmec inima mea, jucria,<text:line-break/>Nepotului tu zburdalnic!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De-a surda implor!<text:line-break/>Dispare strigarea-mi n larma furtunii<text:line-break/>i-n tumultul de vnturi!<text:line-break/>Uraganul se sparge-n gigantic delir<text:line-break/>De sunete oarbe!<text:line-break/>Eu ns prind lmurit n auz<text:line-break/>O dulce-aiurire de harf;<text:line-break/>Un cntec m cheam rzbind slbatec,<text:line-break/>Nespus de duios, dureros de nespus,<text:line-break/>i glasul acesta-l cunosc...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Departe, pe rmul stncoasei Scoii<text:line-break/>Se-nal turnul castelului sur<text:line-break/>Dasupra nprasnicei mri;<text:line-break/>Acolo, subt arcul naltei fereti,<text:line-break/>Vegheaz o mndr femeie bolnav <text:line-break/>Ca umbra uoar, ca marmura alb, <text:line-break/>Ea cnt din harf i cnt din gur<text:line-break/>i vntul i flutur pletele-i lungi<text:line-break/>i-i spulber cntecul trist<text:line-break/>n largul furtunei, pe mare...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 15 iunie 1900</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Noaptea-n cabin </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Legnat ca-n vis de valuri<text:line-break/>i cu ochii ctre cer,<text:line-break/>Stau culcat ntr-un ungher<text:line-break/>Din cabina-ntunecat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Caut dus prin ferestruie<text:line-break/>Sus, la spuza cea de stele,<text:line-break/>Ochii dragostelor mele, <text:line-break/>Legnat ca-n vis de valuri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ochii dragostelor mele<text:line-break/>Stau deasupra mea de paz, <text:line-break/>Tot clipesc, tot scnteiaz<text:line-break/>Drgstos din bolt-albastr...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Astfel ctre bolt-albastr<text:line-break/>Mult vreme caut dus,<text:line-break/>Pn ochii dragi de sus<text:line-break/>Albe neguri mi-i acopr...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n coasta nvii, unde zac<text:line-break/>i-mi razem capul vistor,<text:line-break/>Izbind se frmnt slbatece valuri<text:line-break/>i murmur-ntr-una:<text:line-break/> Copil fr minte!<text:line-break/>Ai braul scurt i ceru-i departe,<text:line-break/>i stelele stau intuite de cer<text:line-break/>Cu inte de aur...<text:line-break/>Dearte dorine! Oftri dearte!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Mai bine-ai face s-adormi n pace...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Visai departe-n zare, un cmp pustiu i nins,<text:line-break/>Linoliu de omturi nemrginit de-ntins.<text:line-break/>i sub omtul rece, n fundul groapei reci,<text:line-break/>Dormeam uitat de veacuri n negura de veci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar sus, din cerul negru, deasupra groapei mele,<text:line-break/>Vegheau fr de numr frumoii ochi din stele,<text:line-break/>Frumoii ochi!  i dnii luceau biruitor<text:line-break/>n linite senin, i totui plini de-amor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T16">Publicat prima oar n </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T17">, 15 iunie 1900</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Srbtoare de primvar </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A primverii trist petrecere-a-nceput:<text:line-break/>Slbticita ceat de gingae fecioare<text:line-break/>Alearg-n aiurire, bocind rtcitoare,<text:line-break/>Cu snul gol, cu prul n aer desfcut:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T30"><text:tab/></text:span>Adonis! Adonis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pustie noapte cade. Pe umede crri<text:line-break/>S-afund-n ntuneric, trecnd cu tore-aprinse,<text:line-break/>i sperie tcerea pdurilor ntinse<text:line-break/>De-att suspin i plnset, i hohot, i strigri:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T30"><text:tab/></text:span>Adonis! Adonis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Pe iarb zace, palid i mort, un ft-frumos,<text:line-break/>l caut prin codri fecioare-ndurerate;<text:line-break/>Plng florile-mprejuru-i, i-s toate-nsngerate,<text:line-break/>Vzduhul tot se umple de vaier dureros:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T30"><text:tab/></text:span>Adonis! Adonis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 15 iulie 1900</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pe nouri luna strlucete... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe nouri luna strlucete,<text:line-break/>O uria portocal,<text:line-break/>Arunc peste marea sur<text:line-break/>Dungi sclipitoare de beteal.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe maluri rtcesc i-s singur,<text:line-break/>Se sparg la maluri albe valuri,<text:line-break/>i parc oapte dulci m cheam<text:line-break/>Din valuri ce se sparg la maluri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ah, noaptea e att de lung<text:line-break/>i inima-mi de dor se-mbat...<text:line-break/>Venii, jucai, frumoase nimfe,<text:line-break/>Cntai n hor fermecat!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A vrea s-adorm la snul vostru,<text:line-break/>Al vostru snt cu trup i suflet...<text:line-break/>Cntai s mor, zdrobindu-mi dulce<text:line-break/>Din suflet ultimul rsuflet!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 15 iulie 1900</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Vedenia</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-a desftat un vis frumos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i negrit de fioros:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e nc mintea tulburat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi bate inima speriat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M pomenesc ntr-o grdin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fantastic, de farmec plin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu multe flori n multe fee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neasemnate-n frumusee...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi ciripesc attea neamuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De paseri mici, sltnd pe ramuri;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mre se-ngn zorile,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stropind cu aur florile.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-mbat mndre buruiene,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adie vnturile-alene...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umblam i nu tiam anume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-s pe pmnt ori pe-alt lume.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mijloc sta o minunat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fntn-n marmur curat;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alturea, o fat dalb</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cltea mereu o pnz alb...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Obraji duioi; n ochi  un rai;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un chip de sfnt cu pr blai;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu tiu cum, dar mi-a pru&apos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strin, i-att de cunoscut!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoasa mea da zor, da zor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tot cnta fermector:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curgi, ap, curgi frumos i lin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i spal pnza mea de in!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre dnsa paii-mi abtui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntreb:  O, n-ai putea s-mi spui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Minune de copil dalb,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe seama cui speli pnza alb?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea repede-mi optete:  Iat-o</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cmaa morii i-am splat-o!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cum gri, cum ai clipi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca spuma totul se topi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-o slbatec pdure</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M pomenesc umblnd aiure:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Creteau copacii pn&apos; la cer,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-am stat uimit de-att mister...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ascult n adncimi, departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum uie-a pustiu i-a moarte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n deset urma mi se pierde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ajung ntr-o dumbrav verde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mijloc, subt un vechi stejar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dau de frumoasa fat iar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cum o vd, m ia fiorul:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea mnuia acum toporul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cioplea-n tulpin i-avnta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toporu-n aer, i cnta:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Topor micu, topor zglobiu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-i zor, s facem un sicriu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre dnsa paii-mi abtui</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntreb:  O, n-ai putea s-mi spui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Minune dalb de copil,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-mi tot ciopleti tu fr mil?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea repede-mi opti:  Zoresc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sicriul tu s-l isprvesc!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cum gri, cum ai clipi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca spuma, totul se topi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prgini, vetede cmpii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-atern n jur pustii, pustii...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu pricep cum s-a fcut:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stam aiurit, ctam pierdut...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pornesc ncet pe calea lung:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe vd o alb dung...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alerg spre ea, alerg  i, iat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dau iar de preafrumoasa fat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum o zresc, m prinde-ngheul:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea mnuia acum hrleul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prea un nger alb de paz,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui m umplea de groaz...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoasa mea da zor, da zor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tot cnta fermector:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai sap, drag hrle, mai sap,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S pregtim curnd o groap!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre dnsa palid m-abtui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ntreb ncet:  O, vrei s-mi spui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copil dalb, nger dulce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo cine-o s se culce?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea repede-mi opti:  Rmi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-am aternut de cpti.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-apuc vorba s sfreasc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i groapa fioroas casc...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cum privesc la ea, m-ntunec,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i m-nfior simind c-alunec</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe gura gropii, aiurit </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci din somn am tresrit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Din volumul Romane i cntece, 1901.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Belszar</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E noapte-ntunecat i ceasul e trziu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n Babilon domnete tcere i pustiu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus numai n palatul regesc e chef nespus:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cohorta lui Belszar benchetuiete sus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n sala triumfal ferestrele lucesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">St regele n frunte la praznicul regesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sclipesc n juru-i sclavii i sorb din cupe vinul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nflcrat ca focul i rou ca rubinul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ciocnesc din cupe sclavii cu urlete de bestii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Belszar afl farmec petrecerii acestii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci iat-l c s-aprinde slbticit la fa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci vinul vechi sporete pornirea-i ndrznea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pornirea-i mi-l orbete i-i rzvrtete firea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El spune vorbe grele, crtind dumnezeirea,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bleastem nprasnic n prada oarbei furii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urlau n hohot sclavii cnd el scrnea injurii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Semeul rege strig, semeul rege ip, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un servitor alearg i iar se-ntoarce-n prip,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Purtnd pe cap o tav cu multe-odoare sfinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sin templul lui Iehovah furate mai-nainte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nelegiuitul rege o cup sfnt-alege,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un sclav i umple cupa din mna sacrilege;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Belszar o ridic i pn-n fund o soarbe;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i hohot-n desfrul mniei sale oarbe;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iehovah, nu mi-e team de tronul tu nemernic:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n Babilon, Belszar e rege-atotputernic!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-abia rostise ns cuvntul plin de faim,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cuprins a fost Belszar de-o neneleas spaim.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ngrozitoul hohot a ngheat n sal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n urma lui se face tcere mormntal.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i uite!... uite-acolo! pe zidul alb deodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsare ca o mn, o mn minunat,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i scrie, scrie, scrie, n groaznica tcere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu litere de par pe zidul alb,  i piere...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Belszar vede totul cu mintea aiurit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe-obrajii lui cei palizi sta groaza-ntiprit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A sclavilor cohort a-ncremenit de fric:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici un cuvnt nu scoate, nici ochii nu-i ridic...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venir mai n urm, dar n zadar cercar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S tlmceasc rostul acelui scris de par.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar sclavii-n rzvrtire atunci au tbrt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i peste noapte fuse Belszar omort.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Din Romane i cntece, 1901</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:soft-page-break/>nchinare</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu trandafiri, cu aur i crngi de chiparos</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A vrea aceast carte s-o-mpodobesc frumos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca pe-un sicriu n care dorm cnturile mele...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, de-a putea iubirea s-o-ngrop aici cu ele!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odihna peste groapa iubirii nflorete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe urm-attui zbucium senin floarea-i crete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci numai pentru mine rsare prea trziu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea va-nflori cnd nsumi n groap am s fiu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aici sunt dar acele cntri, ce-odinioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca lava ce din Etna arunc foc i par,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zbucnir din adncul simirii-mi arztoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n jur mprtiar scntei fulgertoare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum pare c-s moarte, zac ngheate, mute,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i palide ateapt n negur pierdute.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar tresri-vor iari vii cnturile mele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd s-o abate duhul iubirii peste ele...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i inima-mi optete c vremea va s vie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acel duh al iubirii cu rou s le-nvie:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i va cdea n mn aceast carte-odat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, dulcea mea iubire din ar deprtat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci puterea vrjii, iubito, va-nceta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i palidele slove cu jale vor cta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ochii ti cei mndri, fcndu-te s tremuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">opti-vor melancolic poveti din alte vremuri...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>n vis... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vis vzui un om gtit, mic de statur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mergea cu pai de-o schioap pe labe rschirate;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Purta o hain nou i albituri curate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci rsrea-n lumin mojica lui fptur.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n fond era nemernic, meschin,  o strpitur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe dinafar, ns  cu mult demnitate;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rzbuntor i ano, trntea cuvinte late,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ifos fr margini vorbind despre bravur.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">tii cine este? Vino i-l vezi! zmbind mi spune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu viclenie Zeul stnd naintea mea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i magica-i oglind sub ochii mei o pune.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd un altar i-n fa-i stetea piticul famen,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu draga mea alturi; rostir ambii: Da!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mii de draci strigar rznd cu hohot: Amen!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">N-am mpotriva ta nimica... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-am mpotriva ta nimica, chiar de-a nnebuni de jale.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe veci pierduto! n-am nimica, nimic n-am mpotriva ta:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orict de mndr-n strlucire ta de diamante-ai arta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu vei putea s-arunci o raz n noaptea inimioarei taie...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">tiam de mult. n vis, odat, vzui viaa ta ursit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui i noaptea-ntunecat ce inima i-a fost robit-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui i vipera ce muc ascuns-n inim-i, iubito,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-am neles, pe veci pierduto, ct eti de mult nefericit!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dac eti nefericit, nimic n-am mpotriva ta;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubito, soarta blestemat vrea ca s fim nefericii!...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn&apos; ce tot zbuciumul acestor nebune inimi va-nceta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubito, soarta blestemat vrea ca s fim nefericii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci vd eu zmbetul ironic pndind prilej ca s zbucneasc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd ochii ti mrind cu ciud fulgertoarele lumine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vd pornirea de orgoliu ce face snul tu s creasc </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui eti nefericit, nefericit, ca i mine!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n preajma gurei tale totui durerea tremur-n netire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De lacrimi tinuite-n umbr i-s ochii mpinjenii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i snul tu superb ascunde o ran fr lecuire </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubito, soarta blestemat vrea ca s fim nefericii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Din basme vechi... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din basme vechi o alb mn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te cheam fluturnd n zri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-auzi cntnd o mndr zn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De peste nou mri i ri...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea cnt despre-o-mprie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fantastic din soare-apus:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flori mari, necunoscute ie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo strlucesc nespus...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toi arborii acolo sun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnt parca-ar fi un cor:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca muzic de dan rsun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sonore glasuri de izvor,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i doine dragi, cum niciodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu n-ai mai auzit, socot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te leagn i te desfat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn&apos; ce te farmec de tot.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, dac-ai ti-ncotro anume?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo cum ai vrea s pleci!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S uii durerile din lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-acolo s rmi pe veci!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mndra asta-mprie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-apare n somn adeseori;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, ca o negur pustie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se stinge totdeauna-n zori!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Frumos e pe lume... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P28"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumos e pe lume i-n cer e senin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vntul adie agalnic i lin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i rd fericite cmpiile-n floare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tremur-n roua btut de soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i tot veselie, i-i tot srbtoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui spre groap dorina m poart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-adorm lng tine, mireasa mea moart!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Socoata vremii... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Socoata vremii-n ore, minute i secunde, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntiul ornic,  cine l-a nscocit? Rspunde!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fost un singuratec, un suflet trist, pustiu...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n nopile de iarn sta i-asculta, trziu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum oarecii se mic prin umbr de unghere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cariul ritmic toac n tainica tcere...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar srutarea, cine mi-a nscocit-o-n lume?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O gur fericit i dornic de glume...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea sruta cu sete; era n luna mai.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Natura-ntreag parc se preschimbase-n rai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n rai cu flori frumoase i ciripire vie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i soarele-n vzduhuri rdea de bucurie!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntecul lui Pan </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Gottfried Keller</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Smntorul, an. III, nr. 39, 26 septembrie 1904</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Brae-n brae stau stejarii n pdurea secular.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Azi, fiind cu voie bun, vechiul cntec i-l cntar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A-nceput departe-n margeni cel mai tnr s s-alinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i un freamt i un clatin s-au pornit apoi-nainte:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alerga un vajnic ropot, se umflau bogate valuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vrtejul printre vrfuri se rostogoli pe dealuri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar acum cnta-n coroane, uiera-n vzduh furtuna,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn-n rdcini de-a valma duduia trosnind ntr-una.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd i cnd huia stejarul cel mai nalt din cretet, falnic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Codru-n cor ntreg pe urm rspundea vuind nvalnic!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mndru joc era, asemeni unei mri cnd se revars,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alb se btea-n sclipire frunza spre nord-est ntoars.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tata Pan fcea doar nsui vechea ceter s sune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nvnd copiii, codri, melodiile, strbune.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i din cele apte tonuri ce cuprind n ele toate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntecele, vechiul meter ce minuni de cntec scoate!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tinerii poei i cintezi stau i-ascult n tcere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pitulai n tufe dese sorb cntarea cu plcere...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vntul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Adevrul literar, 30 septembrie 1896</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe, n strini plecam...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privii n urma mea pierdut;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spunnd ceva mi-a aprut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubita, sus, la geam.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea mi-a trimis un blnd cuvnt </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tovars bun pe drum pustiu...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ce mi-a spus, nu pot s tiu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C s-a pierdut n vnt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dac n-oi mai ntlni-o,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, vnt slbatec, ru ce-mi eti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu i-e de-ajuns?... S-mi mai rpeti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cel din urm-adio?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Prevestire</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Nikolaus Lenau</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dup-atta ger, ce dulce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bate vntul pe cmpii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un copil zdrenos mi-aduce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Viorele timpurii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dureros e ca salutul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gel dinti al primverii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l primeti tu chiar din mna</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Umilit a mizerii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar a zilelor frumoase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mbucurtoare veste,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd mi-o d nenorocirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mie mult mai scump-mi este:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel, suferina noastr</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Generaiei ce vine</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i aduce blnd solia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unor vremuri mai senine.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Surugiul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Nikolaus Lenau</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vraja dulcei nopi de mai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stpnea afar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus, de-argint pluteau blai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nori de primvar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-auzeai pe lunci i vi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici un glas s sune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur umbla pe ci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Raza blondei lune.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Molcom fremta abia</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numai vntul serii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre a nu trezi cumva</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pruncii primverii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Chiar i tainicul izvor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc amuise,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s crue-a florilor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parfumate vise.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cornul su la gur-atunci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Surugiul pune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-l fcu prin vi i lunci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vesel s rsune.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sunau cei patru cai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sprinteni din copite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce prin nfloritul rai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ropoteau grbite.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i prea c trec n zbor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i alearg toate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Speriind n goana lor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Linitea din sate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd, prin raiul ce-l zrim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum strbatem, iat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr veste-un intirim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochilor s-arat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidul mohort sttea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sprijinit de stnc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crucifixul sfnt veghea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus, n jale-adnc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Surugiul domolind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dintr-o dat trapul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus, la crucifix, privind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trist ntoarce capul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri, mria-ta, de-oprim,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ns n-am ce face:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Colo, sus, n intirim</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un tovar zace.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de cte ori m-ntorn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M neac plnsul:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimeni nu suna din corn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai frumos ca dnsul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de cte ori revin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe-aste locuri iari,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trebuie s-i cnt puin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bunului tovar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctre intirim deci el</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cornul i-l mbie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l aud-n somn acel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aipit sub glie;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-un att de dulce zvon</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dintre stnci ptrunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parc mortul postilion</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din mormnt rspunde.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Repede porni la drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Goana cea nebun:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tnguiosul corn i-acum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n auz mi sun...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Clar de lun </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Smntorul, 23 decembrie 1907</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup Li Tai-pe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lng patul unde stau</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bate luna pe podele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu tiu luna bate, sau</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A czut omt pe ele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fruntea mi-o ridic, privesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luciul zrilor dearte;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fruntea-mi cade i gndesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trist la ara mea departe...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Excelsior! </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T24">de </text:span>Henry Wadsworth Longfellow</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Spre sear, printr-un stior</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din Alpi, un tnr cltor</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Trecea purtnd prin nea i vnt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un steag cu-acest strin cuvnt:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sub geana-i ochiu-ntunecos</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sclipea ca paloul tios,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i, ca din corn de-argint, senin,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Suna cuvntul cel strin:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Lumini de prin bordeie, rar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bteau n fa-i, i, bizar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Ghearii-n noapte strluceau,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i straniu buzele-i opteau:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> <text:span text:style-name="T21">E un prpd n muni acum! </text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">l sftuiete-un mo pe drum </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Prul e ivoi turbat...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El murmur ne-nduplecat:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> <text:span text:style-name="T21">O, vin&apos;, o fat i-a optit,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La pieptul meu, pribeag trudit!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n ochi-albatri-nlcrimai</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Privete-oftnd, nal-un bra:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> <text:span text:style-name="T21">O, nu intra-n brdetul des,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Lavinele n drum i ies!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i strig-n vale un pstor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El pas drept, nepstor:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-n zori, cnd clopotul din schit,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Vibrnd sonor i lmurit,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe frai la rug i-a chemat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Din stele-un glas a rsunat:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cinele-a descoperit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un pelerin ntroienit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe pieptul su un steag  drept scut </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu-acel cuvnt necunoscut:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i tainic mortul surdea</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Spre soarele ce rsrea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i mndru, ca o stea cznd,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Czu din cer un strigt blnd:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Excelsior!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vntul dimineii </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Henry Wadsworth Longfellow</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un vnt s-a ridicat strignd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe mri: Voi, neguri, dai-mi rnd!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nierilor, pe nvi, le-a spus:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Matrozi, e-n zori! La pnze, sus!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lumea mare s-abtu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al deteptrii ceas btu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Intr n codri: Vijii!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Micai toi ramii nflorii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atinse aripe uoare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi ciripii, dragi cnttoare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cocoii, prin ogrzi, trezi:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vestii! s-a luminat de zi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">opti pe cmp, prin grai de aur:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Desfur al tu tezaur!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Intr n turn vijelios:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, clopote, sunai voios!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar atingnd morminte reci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">opti: Dormii, dormii pe veci!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vestitorul biruinii de la Maraton </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Richard von Meerheimb</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">(29 septembre 490 a. Chr.)<text:line-break/>Am biruit, brbai atenieni!<text:line-break/>HERODOT</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Clduros i nobil, cu putere crescnd.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Akropolis!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, sfnt cetate de zei,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cum te nali aurie-n adncul nopii albastre<text:line-break/>i mi vesteti de departe, mre,<text:line-break/>C am ajuns,<text:line-break/>Am ajuns, n sfrit!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Cdei acum, genunchi slbii,<text:line-break/>Sfrii de goana ndelung.<text:line-break/>nete-acum iroi de purpur<text:line-break/>Din pieptul meu rnit de moarte!<text:line-break/>O clip numai druii-mi suflet,<text:line-break/>O zei, nemuritori,<text:line-break/>S le vestesc atenienilor!<text:line-break/>Elada e liber!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zdrobit e pumnul perilor<text:line-break/>Ce amenina s-o puie-n jug,<text:line-break/>i-i mnuit ara grecilor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Cu glas puternic.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ascult-m, crunt portar! Deschide!<text:line-break/>D-mi drumul ntre zidurile-Atenei,<text:line-break/>Aduc biruina,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Aduc biruina de la Maraton!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz. Sfirit, dar cu inim.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Monege, mulumesc. D-mi umrul<text:line-break/>i sprijinete-m n ceasul morii.<text:line-break/>O-nghiitur nc, sunt topit de sete,<text:line-break/>Uscat mi-e cerul gurei de praf i de ari, <text:line-break/>i-acum, din rsputeri rsun,<text:line-break/>Rsun, scutule, izbit de spad,<text:line-break/>Trezete-mi Atena din somn!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Strignd.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Aici, aici, ceteni! Sculai-v!<text:line-break/>Trezii din somn femeile, copiii!<text:line-break/>Aici! Aici!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz. Vesel, micat.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, iat! Gloata zgomotos alearg,<text:line-break/>Minat de voioasa presimire,<text:line-break/>i umple strzile!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Refuznd cu dragoste.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Lsai, lsai, iubiilor, avei rbdare,<text:line-break/>Nu fiecruia n parte,<text:line-break/>Poporului vreau s-i vestesc<text:line-break/>Cum au czut copiii lui i  au nvins!<text:line-break/>Elad sfnt, te apr nc<text:line-break/>Pallas Atena,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mai oelete nc puterea lui Hercule,<text:line-break/>Al grecilor bra!<text:line-break/>Mai bate inima argonauilor<text:line-break/>n pieptul Eladei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cci, fr glum, suflet de erou<text:line-break/>i trebuie cnd vezi nvlind,<text:line-break/>Ca valuri aprinse de aur topit,<text:line-break/>Cumplita armat a dumanului <text:line-break/>De unsprezece ori zece mii <text:line-break/>S-i ii tu piept cu zece mii!<text:line-break/>i groaznica flot-a barbarilor oare<text:line-break/>Nu cotropise de jur mprejur<text:line-break/>Cu armele marea ce prea c este<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Spinarea cu solzi monstruoi<text:line-break/>A unui crocodil uria,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ce crete i se-ntinde spre apus<text:line-break/>Din rmurile Asiei Mici,<text:line-break/>Cscndu-i gura lacom,<text:line-break/>Ameninind Elada?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Cu putere crescnd.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zdarnic ameninare! narmai, sltar copiii Minervei!<text:line-break/>Pe scuturile lor se rsfrnse n flcri<text:line-break/>Ruinea etern-a barbarilor cruni <text:line-break/>Eubea strig, Eretria rspunse.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz. Sfrit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Iertai, prini cinstii ai cetii,<text:line-break/>Slbatica aprindere a mniei,<text:line-break/>Ci amintirea faptei colosale</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">mi umple iari sufletul de-avnt<text:line-break/>i-mi nbuete fiorii reci ai morii!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Rstimp. nviorat.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Pharul acesta  mulmesc <text:line-break/>M face s bnuiesc nectarul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">ie-l nchin, eroul cel mai de frunte al Atenei,<text:line-break/>ie-l nchin, Miltiade!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Miltiade, el a fost, ndrzneul,<text:line-break/>Cel ce,-narmat cu scutul zeilor,<text:line-break/>A smuls din anuri mica noastr ceat<text:line-break/>i-o arunc n cmp deschis,<text:line-break/>Nvalnic, contra puterei de fier a perilor!<text:line-break/>(Cu un gest.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Privii, v rog, btrni prini,<text:line-break/>Spre miaznoapte, unde din Kytheron<text:line-break/>Coboar valea, lung, strmtorat-ntr-una<text:line-break/>De Penos i Penthelikon,<text:line-break/>Cum se deschide-apoi spre es<text:line-break/>La Maraton.<text:line-break/>De-aici vedeai sclipind,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n vuietul ndeprtat de valuri,<text:line-break/>Norii de pnze ai flotei barbarilor,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i lng rm, pestriele corturi<text:line-break/>Ale lui Datis, cpetenia mezilor,<text:line-break/>i-ale tovarului su de arme, Hippias,<text:line-break/>Cel care-a fost tiran odat al Atenei,<text:line-break/>Azi  trdtor de patrie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i iat, cnd Eos cu obraji trandafirii<text:line-break/>Cretea din spuma de valuri,<text:line-break/>necnd n lumina-i vioaie<text:line-break/>Cuprinsul adnc ce vuia de arme,<text:line-break/>Pluteau presimiri de moarte n aer:<text:line-break/>Alei suntei de Styx,<text:line-break/>O, voi, copii ai Aticei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>(Cu nobil avint.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ci vechiul avnt spre jertf-al Eladei<text:line-break/>nflcr din nou ceata aleilor:<text:line-break/>Barbarii drji clcau n picioare<text:line-break/>Al Greciei suflet frumos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(nsufleit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, suflet de viteaz, tu, Miltiade!<text:line-break/>Tu ai fost care, plin de-nelepciune,<text:line-break/>Ai cumpnit, i slbiciunei noastre<text:line-break/>I-ai dat putere uria,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Tu, care ai silit colosul perilor<text:line-break/>S-i strng-aripele ca vulturul rnit,<text:line-break/>Tu, care ai mpins napoi<text:line-break/>ndrzneul potop de clri,<text:line-break/>Silindu-i s rmn pe loc,<text:line-break/>nghesuii, cu sabia-n teac:<text:line-break/>Cci slabele noastre aripe,<text:line-break/>Ferite de muni i copaci rsturnai,<text:line-break/>ngrdeau orice atac din afar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Beat de amintiri, vesel i cu energie.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Atunci, deodat, sunar cimbale i-oboaie<text:line-break/>i, vjind, npdi pe es<text:line-break/>O mare de arme!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar noi n-adstarm nvala furtunii;<text:line-break/>Ca i marinaru-ndrzne ce s-arunc</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu capul n jos n slbatecul clocot<text:line-break/>Al apelor!<text:line-break/>Astfel i noi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Repede, nsufleit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n semicerc, n muni,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n pas de atac, netiut pn-atunci,<text:line-break/>Aa nvlea stnga i dreapta,<text:line-break/>nainte i drept n zidul de sulii,<text:line-break/>De lnci i scuturi ale dumanului<text:line-break/>Plin de uimire!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-n stnga i-n dreapta, i-n dreapta i-n stnga<text:line-break/>oviau aripele perilor,<text:line-break/>oviau  se-ndoiau  se plecau  alergau!<text:line-break/>Fugeau ca antilopele iui de picioare,<text:line-break/>i noi, luptnd din greu cu grindina<text:line-break/>De lnci i sgei,<text:line-break/>Noi dup ei  spre mare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Cu spaim.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar miezul otirii, slbit de tot,<text:line-break/>Dei purtat de mndrii viteji<text:line-break/>Temistocle i Aristide,<text:line-break/>Nu mai putea s in piept nvalei<text:line-break/>Ce ca un orcan l izbea<text:line-break/>Din mijlocul falangelor dumane,<text:line-break/>Strpungnd inima grecilor<text:line-break/>Cu mciuci ghintuite!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>(Pauz.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Un vaier strbate pn la aripi.<text:line-break/>Helenii biruitori aud<text:line-break/>Cum strig fraii lor ajutor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Brusc ncetar goana, i atunci,<text:line-break/>Ca dou clete de fier, uriae,<text:line-break/>Ce se-nconvoaie s prind prada<text:line-break/>i-o strng ntr-o cumplit-mbriare,<text:line-break/>Astfel, deodat se vzu barbarul<text:line-break/>Apucat din ceaf,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-n dreapta i-n stnga drumul nchis<text:line-break/>Spre portul mntuitor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz. Cu gesturi hotrte.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Otirea greceasc i vine n fire,<text:line-break/>Uoarele lnci se-ntorc nainte,<text:line-break/>Al dumanului hohot se schimb-n prohod,<text:line-break/>i spadele uier, ghioagele trosnesc,<text:line-break/>Falange fugare se sfarm-ntre ele,<text:line-break/>i clrimea rpede-a pusiului</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Se spulber spre mare, ca nisipul!<text:line-break/>(Cu pornire crescnd.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">La flot! Toi, la flot! se aude<text:line-break/>Zadarnica strigare a perilor.<text:line-break/>Ci-n stnga i n dreapta fiii grecilor<text:line-break/>Opresc nvala spre rm,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i-n lupta crunt moartea se-nmiete,<text:line-break/>i fierbe, roie, ntunecat,<text:line-break/>Albastra Mare Ionic!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Mndru, triumftor.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Trofeele i corturile, ale noastre!<text:line-break/>Cirezile de dromaderi i elefani,<text:line-break/>ncrcate cu comorile Rsritului,<text:line-break/>Cu perle i podoabe, ale noastre!<text:line-break/>i Datis, capul perilor, mort!<text:line-break/>Mort, trdtorul Hippias,<text:line-break/>necat n mocirl!<text:line-break/>Mori pn la zece mii de barbari!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n portul Pireu se oprete<text:line-break/>Podoaba semea a galerelor,<text:line-break/>ncrcat de grelele lanuri<text:line-break/>Pe seama noastr furite,<text:line-break/>Ducnd i blocul de marmor<text:line-break/>Ce trebuia s rmie<text:line-break/>Monument al ruinii noastre,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Acum stlp de ruine-al nfrngerii lor!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz mai lung. Slbit de tot.)<text:line-break/>De-acum am sfrit!<text:line-break/>Btile slabe ale inimei mele<text:line-break/>mi spun c mi-s numrate clipele.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Pauz. Elegie, plin de melancolie.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>i-acum o dat nc, dulce vnt,<text:line-break/>Ce-adii uor dinspre pdurea sacr,<text:line-break/>Ca o chemare din Eliseu,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mai amintete-mi farmecul vieii,<text:line-break/>S mai respir o dat aerul Greciei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Cu mna-ntins, nflcrat de adinc dragoste.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nu, mam-mam, scump, bun mam,<text:line-break/>Nu te-arunca, bocind, n genunchi!<text:line-break/>Eu am adus cea mai frumoas veste!<text:line-break/>Eti mama unui fiu viteaz,<text:line-break/>i Hellas liber!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">(Sfrit, frnt i totui nsufleit.)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ce-mi pas de aci nainte<text:line-break/>De lumea pmnteasc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">D-mi mna ta, d-mi mna, dulce mam,<text:line-break/>i-aaz-m cu faa,<text:line-break/>Ridic-mi faa,<text:line-break/>Cuprins de sudoarea morii,<text:line-break/>Spre locul unde noi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ne-am ctigat nemurirea,<text:line-break/>S pot privi murind<text:line-break/>Spre cmpul de biruin al Eladei,<text:line-break/>Spre Maraton!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Vzui marea cea mare la rmul mrii<text:line-break/>Cnd tatl meu m-a dus acolo<text:line-break/>S facem sare.<text:line-break/>De voi muri pe mare</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i de m-or azvrli n apa-adnc,<text:line-break/>Veni-vor chiii lacomi,<text:line-break/>Vor nota n preajm-mi i vor ntreba<text:line-break/>Care din ei s-nghit leul<text:line-break/>Ce cade ctre fund?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Eu nu voi auzi.</text:p>
