   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup Multatuli</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Smntorul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 27 iunie 1904</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui marea cea mare la rmul mrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd tatl meu m-a dus acolo</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S facem sare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De voi muri pe mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de m-or azvrli n apa-adnv,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Veni-vor chiii lacomi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vor nota n preajm-mi i vor ntreba:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care din ei s-nghit leul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce cade ctre fund?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu voi auzi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui arznd csua lui Pa&apos;ansu, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El nsui puse foc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-a fost ieit din mini.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De voi muri n flcri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cdea-vor brne-aprinse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe leul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-afar vor fi ipete grozave</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De oameni cari arunc ap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s omoare focul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu voi auzi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui cznd pe micul Si-unah din pom, </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El culegea un rod al pomului</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l duc maicei sale.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De voi cdea din mrul cel nalt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zcea-voi mort lng tulpina lui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca Si-unah,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar mama nu va plnge, ea e moart,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci alii vor striga cu glasul aspru:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Uitai-v, Sadjah e mort!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu voi auzi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui mort pe Pa-lisus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El s-a fost stins de btrnee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Albite-i erau pletele.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De voi muri btrn, cu plete albe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Veni-vor bocitoarele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n jurul meu;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M vor boci ca bocitoarele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe Pa-lisus, i toi nepoii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ei, vor plnge cu amar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu voi auzi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu tiu unde am s mor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vzui atia mori n satul meu:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">I-a-nvemntat n haine albe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-apoi i-au cobort n groap.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De voi muri acas i m-or ngropa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La capul satului, spre rsrit, pe deal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo unde iarba crete-nalt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adinda va veni, i haina-i de mtase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ncet, ncet de tot, o s ating</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n treact iarba-nalt..</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i eu voi auzi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Husarii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un tropot - trmbia rsun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cresc nourii de praf treptat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Husarii sunt! Ei vin n goan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-au ordin ca s mie-n sat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Abia sosii aici, spre sear,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai patriei aprtori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bucurie, dar i team</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cuprinde pe locuitori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici bucuria lor, nici teama</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poate nate din senin:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt chipei, buni biei, husarii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar... cam rvnesc la bun strin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia seama, fata mea, la toate </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">optete mama serioas </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cumva s nu cltoreasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreun lucru mai de pre din cas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odat&apos; cu zorile, husarul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E treaz, i toi srind pe cai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dau pinteni, sun de plecare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dispar departe peste plai.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu o durere negrit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se uit fata dup ei:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumoii ochi noat-n lacrimi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oftnd se umfl pieptul ei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ce eti, fata mea, tu trist?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vorbete: ce s-a ntmplat?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, mam, a plecat husarul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i inima el mi-a furat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Mugur, mugur, mugurel... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n oraul sta am deschis eu ochii;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Salutare, locuri mndre, scumpe mie!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Doina doicei mele din copilrie</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sun-n tot oraul: doica-mi cnt mie?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Glasul ei e-acesta? ori poate m-nel:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A plecat, odat, un copil voios,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Azi, btrn, se-ntoarce tot pe-aceeai cale...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Hei, de-atunci ce mult e... griji, necazuri, boale,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Bucurii puine, i atta jale!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cum mai trece vremea... trist ngn el:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Oare unde suntei, tovari de joc?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">D-a vedea pe unul barem dintre voi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S mai stm de vorb, veseli amndoi,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">S ne rentoarcem anii napoi,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Anii cei de basme, s cnt iar cu el:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Fr de hodin, pasre pribeag</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Care-i cat cuibul cald de-odinioar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd se-ntoarce iar mndra primvar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Gndul meu colind, pretutindeni zboar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i m mir eu singur cte-mi spune el:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sunt copil acuma, iari sunt copil!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe-o nuia ncalec... lumea e a mea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Sare i necheaz murgul meu  nuia,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Merg la jgheab, devale, i i dau s bea...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Hii, murgu, n lume, zboar rndunel...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cltinat rsun clopotul din turn,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Calul, clreul cad de oboseal...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">E-n amurg... acas doica m ia-n poal...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Aipesc, i visuri mndre m nal;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Doica m alint, cnt-ncetinel:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mugur, mugur, mugurel!...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">n tind am intrat... </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Povestea vorbei, 10 octombrie 1896</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n tind am intrat o clip</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S iau crbune pentru pip...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fi luat, desigur, focul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ea ardea, bat-o norocul!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ardea ea, pipa, de minune...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La ce intrai atuncea? Spune!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Intrai, cci am zrit n cas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O fat... i era frumoas!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sufla n foc ca s-l aprind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i flacra btea n tind...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar mai cu seam-n ochii ei...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce flacr juca n ei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea m privi aa ciudat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nct simeam c-s fermecat...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i iat... pipa mea s-a stins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar inima mi s-a aprins.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">La marginea satului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Publicat n Povestea vorbei, an. I, nr. 6, 14 noiembrie 1896</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lng sat e-o grl mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crma, sus, pe mal apare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ferestruiele-n lumin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-oglindesc n unda lin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E trziu i noaptea-i sumbr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luntrea st proptit-n umbr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Neclintit st la stn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cumpna de la fntn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar n crm-i vuiet mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De imbal i de vioare!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Geamurile iuie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i flcii chiuie:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crmri, drag, hi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ad vin bun la flci!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vechi ca mou-meu, colea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zvpiat ca mndra mea!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zi, mi cioar, din vioar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C m-mbt n ast-sar!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zi, m!... c-i pltesc s-mi zici:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vroi s crp jucnd aici!...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bate cineva-n fereastr:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-avei cumpt dumneavoastr?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Hai, destul cu-atta larm,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C boierul vrea s doarm!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieie-l dracu, n-am ce-i face!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, potaie, d-ne pace!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zi, m!... iaca numa-n ciud,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zi-i, ncalte s ne-aud!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cineva la geam iar bate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai ncetinel se poate?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Maica mea aa v roag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C, srmana,-i greu beteag...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stau flcii, nu rspund,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toi beau vinul pn-n fund;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Muzicei fac semn s tac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i, frumos, acas pleac...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Planuri de prisos </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Adevrul ilustrat</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 23 decembrie 1896</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Toat calea ctre cas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-un gnd am petrecut-o:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce s-aduc eu mamei scumpe?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce de mult n-am mai vazut-o?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd cu drag ea va deschide</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Braele, eu ce s-i zic?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ales cuvnt acelei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce m legnase mic?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi venir sumedenii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De gndiri frumoase-n minte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vremea parc se oprise...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Carul doar fugea-nainte...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-am intrat n casa mic...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mi zbur n brae mama:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mut... i atrnam de buze...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum de vreji atrn poama.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Departe</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">St departe-n plaiul Dunrii cel mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O csu alb, nencptoare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochii mei noat-n lacrimi de cin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd mi vine-n minte mica locuin.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dac-a fi rmas acolo pn&apos; la moarte!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar pe om l poart tot dorini dearte...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aripe de vultur cnd ntinde dorul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimenea nu poate s-i opreasc zborul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sta pierdut mama-n dezndjduire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd ceream srutul ei la desprire.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, nici pn astzi lacrimele-i nc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-au putut s stng jalea ei adnc!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tremurnd ntins-a braele i plns-a</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S rmn acolo linitit, cu dnsa.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De vedeam atuncea toate-aa de clar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ar fi plns, srmana, poate, n zadar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A speranei noastre stea strlucitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne arat basme fermecate-n zare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numai cnd zrim pustiul dinainte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne trezim plngnd din basmul ce ne minte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">C pe mine tot un vis frumos, nebun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-a purtat n lume, trebuie s spun?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i c lumea singur de cnd o strbat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mii de ghimpi n cale m-au nsngerat?...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">...Pmnteni se-ntorc n ara mea frumoas:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce s-i spun mamei de-or ajunge-acas?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spunei-i, prieteni  drumul de v este</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe la pragul nostru  spunei bun veste...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nobil</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La scar l-au ntins, pe ticlos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l bat, cci a fost nelegiuit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci a minit, i a furat, i dracul tie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce ruti i crime a svrit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar el se mpotrivea mereu, strignd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu v-atingei voi de trupul meu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci n-avei dreptul sta, dup lege...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt nobil eu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai auzit, voi, duhuri strmoeti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acest cuvnt, aceast provocare?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-acum nici n-ar mai trebui btut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci dus d-a dreptul la spnzurtoare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Eroi n zdrene </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mbrac n haine pe msur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n rime mndre versul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S poat mai uor strbate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Azi prin saloane,  pot i eu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci gndurile mele sfinte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-s tineri lenei cari se-mbrac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mod, n mnui i fracuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cari triesc ca s petreac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Azi spada nu mai zngnete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i puca ruginit doarme.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar e rzboi!... n lupt ns</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Slujesc idei n loc de arme.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo stau i eu n lupt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntre soldaii stui veac!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu lupt cu versuri: un rzboinic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E orice cntec care-l fac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ostai n zdrene, dar eroici,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dintr-nii la nici unul nu-i...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vitejia face cinstea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unui osta, nu haina lui!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nu m-ntreb eu: dup moarte-mi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tri-vor cntecele mele?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S piar, de li-i scris, n lupt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu nu m ngrijesc de ele.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar sfnt-i cartea unde-or zace</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ideile-mi de mult uitate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mormnt d-eroi care murir</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lupta pentru libertate!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un vis</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P41">Iubesc cum nc om pe lume<text:line-break/>N-a fost n stare s iubeasc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubita mea e sfnt, mare,<text:line-break/>Dar nu-i fiin pmnteasc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iubesc o zeie exilat<text:line-break/>Din cer, i-n veci o voi iubi:<text:line-break/>E libertatea. Dar, durere!<text:line-break/>n vis numai o pot zri.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n versurile mele ns<text:line-break/>Mi-apare falnica iubit.<text:line-break/>Chiar ast-noapte-a fost cu mine<text:line-break/>ntr-o grdin nflorit.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ngenunchind i-am spus iubirea-mi<text:line-break/>i m-am plecat s rup o floare<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Ca s i-o dau  o mic jertf...<text:line-break/>Atunci  cu spada sclipitoare </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">La spate-mi apru clul,<text:line-break/>i capul meu czu trunchiat...<text:line-break/>n mini chiar mi czu, i dnsei<text:line-break/>n loc de floare i l-am dat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Stelelor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu v-am cntat att de-adesea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu drag, n versurile mele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i v mai cnt i astzi nc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scnteietoare stele!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O lume mai frumoas parc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fgduiete raza voastr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i v iubesc c-mi tot surdei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">din deprtarea-albastr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i drag mi-e s privesc de-a pururi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo unde mai exist</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puin veselie nc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe lumea asta trist!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Poezii alese, 1897</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Zdrnicia</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zdrnicia-i rege peste regi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Palatul ei e largul lumii-ntregi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cutreier palatu-n lung i-n lat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nimic nu las ea necercetat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unde merge... toate se desfac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se prbuesc i pier... n juru-i zac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Coroane sparte, tronuri sfrmate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flori vetejite, inimi sfiate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Poezii alese, 1897</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un nelept odinioar </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P33"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un nelept odinioar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe un mgar cltorea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar vremea este schimbtoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i lumea s-a ntors pe dos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mgarii azi umbl clare...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un nelept merge pe jos.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Poezii alese, 1897</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Sunt catan </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am slujit n oaste i am fost catan,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici cprar n-am fost eu, ci mereu catan.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mndra tineree-n oaste mi-am lsat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cu btrneea m-am ntors n sat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi fceam corvada, stam la toate gata,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-am luat pedeaps un minut mcar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar, la liberare, care mi-a fost plata?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M-a btut pe umr domnu ghinrar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Poezii alese, 1897</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ap beu! </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Privii la mine, oh, prietini,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i v crucii de fapta mea:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La noi aa minune mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cam rar s-a mai putut vedea!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-aa ceva</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M mir i eu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar adevrului m-nchin:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu vin... ci ap beu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Da, ap beu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">M ntrebai, nu cumva oare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O grindin a dat prin vii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori frigul a stricat recolta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i viile-au rmas pustii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, nu! cci vin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ct tiu eu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fost st an destul i bun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui... ap beu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Da, ap beu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori m nvinuii voi, poate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C nu-s setos? Aceasta-i grav!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe dracu! Dimpotriv, setea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">M arde n gtlej grozav.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i chiar de vin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Setos sunt eu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i totui... ap beu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe Dumnezeul meu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ca s nu v doar capul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-atta ce v minunai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">V lmuresc eu ntr-o clip</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aceast tain. Ascultai:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E mnios</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crmarul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Parale n-am, nici credit n-am...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-aceea... ap beu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-aceea, zeu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Poezii alese, 1897</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Luntraul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I6"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Soarele de mult vreme s-a ascuns n asfinit,<text:line-break/>Obosii de munca zilei, toi luntraii-au adormit.<text:line-break/>Dorm luntraii n colib i e linite adnc,<text:line-break/>Numai tefan Sila singur n-a nchis nici ochii nc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/> tefan Sila, o-ntrebare vreau s-i pun, rspunde-mi drept:<text:line-break/>Obosit eti tu, i totui pentru ce rmi detept?<text:line-break/> La aceast ntrebare eu rspund numai att:<text:line-break/>Dragostea mi-alung somnul i mi ine de urt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Luminoas era noaptea. tefan Sila desfcea<text:line-break/>De la rm luntrea lui mic, dup ce srea n ea,<text:line-break/>Apuca n mn vsla i, plutind uor pe ape,<text:line-break/>Ct clipeti, intra-n ostrovul care nu-i pru aproape.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cci acolo, n mijlocul Dunrii, insula mic,<text:line-break/>Vesel ca o grdin nflorit, se ridic,<text:line-break/>ns floarea cea mai mndr n al insulei hotar<text:line-break/>Este tnra copil a btrnului pescar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n coliba lui srac, tolnit pe uba-i mare,<text:line-break/>Doarme tatl ei; moneagul sforie destul de tare;<text:line-break/>Iar tnra copil a pescarului btrin,<text:line-break/>Stnd pe rm, cu drag ateapt pe al inimii stpn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnd ajunse mndrul tinr, de-i sri iubita-n drum,<text:line-break/>Bucuria ntlnirii n-a fost proast nicidecum.<text:line-break/>Mai nti se srutar dar mai bine tac din gur:<text:line-break/>Lumea e clevetitoare i pornit ctre ur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cel mai stranic vin nu face ct srutul m<text:span text:style-name="T29">n</text:span>drei fete!<text:line-break/>Un srut al ei e-n stare, ca prin farmec, s te-mbete,<text:line-break/>Pare-mi-se i lui Sila mintea i se tulburase,<text:line-break/>De-i venea s spuie-ntr-una vorbe-aa de curioase:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Lidi, Lidi, drag Lidi, tu-mi eti singurul tezaur!<text:line-break/>Porumbia mea cea alb, petiorul meu de aur,<text:line-break/>Floarea mea de nestemate, steaua mea strlucitoare<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pn-n zori de zi alung-mi grijile cu-o srutare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Blnd albastra ta privire genele o adumbresc,<text:line-break/>i precum, fr de veste, nourii se risipesc,<text:line-break/>Deschiznd frumoas zare de albastru luminos,<text:line-break/>Ca i steaua n albastru arde ochiul tu frumos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De s-ar mpleti-n cunun florile din lumea toat,<text:line-break/>Dragostea s mi-o cuprind n-ar ajunge niciodat,<text:line-break/>Cci e mai nemrginit dect lumea asta-ntreag,<text:line-break/>i a ta e toat, drag!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Da, e mai nemrginit dect lumea asta mare,<text:line-break/>ns dragostea ta, drag, tot aa s fie oare?<text:line-break/>Nu cumva s-ajungi vreodat la al dragostei hotar,<text:line-break/>Cci atunci amar de mine i de amindoi amari</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Doarme-un uria acolo, pus de dragoste drept paznic,<text:line-break/>Este patima mea oarb uriaul cel nprasnic:<text:line-break/>Cum ajungem noi acolo, se deteapt, i apoi<text:line-break/>Ne sfie p-amndoi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Mult vreme-i povestir cte-n lun i n soare<text:line-break/>Din tufi suna in preajm cntec de privighetoare,<text:line-break/>Unii spun c n-a fost cntec de privighetoare poate,<text:line-break/>Ci era doar numai imnul inimilor fermecate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n sfrit, se desprir. i luar bun rmas<text:line-break/>Dup ce se-mbriar Fata se ntoarse-acas,<text:line-break/>Promind c-o s-l atepte noaptea viitoare iari.<text:line-break/>Tnrul se-ntoarse vesel n colib, la tovari.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>n inutu-ntreg domnete acum linite deplin,<text:line-break/>Luna palid, frumoas, spre apusu-i se nclin,<text:line-break/>Ruda carului din ceruri e-ndreptat spre apus,<text:line-break/>Licrete-n miezul-nopii cloca i cu puii, sus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">E trziu de tot, i hanul barcagiilor e-nchis,<text:line-break/>Zuitat de vnt zvoiul doarme adncit n vis,<text:line-break/>Nu s-aude doar un zgomot: cnd i cnd un molcom val,<text:line-break/>opotind, atinge barca ce se leagn la mal.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Este trg de sptmn; spre ora n sus pornete<text:line-break/>Azi pescarul, i n barc duce la vnzare pete.<text:line-break/> Vrei s vii cu mine, drag? o ntreab el pe fat.<text:line-break/>Fata grabnic i rspunde:  Dac vrei tu, drag tat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Astfel la ora plecar tatl, fata, mpreun<text:line-break/>Hei, de n-ar fi fost chiar vineri! Ziua asta n-a fost bun.<text:line-break/>Se ducea ntia oar la ora frumoasa fat,<text:line-break/>D-aia nu-i plcu lui Lidi ziua asta niciodat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">ns vlmagul, larma negrit din cetate<text:line-break/>O fcur ca s uite i de grije, i de toate,<text:line-break/>Chipei domniori venir, ca-ndeobte, prin pia,<text:line-break/>i-ncepur s glumeasc cu fetia cea istea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zise-un domnior cu faa palid i zmbitoare,<text:line-break/>Stnd alturea de dnsa:  Unde te-ai nscut tu, floare?<text:line-break/> Nu-i departe, zise Lidi, locul unde m-am nscut<text:line-break/>n ostrovul mic, devale, dac-i este cunoscut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Zise-atuncea domniorul:  Minunat! Ce bine-mi pare,<text:line-break/>C i eu sunt tot din partea locului. Dar o-ntrebare<text:line-break/>Spune-mi mie, mndr fat, ai ibovnic? Dac ai,<text:line-break/>Uit-l; dac n-ai, atuncea dar pe mine nu m vrai?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Dac am sau nu ibovnic, Lidi i-a rspuns degrab,<text:line-break/>N-am s dau eu socoteal, despre asta, cui m-ntreab.<text:line-break/>ns dac vrea s afle domniorul i oricine:<text:line-break/>Snt ignci cari dau cu bobii i ghicesc din cri mai bine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Deci se duse domniorul. i plcuse mult fetica,<text:line-break/>ns la rspunsu-i neted nu a mai rspuns nimica<text:line-break/>Totui, inima de fat fr de prihan nu-i:<text:line-break/>Lidi mai privi o dat, pe furi, n urma lui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dup vreme-ndelungat<text:line-break/>Lidi sta pe rm, odat;</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Flori slbatice n preajm-i o fceau i mai frumoas,<text:line-break/>Mna ei mic i alb harnic mpletea o plas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Soarele-notnd n aur scpata ctre apus<text:line-break/>i vopsea tufiurile cu un colorit nespus:<text:line-break/>Cnd cu rou, cnd cu galben; i pe<text:span text:style-name="T29"> </text:span>Dunre-ntindea<text:line-break/>Aurita lui perdea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Lidi aprea-n lumin ca o zin din poveste<text:line-break/>Cnd un zgomot se aude n tufi, fr de veste.<text:line-break/>Cine este? Cine vine? E un chipe vntor.<text:line-break/> Bun seara, puiculi; ce lucrezi cu-atta zor?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Cine are ochi s vad, vede! dac nu, ce-mi pas?!<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Pi nu vede domniorul c stau i-mpletesc la plas?!<text:line-break/>Astfel fu rspunsul fetii, fr-ncunjur i hain,<text:line-break/>i pi de ea aproape vntorul cel strin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zise vntorul mndru:  Ce mai bobocel de fat!<text:line-break/>Trandafir fr de ghimpe s-a mai pomenit vreodat?<text:line-break/>Vd eu c eti tot cea veche, nu te-ai mai schimbat de-atunci;<text:line-break/>Vorba, ochii ti, ireato, fac n suflet rni adnci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar tu m cunoti pe mine? Nu cumva i-aduci aminte<text:line-break/>C ne-am ntlnit odat i-am vorbit, mai nainte?<text:line-break/>La un trg de sptmn ne-am vzut i am vorbit<text:line-break/>Adu-i numai bine-aminte, ngeraul meu iubit</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i rspunse-atuncea Lidi:  Poate, nici eu nu zic ba,<text:line-break/>C m-a ntlnit vreodat domniorul undeva.<text:line-break/>Dar nici faa dumisale nu mi pare-aa podoab<text:line-break/>Ca s-o vezi o dat numai i s n-o mai uii degrab!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Astfel, n-apuca s-i pun vntorul o-ntrebare,<text:line-break/>Cci, la toata vorba, fata nu i rmnea datoare.<text:line-break/>Totui, vntorul tnr nu simea de fel mnie<text:line-break/>Ctre fata asta mic, i hain, i hazlie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar nici nu luase seama, tlcuind la vorbe-alese,<text:line-break/>C ncet, pe nesimite, neagra noapte se-ntinsese.<text:line-break/> tii tu, drag, zise-atuncea vntorul prefcut,<text:line-break/>C de vreme ce e noapte, drumul nu mi-e cunoscut?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Singur i strin, vezi bine, e ngrozitor, copil<text:line-break/>ns tu eti fat bun, i o s te nduri de mil.<text:line-break/>Vrei s-mi fii tu cluz pin la zvoi afar,<text:line-break/>Ori chiar pn la mine-n cas? nu-i aa departe doar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Lidi se gndi o clip i i zise-apoi n sine:<text:line-break/>Domnul sta, orice-a zice, a grit frumos cu mine;<text:line-break/>Blnd, cu inima deschis i att de cuviincios,<text:line-break/>Cum s fiu cu el mojic dac s-a purtat frumos?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Pentru lumea asta-ntreag nu pot s m port mojic!<text:line-break/>Zise Lidi hotrt, adic era s zic.<text:line-break/>i pe urm zise tare, cu un glas tremurtor,<text:line-break/>Aintind cu ochii limpezi pe frumosul vntor:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Eu cluzesc pe domnul, s pofteasc dar cu mine,<text:line-break/>ns chiar pn acas, nu, cci nici nu se cuvine;<text:line-break/>Pin la marginea pdurii pot s te cluzesc<text:line-break/>Cci pe seama unei fete cte nu se iscodesc?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i plecar. Se ntoarse singur la rm copila<text:line-break/>Acolo, de mult vreme, o ateapt tefan Sila.<text:line-break/> Te atept de mult vreme, unde-ai fost, drgua mea?<text:line-break/>Lidi nu tiu degrab s rspund cum vroia.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nu-i plcu lui tefan Sila nicidecum rspunsul dat,<text:line-break/>Lidi n aceast sear se purt foarte ciudat,<text:line-break/>Tresrea la orice vorb i prea ngndurat<text:line-break/>i o neagr bnuial l cuprinse-atunci ndat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Hei, i bnuiala este un copil care se nate<text:line-break/>Din nimic, fr de veste, la-nceput nu se cunoate,<text:line-break/>ns e flmnd, e lacom, n-are saiu niciodat,<text:line-break/>Si cnd e hrnit, se schimb n dihanie turbat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Ce fcu deci tefan Sila? Chiar n seara urmtoare<text:line-break/>S-a ascuns la pnd-n tain Stnd acolo-n ateptare,<text:line-break/>Singur nu tia ce-nsamn teama asta, nerbdarea<text:line-break/>Atepta numai s vad ce aduce ntmplarea.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nu trecu prea mult vreme, iac vine vntorul<text:line-break/>Ea se mpotrivea la vorb, el o ia cu biniorul,<text:line-break/>Lidi-l asculta sfioas, toat roie ca mrul,<text:line-break/>i simi odat Sila cum i se zburlete prul.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">De-ar fi fost atta numai! Vorbe dulci, spuse n glum,<text:line-break/>Dar acuma vntorul ctre fat se ndrum,<text:line-break/>O cuprinde, o srut se nmldie copila<text:line-break/>Mii de iaduri rzvrtite fierb in sufletul lui Sila.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Sare-n sus i d nval ctre domnul aiurit:<text:line-break/> Uciga, ho, gde, diavol, ticlos, nelegiuit!<text:line-break/>Astfel i bai joc tu, cne, de o dragoste? Ateapt!<text:line-break/>i smulgnd din bru cuitul, ctre dnsul l ndreapt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">O, de-ar fi ajuns cuitul, drept la inim intise!<text:line-break/>Dar din puc scut fcndu-i, vntorul se ferise<text:line-break/>Iute-apoi cu patul putii, ct ai zice un cuvnt,<text:line-break/>l izbete-n cap pe Sila i-l lungete la pmnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Cnd i-a revenit in fire, se ridic binior,<text:line-break/>Caut in dreapta,-n stnga nu e nici un vntor,<text:line-break/>Nu-i nici Lidi.. parc-ntrase n pmnt i st mirat,<text:line-break/>Nu-i aduce bine-aminte i se pare c-a visat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar c n-a fost vis acesta se ncredin-n curnd,<text:line-break/>Cnd simi pe fruntea-i rece sngele cald picurnd<text:line-break/>n nebuna lui durere ncepu atunci a plnge,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i splar lacrimile faa lui scldat n snge</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4">IV</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zilnic vntorul mndru prin ostrov i face drum,<text:line-break/>i pe Lidi fr grij o mbrieaz-acum.<text:line-break/>Nu mai are nici un duman de acuma de temut:<text:line-break/>tefan Sila, ca prin farmec, dispruse din inut.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">n durerea lui cea mare, tefan Sila pribegise;<text:line-break/>Unde rtcete oare, alungat de negre vise?<text:line-break/>Turburarea-i sufleteasc fu puternic uragan<text:line-break/>i l azvrli departe pe luntraul meu srman</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Pribegi fr odihn, fr s cate-n urma lui,<text:line-break/>Pnce se trezi odat n adncul codrului.<text:line-break/>Se opri atunci acolo, i n codru secular<text:line-break/>Se trnti la rdcina unui uria stejar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Acolo a stat, dar numai trupul lui avu odihn,<text:line-break/>Sufletul, rnit de moarte, nu putea s aib tihn,<text:line-break/>Trupul lui era ca iazul, sufletu-i ntr-nsul pete <text:line-break/>Iazul st, petele-n ap neoprit se zvrcolete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Am s fiu tlhar de codri, s ain la oameni calea,<text:line-break/>n spnzurtori, pe urm, poate o s-mi mntui jalea.<text:line-break/>Cnd voi atrna acolo ntr-o bun diminea,<text:line-break/>O s-mi fie ceasul sta cel mai fericit din via!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i se pironi in largul drumului n ateptare,<text:line-break/>Atepta s-i cad-n palm vreun boier cu stare mare,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Un boier care s poarte bani ati n portofel<text:line-break/>Ct curaj i vitejie-n inim avea i el.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Nici nu trebui s-atepte pn s i se urasc,<text:line-break/>Patru armsari n goan aduceau ntr-o caleasc<text:line-break/>Pe un boier. Mndr caleasc, i ce telegari voinicii<text:line-break/>Surugiu, fecior pe capr, n vestminte cu panglici.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Stai pe loc! cu mna-ntins tefan Sila le rcnete.<text:line-break/>S mai fac o micare cine moartea i-o dorete!<text:line-break/>ns nu-i veni n minte dor de moarte nimnui,<text:line-break/>i cu toii nghear tresrind la vorba lui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Se apropie de dnii, i lu la cercetare,<text:line-break/>Strnse frumuel toi banii ce-i gsi prin buzunare;<text:line-break/>Ca un ho care se simte, ca un vrednic, bun tilhar,<text:line-break/>Nu le mai ls n pung nici s bea un vin mcar.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Hai, pornii! strig pe urm tefan Sila mndru. Hei!<text:line-break/>Stai pe loc! strig el iari i s-apropie de ei.<text:line-break/>Vizitiul chiar plesnise biciul, gata de plecare<text:line-break/> Nu-s nscut eu ho de codru, ca s prd la drumul mare!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ia-i, boierule, toi banii! numr-i, c nu te-nel.<text:line-break/>Tremurnd stetea boierul i privea mirat la el.<text:line-break/>Nu tia ce s mai cread i nimic nu-nelegea,<text:line-break/>i zicea: Poate tlharul numai s glumeasc vrea?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar Sila-i dete banii, nu tia el s glumeasc,<text:line-break/>Fluiernd apoi ntoarse spatele ctre caleasc<text:line-break/>i porni ducnd cu sine, fr gnduri, fr int,<text:line-break/>Sufletu-i cuprins de ciud, inima-i de jale frnt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Ct vreme rtcit-a i-a btut cale pustie,<text:line-break/>Unde-a fost, n care parte? Sila singur el nu tie,<text:line-break/>Cnd o dat se trezete, prin al ntmplrii joc,<text:line-break/>Chiar la Dunre acas, i, mirat, se oprete-n loc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Vede hanul i coliba i se uit-n preajm-i dus,<text:line-break/>Toate parc-s neschimbate n lumina din apus,<text:line-break/>Insula  de ceea parte  se rsfa n tcere<text:line-break/>i ofteaz tefan Sila n adnca lui durere:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Lidi, Lidi, drag Lidi, cum de-ai fost neltoare?<text:line-break/>Ci, srman fat, poate plngi acum i ru i pare,<text:line-break/>Poate i-ai bocit iubitul, care nu poate uita,<text:line-break/>Cci a suferit atta numai din pricina ta!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dac ai clcat credina ce-mi jurai cu lacrmi sfinte,<text:line-break/>Uit eu cele ntmplate de acuma nainte.<text:line-break/>Fii tu numai cumsecade, i pe tine te cinstete,<text:line-break/>Cci uor poate s ierte inima care iubete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Astfel zise el i sprinten puse mna pe lopat, <text:line-break/>Dup ce sri n barc,  vrnd s plece-acu ndat.<text:line-break/>Spre ostrov, s-i vad mndra i s-i spun bietei fete<text:line-break/>Toate cte i spusese singur el, pe ndelete.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar abia vsli o dat, se ntoarse napoi:<text:line-break/> Hei, luntraule, ascult, poi s ne atepi pe noi?<text:line-break/>C i noi dorim s trecem peste ap chiar acum,<text:line-break/>O s ai o bun plat dac faci acelai drum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ct p-aci s cad Sila, apucat de ameeal,<text:line-break/>Se uit la dnii bine, i pru c se nal.<text:line-break/>Dar dei erau departe amndoi i nserase,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>El recunoscu pe Lidi i p-acela ce strigase.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Oerit, cu faa ntoars, atept deci tefan Sila<text:line-break/>Pn ce coborr-n luntre vntorul i copila.<text:line-break/>Hei, dar cnd se pomenir cu luntraul fa-n fa,<text:line-break/>Galbeni amndoi ca ceara; inima  un sloi de ghea!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">tefan Sila sta la crm i vslea cu brbie.<text:line-break/>Ei tceau, cuprini de spaim Cine ar putea descrie<text:line-break/>Chinul ce-i muncea acuma p-amindoi? Stteau ca mui,<text:line-break/>Nu tiau cum s nceap vorba i priveau pierdui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Molcom sta i tefan Sila, dar vslea nencetat,<text:line-break/>Insula cretea din cea, apa plescia-necat,<text:line-break/>ns cnd vzu c barca nu mai e de rm departe,<text:line-break/>Repede-i veni n fire i-o crmi n alt parte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Unde? ntreb atuncea domniorul speriat.<text:line-break/>napoi?  O, nu, rspunse tefan Sila aezat.<text:line-break/>Numai pn la mijlocul Dunrii; departe nu-i.<text:line-break/>Am cu voi o socoteal: acolo am s v-o spui!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i abia rosti acestea, ncepu iar s vsleasc;<text:line-break/>Luntrea luneca greoaie, valul ncepea s creasc.<text:line-break/>Cnd sosi aici, departe arunc lopata-n ap,<text:line-break/>i-aezndu-se-ntr-o parte, zise rar, ca s-l priceap:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> tii voi, dragii mei, un lucru? Nu mi-e drag viaa mie,<text:line-break/>i e numai vina voastr c mi-e inima pustie,<text:line-break/>A pleca pe ceea lume ca s nu mai viu napoi<text:line-break/>Mi-e urt s plec eu singur o s m-nsoii i voi!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Zice i pe loc rstoarn barca dintr-o smncitur.<text:line-break/>Apa nvli setoas, cteitrei n ru czur,<text:line-break/>El cuprinse-atunci n brae pe iubita-neltoare,<text:line-break/>S-o mai strng nc-o dat lng piept, mcar cnd moare.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">ns cnd bg de seam c ncepe s noate<text:line-break/>Domniorul, c noat bine i-o s scape poate,<text:line-break/>l ajunse-not i-l prinse strns in brae, ca de fiar,<text:line-break/>i luptar mpreun pn ce se cufundar.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Trei feciori </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i a zis btrnul tat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiului celui mai mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care-i nlase calul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sta gata de plecare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoate eaua, las murgul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu pleca acum, copile</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe btrnul tu printe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrei tu s-l omori cu zile?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ns fiul i rspunse:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tat, vreau s plec n lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n rzboaie sngeroase</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-mi ctig un mare nume!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i srind pe murgul sprinten,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu picioarele n scri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A plecat peste hotare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-a pierit n negre zri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a ntors acas murgul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur st n faa porii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Necheznd prelung, aduce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vestea-ngrozitoare-a morii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde i-a lsat stpnul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Grea urgie l-a ajuns:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A czut n btlie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De o lancie strpuns.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i a zis btrnul tat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Celuilalt mai mic fecior,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care-i nlase calul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-atepta nerbdtor:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scoate eaua, las murgul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu pleca acum, copile</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe btrnul tu printe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrei tu s-l omori cu zile?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar feciorul i rspunse:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tat, trebuie s plec,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreau s strng comori i-n urm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr grije s petrec.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i srind pe murgul sprinten,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu picioarele n scri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A plecat peste hotare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Disprnd n negre zri.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a ntors acas murgul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Singur st n faa porii;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Necheznd prelung, aduce</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vestea-ngrozitoare-a morii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde i-a lsat stpnul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-a ajuns o grea urgie:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu tlhari pe drumul mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El a prins tovrie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-o noapte, cu tlharii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sta n inima pdurii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-mprea comori furate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-au nconjurat pandurii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prins, l-au pus s putrezeasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-o umed-nchisoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i apoi, ca s-l usuce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sus, ntr-o spnzurtoare.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ctre fiul cel din urm</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bietul tat se ndreapt:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du-te-acum, i tu, n lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea te cheam, te ateapt.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Du-te de-i ctig nume</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i comori o, pleac iute</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe btrnul tu printe</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Las-l morii singur du-te!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar feciorul i rspunse:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tat, eu rmn cu tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Glorie, comori de-a pururi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu m-ademenesc pe mine.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici gndirea mea nu zboar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dincolo de sat, departe.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tat, eu rmn cu tine,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numai moartea ne desparte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-a inut fgduina,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-a rmas acas-n sat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fr glorie i-avere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A trit ndestulat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doarme-n cimitir alturi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu iubitul su printe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cea mai frumoas floare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le-nflorete pe morminte.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Profeie</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Sndor Petfi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, mam, zici c visurile noastre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ni le trimite Atoatetiutorul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C visu-i o fereastr fermecat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin care ne surde viitorul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Visai i eu un vis, iubit mam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un vis frumos... Mi-l lmureti tu mie?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Visai azi-noapte c-mi crescuse aripi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i am zburat cu ele-n venicie!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copile, tu lumina vieei mele!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luceafr blnd al sufletului meu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fii vesel, vesel, c-i fgduiete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ndelungate zile Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">...Crescu biatul  mare i puternic:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din pieptu-i tnr izbucni deodat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Slbateca vpaie-a tinereii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n inim-i gemuse-nctuat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">El prinde harfa i izbete-n strune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dus n extazul sfnt al inspirrii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simirea lui  mre vultur  plutete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n lumea larg pe-aripa cntrii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se-nal pnla porile triei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al cntecului glas naripat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Desprinde stelele din cer s-ncununeze</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu raze fruntea lui de inspirat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar e venin a cntecului miere;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu fiecare cntec smuls din strune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El pierde-o floare din cununa vieii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nc-o zi din viaa lui apune...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se schimb-n iad simirea-i arztoare;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se mistuie, dat flcrilor prad;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un singur ram din arborele vieii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cea din urm frunz st s cad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo, zace-acum pe patul morii.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilul suferinii... Biata mam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nebun de durere, plnge-n hohot...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El, ca prin vis, aude cum blesteam:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu mi-l rpi din brae, moarte hd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-mi stnge, moarte, steaua vieii mele!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, visul i menise multe zile...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori visele, atunci, ne mint i ele?!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu minte, mam, visul, niciodat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La groap numai lutul mi-l petreci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar numele poetului triete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i va tri mereu  n veci de veci...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat n Floare-albastr, an. I, nr. 9, 6 decembrie 1898.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Thogrul i strjerul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Saadi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odat, cnd, pe-o noapte furtunoas,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Thogrul trecea pe lng-un biet strjer</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i la vzut n bunda-i zdreneroas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum zgribura, nvineit de ger,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i zise, cci era milos din fire:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am s-i trimit pe loc o hain groas.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zicnd aa, cu inima-mpcat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Intr-n palatu-i plin de strlucire:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo ns-i rsri n prag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Soia lui, fptur minunat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care-l primi zmbind cu-atta drag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nct uit fgduiala dat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum uit i pe strjer i gerul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ia aminte tu ce-a zis strjerul:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A zis:  O, rege, tu m-ai dat uitrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci ai dormit n raiul desftrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai dus-o noaptea ntr-un vis plcut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i pas noaptea mea cum a trecut!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-i pas caravanei care scap</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-aceia ce-n nisip i afl groap!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un blnd noroc te leagn n somn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ai cluz bun i eti domn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu te oprete dealul, valea, nu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La cei rmai gndeti vreodat tu?...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De pe cmila-nalt ct un munte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simi tu ce-i valea grijilor mrunte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Voi, cari, sub cald poclit, trii ca-n cer,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndii la cei ce-n frig i foame pier.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Albina</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, an. VIII, nr. 4, 24 octombrie 1904.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T19">Thogru</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">= un principe al turcilor (</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">n.a</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">)</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Sfat n pustie </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup Saadi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dormeam odat n pustiul mare,<text:line-break/>Furat de visul unei nopi senine,<text:line-break/>Dar cluzul de cmile vine,<text:line-break/>M scutur din somn, i-mi strig tare:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sus i la drum! gtete-te degrab,<text:line-break/>C vremea trece, vremea nu te-ntreab,<text:line-break/>i ceasul de pornire bate-acum!...<text:line-break/>Ori poate vrei s mori rzle pe drum?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Hei, sunt trudit i eu, i de-ar fi chip<text:line-break/>A mai dormi mcar i eu oleac,<text:line-break/>Dar caravana pleac,<text:line-break/>i vai,  o mare larg de nisip <text:line-break/>Pustiul fr de hotar se pierde<text:line-break/>i ce departe este oaza verde!</text:p>
   <text:list xml:id="list2535915330" text:style-name="L7">
