     <text:p text:style-name="P57"/>
    </text:list-item>
   </text:list>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:line-break/>Tu care dormi cu zmbetul pe buze<text:line-break/>i nu asculi de glasuri cluze,<text:line-break/>Trezete-te, fii gata de plecare,<text:line-break/>C, uite, se urnete caravana...<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Auzi departe, mai departe-n zare<text:line-break/>Ce vesel rsun darabana!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i-acela care cel dinti pornete<text:line-break/>i nu se las mbiat, firete<text:line-break/>C i ajunge cel dinti la el...<text:line-break/>De-aceea zic: e fericit acel<text:line-break/>Ce i-a urcat desagii n spinare<text:line-break/>C-un ceas chiar mai-nainte de plecare,<text:line-break/>Cci ce folos c tresrim n vis<text:line-break/>Cnd mna morii ochii ne-a nchis?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Albina</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 24 octombrie 1904</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Mnua</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Friedrich Schiller</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n faa grdinii sale cu lei,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cnd gata-i s-nceap lupta de fiare,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">St regele Francisc pe tron.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n preajm-i stlpii coroanei,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i de jur mprejur, pe naltul balcon,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cunun de mndre femei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i la un semn s-a deschis colivia,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i grav, n aren, un leu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i poart mndria</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i caut mut, de jur mprejur,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cscnd fioros.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i scutur coama-ncurcat</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i se ncovoaie o dat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Apoi se culc jos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i regele d un semn iar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i prin poarta cealalt</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Un tigru slbatic salt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cum vede pe leu, rcnete</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i n cerc, fricos, l nconjoar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu limba-ncordat-n afar,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu coada vlvoi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i sforie turbat, furios</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i mrie drz, apoi</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se culc alturea, jos.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i craiul mai d un semnal,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i pe dou guri colivia</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Stupete doi leoparzi deodat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei cad furtunatici, cu lcomia</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De lupt-ndrznea,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Pe tigru nval,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Acesta turbat i nha</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu laba-ncruntat,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar leul n sus</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se-nal urlnd, i toi s-au supus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>i tac mbufnate,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n cerc ntinse,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De setea sngelui aprinse</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Felinele nfricoate.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Atunci, din balcon</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cade-o mnu din mini delicate</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">ntre tigru i leu, la mijloc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar Cunigunda-n btaie de joc</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se-ntoarce spre cavalerul Delorges:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> <text:span text:style-name="T21">De-i este amorul aa de aprins</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i vrei s mi-o dovedeti dinadins,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ei, ad-mi atunci mnua de jos!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cavalerul pornete n prip,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Coboar-n arena ngrozitoare</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu pas apsat, ndrzne,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i dintre fiare</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Smucete mnua c-un gest de dispre.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i cu uimire, cu groaz,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cavaleri i nobile dame</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Se grmdesc s-l vaz.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i el, linitit, aduce mnua-napoi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Curtenii prind s-l aclame.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar Cunigunda jubileaz,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Norocu-i rde n ochii vioi:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Ce ginga zmbete, primind pe viteaz!...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">El, mndru, i-arunc mnua-n obraz:</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"> <text:span text:style-name="T21">Rsplata, doamn, n-o mai vroi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i pleac, fr s cate-napoi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Copila din strini</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Friedrich Schiller</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Traducere de tefan Octavian Iosif</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntr-un ctun, pe la Florii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venea n orice primvar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu cele dinti ciocrlii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O mndr, tainic fecioar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea nu era nscut-n plai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu se tia de unde este,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i urmele i le pierdeai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La desprire, fr&apos; de veste.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n sfnta ei apropiere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era atta-nsufleire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar o noble, o putere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O-ndeprta de iscodire.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Venea cu fructe i cu flori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le aducea din deprtare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din cmpii cei mai roditori,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De rou plini i plini de soare,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu drag le mprea apoi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unuia fructe  altuia flori:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrni n crji i juni vioi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mergeau spre cas zmbitori.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toi erau binevenii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cnd s plece din ctun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea dete darul cel mai bun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unei perechi de-ndrgostii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat prima oar n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Viaa</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 12 martie 1895</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>La o ciocrlie </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup Shelley</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Salut, zei a cntrii! Cci pasere nu poi s fii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, care, plin de simire</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin viersu-i miestrit din fire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Reveri din bolile triei aa voioase melodii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntocmai unui nor de par mai sus i tot mai sus te-avni:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n adncimile albastre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rsuni dasupra lumei noastre,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tot cntnd te urci ntr-una, precum urcnd ntr-una cni.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n slava soarelui ce-apune scldat n valuri aurii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te legeni tu, fermectoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btnd cu drag din aripioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Asemeni unei ideale, nermurite bucurii.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Plutind prin purpura-nserrii, te pierzi i nu te mai zrim;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum piere steaua cnd o-nghite</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lumina zilei strlucite,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar eu i-aud, ca i-nainte, recitativul tu sublim;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum n amijit de ziu luceafrul ne-apare ters.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ndeprtata-i scnteiere.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dei se stinge din vedere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne urmrete mai departe, urmndu-i calea-n univers,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot astfel cntecele tale triumf pe pmnt i-n cer,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum din norul ce-o ascunde,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lumina lunei blnd ptrunde</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-nsenineaz firmamentul n noaptea plin de mister.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ce-a putea s te asamn? Nu plou norii aurii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd rde curcubeu-n zare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai vesele mrgritare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca ploaia trilurilor tale armonioase i zglobii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum n lumea-i ideal poetul cnt solitar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Smulgnd superbe-accente lirii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sdete-n snul omenirii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fiori de temeri i sperane de cari ea nici n-avea habar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum o nobil fecioar, n turnul vechiului palat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrjit de iubirea-i cast,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnt dorul la fereastr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ceasuri de singurtate visnd subt cerul nstelat;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum un licurici spre sear, cnd roua proaspt-a czut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu licritul lui eteric</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atrage ochii-n ntuneric,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, adumbrit de flori i ierburi, rmne totui nevzut;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Precum, n adieri uoare, un trandafir mbobocit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-alint risipind pe drumuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ameitoarele-i parfumuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nct, rotindu-se mprejuru-i, tlharul zboar buimcit;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici ropotul primvratec pe dmburi verzi curgnd pru,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici frunzele fonind vioaie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nviorate dup ploaie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nmic nu-i falnic i zburdalnic i limpede ca versul tu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce tainice simiri te-nspir, o! pasre sau heruvim!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntm noi vinul i iubirea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar unde este fericirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dumnezeietilor avnturi ce ne cuprind, cnd te-auzim?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntrile de biruin i corul nostru nupial</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ling imnurile tale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt scncete pustii i goale:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simim n cntecele noastre un nu-tiu-ce lipsind fatal.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci spune-mi, de-unde-i ia izvorul i zborul glasul tu divin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din care cer? Din care valuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fnee, cmpuri? vi sau dealuri?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce dragoste de tine nsi? Ce netiin de-orice chin?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci n etern veselie tu viaa toat o petreci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici umbra grijii-ntunecate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n veci asupr-i nu s-abate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubeti, dar patima iubirii nu poi s o cunoti n veci I</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aievea sau visnd tu, poate, vezi alt lume dect noi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cunoti secretul morii poate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i le pricepi mai bine toate </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum ai cnta altminteri oare aa de clar i de vioi?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Noi iscodim trecutul searbd, ori viitorul ndoios,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n viaa noastr-att de trist</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rvnim mereu ce nu exist,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cel mai dulce cnt al nostru e plnsul cel mai dureros.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i chiar de-am fi strini de rele, de-am rmnea de-a pururi prunci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n veci cu lacrime durerea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S nu ne-ntunece vederea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Socot c n-am putea cuprinde norocul tu, ah, nici atunci!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Poetul s-ar cdea s pun pe arta ta mai mare pre</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca-n tot ce-a grmdit de veacuri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Gndirea omeneasc-n bracuri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, cntre ce-ascuns n ceruri msori pmntul cu dispre!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-mi mie numai jumtate din toat veselia ta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-un imn mre, n toat slava,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci din pieptu-mi rsuna-va,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci, cum eu te-ascult acuma, pmntu-ntreg m-ar asculta!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, an. XXXIV, nr. 5, 15 mai 1900.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Blestemul bardului </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Ludwig Uhland</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A fost de mult un mndru castel, cu vlf mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strlucitor departe pn&apos; la albastra mare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n jurul lui prin parcuri, cu nflorite-alee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sltau fntni vioaie n joc de curcubee.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Domnea un crai acolo, n ri i przi avut.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n tron de fier sta palid i de supui temut;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci cugetu-i e spaim, privirea lui  urgie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i bici e tot ce spune, i snge-i tot ce scrie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spre-acest castel venir doi clrei de frunte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu plete blonde unul, iar cellalt  crunte.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnul bard cu harfa-i, pe-un roib mpodobit;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pea alturi sprinten tovarul iubit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilul meu, fii gata, gri btrnul lin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adnc din pieptu-i smulge i cnt viers deplin.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Revars dor i patimi, tot sufletul n el,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-nduioem pe craiul cu inim de-oel.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sub boli strvechi, n sala mrea ei intrau;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i craiul i criasa pe tron acolo stau:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El  fioros ca zarea din noduri sngerat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea  ginga ca luna, la dreapta lui s-arat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i unde prinde-a zice din strune bardul falnic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adnc vrjete harfa ce clocote nvalnic;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar glasul tnr urc divin rsuntor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnul parc cheam al duhurilor cor...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei cnt veacul de-aur, mrirea cea strbun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i dulcea primvar, i dragostea nebun;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei cnt tot ce-ncnt viaa pe pmnt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ei cnt tot ce-i mndru i-nltor i sfnt</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Curtenii cei mai trufai stau cu plecate fruni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nduioai ascult otenii cei mai cruni;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Criasa, aiurit de dor i chin nespus,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Arunc de la snu-i un trandafir, de sus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-ai scos din mini poporul, acum femeia vrei?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rcnete groaznic craiul intind pe cntrei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De sus azvrle spada-i ce fulgere rsfrnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n loc de viers de aur, zbucnete-un val de snge.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca risipii de vifor, toi se trezesc din vis,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnu-i ia pe brae tovarul ucis,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">I urc-n a, aaz mantaua peste el,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">l leag drept i iese cu dnsul din castel...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci-n faa porii-nalte a stat btrnul bard:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-un stlp de marmur harfa cea fr pre i-a spart,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi n glas puternic se-ntoarce cu blestem,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nct i boli i parcuri nfiorate gem:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai vou, ziduri mndre! n veci s nu mai sune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n ncperea voastr nici viers, nici glas de strune!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu, ci fricoase psuri de sclav, suspin i plngeri,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn&apos; vei cdea trsnite de-al rzbunrii nger!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai vou, mndre parcuri strlucitoare-n rou!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cadavru-acestui tnr vi-l pun n fa vou,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vetejii ca dnsul, secnd orice izvoare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S fii un loc de spaim n zile viitoare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vai ie, crai slbatic! A barzilor urgie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deart lupta-i crunt spre glorie s fie!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i piar negru-i nume n negura uitrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum cel din urm geamt se stinge-n hul zrii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strig btrnul; cerul i auzi cuvntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zidirile-s ruin prin sli vuiete vntul.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din fosta slav numai un stlp mai st dovad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-acela, rupt, n dou, la noapte va s cad...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zac parcurile moarte i-s przile pustiei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar craiul n-are nume n cartea vitejiei!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici un hrisov nu-l scrie, i nici n cntec nu-i;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pierdut, uitat! Acesta-i blestemul bardului.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Convorbiri literare</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, an. XXXV, nr. 8, 1 august 1901.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Din italienete </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-a stins virtutea-n a Italiei ar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-a fost regina lumii n vechime.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De muzele Castaliei azi nime</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu poart grij; toi le delsar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A laurului verde frunz rar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E pngrit ntr-un veac de crime</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i lcomie; iar din adncime</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Desfrul scoate fruntea drz afar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De ne-au lsat strbunii-n zile bune</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumosul stil al versului i-al prozei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-mi pare-a fi aceasta vreo minune...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci vin&apos; s plngem zilele de fa,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Modernul gust ce-i are azi rapsozii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i decadena-n care se rsfa.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Smntorul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 28 septembrie 1908</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pinea noastr cea de toate zilele</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup un vechi cntec german</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, drag mam; nu e pne?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, i s tii c am s mor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai rabd, puiul mamii, pn mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C mne iese plugul n ogor.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, drag mam; nu e pne?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-amar de vreme tot m-ai amnat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai rabd, puiul mamii, pn mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C mne vom iei la semnat...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, drag mam; nu e pne?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-i este team, oare, c-oi muri?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai rabd, puiul mamii, pn mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C grul pn mni va rsri...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, drag mam; nu e pne?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vezi, inima mea bate tot mai rar...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai rabd, puiul mamii, pn mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C grul nostru este la morar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-e foame, drag mam; nu e pne?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, tare mi-e team c-o s mor...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai rabd, puiul mamii, pn mne,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C mne scoatem pnea din cuptor...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cnd crescu mirosul pnii copate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odorul mamii, galben ca un spic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nchinase fruntea peste noapte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i de-atunci n-a mai cerut nimic.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Smntorul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 23 martie 1908</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Daine din Litvania </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Dor_de_ar"/>Dor de ar</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">A vrea s-adorm, s dorm mereu,<text:line-break/>i n-aflu loc n nici o parte.<text:line-break/>i dor mi-e, dor de satul meu,<text:line-break/>i satul e-aa departe.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">-a vrea s merg, s merg mereu,<text:line-break/>i dor mi-e, dor mi-e de-o grdin,<text:line-break/>Grdin mndr-n satul meu,<text:line-break/>Acolo a gsi hodin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Acolo vntul pe-nserat<text:line-break/>Adie dulce i suspin,<text:line-break/>-a tot dormi netulburat<text:line-break/>Sub flori de cimbru i sulfin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smntorul</text:span>, 26 octombrie 1903</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Dor_de_mam.C4.83"/><text:bookmark text:name="Dor_de_mam"/>Dor de mam</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">i cnd m scol de diminea<text:line-break/>De-mi spl cu rou ochii mei,<text:line-break/>Mndrua-i galben la fa<text:line-break/>i plni sunt ochiorii ei.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Mndruo, pentru ce plngi, drag?<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>i s-a urt de casa mea?<text:line-break/>De ce suspini tu noaptea-ntreag?<text:line-break/>Eti suprat de ceva?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> i chiar de nu sunt suprat,<text:line-break/>De dor, bdi, m usuc;<text:line-break/>D-mi drumul numai nc-o dat<text:line-break/>Acas&apos; la mama s m duc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Dar pn&apos; la casa mamei tale,<text:line-break/>Mndruo, cum o s te duci?<text:line-break/>Rsuri i maci crescur-n cale<text:line-break/>i nu tii ncotro s-apuci.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Ruga-m-voi de flori cu jale<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi arate drumul lung,<text:line-break/>i ele mi-or deschide cale<text:line-break/>i la micua tot ajung!<text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Smntorul</text:span>, 30 noiembrie 1903</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Populare maghiare </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="De-a_fi_rege"/>De-a fi rege</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Ah, rege dac-a fi, iubit,<text:line-break/>Stpn pe-o-mprie-ntreag,<text:line-break/>Te-a mbrca n straie de-aur,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Att de mult, de mult mi-eti drag!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dar sunt srac de tot, iubit,<text:line-break/>i aur n-am, tu tii prea bine,<text:line-break/>Am numai braele-amndou:<text:line-break/>Le-nal cu dor, cu dor spre tine...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Strluce aurul... De ghea<text:line-break/>E strlucirea lui, iubit!<text:line-break/>Dar cnd te voi cuprinde-n brae,<text:line-break/>Vei fi cu mult mai fericit...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Floare-albastr</text:span>, 15 noiembrie 1898</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Iubire"/>Iubire</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Tu mi-ai destinuit iubirea,<text:line-break/>i, ca prin farmec, am zrit<text:line-break/>ntunecatul cer al nopei<text:line-break/>Zmbind voios la rsrit...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Chiar gerul i-a uitat urgia:<text:line-break/>Blnd aipind, fr de veste,<text:line-break/>Viseaz flori d-atunci, i uite!<text:line-break/>Le zugrvete pe ferestre...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Floare-albastr</text:span>, 15 noiembrie 1898</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="A.C8.99teptare"/><text:bookmark text:name="Ateptare"/><text:soft-page-break/>Ateptare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Plou i te-atept acas...<text:line-break/>Cum aud un pas, tresar <text:line-break/>Ah! m tem s nu-mi rmn<text:line-break/>Ateptarea n zadar!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Zbovete-n alt parte<text:line-break/>Dragul meu, de nu-mi mai vine?<text:line-break/>Ori s-a rtcit prin noapte?<text:line-break/>Roibul tie drumul bine...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Las&apos; s plou!... Tu, iubite,<text:line-break/>Numai tu s-mi vii acas...<text:line-break/>i-oi zvnta obrajii umezi<text:line-break/>Cu nfram de mtas!...<text:line-break/></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Floare-albastr</text:span>, 15 noiembrie 1898</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Craiul ielelor </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Johann Wolfgang von Goethe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cin&apos; zboar prin viscol aa de trziu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n noapte? E tatl cu scumpul lui fiu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El ine copilul lipit de-al su piept,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vegheaz asupr-i cu ochiul detept.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copile, tu tremuri; i-e fric; ce ai?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu vezi, tat drag, pe-al ielelor crai,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu lunga lui coad, coroan purtnd?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copile, e cea purtat de vnt.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, drag copile, o, vin ca s-i fac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La jocuri frumoase, s-i fie pe plac.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Flori mndre, pestrie, din plai strnge-vei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i maica te-mbrac n aur de vrei!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, tat, ei, tat, auzi ce mi-a zis,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce craiul n umbr optind mi-a promis?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Taci molcom, copile, i fii linitit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">E vntul ce-n vetedul crng a vuit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, vrei tu, copile, cu mine s vii?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Surorile mele cu drag te-or pzi.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ap ies ele cnd este senin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n cnturi i-n jocuri te leagn lin!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar, tat, ah, tat, nu vezi la un loc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin negur, ielele prinse n joc?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd, drag copile, eu vd lmurit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum ramii i mic un plop grbovit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frumos eti, copile, i drag tu mi eti;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Te smulg cu puterea, dei te fereti!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, tat, iat-l, m prinde-acum, vai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acum m strivete al ielelor crai.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnul cu groaz fugaru-nteete;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilul ce geme de sn i-l lipete.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Abia el ajunge acas cu chin...</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copilul de spaim-i murise la sn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Regele din Thule </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Johann Wolfgang von Goethe</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era n Thule, departe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un rege ludat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cruia, iubita, la moarte,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O cup de aur i-a dat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">El bea din ea la ospee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">inea nespus la ea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i ochii-i mureau de tristee</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cte ori o sorbea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i cnd a fost s moar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urmailor ls</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Oraele toate din ar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar cupa o pstr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo, pe rmul mrii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n sala din vechiul castel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu toi fruntaii rii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La mas ade el.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrnul crai se scoal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nchin nc-o dat&apos;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-azvrle cupa goal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n valul nspumat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu ochii stini sub pleoape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O vede cum czu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luat-ncet de ape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n veci nu mai bu!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat prima oar n Lumina literar, 17 martie 1913</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Trei sonete </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="I7"/>I</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Traumbilder)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">n vis, prea la nunt c m-nvit;<text:line-break/>i se fcea c eu plecam de-acas<text:line-break/>n frac de gal, vest de mtase;<text:line-break/>n faa mea sta dulcea mea iubit.<text:line-break/>M-am nchinat i-am zis: Suntei mireas?<text:line-break/>Eh, v doresc via fericit!<text:line-break/>Dar vorba mea era aa silit,<text:line-break/>Pe ct de rece i politicoas.<text:line-break/>Atunci iubita izbucni n plns,<text:line-break/>i-n lacrimile ce-i curgeau ntruna,<text:line-break/>ncnttorul chip al ei s-a stins.<text:line-break/>O, dulcii ochi, evlavioase stele,<text:line-break/>De m minesc aievea-ntotdeauna,<text:line-break/>Mcar n vis m-ncred cu drag n ele.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="II8"/>II</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(Mamei sale B. Heine, nscut von Gelden)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Sunt nvat s port sus a mea frunte,<text:line-break/>Cci firea mea e drz i-ndrznea;<text:line-break/>Chiar regele de m-ar privi n fa,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>Privirea mea ar ti cum s-l nfrunte.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar, scump mam, orict de semea<text:line-break/>Figura mea ar sta s se ncrunte,<text:line-break/>Eu oviesc, cu pletele crunte<text:line-break/>Cnd mi te-apropii, sfnt i mrea.<text:line-break/>Spiritul tu poate m umilete,<text:line-break/>Spirit nalt, ce nu cunoate fric<text:line-break/>i fulgerul spre ceruri se ridic.<text:line-break/>O amintire m nelinitete,<text:line-break/>Purtarea mea cea rea posomort-a<text:line-break/>Inima care m-a iubit atta?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="III5"/>III</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P34">Ca un nebun te-am prsit odat,<text:line-break/>n lumea larg dorul m gonise<text:line-break/>S cat iubirea-ntrevzut-n vise,<text:line-break/>Ca s-o cuprind n inima mea toat.<text:line-break/>i am cerit pomana ne-nsemnat<text:line-break/>Rtcitor, cu braele deschise,<text:line-break/>i am btut la porile nchise,<text:line-break/>Dar numai ur-mi dar ca rsplat.<text:line-break/>Ci eu doream iubirea,-n veci iubirea,<text:line-break/>i asta n-am gsit-o nicirea.<text:line-break/>Bolnav i trist m-am rentors acas.<text:line-break/>Tu mi-ai ieit atunci n prag duioas,<text:line-break/>i, ah, n ochii ti sta zugrvit<text:line-break/>Iubirea sfnt, dulce, mult dorit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Consilii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Heinrich Heine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ibovnica dac te-a amgit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu caut alta s-i plac; -</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ori las mai bine oraul iubit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ia-i traista n spate i pleac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Un lac lin, albastru, gsi-vei uor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i slcii slbatice, triste.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo-i vei plnge ngustul tu dor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerile mici, egoiste.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci dac te urci la muni, cu pduri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Durerea-i va fi mai uoar;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe stncile sure vezi numai vulturi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i iptul lor te-nfioar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo devii tu nsui vultur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Renati din senin -o s-i par</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C lumea-i a ta, cnd caui n jur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nici n-ai pierdut vro comoar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Un vis </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Mihail Lermontov</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">La Daghestan, n valea cea pustie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rnit la piept, zceam n nemicare:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btea n flcri rana nc vie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i sngele zbucnea n picuri rare...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zceam nsetoat; nesimitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stau stncile pleuve-n jurul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i scnteia n aria de soare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nisipul galben. Eu dormeam mereu...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Visam c-n ara mea e srbtoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vedeam saloane strlucite, pline</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De musafiri voioi; i, zmbitoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Femei frumoase se gndeau la mine...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doar una sta-ntr-un col uitat de lume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prea c nici nu vrea s-o ia n seam;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-o atrgeau pe ea nici dan, nici glume,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea urmrea un vis cu mult team:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Departe-n vale un rnit zrea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i cunotea att de bine chipul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n agonie rana tresrea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-un val de snge nroea nisipul...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Epigramatice</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup Lessing</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Amgire"/>Amgire</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Obraznic, cu snii goi,<text:line-break/>Cu un cel pe bra,<text:line-break/>Sta Lote... Ci n-au tresrit<text:line-break/>Rvnind-o cu neas!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Privind spre ea pe gnduri dus,<text:line-break/>M-apropiai ncet...<text:line-break/>Hai! i-sta-i prins, i zise ea,<text:line-break/>i-mi rse-n nas, iret.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"><text:soft-page-break/>Dect, rmn ntre noi,<text:line-break/>S-a nelat amar,<text:line-break/>Privisem la celul ei:<text:line-break/>Un soi de cine rar.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Duel"/>Duel</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">De ce-au scos, drji de neagr ur,<text:line-break/>Sistan i cellalt tovar<text:line-break/>Din teac spadele?.. Oroare!<text:line-break/>Ca s le bage-n teac iari.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Curios_.21"/><text:bookmark text:name="Curios_!"/>Curios!</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">mi pare foarte curios <text:line-break/>Zicea Pcal unei rude-a sale <text:line-break/>C numai oamenii bogai<text:line-break/>Au cele mai multe parale!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicate n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Adevrul ilustrat</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 15 iulie 1896</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Glontele</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Henry Wadsworth Longfellow</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E mort de-acum frumosul tnr, czut viteazul nenvins,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i inima-i nvpiat i-obrajii lui aprini s-au stins!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El  sufletul ndejdii noastre, el  rsfatul de noroc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe care cu mndrie ochii l urmreau din loc n loc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A crui voce mngioas, al crui zmbet plin de vraj</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fcea s crezi c pretutindeni un nger bun i st de straj...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri noapte-naintam o ceat prin pas, n munte, spre pichet,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eram ferii de ntuneric;  el clrea cntnd ncet:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Port dou roze roii</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La plria mea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A treia-n vrful spadei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi va-nflori i ea...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci din margine de codru un glonte uiernd iei:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cntarea-i amui pe buze i, brusc, un trup se prbui,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Simii c sngele-mi nghea, fiori de groaz m-au ptruns.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i l-am strigat uor pe nume, dar, vai! n-am cptat rspuns!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-am rdicat pe cal cu trud i-ncet, prin ploaie i noroi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin noapte i prin cea, iat-l adus la tabr-napoi!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">La raza unei mici lanterne, sub cort, vzut-am dup-aceea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe faa-i dou roze</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">albe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">,  la piept i sngera a treia...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-un vis acum mi-arat ns acelai glonte uciga</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum uier zburnd departe, se duce uiernd n zbor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strbate muni i vi, ajunge departe-n nordicul ora,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n mijlocul unei cscioare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din ulia plin de soare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atinge-o inim, oprindu-i btile, fulgertor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-acolo, dinspre nord, departe, aud un clopot trist sunnd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vecinul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T20">Ei</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">se minuneaz cum de-a murit aa curnd!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat n Pagini literare, 9 aprilie 1900</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Dunrea</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Eduard Mrike</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe Dunre uor plutea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O barc, doi copii n ea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El  de o parte, ea  de alta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea zice:  Drag, spune dar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce lucru vrei s-i dau n dar?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea mnica i-o sufleca</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i peste ap se pleca.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Biatul rse i, la fel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ap s-aplec i el.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, d-mi un dar, frumoas Dun,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu, care eti aa de bun!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">O mndr spad scoase ea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De mult biatul o dorea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Biatul ns-n mni ce are?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">O salb de mrgritare!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">I-o aez n negru-i pr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prea-o prines-n adevr!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mai d-mi un dar, frumoas Dun.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tu care eti aa de bun!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Copila mai ncerc iar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i scoate-un scut de-oel afar.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Biatul rde aiurit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i scoate-un piepten aurit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">A treia oar ea ncearc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ah! alunec din barc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">El sare dup ea s-o scape,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar Duna-i fur ntre ape.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i pare ru de comoara ei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i se rzbun acum pe ei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pustie barca se scufund</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i soarele st s s-ascund,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar luna cnd iei pe deal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iubiii mori pluteau spre mal,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">El  de o parte, ea  de alta.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer">Publicat n Smntorul, 19 august 1907</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cataracta Lodorei </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Robert Southey</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum vine oare apa la Lodora?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Odrasla ntr-o bun zi mi cere</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i povestesc. Eu, vrnd s-i fac plcere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Numaidect s-altur i sora,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-o alt surioar mai veni.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i mare fu dorina tuturora</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i toi voiau cu orice pre a ti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum se coboar apa la Lodora,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n furia i mreia ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa precum o mai vzuse ei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deci, nu m las nici eu prea mult rugat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cci, ndrgit al rimelor sonore,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sunt i al lor, n anumite ore,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-al regelui poet laureat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din obria plin de izvoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Care nesc ntr-un adnc bazin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Al muntelui stncos, apele vin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i se preling ncet i se strecoar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alunec-n zigzaguri, dau ocol,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin fereg i muchi fcndu-i cale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se duc aproape nesimit la vale,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Apoi adorm ici-colo-n cte-un ghiol;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-acolo apa ce prea c-i moart</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Deodat-i sparge singur o poart,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-acum curgnd prin stuf o intrevezi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Printre mesteceni, pajiti i livezi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin rariti trece vesel strlucind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sau umbrele pdurii o cuprind.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srind ca o rzboinic viteaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Zgazele ce drumul i-l brzdeaz</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn la-nlimea malului rpos.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum curge apa la Lodora-n jos?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aicea, iat-o viu fierbnd n clocot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dincoace, iat-o iari aipit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici spumegnd, vuind, fugind cu ropot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nfuriat i nepotolit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urmndu-i calea-n goan nentrerupt,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sltnd n sus i-n jos, chemnd la lupt</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-ameninnd s surpe, s prvale</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Stnci, peteri  tot ce i se pune-n cale.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Srind agajnic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Crescnd nvalnic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Slbind, trindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">nind, lfindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Fugind, azvrlindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aiurind, zvrcolindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ocolind, plecndu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sltnd, rentorcndu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De peste tot i-adun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n goana-i ce detun</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">uviele ei sltree,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Din care sar alte rzlee,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe care-apoi iari le-ndrug</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pn la o nou fug.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scurmnd i opintindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luptnd i despletindu-se,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ea i urzete estura ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">C stai uimit, i pleoapele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Le-nchizi fr s vrei.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rmi aa nedumerit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i asurzit, i aiurit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De larma ce-o fac apele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n cursul lor nemaioprit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sgeat pornind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">optind, forfotind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Clocotind i cotind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Smorcind, horcind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici picnd strop cu strop,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ici jucnd n potop,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nruind, struind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tremurnd, murmurnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">rind, prind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ropotind, bobotind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Duduind, zguduind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vjind, gfind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aromind i momind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i murind, tresrind i srind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i fierbnd i turbnd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Galopnd i spnd i rupnd i surpnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Strlucind, clipocind, nlucind, rtcind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Lunecnd, zdrumicind, i jucnd i trecnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unduind, erpuind, i suind i vuind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spumegnd, fumegnd, rpgnd i strignd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dnuind, chefuind, duduind i huind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Bolborosind, regsind, poposind i sosind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">opind, ropind, opind, hopind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Frmntnd i cntnd, desftnd i sltnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mereu, mereu coboar, domoal ori zglobie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Btrna cataract, vulcan de ap vie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mpreunnd tot soiul de zgomote ciudate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu-a valurilor sale schimbri nencetate,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-i trmbi sonora</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i vesela solie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa coboar apa-n cdere la Lodora</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Visul lui Aenea </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Virgiliu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Tempus erat quo prima quies morlalibus degris<text:line-break/>Incipit et dono divum gratissima serpit.<text:line-break/>In somnis ecce ante oculos maetissimus Hector<text:line-break/>Visus adesse mihi etc.<text:line-break/>(Din Aeneida, C. II)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era acum rstimpul cnd primul somn nal </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Alunecnd n suflet fermector de blnd </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe muritorii palizi de griji i de-obosal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i iat,-n vis, a Troiei nentrecut fal</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi se arat: Hector, cu hohote plngnd.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Aa cum fu de-a valma, din goana nendurat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La glezne de curele ptruns, trt de roi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Negrit de colbu-n snge, vai, astfel mi s-arat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce deprtat de Hector acel pe care-odat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">L-am cunoscut, de Hector temut de-acheii toi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Era-nclcit barba-i, i pletele lui grele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">n snge nchegate, stropite de noroi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i acoperit tot trupul cu rnile acele</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce le primise  parte mai mare dintre ele </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Luptnd sub murii Troiei, alturea de noi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am izbucnit, privindu-l, n bocete nebune:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O, tu, lumina Troiei, sperana noastr, tu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n vremuri de restrite, ca i n vremuri bune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ne-ai strlucit! Ce-nsamn zbava asta? Spune,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe ce trmuri triste, ce vnt te abtu?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Muli frai czui n lupt avurm noi a plnge</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De cnd te-ai dus, i multe dureri de ndurat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar ce frdelege asupr-i se rsfrnge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Scldndu-i faa mndr n lacrime i-n snge,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s te-ari nainte-mi att de tulburat?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci pornete umbra a geme cu durere,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i nici nu se oprete la vorbele-mi pustii:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O! fugi, fiu al zeiei, fugi fr-ntrziere!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dumanu-i n cetate, Teucru-n flcri piere:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se prbuete Troia-n ruini din temelii!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ajung atte jertfe i trec peste msur!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ursit e pieirii domnia lui Priam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i patria-i pierdut, cci zeii nu se-ndur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd nici aceste brae viteze nu putur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-abat-n drum cderea mreului Pergam!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Penai i-obiecte sacre i sunt ncredinate:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vei pribegi cu ele, pe ocean, fugar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">ndelungat vreme, spre rmuri deprtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Acolo-ntemeia-vei o falnic cetate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce va ntinde umbr p-al lumii-ntregi hotar!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel grindu-mi Hector cu voce-mpuntoare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se deprteaz-o clip, se-ntoarce iar zorit:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Mi-aduce focul vecinic i sfintele odoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i chipul sfnt al Vestei, al falnicei fecioare,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">n vreme ce eu caut la el nmrmurit.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Atunci mi-atinge-auzul o larm deprtat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce crete tot mai vajnic afar, iar i iar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Surd, vuietul de arme ajunge s strbat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">La casa lui Anchize, a scumpului meu tat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dei zcea ascuns n parcul solitar</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tresar din somn urc grabnic pe-acoperi i, iat!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O groaznic icoan vederii mi s-arat!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot astfel, cnd potopul de flcri nvlete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pornit de vnt, n holde, slbatec, furios,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot astfel, cnd uvoiul de munte vine, crete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Urlnd grozav, la vale, i smulge, i trete</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pduri ntregi i turme n rul spumegos,</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-neac ntr-o clip frumoasa artur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i tot ce-agonisise plugarul biet, din greu </text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe stnc st pstorul, i parc nu se-ndur</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S cread-aieve cele ce ochii lui vzur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum de pe culmea casei privind, nu cred nici eu</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vntul</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Virgiliu</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Astzi sunt zefirul care<text:line-break/>tie numai s dezmierde,<text:line-break/>Hoinrind ct ine ziua,<text:line-break/>Vesel, pe cmpia verde.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Drgstos srut n treact<text:line-break/>Florile mbobocite,<text:line-break/>i-n sruturile calde<text:line-break/>Florile tresar vrjite.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Dragi copii ai primverii,<text:line-break/>nflorii i v deschidei!<text:line-break/>Le optesc eu la ureche <text:line-break/>nflorii, trii, surdei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Iar florile, sfioase,<text:line-break/>Se desfac ncetior;<text:line-break/>i, mpovrat de visuri,<text:line-break/>Blnd adorm pe snul lor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Mine sunt vrtej slbatec<text:line-break/>Ce rstoarn, vuie, geme.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cntec din Caucaz</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Snt trist, mi-e urt, mi-e fric,<text:line-break/>i ce s fac, eu nu mai tiu,<text:line-break/>Cci dragu-i dus i e trziu:<text:line-break/>L-atept acas singuric.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">A vrea s torc, dar nu pot, iat,<text:line-break/>Se rupe firul, fusu-i greu...<text:line-break/>Oi toarce mni... Ce Dumnezeu!<text:line-break/>Prea-s trist azi i suprat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu stau i plng de dor n cas,<text:line-break/>Cnd poate dnsul m-a lsat...<text:line-break/>Va fi gsit pe alta-n sat<text:line-break/>i azi de mine nu-i mai pas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>De-a ti c pe alta dezmiard<text:line-break/>i m-a lsat fr noroc,<text:line-break/>Mai bine satul tot s ard,<text:line-break/>S ard cu satul la un loc!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smntorul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 11 ianuarie 1904</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Chef pe lun </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dup un poet chinez</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Stau n chiocul luminat de lun,<text:line-break/>nainte-mi un ulcior cu vin.<text:line-break/>N-am tovar, dar ce-mi pas mie?<text:line-break/>Singur eu cu mine am s-nchin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Haide dar! ridic voios paharul,<text:line-break/>Lun, tu, s-mi ii de-urt nu vrei?<text:line-break/>Iat, mi, i umbra mea de colo!<text:line-break/>Hai, acuma sntem tocmai trei!</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Dar cu vinul parc nu-i deprins<text:line-break/>Drglaa mea amic, luna.<text:line-break/>Umbra mea n schimb e bun tovar,<text:line-break/>Cel puin o vd c bea ntr-una.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Eu ncep s ct de voie bun,<text:line-break/>Luna salt-ncolo i ncoace...<text:line-break/>Prind s joc, i iat c ncepe<text:line-break/>Umbra mea pe loc i ea s joace.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>Luna trece peste chioc acuma,<text:line-break/>Norii-ncet-ncet i dau ocol,<text:line-break/>Umbra, nu tiu unde-a disprut, i singur<text:line-break/>nainte-mi st ulciorul gol...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smntorul</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 7 octombrie 1907</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Desprire</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">Dain din Litvania</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">O, uite, draga mea copil,<text:line-break/>La poart cine st i scrie?<text:line-break/>Sunt ofieri cari vin s-l duc<text:line-break/>Pe feciora n ctnie.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">Cu pr blai, cu-obrajii rumeni,<text:line-break/>Cnd l vedea, rdea cmpia;<text:line-break/>i, ridicndu-se-n vzduhuri,<text:line-break/>Cnta voioas ciocrlia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i ce-i st acum alturi?<text:line-break/>St mndra. Plnge i suspin:<text:line-break/> Nu suspina i nu mai plnge,<text:line-break/>Tu, mndr floare de grdin.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg">i-oi scrie un rva, mndruo;<text:line-break/>Rmi acas tu i toarce,<text:line-break/>Cluul meu i-l va aduce,<text:line-break/>De cumva nu m-oi ntoarce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"><text:soft-page-break/>n lad s-mi grijeti rvaul,<text:line-break/>Drgua mea, frumos mi-l strnge,<text:line-break/>i-ades cnd vei deschide lada,<text:line-break/>Gndind la mine, tu vei plnge...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicat n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Voina naional</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 19 noiembrie/12 decembrie 1903</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Roman</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">din poezia popular maghiar</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Spune-mi, of, cumetre drag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-ai vzut pe omul meu?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">A plecat n trg, din ceart,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-l atept de ieri mereu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri la mas n-a venit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde s-o fi rtcit?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-l bate gndul, vntul?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Doar nu l-a-nghiit pmntul</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrei s-i spun, cumtr drag?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iac, -i spun i de ce nu?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri, plngnd, n zori de ziu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Pe la poarta mea trecu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum i blstma viaa!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">N-a dat bun dimineaa</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar nu tii, cumetre drag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Unde-a mers, n care parte?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Am s plec n lumea toat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-l gsesc, ct de departe:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S m bat, s m certe,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">O s-l rog ca s m ierte!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vrei s tii, cumtr drag?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu-l mai cuta-n zadar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C s-a spnzurat, srmanul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De o crac de stejar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Colo-n crng, ieri dimineaa.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Astfel i-a sfrit viaa.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Of, ce ru sunt blestemat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">C mi-am omort brbatul!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-a posti o via-ntreag,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Tot nu-mi ispesc pcatul;</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">D-mi un treang, c vreau s mor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vreau i eu s m omor!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dumneata ai gnduri rele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vd c s-a-ntrecut cu gluma;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dac juri c-i fi cuminte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i c nu-l mai faci de-acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">S-i mai ieie lumea-n cap,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vorbe multe nu ncap:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">E la han, joac i bea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca s uite de belea!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Poezii populare maghiare </text:h>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Susnica"/>Susnica</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Frumoasa Susnica zace,<text:line-break/>Srmana, mai pe pat de moarte;<text:line-break/>De sete arde toat-n par,<text:line-break/>Dar, vai! prul e departe.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Ia, mam, repede cofia<text:line-break/>i ad-mi ap din pru...<text:line-break/>Pn ce btrna d o fug,<text:line-break/>St cu bolnava un flcu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38"> Ce bun eti, tu, drag mam,<text:line-break/>M simt cu mult mai bine-acum;<text:line-break/>Mai ad-mi nc, dar, mmuc,<text:line-break/>Nu te grbi aa pe drum...</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_4" text:outline-level="4"><text:bookmark text:name="Fata_cr.C3.AE.C8.99marului"/><text:bookmark text:name="Fata_crmarului"/>Fata crmarului</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Dac-mi fac n crm vacul,<text:line-break/>Dus cu una nu m dau!<text:line-break/>Crezi, crmare, i te-ai prinde<text:line-break/>C mantaua eu mi-oi vinde<text:line-break/>Ca s beu?</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P38">Eu, din vinurile-i scumpe,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>N-a sorbi o linguri!<text:line-break/>Fetei tale doar i-a cere<text:line-break/>Ca s-mi dea un pic de miere<text:line-break/>Din guri...</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="lg"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="Trailer"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Publicate n</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">Floare albastr</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T2">, 7 februarie 1899</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nu este-aa? </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Paul Verlaine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu este-aa c-n ciuda acelor proti i ri</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce vor privi cu pizm a noastr bucurie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom fi arare mndri i buni n veci cu ei?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nu este-aa c-n tihn i plini de voioie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Vom merge calea dreapt ce steaua ne-o arat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nepstori de cine ne vede ori ne tie?</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rznite ca-ntr-o neagr pdure fermecat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">A noastre dou inimi cnta-vor n iubire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cum cnt noaptea dou privighetori deodat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar lumea, de-o fi bun cu noi, ori cu-ndrjire,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puin o s ne pese. De-ar fi s ne sfie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nici dragoste, nici ur, nimic n-o s ne mire.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Legai de cea mai scump i trainic frie,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca ntr-o za vrjit noi vom pi-n lumin,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Iar team de nimica atunci n-o s ne fie.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ci fr nici o grij de valul ce-o s vin</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Eu mna mea voi pune-o duios n mna ta,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-om merge-aa nainte, cu inima senin</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P13">A celor ce s-ador deoparte, nu-i aa?</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Amorul sfrmat </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Paul Verlaine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri peste noapte vntul a sfrmat Amorul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-n colul cel mai dulce ce-l tinuiete parcul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adesea ne oprise din drum, sgettrul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cu zmbetul pe buze, tinznd n aer arcul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ieri peste noapte vntul l-a sfrmat. i-acuma</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Puzderia de marmor rotete-n zori - i-i trist</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">S vezi sub arbor soclul ce mai pstreaz numa</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Isclitura tears a bietului artist.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce trist se-nal soclul stingher! Lundu-i zborul,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">ntristtoare gnduri se duc iar, ca s vie</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n visul meu de jale n care viitorul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">mi prevestete-o soart mhnit i pustie...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">E trist din cale-afar... Chiar tu, aa-i, femeie?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Rmi pierdut parc, dei firea-i uoar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Se bucur de-un flutur de purpur ce zboar</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Prin pulberea de marmor purtat pe alee...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Colocviu sentimental </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Paul Verlaine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n parcul vechi i rece i pustiu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Trec dou umbre-n ceasul cenuiu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Li-s ochii ofilii, au buze moi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i deslueti cu greu ce-i spun ei doi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">n parcul vechi i rece i pustiu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Nlucile i fac trecutul viu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">i aminteti extazul nostru vechi?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce tot mi torci trecutul n urechi!</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dar astzi m mai strigi pe nume tu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i-n vis i mai rsar eu oare?  Nu.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ah, zile dragi cum altele n-om ti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Cnd gurile ni se uneau!  O fi ...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce boli albastre, ce sperane mari!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T10"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T4">Sperana-i azi prin norii funerari.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">i astfel merg strnind ovzu-n drum</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i noaptea i aude doar, prin fum...</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>n surdin </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">de Paul Verlaine</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Linitii n adumbrirea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce din ramuri se desface</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dragostea s ne-o ptrundem</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">De-o aa adnc pace.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ca-ntr-un vis frumos i tainic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Dui s ne topim cu-ncetul</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">n melancolia vag</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ce-o mprtie brdetul.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">ine-i braele n cruce,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Ochii-nchii pe jumtate</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">i din inima i-alung</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Orice dor ntr-nsa bate.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P37"><text:span text:style-name="T4">S ne-adoarm ca ntr-un leagn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T4">Adierile uoare</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P9"/>
